23640	40	15	6	Hiaa' koi' metudui' hewa toi: uma-pi mingki' tabila' tina pai' tuama-ta, asala ta'uli' -raka hewa toi: `Napa to masipato' kuwai' -kokoi totu'a, mpolia' kutonu-mi hi Alata'ala.' Jadi', Lolita Alata'ala uma nisaile'. Ada-ni moto to nipomobohe.
23641	40	15	7	Hi mali-na-wadi petuku' -ni hi Alata'ala tetu-e! Makono mpu'u lolita nabi Yesaya owi to mpolowa-koi, hewa toi moni-na:
23642	40	15	8	Na'uli' Alata'ala: `Tauna tohe'era mpobila' -a hi wiwi-ra-wadi, nono-ra molaa ngkai Aku'.
23643	40	15	9	Uma ria kalaua-ra mpopue' -a, apa' tudui' -ra tudui' manusia' -wadi, bela tudui' ngkai Aku'.'"
23644	40	15	10	 Oti toe, Yesus mpokio' tauna to wori' mpomohui' -i, na'uli' -raka: "Epe-koi bona ni'inca:
23645	40	15	11	Pongkoni' to mesua' hi nganga-ta, bela-hawo toe to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala. Lolita to mehupa' ngkai nganga-ta, toe-die to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala-e."
23646	40	15	12	Ngkai ree, tumai-ramo ana'guru-na mpo'uli' -ki: "Nu'inca wa kapeda' nono-ra to Parisi mpo'epe lolita-nue we'i?"
23647	40	15	13	
23648	40	15	14	Na'uli' Yesus: "Pelele' -ramo to Parisi toera lou! Apa' butu nyala hinu'a to uma nahu'a Tuama-ku to hi rala suruga, bate rawuka. To Parisi toe-rale hewa pangkeni to wero, apa' uma ra'incai ohea to makono hilou hi Alata'ala. Pai' ane towero mpotete' hingka towero-na, bate moluli' roduaa-ra mpai' hi rala kinali."
23649	40	15	15	Na'uli' Petrus: "Guru, notohi-kakai lolita rapa' tetu-e we'i."
23650	40	15	16	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ha uma oa' -di nipaha-e!
23651	40	15	17	Pongkoni' to mesua' hi rala nganga-tale kaliliu hi rala ta'i-ta, pai' ngkai ree kaliliu tatadi. Bela-hawo toe to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala-e.
23652	40	15	18	Aga lolita to dada'a to mehuwu ngkai rala nono-ta pai' to howa' hi wiwi-ta, toe-mi to mpakada'a tauna hi poncilo Alata'ala.
23653	40	15	19	Apa' ngkai rala nono pehupaa' pekiri to dada'a, pai' alaa-na ria to mepatehi, mobualo', mogau' sala' hi tobine ba tomane, manako, mosabi' boa' pai' metipo'.
23654	40	15	20	Kehi to hewa toe-mi lau to mpakada'a tauna hi poncilo Alata'ala. Ane ngkoni' uma leba' mowano, bela-hawo toe to mpakada'a tauna hi poncilo Alata'ala."
23655	40	15	21	 Ngkai ree hilou-imi Yesus hi tana' to mohu' ngata Tirus pai' Sidon.
23656	40	15	22	Ria hadua tobine to Kanaan, bela-i to Yahudi. Tobine toei tumai hi Yesus ntora mekio', na'uli': "Pue', muli Magau' Daud! Poka'ahi' -a-kuwo! Ana' -ku tobine kahawia' seta, hangaa uma-ipi katonoa toe-e ria."
23657	40	15	23	Uma-i winihi Yesus. Tumai ana'guru-na mpomohui' -i, ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, popalai-i tobine tetui, daa' kakakio' -kio' -i mpotuku' -ta."
23658	40	15	24	Na'uli' Yesus hi tobine toei: "Alata'ala mpohubui-a tumai mpotulungi muli to Israel-wadi, apa' hewa bima to puha-ramo, uma-rapa mpotuku' konoa Alata'ala."
23659	40	15	25	Ngkai ree, tumai lau-imi tobine toei motingkua' hi nyanyoa Yesus, mpo'uli' -ki: "Pue', tulungi-a-kuwo!"
23660	40	15	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma lompe' mpo'ala' koni' ana' pai' rarora-ki dike'."
23661	40	15	27	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Makono moto-di Pue', aga biasa moto-hawo dike' ngkoni' rupu' koni' to mohewu' ngkai lolo meja' hi tomi pue' -na."
23662	40	15	28	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Bohe mpu'u pepangala' -nu, totina! Wae-pi, jadi' -mi hewa konoa-nu." Hinto'u toe, mo'uri' mpu'u-imi ana' -na.
23663	40	15	29	 Oti toe, me'ongko' wo'o-imi Yesus ngkai ree, mako' mewiwi' rano Galilea. Manake' -i lou hi bulu' -na, pai' -i mohura metudui'.
23664	40	15	30	Mo'iko tauna mpotoa' -i, ngkeni to pungku, to keru, to wero, to uma howa' mololita pai' to peda' ntani' -na wo'o. Ratu'u-ra hi nyanyoa Yesus, pai' napaka'uri' -ra.
23665	40	15	31	Konce-ramo ntodea mpohilo hawe'ea tauna to napaka'uri' Yesus: tauna to uma howa' mololita, howa' -mi mololita, to keru mo'uri' -mi, to pungku momako' -mi, to wero pehilo-mi. Toe pai' mpobila' -ramo Alata'ala to rapue' to Israel.
23666	40	15	32	Oti toe Yesus mpokio' ana'guru-na, na'uli' -raka: "Tuna-kuna nono-ku mpohilo tauna to wori' toera lau. Tolu eo-ramo dohe-ku, uma ria pongkoni' -ra. Uma lau nono-ku mpohubui-ra nculii' ntali oro' -ra, molinga' -ra mpai' hi ohea."
23667	40	15	33	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Beiwa-mile, apa' wao' -di hi rehe'i-e lau. Tarata hiapa-mile pongkoni' tapokoni' -raka tauna to hewa toe lau kawori' -rae?"
23668	40	15	34	Yesus mpekune' -ra: "Hangkuja roti to ria hi koi' -e?" Ratompoi' -i: "Pitu meha', pai' bau' uru to kedi' ba hangkuja ma'a-wadi."
23669	40	15	35	Ngkai ree nahubui-ramo tauna to wori' mohura hi tana'.
23670	40	15	36	Na'ala' -mi roti to pitu pai' bau' kedi' to ba hangkuja ma'a toe, pai' -i mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala. Oti toe napihe-pihe-mi pai' nawai' -raka ana'guru-na bona rabagi-raka tauna to wori' toera.
23671	40	15	37	Ngkoni' -ramo omea duu' -ra bohu. Ka'oti-ra ngkoni', ana'guru-na mporumpu toro-na, pitu luncu-pi.
23672	40	15	38	Kawori' -ra to ngkoni' nto'u toe, opo' ncobu tomane, uma tebila' tobine pai' ana'.
23673	40	15	39	Oti toe, nahubui-ramo nculii' hilou hi tomi-ra, pai' -i mpohawi' sakaya hilou hi tana' Magadan.
23674	40	16	1	 Ria wo'o ba hangkuja dua to Parisi pai' to Saduki rata hi Yesus doko' mposori-i. Merapi' -ra hi Yesus, ra'uli' -ki: "Babehi anu to mekoncehi bona monoto ki'inca kangkai Alata'ala-nu."
23675	40	16	2	Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane neo' limpa-mi eo pai' mperelei langi', ni'uli': `Morawa mpai' raoa.'
23676	40	16	3	Ane mepupulo ni'uli': `Udaa mpai' toi-e, bo mperelei pai' mojimuu' -di oo lau.' Ni'inca lia mpelence raoa. Aga uma ni'incai mpelence napa to nababehi Alata'ala tempo toi.
23677	40	16	4	Uma mowo kadada'a-ni, nisapuaka oa' -pidi Alata'ala! Merapi' -koi tanda mekoncehi. Aga uma hanyalaa tanda mekoncehi to rapopohiloi-kokoi. Sampale-wadi to rapopohiloi-kokoi, tanda hewa to jadi' hi nabi Yunus owi." Oti toe malai-imi mpalahii-ra.
23678	40	16	5	 Hilou-ramo Yesus hante ana'guru-na medipo rano, aga ana'guru-na uma mpokiwoi ngkeni boku. Ngkai ree, na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka:
23679	40	16	6	"Pelompehi, mo'inga' -inga' -koi hi ragi to Parisi pai' to Saduki-e'!"
23680	40	16	7	Aga uma ra'incai batua-na walatu toe, helee momepololitai moto-ramo, ra'uli': "Pai' na'uli' hewa toe-le, apa' uma takiwoi ngkeni roti we'i."
23681	40	16	8	Ntaa' na'inca-di Yesus napa to ra'uli' ana'guru-nae, toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' ntora mpololita ka'uma-ni ngkeni roti-e! Kura' rahi pepangala' -ni!
23682	40	16	9	Ko'ia oa' -tano nipaha-e! Ha uma-pi nikiwoi roti to lima meha' to kupokoni' -raka tauna to lima ncobu-e? Pai' hangkuja luncu-pi toro-na to nirumpu?
23683	40	16	10	Pai' beiwa wo'o hante roti to pitu meha' kupokoni' -raka tauna to opo' ncobu-e? Hangkuja luncu wo'o-pi toro-na to nirumpu?
23684	40	16	11	Napa pai' uma oa' nipaha kabela-na roti mpu'u to ku'uli' -e! Mo'inga' -inga' -koi hi ragi to Parisi pai' to Saduki."
23685	40	16	12	Lako' ra'inca-di we'i ana'guru-nae kabela-na ragi to ragalo-ki roti to na'uli' Yesus-e. Patuju lolita-na, bona mo'inga' -inga' -ra hi tudui' to Parisi pai' to Saduki.
23686	40	16	13	 Hilou-ramo Yesus hante ana'guru-na hi tana' to mohu' hi Kaisarea Filipi. Hi ree mepekune' Yesus hi ana'guru-na: "Ntuku' ponguli' -ra ntodea, hema-a Aku' Ana' Manusia' toi-e?"
23687	40	16	14	Ratompoi' ana'guru-na: "Ria-ra to mpo'uli' Yohanes Topeniu' -ko tuwu' nculii'. Ria wo'o-ra to mpo'uli' Iko hadua nabi to owi mehupa' nculii', hewa nabi Elia, nabi Yeremia, ba nabi to ntani' -na."
23688	40	16	15	Napekune' tena-ra, na'uli': "Hiaa' koi' -koiwo mpo'uli' hema-a Aku' toi-e?"
23689	40	16	16	Natompoi' Simon Petrus: "Iko-mile Magau' Topetolo' -e, Ana' Alata'ala to Tuwu'."
23690	40	16	17	Na'uli' Yesus: "Marasi' mpu'u-ko, Simon ana' Yunus, apa' bela manusia' to mpopo'incai-ko tetu-e, Tuama-ku to hi rala suruga-hana.
23691	40	16	18	Jadi', toe pai' rahanga' Petrus-ko-- batua-na `watu.' Pai' hi lolo parawatu tohe'i kuwangu tomi-ku-- batua-na, kurumpu hawe'ea tauna to mpopangala' -a. Hawe'ea kuasa anudaa' uma mpokulei' mpodagi-ra.
23692	40	16	19	Kuwai' -ko kuasa mpototu'ai ntodea Alata'ala. Napa to nubotuhi hi dunia', tetu wo'o to nabotuhi Alata'ala hi rala suruga: Ane nu'uli' neo', Alata'ala-mi to mpo'uli' neo'. Ane nu'uli' ma'ala moto, Alata'ala-mi to mpo'uli' ma'ala moto."
23693	40	16	20	Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Neo' ulu ni'uli' hi hema-hema ka'Aku' -na Magau' Topetolo'."
23694	40	16	21	 Ntepu'u ngkai tempo toe, Yesus mpakanoto hi ana'guru-na napa to kana jadi' hi woto-na. Na'uli' -raka: "Kana hilou-a hi Yerusalem. Hi ria mpai' totu'a ngata, imam pangkeni hante guru-guru agama mpobalinai' -a pai' mposesa' -a. Rapatehi-a mpai', aga hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
23695	40	16	22	Aga Petrus mpo'ai' -i hi ncori-na pai' nakorai' -i na'uli': "Neo' Pue'! Kuperapi' hi Alata'ala bona nawi'iha tetu lau ngkai Pue'."
23696	40	16	23	Hampe'ili' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Palai-ko topesori! Doko' nulawa' -a, bona ngalai' neo' -a mpotuku' konoa Tuama-ku? Pekiri-nu tetu-le pekiri manusia', bela pekiri Alata'ala."
23697	40	16	24	 Oti toe Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Hema to doko' mpotuku' -a kana mpobahaka konoa-na moto, pai' kana napaha'a kaju parika' -na-- batua-na: kana natuku' hawa' -ku nau' napopate-ki. Oti toe-di pai' lako' ma'ala-i mpotuku' -a.
23698	40	16	25	Hema to mpentaei konoa-na moto, uma-i mpai' mporatai katuwua' to lompe'. Aga hema to mpobahaka konoa-na moto sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', nau' napopate-ki, hi'a mpai' to mporata katuwua' to lompe'.
23699	40	16	26	Napa kalaua-na tarumpu hawe'ea ka'uaa' dunia', ane uma taratai katuwua' to lompe' hi eo mpeno-na. Apa' uma ria napa-napa to ma'ala tasula' -ki katuwua' to lompe' toe.
23700	40	16	27	Bate rata mpai' tempo-na, Aku' Ana' Manusia' tumai ngkai suruga mpopehuwu kabaraka' -ku, to hewa kabaraka' Tuama-ku, pai' wori' wo'o mala'eka mpodohei-a. Nto'u toe mpai', bate kuhiwili kehi butu-butu dua tauna.
23701	40	16	28	Mpu'u-mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: ngkai olo' -ni koi' toi, ria-koi mpai' to ko'ia mate kako'ia-na nihilo-a, Aku' Ana' Manusia', rata jadi' Magau'."
23702	40	17	1	 Ono mengi ngkai ree, Yesus mpobawai tolu ana'guru-na hilou dohe-na hi bulu' to molangko. Ana'guru to tolu toera: Petrus, Yakobus pai' Yohanes ompi' -na Yakobus. Muntu' Yesus hante ana'guru-na to tolu toera-wadi to hi ria.
23703	40	17	2	Bula-ra hi ria, mobali' -mi lence-na. Lio-na mehini hewa eo, pai' pohea-na mengea' meringkila'.
23704	40	17	3	Muu-mule' rahilo-rawo ana'guru-nae, ria wo'o rodua nabi to owi mpololitai Yesus. Nabi to rodua toera, Musa pai' Elia.
23705	40	17	4	Ngkai ree Petrus mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pue', lompe' lia-ta mo'oha' hi rehe'i. Ane nupokono Pue', kubabehi tolu bamaru' hi rehe'i: hameha' bagia-nu Pue', hameha' bagia-na Musa pai' hameha' wo'o bagia-na Elia."
23706	40	17	5	Bula-na mololita-pidi Petrus, muu-mule' hompo-mi limu' to mehini mpokamoui-ra, pai' ngkai rala limu' toe mpo'epe-ra topololita to mpo'uli': "Hi'a toi-mi Ana' -ku to kupe'ahi'. Hi'a mpakagoe' nono-ku. Pe'epei-mi lolita-na!"
23707	40	17	6	Wae kara'epe-na ana'guru-na lolita toe, tetumpopo' -ramo hi tana' apa' me'eka' lia-ra.
23708	40	17	7	Tumai-i Yesus mpoganga-ra, na'uli' -raka: "Memata-mokoi, neo' me'eka'!"
23709	40	17	8	Kamenaa-ra, uma-pi ria hewa to rahilo-e we'i, muntu' Yesus-damo.
23710	40	17	9	Pana'u-ra ngkai lolo bulu' toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' ulu ni'uli' hi hema-hema napa to nihilo we'i duu' -na Aku', Ana' Manusia', rapotuwu' nculii' ngkai kamatea."
23711	40	17	10	Mepekune' -ramo ana'guru-na, ra'uli': "Napa pai' guru agama mpo'uli' nabi Elia ncala' -di to ri'ulu rata, pai' lako' rata-idi Magau' Topetolo' -e?"
23712	40	17	11	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u-di, Elia kana rata mperi'ulu, apa' hi'a to mporodo hawe'ea-na.
23713	40	17	12	Aga ku'uli' -kokoi, mpolia' rata-imile Elia-e, aga pangkeni ngata-ta uma mpo'incai-i. Ra'ewa lau-idi ntuku' konoa-ra. Wae wo'o mpai' Aku' Ana' Manusia' ra'ewa ntuku' konoa-ra."
23714	40	17	13	Ngkai ree, rapaha-mi ana'guru-na lolita Yesus-e we'i: to rarapai' -ki nabi Elia, hi'a-mi Yohanes Topeniu'.
23715	40	17	14	 Kanculii' -ra Yesus hante ana'guru-na to tolu toera mpohirua' -raka ntodea, ria hadua tomane tumai mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na, mpo'uli' -ki:
23716	40	17	15	"Pue', poka'ahi' -ka-kuwo ana' -ku. Mohaki' limpuangaa-i, pai' jau-i molimpu' nakeni haki' -na. Jau-i modungka hi rala apu, jau wo'o-i modungka hi rala ue.
23717	40	17	16	Kukeni-imi hi ana'guru-nu, aga uma-di rapakulei' mpaka'uri' -i."
23718	40	17	17	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma mowo-koie'! Ko'ia oa' -tano mepangala' -koie! Mesapuaka oa' -pidi-koi mposapuaka konoa Alata'ala! Ni'uli' -koina hangkuja tena-pi kahae-ku dohe-ni, hangkuja tena-pi kahae-na kupengkatarii kalente pepangala' -nie! Keni tumai ana' tetui!"
23719	40	17	18	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpopetibo' anudaa' to mpopedahi ana' toei. Palai-nami anudaa', pai' mo'uri' -imi-hawo topeda' toei.
23720	40	17	19	Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na malai ngkai ree, pai' ana'guru-na mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Guru, napa pai' uma kipakulei' mpopalai anudaa' toei-e we'i?"
23721	40	17	20	Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae moto-hawo-le, apa' hangkedi' rahi pepangala' -nie. Ku'uli' -kokoi: ane rii-ria-mi pepangala' -ta nau' hangkutuno' -wadi, uma ria to uma-na madupa'. Ma'ala ta'uli' -ki bulu' toe mai: `Mentoli-ko ngkai retu!' bate mentoli-ile. ((
23722	40	17	21	Aga seta to hewa toe we'i, sampale-i malai ane mosampaya pai' mopuasa' -koi.))"
23723	40	17	22	 Nto'u Yesus hante topetuku' -na morumpu hi Galilea, na'uli' -mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Aku' Ana' Manusia', ratonu-a mpai' hi kuasa manusia'.
23724	40	17	23	Rapatehi-a mpai', aga hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii' -a." Peda' lia-mi nono topetuku' -na mpo'epe lolita-na.
23725	40	17	24	 Karata-na Yesus hante topetuku' -na hi ngata Kapernaum, rata to mpesingarai' paja' Tomi Alata'ala hi Petrus pai' mpekune' -i: "Ha nabayari moto-hawo Guru-ni paja' Tomi Alata'ala-e, ba uma-di?"
23726	40	17	25	Na'uli' Petrus: "Nabayari moto!" Ngkai ree, nculii' -imi Simon Petrus hilou hi tomi po'ohaa' -ra. Rata hi ria, ko'ia-di napoka'alai mololita-e, ncaliu Yesus-mi mpekune' -i: "Simon, beiwa-kowo pomporata-nu: hema to kana mpobayari paja' pai' pepue' hi raja to mpokuasai ngata doo? Ntodea-na moto-di, ba pue' ngata to nakuasai-di?"
23727	40	17	26	Na'uli' Petrus: "Tantu pue' ngata to nakuasai to kana mpobayari." Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae, ntodea-na moto uma mingki' mpobayari. Wae wo'o kita' to jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala, uma-ta mingki' mpobayari paja' Tomi Alata'ala.
23728	40	17	27	Aga nau' wae, agina mobayari moto-tamo, bona neo' kedi' nono-ra hi kita'. Jadi', hilou-moko hi rano mopeka. Ala' bau' uru to lomo' -na nupeka. Nurata doi hi rala nganga-na hono' pobayari paja' hi kita' rodua. Ala' doi tetu, pai' nubayari-ki paja' Tomi Alata'ala."
23729	40	18	1	 Hinto'u toe, tumai-ra ana'guru Yesus mpomohui' -i, ra'uli': "Pue', ane jadi' Magau' -poko mpai', hema to meliu kabohe tuwu' -na hi rala Kamagaua' -nu?"
23730	40	18	2	Yesus mpokio' hadua ana' to kedi', napopokore hi laintongo' -ra,
23731	40	18	3	pai' na'uli' -raka: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: ane uma nibalii' kehi-ni pai' jadi' hewa ana' to kedi' toii, uma-koi mpai' jadi' ntodea Alata'ala.
23732	40	18	4	Hema to mpakadingki' nono-na pai' jadi' hewa ana' to kedi' tohe'ii, hi'a-mi to bohe mpu'u tuwu' -na ngkai hawe'ea ntodea Alata'ala.
23733	40	18	5	Hema to mpotarima hadua ana' to kedi' hewa ana' toii sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', batua-na Aku' -mi to natarima.
23734	40	18	6	"Aga hema to mpopanawu' hadua ana' to kedi' alaa-na uma-ipi mepangala' hi Aku', bohe mpu'u pehuku' Alata'ala hi tauna tetui. Agina lau-pi hameha' watu po'ahaa' to bohe ratoe hi wuroko' -na pai' -i ratene' hi rala tahi'.
23735	40	18	7	 Silaka tauna hi dunia' toi, apa' wori' to mpopanawu' -ra. Bate ria mpu'u-di to mepanawu' -e, aga silaka-ra tauna to mepanawu' toera.
23736	40	18	8	"Ane rapa' -na pale-ta hamali ba witi' -ta hamali to mpakeni-ta mojeko', pua' lau-mi pai' petadi. Agina hamali-damo pale-ta ba witi' -ta, asala mporata-ta katuwua' to lompe' dohe Alata'ala. Agina lau-pi toe, ngkai palea ntimalia pai' witia' ntimalia, hiaa' ka'omea-na ratadi-ta hi rala apu to jela' ncuu.
23737	40	18	9	Pai' ane rapa' -na mata-ta hamali to mpakeni-ta mojeko', jungki' pai' petadi. Agina hamali-wadi mata-ta pai' mporata katuwua' to lompe' moto-ta dohe Alata'ala, ngkai mataa ntimalia, hiaa' ka'omea-na ratadi-ta hi rala apu naraka.
23738	40	18	10	"Jadi', pelompehi mpu'u-koi, neo' -koi uma mposaile' ana' -ana' to kedi' hewa ana' tohe'ii, nau' hadua. Apa' mpu'u-mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: mala'eka to mpodoo-ra tida ncuu hi nyanyoa Tuama-ku to hi rala suruga. ((
23739	40	18	11	Apa' patuju-ku Aku' Ana' Manusia' tumai hi dunia', bona mpopali' tauna to molaa ngkai Alata'ala pai' mpohore-ra ngkai huku' jeko' -ra.))
23740	40	18	12	"Beiwa pomporata-ni? Ria hadua tauna to ria bima-na ha'atu ma'a-na. Ane moronto hama'a, napa to nababehi? Tantu napalahii bima-na to sio mpulu' sio hi panapa bulu', pai' -i hilou mpopali' to hama'a to moronto toei.
23741	40	18	13	Pai' ane narua' nculii' -ipi, mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi meliu-mi kagoe' -na mpokagoe' bima to hama'a toei, ngkai bima-na to sio mpulu' sio to uma-ra-rana moronto.
23742	40	18	14	Wae wo'o Tuama-ni hi rala suruga, uma napokonoi ane ria hadua ngkai ana' to kedi' toi to molaa ngkai Hi'a.
23743	40	18	15	 "Ane ria ompi' hampepangalaa' -ta to masala' hi kita', hilou-ta mpohirua' -ki, pai' uli' -ki sala' -na. Tababehi toe hante uma ria to ngincai, muntu' kita' tau rodua-wadi. Ane napangala' lolita-ta, lompe' nculii' -mi pohintuwu' -ta.
23744	40	18	16	Aga ane uma-i dota mpangala' lolita-ta, po'ema' hadua ba rodua dohe-ta hilou mpololitai-i. Apa' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' owi te'uki' hewa toi: `Ane ria tauna to rapakilu mpobabehi sala', kana ria nte rodua ba tolu to jadi' sabi', bona monoa' -mi kara-kara-na.'
23745	40	18	17	Ane uma-i dota mpangala' lolita sabi' toera, bua' -imi hi hawe'ea ompi' hampepangalaa'. Ane uma oa' napangalai' nau' hawe'ea ompi' hampepangalaa' mpoparesai' -i, pelele' lau-imi-hana, taponcawa hewa tauna to uma mpo'incai Alata'ala lau-imi, pai' hewa tauna to dada'a kehi-ra.
23746	40	18	18	"Penonoi-koi! Napa to nibotuhi hi dunia', tetu wo'o to nabotuhi Alata'ala hi rala suruga: Ane koi' mpo'uli' neo', Alata'ala-mi to mpo'uli' neo'. Ane koi' mpo'uli' ma'ala moto, Alata'ala-mi to mpo'uli' ma'ala moto.
23747	40	18	19	Ku'uli' wo'o: ane ria-koi hi dunia' toi nte rodua to hintuwu' mekakae mperapi' ba napa-napa, posampaya-ni toe natompoi' Tuama-ku to hi rala suruga.
23748	40	18	20	Apa' hiapa tauna morumpu sabana Aku', nau' rodua ba tolu-ra-wadi, ria-a dohe-ra."
23749	40	18	21	 Oti toe, Petrus mpomohui' Yesus pai' mpekune' -i, na'uli': "Pue', ane ompi' hampepangalaa' -ku masala' hi aku', hangkuja ngkani kana ku'ampungi-i? Nte pitu ngkani?"
23750	40	18	22	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma wule' pitu ngkani-wadi. Nau' mo'atu-atu ngkani-nai masala' hi kita', kana ta'ampungi-i.
23751	40	18	23	Apa' Alata'ala hewa magau' to hi rala lolita rapa' toi: Ria hadua magau' doko' mpowile inta batua-na.
23752	40	18	24	Lomo' -na, ria hadua batua rakeni hi nyanyoa-na to mo'inta hi juta-na.
23753	40	18	25	Uma mpu'u-hawo nakulei' mpobayari inta-na toe. Jadi', mohawa' -mi magau' toei, na'uli': `Pobalu' lau-imi batua tetui hante ana' -na pai' tobine-na pai' hawe'ea rewa-na, pobayari-ki inta-na.'
23754	40	18	26	"Powingkotu' -nami batua toei hi nyanyoa magau', mpopepoka'ahi', na'uli': `Mosabara-ko Magau', kubayari moto-kuwo mpai' inta-ku!'
23755	40	18	27	"Ngkai ree, metumu' lau-mi ahi' -na magau' mpoka'ahi' batua-na toei. Nabahaka-imi pai' na'uli' -ki: `Inta-nu, uma-pi mingki' nubayari.'
23756	40	18	28	"Palai-na batua toei, napohirua' -ki hadua hingka batua-na to mo'inta hi hi'a hi ncobu-na-wadi. Napentoe doo-na toei, nabaga' pai' na'uli' -ki: `Bayari omea-mi inta-nu!'
23757	40	18	29	"Powingkotu' -nami-hawo doo-na toei mpopepoka'ahi', na'uli': `Mosabara-ko ulu bale, kubayari moto-kuwo mpai' inta-ku!'
23758	40	18	30	Aga uma napangalai' pomperapia' -na toe. Napopesua' lau-imi hi rala tarungku' duu' -na tebayari omea inta-na.
23759	40	18	31	"Karahilo-na batua to ntani' -na napa to jadi' tohe'e, peda' lia-mi-rawo nono-ra. Hilou-ramo hi magau' mpo'uli' kehi batua toei-e we'i.
23760	40	18	32	Mpo'epe toe we'i, kamoroe-nami magau'. Mpohubui-i tauna hilou mpokio' batua to dada'a gau' -na tohe'ei. Karata-na, na'uli' -ki: `Dada'a lia-ko! Inta-nu kupori-mi ngkai rala buku-ku, apa' moranempale-moko hi aku'.
23761	40	18	33	Napa-di-kona pai' uma nupoka'ahi' hingka batua-nu, hewa aku' mpoka'ahi' -koe!'
23762	40	18	34	Uma-pi mowo roe-na magau'. Batua to dada'a gau' -na toei napopesua' hi rala tarungku' duu' -na tebayari oti inta-na."
23763	40	18	35	Napohudu Yesus lolita rapa' toe, na'uli': "Wae wo'o Tuama-ku to hi rala suruga mpobabehi hi koi' -e, ane uma-koi mpo'ampungi doo-ni ngkai nono-ni mpu'u."
23764	40	19	1	 Kahudu-na Yesus mpololita hawe'ea toe, malai-imi ngkai tana' Galilea hilou hi tana' Yudea to hi dipo ue Yordan.
23765	40	19	2	Wori' tauna mpotuku' -i, pai' to peda' napaka'uri'.
23766	40	19	3	 Ria ba hangkuja dua to Parisi tumai mposori Yesus. Rapekune' -i: "Ntuku' atura agama-ta, ba ma'ala moto-hawo tomane mpogaa' -ki tobine-na nau' to uma kojerea'?"
23767	40	19	4	Natompoi' Yesus: "Kiwoi napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' owi: lomo' -na Topejadi' mpajadi' hadua tomane pai' hadua tobine.
23768	40	19	5	Pai' oti toe na'uli': `Tomane kana mpalahii tina pai' tuama-na, pai' kana tuwu' hintuwu' hante tobine-na, bona hira' tau rodua toe jadi' hewa hadua lau-ra-damo.'
23769	40	19	6	Jadi', hi poncilo Alata'ala, tau hancamoko uma-pi rodua, hadua lau-ramo. Toe pai' ku'uli' -kokoi: ane ntoa' Alata'ala mpoposidai' -ra, manusia' uma ma'ala mpogaa' -ra."
23770	40	19	7	Mehono' -ra to Parisi: "Ane wae, napa pai' Musa mohawa' bona tomane mpowai' sura pogaa' hi tobine, ane doko' napogaa' -ki?"
23771	40	19	8	Na'uli' Yesus: "Musa mpiliu-koi mogaa' -le, apa' ngkai kamotu'a nono-ni, uma tuduia'. Aga kakoo-kono-na, uma hewa toe ngkai lomo' -na.
23772	40	19	9	Bona ni'inca: hema to mpogaa' -ki tobine-na pai' -i motobinei to ntani' -na, mobualo' -i-hana. Sampale-di ane mobualo' tobine-nae, ma'ala-mi napogaa' -ki."
23773	40	19	10	Ngkai ree, ana'guru-na mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ane wae-di kamokoro-na ada poncamoko, agina lau-pi-hawo neo' ncamoko."
23774	40	19	11	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma hawe'ea tauna bisa ntarima lolita tetu. Aga ria moto tauna to napakatantu Alata'ala bona uma-ra ncamoko.
23775	40	19	12	Ria tauna to uma ncamoko apa' lawi' hewa toe-hawo ngkai kaputu-ra. Ria wo'o to uma ncamoko apa' babehia tau ntani' -na. Ria wo'o to uma ncamoko apa' lawi' kadota-ra moto-rawo, bona mologa-ra mpobago bago Alata'ala. Hema to mpakule' mpotuku' tudui' toi, lompe' ane natuku'."
23776	40	19	13	 Hangkani, ria tauna to mpokeni ana' -ra hi Yesus bona najama-ra pai' naposampayai. Aga ana'guru-na mpokaroe tauna toera.
23777	40	19	14	Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Pelele' moto-ra ana' tetura tumai hi Aku', neo' -ra nitagi. Apa' tauna to hewa toe-ramo to jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
23778	40	19	15	Ngkai ree, najama-ramo ana' toera, pai' -ra nagane'. Oti toe, malai-imi ngkai ree.
23779	40	19	16	 Hangkani, ria hadua tomane rata hi Yesus mpopekune' -i: "Guru, kehi napa to lompe' kana kubabehi bona mporata-a katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae?"
23780	40	19	17	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa pai' nupekune' -a beiwa kehi to lompe' -e? Uma ria ntani' -na to lompe', hadua Alata'ala-wadi. Ane doko' mporata katuwua' to lompe' -ko, tuku' -mi parenta Alata'ala."
23781	40	19	18	Mepekune' tena-i tau tohe'ei: "Parenta to'uma?" Natompoi' Yesus: "Neo' mepatehi, neo' mobualo', neo' manako, neo' mosabi' boa',
23782	40	19	19	kana tabila' tina tuama-ta, pai' poka'ahi' doo-ta hewa kampoka'ahi' -ta woto-ta moto."
23783	40	19	20	Na'uli' kabilasa toei: "Hawe'ea parenta tetu lau, kutuku' omea-mi. Napa-pi to kana kubabehi?"
23784	40	19	21	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane doko' -ko mpotuku' Alata'ala hante karoli' -roli' nono-nu, lou-moko ulu mpobalu' rewa-nu, pai' doi oli-na wai' -raka tokabu. Ane nubabehi hewa toe, bohe mpai' rasi' to nurata hi rala suruga. Oti toe, pai' tumai-moko mpotuku' -a."
23785	40	19	22	Mpo'epe toe we'i, kapeda' -nami nono-na pai' -i malai-mi, apa' wori' rewa-na.
23786	40	19	23	 Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus hi ana'guru-na: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: mokoro rahi tauna to mo'ua' jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na.
23787	40	19	24	Ku'uli' wo'o: mojoli-pi hama'a unta ntara hi wulou' jaru ngkai tauna to mo'ua' mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra."
23788	40	19	25	Kara'epe ana'guru-na lolita Yesus toe, rapokakonce lia, ra'uli': "Ei', ane wae-di, hema lau-damo to ma'ala mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae!"
23789	40	19	26	Yesus mponaa-ra pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ane hante pakulea' manusia' -le, uma ami' hema. Aga ane Alata'ala, uma ria to uma napakule'."
23790	40	19	27	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi-hawo Petrus: "Hiaa' kai', kipalahii omea-mi-kaina bona mpotuku' -ko. Hiwili napa mpai' to kirata?"
23791	40	19	28	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hi eo mpeno-na nto'u Alata'ala mpobo'ui omea, Aku' Ana' Manusia' mohura hi pohuraa to ncola moparenta. Nto'u toe mpai', koi' to mpotuku' -a toi-e, mohura wo'o-ko-koiwo hi pohuraa to hampulu' romeha', mpoparentai to Israel to hampulu' rontina.
23792	40	19	29	Hema-hema to mpalahii ompi' -na, tuama-na ba tina-na, ana' -na ba tomi-na ba bonea-na sabana mpotuku' -a, bate mporata-i mpai' ha'atu ngkani hiwili-na, pai' mporata wo'o-i katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
23793	40	19	30	Aga wori' tauna to bohe tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' kedi' tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno. Pai' wori' wo'o tauna to kedi' tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' bohe tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno."
23794	40	20	1	 Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane Alata'ala jadi' Magau', kajadi' -na hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i: Hadua pue' bonea anggur hilou mpopali' tauna to dota mobago hi bonea-na. Mepupulo modao' -i mporua' tauna,
23795	40	20	2	na'uli' -raka: `Hilou-koi mobago hi bonea-ku, kuwai' -koi hore hampepa' doi pera' gaji' -ni ha'eo.' Rapo'io' -mi lolita-na toe, hilou mpu'u-ramo.
23796	40	20	3	Jaa sio, hilou wo'o-imi mpali' to ntani' -na, nahilo ba hangkuja dua tauna ntora-ntora hi wiwi' karajaa.
23797	40	20	4	Na'uli' -raka: `Hilou-koi mobago hi bonea-ku, kuwai' moto-koi gaji' to masipato'.' Hilou mpu'u-ramo-rawo.
23798	40	20	5	Tebua' eo, hilou wo'o-imi mpopali' tauna, na'uli' -raka: `Hilou-koi mobago hi bonea-ku.' Wae wo'o jaa tolu libe eo.
23799	40	20	6	"Ncimonou' -mi, ba neo' jaa lima, modao' wo'o-imi mporua' tauna to ntora. Napekune' -ra: `Napa pai' ntora-ntora mara-wadi-koi ha'eoa, uma-ko-koina mobago-e?'
23800	40	20	7	"Ratompoi' -i: `Apa' uma hema to mpopobago-kai.' "Na'uli' pue' bonea toei: `Ane wae, hilou-mokoi mobago hi bonea-ku.' Hilou mpu'u-ramo-rawo.
23801	40	20	8	"Limpa-mi eo, na'uli' -mi pue' bonea hi mantoro' -na: `Kio' -ramo topobago toera ria, pai' wai' -ramo gaji' -ra. Wai' ulu gaji' hi tauna to lako' ntepu'u mobago jaa lima we'i. Oti toe, wai' gaji' hi tauna to ntepu'u mobago jaa tolu, duu' rata hi tauna to mobago ngkai mepuloa.'
23802	40	20	9	"Tumai mpu'u-ramo to mobago ntepu'u jaa lima ncimonou', mporata-ramo gaji' himpau hampepa' doi pera'.
23803	40	20	10	Kawae-kawae-na duu' -na rata wo'o-ra-rawo to mobago ngkai mepuloa-e ngone. To mobago ngkai mepulo toera mpo'uli' hi rala nono-ra: `Tantu meliu mpai' to nawai' -taka kita', apa' ha'eoa-ta-tana mobago!' Ntaa' we'i, bate hampepa' doi pera' wo'o-wadi-rawo to rarata-e.
23804	40	20	11	Kampohilo-ra gaji' -ra tohe'e, ngkunuti-ramo mpongkunutii pue' bonea, ra'uli':
23805	40	20	12	`To lako' rata mobago hi ka'omea-na, muntu' hajaa-ra-wadi mobago. Hiaa' kai', mobago ha'eoa-ka-kaina, nahimai' eo to ngkerepa'. Napa-di pai' nubayari-ra hibaa-balia hante kai'?'
23806	40	20	13	"Hampetompoi' pue' bonea toei: `Uma-a masala' hi koi', bale. Ha uma pojanci-tami mporata-koi gaji' hampepa' doi pera' rala-na ha'eo?
23807	40	20	14	Ala' -mi-koiwo gaji' -ni pai' hilou-mokoi! Konoa-kumi mpowai' gaji' hi tauna to rata ka'omea-na hibalia hante to kuwai' -kokoi koi'.
23808	40	20	15	Ha uma ma'ala kubabehi ntuku' konoa-ku hante doi-ku? Napa pai' mohingi' -koi hi doo ane lompe' nono-ku hi hira'?'"
23809	40	20	16	Napohudu Yesus lolita rapa' toe, na'uli': "Wae wo'o mpai' hi eo mpeno-na: wori' tauna to kedi' tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' bohe tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno. Pai' wori' wo'o tauna to bohe tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' kedi' tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno."
23810	40	20	17	 Nto'u toe, Yesus mako' mpotoa' ngata Yerusalem. Hi lengko ohea nakio' -ra ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua morumpu mopatani', pai' na'uli' -raka:
23811	40	20	18	"Epe-koi! Hilou-tamo tohe'i-e mpotoa' Yerusalem. Hi ria mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia' ratonu hi imam pangkeni pai' guru agama, pai' rabotuhi bona rapatehi-a.
23812	40	20	19	Oti toe mpai', ratonu-a hi tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi, rapopo'ore', raweba', pai' rapatehi-a hi kaju parika'. Aga hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
23813	40	20	20	 Nto'u toe, rata tobine-na Zebedeus hante ana' -na rodua hi Yesus. Motingkua' -i hi nyanyoa-na apa' ria to naperapi'.
23814	40	20	21	Napekune' Yesus: "Napa to nuperapi' -e?" Na'uli' totina toei: "Pomperapia' -kule, bona ane jadi' Magau' -poko mpai', ana' -ku to rodua tohe'ira mohura pai' moparenta hangkaa-ngkania dohe-nu, hadua hi mali ka'ana-nu, hadua hi mali ki'ii-nu."
23815	40	20	22	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Uma ni'incai napa to niperapi' tetu. Ha nipakule' mpai' mpokolo kaparia to kana kukolo-e?" Ratompoi' ana'guru to rodua toera: "Kipakule' moto!"
23816	40	20	23	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u, bate nikolo mpai' kaparia hewa to kukolo. Aga hema to mohura hi mali ka'ana-ku pai' hi mali ki'ii-ku, bela Aku' to mpakatantu. Tuama-ku-hana to mpakatantu hema to mporata bagia tetu."
23817	40	20	24	Kara'epe-na ana'guru-na to hampulu' pomperapia' doo-ra to rodua toera, kamoroe-rami mpokaroe-ra.
23818	40	20	25	Toe pai' Yesus mpokio' -ra omea pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ni'inca moto kasoa-ra topoparenta to uma mpo'incai Alata'ala mpoparentai ntodea-na. Tauna to bohe pangka' -ra mpewuku ntodea-na mpotuku' hawa' -na.
23819	40	20	26	Aga koi', neo' hewa toe kehi-ni. Hema-koi to doko' bohe pangka' -na, kana jadi' pahawaa'.
23820	40	20	27	Pai' hema to doko' bohe hanga' -na kana jadi' batua-ni.
23821	40	20	28	Kana nituku' po'ingku-ku, Aku' Ana' Manusia'. Patuju-ku tumai hi dunia', uma bona jadi' topohawa'. Pai' -a tumai-le, bona jadi' pahawaa', duu' -na mpewai' woto-ku rapatehi mpotolo' sala' tauna to wori'."
23822	40	20	29	 Kamalai-ra Yesus pai' ana'guru-na ngkai ngata Yerikho, mo'iko-ra-damo tauna mpotuku' -i.
23823	40	20	30	Hi wiwi' ohea, ria rodua tauna to wero mohura. Kape'epe-ra towero toera Kayesus-na to liu, mekio' -ramo, ra'uli': "Pue', muli Magau' Daud! Poka'ahi' -ka-kaiwo!"
23824	40	20	31	Tauna to wori' hi ree mpokaroe-ra, ra'uli': "Ngkalino-koi!" Uma-rawo rapangalai', rahuduwukui lau-mi mejeu': "Pue', muli Magau' Daud, poka'ahi' -ka-kaiwo!"
23825	40	20	32	Mento'o-imi Yesus, pai' -i mpokio' -ra tumai, na'uli' -raka: "Napa to nipokono kubabehi-kokoi?"
23826	40	20	33	Ratompoi' -i: "Pue', doko' -ka-kaiwo pehilo!"
23827	40	20	34	Metumu' -mi ahi' -na Yesus, toe pai' naganga mata-ra. Ncaliu pehilo-ramo, pai' -ra mpotuku' Yesus.
23828	40	21	1	 Mohu' -ramo hi Yerusalem, rata-ra hi ngata Betfage hi Bulu' Zaitun. Hi ree, Yesus mpohubui rodua ana'guru-na hilou meri'ulu,
23829	40	21	2	na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-koi hi ngata to tanyanyohi toe mai. Rata-koi mpai' hi ria, nihilo hama'a keledai to tehoo' pai' ana' -na mohu' dohe-na. Bongka koloro-na pai' keni-ra tumai.
23830	40	21	3	Ane ria to mpokamaro-koi, uli' -raka: `Apa' Pue' mparaluu-ra. Napoponculi' moto-kokoi mpai'.'"
23831	40	21	4	Tohe'e majadi' bona madupa' napa to na'uli' nabi owi, hewa toi:
23832	40	21	5	"Uli' -raka pue' ngata Sion: Hilo, etu-imi tumai Magau' -ni! Dingki' nono-na, mpohawi' -i hama'a keledai, mpohawi' -i hama'a ana' keledai to mongura."
23833	40	21	6	Jadi', hilou mpu'u-ramo ana'guru-na to rodua toera, rababehi hewa to nahubui-raka.
23834	40	21	7	Rakeni keledai to ntali ana' toera, ralampii hante baju-ra. Oti ralampii, mehawi' -imi Yesus.
23835	40	21	8	Hilou-ramo mpotoa' Yerusalem. Hi kaliua-na Yesus toe, wori' lia tauna mpokodo pohea-ra hi mata ohea, pai' hantongo' mpoho'a rau kaju pai' rakodo hi mata ohea bona mpobila' -i.
23836	40	21	9	Wori' tauna mpotuku' -i, ria-ra to meri'ulu, ria wo'o-ra to hi boko'. Ntora mogora-ra mpo'uli': Une' -imi muli Magau' Daud!" Pue' Ala mpogane' Magau' to tumai mpokeni hanga' -na!" Une' -imi Pue' Ala to hi rala suruga!"
23837	40	21	10	Pesua' -na Yesus hi ngata Yerusalem, konce-mi pue' ngata, ra'uli': "Hema-idie?"
23838	40	21	11	Ratompoi' tauna to dohe-na: "Yesus-le, nabi ngkai Nazaret tana' Galilea."
23839	40	21	12	 Oti toe, mesua' -imi Yesus hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala, pai' -i mpopalai hawe'ea tauna to mobabalu' hi ree. Nabilingko-raka meja' -meja' posulaa' -ra doi, pai' nabilingko wo'o pohuraa topobabalu' danci mangkebodo.
23840	40	21	13	Na'uli' -raka: "Hi rala Buku Tomoroli' Alata'ala mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Tomi-ku mpai' rakahangai' tomi posampayaa.' Hiaa' koi' -koina, niponcawa tomi toperampaki-di!"
23841	40	21	14	Hi Tomi Alata'ala, tauna towero pai' topungku rata hi Yesus, pai' napaka'uri' -ra.
23842	40	21	15	Aga imam-imam pangkeni pai' guru-guru agama, moroe-ra mpohilo tanda mekoncehi to nababehi Yesus. Gigi nono-ra mpo'epe ana' to mogora hi rala Tomi Alata'ala to mpo'uli': "Une' -imi muli Magau' Daud!"
23843	40	21	16	Toe pai' ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Nu'epe wa napa to ra'uli' -e!" Na'uli' Yesus: "Ku'epe moto. Ko'ia-tano nibasa hi rala Buku Tomoroli' -e to mpo'uli': `Nutudui' -ramo ana' -ana' pai' ana'lei mpohowa' lolita pe'une' hi Iko.'"
23844	40	21	17	Ngkai ree, malai-imi Yesus mpalahii-ra hilou hi mali ngata, turu hi Betania.
23845	40	21	18	 Kampeneo-na mepulo ngkii, hi pomako' -ra Yesus pai' ana'guru-na nculii' hilou hi Yerusalem, mo'oro' -imi Yesus.
23846	40	21	19	Mpohilo-i hi wiwi' ohea hangkaju kaju ara. Hilou-i hi tawu-na mpali' wua' -na, aga uma ria nau' hantakua, muntu' rau-na-wadi. Toe pai' Yesus mpototowi kaju toei, na'uli': "Ngkai eo toe lau, uma-poko mowua' -wua' kaju toi-ko!" Kamolaju-nami kaju ara toei.
23847	40	21	20	Wae karahilo-na ana'guru-na to jadi' toe, rapokakonce, ra'uli': "Beiwa pai' kaliliu molaju kaju ara toei-e mai?"
23848	40	21	21	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi, ane nipangala' pai' uma-koi morara', ma'ala wo'o-ko-koiwo mpobabehi hewa to kubabehi hi kaju toe we'i. Pai' uma muntu' tohe'e, ma'ala-koi mpololitai bulu' tohe'i: `Te'ongko' -moko, pengkanawu' -ko hi rala tahi'!' bate majadi' tetu.
23849	40	21	22	Napa-napa to niperapi' hi rala posampaya-ni, ane nipangala', bate nitarima."
23850	40	21	23	 Mesua' wo'o-imi Yesus hi rala Tomi Alata'ala pai' metudui'. Bula-na metudui', rata-ramo imam pangkeni hante totu'a to Yahudi mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Uli' -kakai, ngkaiapa huraa-nu mpobabehi hawe'ea tetu hi Tomi Alata'ala! Hema to mpowai' -ko kuasa hewa tetu?"
23851	40	21	24	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku', ria wo'o-kuwo pompekunea' -ku hi koi'. Ane nitompoi' -ka, bo ku'uli' -kokoi kangkaiapa-na kuasa-ku mpobabehi hawe'ea toe lau.
23852	40	21	25	Uli' -ka pe': ngkaiapa kuasa-na Yohanes Topeniu' mponiu' tauna? Ngkai Alata'ala-di, ba ngkai manusia' -di?" Momepololitai-ramo pangkeni to Yahudi toera, ra'uli': "Beiwa-tale' mpotompoi' -ie? Ane ta'uli' ngkai Alata'ala kuasa-na, na'uli' -taka mpai': `Ane wae, napa pai' uma-i nipangala'?'
23853	40	21	26	Hiaa' ane ta'uli' ngkai manusia' -wadi kuasa-na, mpoka'eka' -ta ntodea, apa' ntodea toera mpo'uli' Yohanes toe hadua nabi."
23854	40	21	27	Jadi', ratompoi' -i: "Uma ki'incai." Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane wae, uma wo'o-kuwo ku'uli' -kokoi kangkaiapa kuasa-ku mpobabehi toe lau."
23855	40	21	28	 Napokaliliu Yesus lolita-na hi pangkeni agama Yahudi toera, na'uli': "Beiwa pomporata-ni tohe'i: Ria hadua tuama, rodua-ki ana' -na, paka' tomane. Hilou-i hi to tuaka, na'uli' -ki: `Uto', eo toe lau, hilou-ko mobago hi bonea.'
23856	40	21	29	"Natompoi': `Oja' -a Mama!' Aga ka'omea-na mobali' nono-na, hilou moto-i mobago hi bonea.
23857	40	21	30	"Ngkai ree, hilou wo'o-i hi ana' -na to tu'ai, na'uli' -ki: `Uto', hilou-ko mobago hi bonea.' "Natompoi' ana' toei: `Io', hilou moto-a Mama.' Ntaa' uma-idi hilou-e!"
23858	40	21	31	Ngkai ree, mepekune' -i Yesus hi pangkeni agama Yahudi, na'uli': "Jadi', ngkai ana' to rodua toera, hema to mpotuku' hawa' tuama-ra?" Ra'uli' pangkeni to Yahudi toera: "To lomo' -na." Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: tauna topojeko', hewa topesingara' paja' pai' tobine to uma tumotoa gau' -ra, hira' lau-mi to natarima Alata'ala jadi' ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na, bela koi'.
23859	40	21	32	Apa' Yohanes Topeniu' mpotudui' -koi ohea to monoa', aga uma-koi dota mpopangala' -i. Hiaa' topesingara' paja' pai' tobine to uma tumotoa gau' -ra, rapangala' -i-rana. Pai' nau' nihilo-mi toe, uma oa' nibalii' gau' -ni pai' uma oa' nipangala' -i."
23860	40	21	33	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka pangkeni agama Yahudi: "Epe wo'o-koi lolita rapa' tohe'i. Ria hadua pue' bonea mpohu'ai bonea-na hante anggur. Nawala ntololikia-na, nababehi pompeaa' anggur, pai' natunya' wo'o pongko pompodooa. Oti toe, napewai' bonea-na rapobago hi ba hangkuja dua tauna, pai' hilou-imi hi ngata to molaa.
23861	40	21	34	Rata-mi tempo pohopua' wua' anggur, napahawa' -ra ba hangkuja dua batua-na hilou mperapi' bagia-na.
23862	40	21	35	Aga topobago bonea toera mpohoko' batua to napahawa': ria-ra to rapao', ria to rapana' watu, ria wo'o to rapatehi.
23863	40	21	36	Pue' bonea toei mpahawa' tena batua-na to ntani' -na, meliu kawori' -ra ngkai to lomo' -na. Aga rapohewa toe wo'o-ra-wadi.
23864	40	21	37	Ka'omea-na, na'uli': `Agina ana' -ku moto-mi kupahawa' hilou, bate rapengkorui-i mpai'.'
23865	40	21	38	"Ntaa' we'i, karahilo-na topobago bonea toera ana' pue' bonea tohe'ei, mohawa' -ramo ra'uli': `Etu-imi tumai ana' -na, hi'a mpai' to jadi' pue' bonea toi-e. Kita tapatehi-i, bona bonea toi kita' -mi mpai' pue' -na.'
23866	40	21	39	Karahoko' -nami ana' toei, radii' hilou hi mali bonea pai' rapatehi."
23867	40	21	40	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka pangkeni agama Yahudi: "Jadi', ane rata nculii' -ipi pue' bonea-e, napopai-ra topobago bonea-na toera-e?"
23868	40	21	41	Ratompoi' -i: "Tantu napatehi-ra tauna to dada'a toera, pai' bonea-na nawai' -raka tau ntani' -na to dota mpowai' -i bagia-na hi tempo-na."
23869	40	21	42	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Tantu nibasa-mi lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpolowa pesapuaka-ni hi Aku', hewa toi moni-na: `Watu to ratadi topowangu tomi, watu toe lau-mi to jadi' poko parawatu. Tohe'e majadi' ntuku' konoa Pue' Alata'ala, uma mowo kalompe' -na hi poncilo-ta.'"
23870	40	21	43	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Jadi', apa' oja' -koi mpotarima-a jadi' Magau' -ni, wae-pi, bagia-ni hi rala Kamagaua' -na Alata'ala, ra'ala' ngkai koi' pai' rawai' -raka tauna to mpobabehi po'ingku to natao hi ntodea Alata'ala. ((
23871	40	21	44	Hewa kura to monawu' hi watu mopengka, pai' hewa kura to napitihi watu moreja', hewa toe wo'o mpai' tauna to mposapuaka-a.))"
23872	40	21	45	Kara'epe-na imam pangkeni pai' to Parisi lolita-lolita rapa' Yesus toe, ra'inca kahira' -na to natoa'.
23873	40	21	46	Toe pai' rapali' -mi ohea-ra mpohoko' -i. Aga uma-ra daho', apa' mpoka'eka' -ra ntodea, apa' ntodea mpo'uli' Yesus hadua nabi.
23874	40	22	1	 Mololita tena-i Yesus hi pangkeni agama Yahudi toera, mpo'uli' -raka hanyala-pi lolita rapa'. Na'uli':
23875	40	22	2	"Alata'ala hewa magau' to hi rala jarita toi: Hadua magau' mpobabehi karamea hi poncamokoa ana' -na.
23876	40	22	3	Mohawa' -i hi pahawaa' -na hilou mpokio' tauna to rahinta' hewa toi: `Hilou-tamo ngkoni' hi posusaa' poncamokoa!' Aga hawe'ea to rakio' toera, uma-ra dota hilou.
23877	40	22	4	Toe pai' nahubui tena pahawaa' -na to ntani' -na, na'uli' -raka: `Uli' -raka to rahinta': pongkoni' taha' -mi, japi hante porewua to morudu' ntani' -na rasumale' -mi, rodo-mi omea. Kita-mi hilou hi posusaa' poncamokoa!'
23878	40	22	5	Aga hawe'ea to rakio' toera uma mposaile' pekio' toe. Hore-hore hilou hi pobagoa-ra moto-ra. Ria-ra to hilou hi bonea-ra, ria-ra to hilou hi bago-ra ntani' -na.
23879	40	22	6	To ntani' -na wo'o-ra mpohoko' pahawaa' magau' toe, rapao' pai' rapatehi.
23880	40	22	7	Kana'epe-na magau' napa to jadi' tohe'e, moroe lia-imi. Nahubui tantara-na hilou mpatehi topepatehi toera, pai' mposuwe ngata-ra.
23881	40	22	8	"Oti toe, nakio' wo'o-ramo pahawaa' -na, na'uli' -raka: `Susa' poncamokoa rodo-mi, aga tauna to kukio', uma-ra natao mpokaralai.
23882	40	22	9	Wae-pi, hilou-mokoi hi ohea kama, hema-hema to nirua', bawai-ramo tumai mpokaralai susa' poncamokoa.'
23883	40	22	10	Kahilou-rami-rawo pahawaa' toera hi ohea mporumpu hawe'ea tauna to liu, uma mpenara' ba to lompe' gau' -ra ba to dada'a. Ka'omea-na ihia' mpu'u-mi tomi posusaa' hante torata.
23884	40	22	11	"Mesua' -imi magau' toei mpokamata torata. Nahilo-hawo hi olo' torata, ria hadua to uma moheai pohea posusa'.
23885	40	22	12	Na'uli' magau': `Bale, napa-kona pai' tumai-ko hi posusaa' uma-ko moheai pohea posusa' -e?' Uma-i-hawo winihi.
23886	40	22	13	Ngkai ree, mohawa' -imi magau' mpo'uli' -raka pahawaa' -na: `Hilu' witi' -na, hoo' pale-na, petadi-i hi mali-na rala kabengia-na! Hi ria-i mpai' geo' pai' ntodohaka.'"
23887	40	22	14	Napohudu Yesus lolita rapa' -na hewa toi: "Wori' tauna to nakio' Alata'ala, aga hangkedi' -ra-wadi to napelihi jadi' ntodea-na."
23888	40	22	15	 Ngkai ree, malai-ramo to Parisi ngkai Tomi Alata'ala. Mohawa' -ra mpali' akala beiwa-ra ma'ala mpo'opa kahala' lolita-na Yesus mpotompoi' pompekunea' -ra.
23889	40	22	16	Rarata-mi akala-ra: mpahawa' -ra ba hangkuja dua topetuku' -ra hante ba hangkuja dua tauna to tono' hi Magau' Herodes hilou hi Yesus. Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki: "Guru, ki'inca Guru tau manoa'. Monoa' lia tudui' -nu mpo'uli' napa konoa Alata'ala hi manusia'. Uma nupengkorui ba hema-hema, apa' uma-ko mpelence tauna.
23890	40	22	17	Toe pai' kiperapi' bona nu'uli' -kakai, beiwa pomporata-nu Guru: ntuku' atura agama-ta, ba ma'ala moto-ta mpobayari paja' hi Kaisar, ba uma-di?"
23891	40	22	18	Na'inca Yesus patuju nono-ra to dada'a toe, toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Hilo mpu'u-koie' topebagiu! Napa pai' doko' ni'opa kahala' lolita-ku!
23892	40	22	19	Popehuwu-ka pe' doi to biasa nibayari-ki paja' -e." Ratonu-miki hampepa' doi pera'.
23893	40	22	20	Na'uli' Yesus: "Lence hema pai' hanga' hema to hi doi toi?"
23894	40	22	21	Ratompoi': "Lence pai' hanga' Kaisar." Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae-di, wai' -ki Kaisar napa to kasipato' -na rawai' -ki Kaisar, pai' wai' -ki Alata'ala napa to kasipato' -na rawai' -ki Alata'ala."
23895	40	22	22	Kara'epe-na petompoi' Yesus tohe'e, rapokakonce. Kamalai-rami mpalahii Yesus.
23896	40	22	23	 Hi eo toe wo'o, ba hangkuja dua to Saduki rata hi Yesus. To Saduki toera, pangkeni agama Yahudi to mposapuaka tauna to mate tuwu' nculii' hi eo mpeno.
23897	40	22	24	Rata to Saduki toera mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, nabi Musa metudui' hewa toi: Ane hadua tomane mate, hiaa' uma-ki ria ana' -na, pudupuhe-na kana mpotobine balu-na, bona ria-ki-hawo muli-na tomate toei.
23898	40	22	25	Jadi', ria pitu to ntali ompi' paka' tomane. To ulumua' motobinei, mate-i uma ria ana' -na. Balu-na napotobine tu'ai-na.
23899	40	22	26	Ko'ia wo'o rapoka'alai mo'anai', mate wo'o-imi-hawo to tu'ai toei. Wae oa' -mi majadi' hi katolu-na duu' -na hi kapitu-na.
23900	40	22	27	Ka'omea-na, mate wo'o-imi-hawo tobine toei.
23901	40	22	28	Jadi' hi eo mpeno-na, ane tuwu' nculii' mpu'u-di hawe'ea tomate-e, hema-ramo mpai' pue' tobine toei? Apa' hawe'ea-ra mpotobine-imi."
23902	40	22	29	Na'uli' Yesus: "Sala' rahi pekiri-ni tetu, apa' uma nipaha ihi' Buku Tomoroli', uma wo'o ni'incai baraka' -na Alata'ala.
23903	40	22	30	Apa' ane tuwu' nculii' -ramo tauna to mate, katuwu' -ra hewa katuwu' mala'eka hi rala suruga, uma-rapa motobinei ba motomanei.
23904	40	22	31	Ha ko'ia ria nibasa lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpakanoto katuwu' -ra nculii' tomate-e? Ria Lolita Alata'ala owi to mpo'uli' -kokoi hewa toi:
23905	40	22	32	`Aku' toi-mi Alata'ala to napue' Abraham, Alata'ala to napue' Ishak, Alata'ala to napue' Yakub.' Batua-na, nau' mahae-ramo mate Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub, bate tuwu' moto-ra. Apa' bela tauna to mate to mepue' hi Alata'ala, tauna to tuwu' -hana to mpopue' -i."
23906	40	22	33	Kara'epe-na ntodea tudui' -na Yesus toe, rapokakonce.
23907	40	22	34	 To Saduki uma-pi tepehono', apa' nadagi-ramo Yesus. Kara'epe-na to Parisi toe, moromu wo'o-ramo-rawo mpopali' akala-ra mpo'akalai Yesus.
23908	40	22	35	Hadua ngkai laintongo' -ra, hadua guru agama, mperao mpo'opa petompoi' Yesus hante pompekunea' -na, na'uli':
23909	40	22	36	"Guru, ngkai hawe'ea parenta hi rala Atura Pue', parenta to'uma to meliu kabohe-na?"
23910	40	22	37	Na'uli' Yesus: `Kana tapoka'ahi' Pue' -ta Pue' Alata'ala hante nono-ta mpu'u, tatonu hawe'ea katuwu' -ta hi Hi'a, pai' tapoka'ahi' -i hudu inca-ta.'
23911	40	22	38	Toe-mi parenta to meliu kabohe-na, pai' to lomo' -na mpu'u.
23912	40	22	39	Pai' parenta karonyala-na to hibalia hante to lomo' -na toe: `Kana tapoka'ahi' doo-ta hewa pompoka'ahi' -ta woto-ta moto.'
23913	40	22	40	Hawe'ea Atura Pue' pai' tudui' nabi-nabi mentoe hi parenta to ronyala toe."
23914	40	22	41	 Bula-ra to Parisi ria-pidi morumpu hi retu, Yesus mpekune' -ra:
23915	40	22	42	"Beiwa pomporata-ni, hema-i Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Alata'ala-e? Muli hema-i?" Ratompoi': "Muli Magau' Daud."
23916	40	22	43	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae-di, napa pai' Daud mpokahangai' -i Pue' -na? Hante petete' Inoha' Tomoroli', Daud mpotompo'wiwi Magau' Topetolo' hewa toi:
23917	40	22	44	Pue' Ala mpo'uli' -ki Pue' -ku: `Mohura-moko hi mali ngka'ana-ku, duu' -na kupopengkoru hawe'ea bali' -nu hi Iko.'
23918	40	22	45	Jadi', ane muli Daud mpu'u-idi Magau' Topetolo' -e, napa pai' Daud mpokahangai' -i Pue' -na?"
23919	40	22	46	Uma ria haduaa to mpotompoi' -i. Ntepu'u ngkai eo toe, uma-pi hema to daho' mpekune' ba napa-napa hi Yesus.
23920	40	23	1	 Ngkai ree, Yesus mpololitai ntodea pai' topetuku' -na, na'uli':
23921	40	23	2	"Guru-guru agama pai' to Parisi mohura hi pohuraa Musa, apa' hira' to mpotudui' -koi Atura Musa.
23922	40	23	3	Toe pai' kana nituku' omea napa to ratudui' -kokoi. Aga neo' nipenau' po'ingku-ra, apa' hira' toe uma mpotuku' napa to ratudui' -kokoi.
23923	40	23	4	Hira' toe mpopokoloi ntodea hante parenta pai' ada to motomo, hiaa' hira' moto, uma-ra mpotulungi ntodea mpotuku' parenta pai' ada toe.
23924	40	23	5	"Wori' moto-hawo po'ingku-ra to lompe', aga patuju-ra mpobabehi po'ingku toe, bona rahilo doo-wadi. Mpopake' -ra tali posampaya to mopepa' -pepa', pai' rapokaloe wua' baju-ra, bona petuku' -ra hi Atura Musa ma'ala rahilo doo.
23925	40	23	6	Goe' -ra ane rapopohura-ra hi pohuraa to lompe' hi posusaa'. Goe' -ra rapopohura hi pohuraa karabilaa' hi tomi posampayaa.
23926	40	23	7	Goe' -ra ane ria tauna hi wiwi' karajaa motingkua' mpotabe-ra pai' mpokahangai' -ra `Guru.'
23927	40	23	8	"Aga koi', neo' -koi mpopebila' pai' doko' rakahangai' `Guru,' apa' hadua-wadi Guru-ni, pai' koi' omea ntali ompi' -wadi.
23928	40	23	9	Pai' neo' wo'o nipomolangko rahi ba hema-hema hi dunia' toi pai' mpokahangai' -ra `Tuama,' apa' Tuama-ni hadua-wadi, Hi'a-mi Tuama-ni to hi rala suruga.
23929	40	23	10	Pai' neo' wo'o-koi doko' rakahangai' `Pangkeni,' apa' Pangkeni-ni hadua-wadi, Hi'a-mi Magau' Topetolo'.
23930	40	23	11	Hema-koi to doko' bohe tuwu' -na, kana jadi' pahawaa' hi doo-na.
23931	40	23	12	Tauna to mpakalangko nono-ra, Pue' Ala bate mpodingkihi-ra, pai' tauna to mpakadingki' nono-ra, Pue' Ala mpomolangko-ra.
23932	40	23	13	 "Pai' koi' guru agama pai' to Parisi! Bate mporata silaka-koi mpai'! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Tauna to doko' jadi' ntodea Alata'ala, nitagi-ra. Koi' moto uma dota jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala, pai' tau ntani' -na to doko' jadi' ntodea-na, nihalawai' lau-rada. ((
23933	40	23	14	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Nibagiu tobine tobalu pai' nihagoi tomi-ra. Pai' mosampaya-koi nipomoloe-loe, bona tewunii' gau' -ni to dada'a tetu. Motomo lia mpai' huku' -ni.))
23934	40	23	15	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Mako' molaa-koi medipo tahi' modao' hi role-na, bona ngalai' ria nte hadua tauna to jadi' topetuku' -ni. Pai' ane ria-pi topetuku' -ni, nitudui' -ra mpotuku' pebagiu-ni, alaa-na meliu kadada'a gau' -ra ngkai koi', pai' meliu kamasipato' -ra rahuku' hi naraka ngkai koi'.
23935	40	23	16	"Bate silaka-koi mpai'! Koi' hewa to wero to doko' mpotete' doo! Metudui' -koi hewa toi: Ane ria tauna to mpobabehi pojanci pai' mosumpa-i mpokahangai' Tomi Alata'ala, ni'uli' uma-i tehoo' hante sumpa-na toe. Hiaa' ane mpokahangai' -i bulawa to hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, tehoo' -i hante sumpa-na toe.
23936	40	23	17	Wojo mpu'u-koi, hewa to wero-koi! Ha ni'uli' -koina bulawa to meliu ngkai Tomi Alata'ala! Hiaa' bo Tomi Alata'ala toe-di to mpomoroli' bulawa to hi rala-na.
23937	40	23	18	Metudui' wo'o-koi hewa toi: Ane tauna mosumpa mpokahangai' meja' pontunua pepue' to hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, uma-i tehoo' hante sumpa-na toe. Aga ane mpokahangai' -i pepue' to ratunu hi lolo meja' toe, ni'uli' bate tehoo' -i hante sumpa-na.
23938	40	23	19	Hewa to wero mpu'u-koi! Ha ni'uli' -koina, pepue' to meliu ngkai meja' pontunua pepue'? Uma-e', apa' meja' toe-di to mpomoroli' pepue' to hi lolo-nae.
23939	40	23	20	Ane tauna mosumpa mpokahangai' meja' pontunua pepue', batua-na mpokahangai' -i meja' toe pai' hawe'ea to ratunu hi lolo-na.
23940	40	23	21	Pai' ane tauna mosumpa mpokahangai' Tomi Alata'ala, batua-na mpokahangai' -i Tomi Alata'ala pai' Alata'ala to mo'oha' hi tomi toe.
23941	40	23	22	Pai' ane tauna mosumpa mpokahangai' suruga, batua-na mpokahangai' -i pohuraa Alata'ala, pai' mpokahangai' wo'o-i Alata'ala to mohura hi pohuraa toe.
23942	40	23	23	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Ntahawe' hinu'a to kedi', hewa tarangkada', ngkoromonyi' pai' wunga bonea, nipopepue' hampobagiahampulu' hi Alata'ala. Hiaa' parenta hi rala Atura Pue' to bohe mpu'u, hewa po'ingku to monoa', ma'ahi' hi doo, pai' mpo'ihii' janci, uma nisaile'. Kakoo-kono-na, ke parenta to bohe toe-hanale to kana nituku' -e, pai' neo' wo'o nilipo' mpotuku' parenta to kedi'.
23943	40	23	24	Koi' hewa towero to mpotete' doo. Koi' hewa tauna to mpolali koromu' nete' ngkai ue ininu-ni, hiaa' hama'a unta, to bohe lia, ni'ome' lau.
23944	40	23	25	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Koi' hewa tauna to mpobohoi' sangkiri' pai' piri hi mali-na-wadi, hiaa' hi rala-na babo' moto. Ada agama to kahiloa hi mali-na-wadi nituku' lia. Hiaa' hi rala nono-ni jampa pai' mpokahina anu doo-koi.
23945	40	23	26	Hewa towero mpu'u-koi, koi' to Parisi! Bohoi' ulu rala-na sangkiri', bona lompe' wo'o to hi mali-na.
23946	40	23	27	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Hewa daeo' to rasapuru' bula-koi: hi mali-na lompe' -damo hiloa-na, hiaa' bo hi rala-na paka' wuku kiu pai' wori' nyala to merungkui.
23947	40	23	28	Wae wo'o koi': ane hi pogau' to hi mali-na to rahilo doo, monoa' -koi. Hiaa' hi rala nono-ni topebagiu-koi pai' dada'a kehi-ni.
23948	40	23	29	"Silaka-koi, guru agama pai' to Parisi! Lompe' hi mali-na-wadi-koi! Nipenasa-damo mpakalompe' daeo' -ra nabi-nabi pai' tauna to monoa' owi.
23949	40	23	30	Molangko nono-ni, ni'uli': `Ane ke rapa' -na tuwu' -makai hingkala'ia hante totu'a-kai owi, ke uma-ka-kaina mpodohei-ra mpatehi nabi-nabi.'
23950	40	23	31	Jadi', nipangaku' moto kakoi' -na muli-ra to mpatehi nabi-nabi, pai' kehi ntu'a-ni tetu bate ni'uhi.
23951	40	23	32	Wae-pi, pokaliliu lau-mi mpobabehi jeko' hewa to rababehi ntu'a-ni tetu!
23952	40	23	33	"He topebagiu, he koi' to bengku' gau' -ni! Ha ni'uli' -koina tewi'iha-koi mpai' ngkai huku' -ni hi rala naraka-e?
23953	40	23	34	
23954	40	23	35	Ntu'a-ni owi mpopatehi wori' tauna to monoa' ingku-ra, ntepu'u ngkai kampopatehi-ra Habel, tauna to monoa' ingku-na owi, rata-rata hi kampopatehi-ni Zakharia ana' Berekia, to nipatehi hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala hi olo' tomi to moroli' pai' meja' pontunua pepue'. Jadi', hi koi' to tuwu' tempo toi, kupahawa' wo'o mpai' nabi, tauna to pante pai' guru to mpotudui' -koi lolita-ku. Hantongo' -ra mpai' nipatehi, hantongo' -ra niparika', ria wo'o-ra to niweba' hi rala tomi posampayaa-ni, ria wo'o-ra to nidapa' hilou hi ngata-ngata petiboa' -ra. Ka'omea-na mpai', koi' to tuwu' tempo toi-mi to mpokolo hawe'ea kasalaa' totu'a-ni to mpatehi tauna to monoa' owi.
23955	40	23	36	Wae mpu'u-di! Koi' to tuwu' tempo toi bate rahuku' sabana hawe'ea kasalaa' -ra totu'a-ni toe.
23956	40	23	37	"Ee to Yerusalem! to Yerusalem! Nipatehi-ra-koina nabi-nabi, pai' nipana' watu-ra-koina tauna to nasuro Alata'ala hi koi'. Wori' ngkani-mi kupehuka' ngkupui-koi, hewa hama'a manu' tina mpo'urui ana' -na hi une' pani' -na, aga uma-koi dota.
23957	40	23	38	Bona ni'inca: tomi pepuea' -ni toi napalahii-kokoi mpai' Alata'ala.

23959	40	24	1	 Malai-imi Yesus ngkai Tomi Alata'ala. Tumai-ramo ana'guru-na mpotudo' -ki kalompe' pompowangu-na tomi toe.

23968	40	24	10	Wori' tauna ngkala'ura ngkai petuku' -ra hi Aku'. Ria to mpewai' doo-ra hi bali' -ra. Wori' tauna momepokahuku'.

24011	40	25	2	Lima-ra to wojo, lima-ra to monoto nono-ra.

24042	40	25	33	Tauna to mpobabehi konoa Alata'ala kupahantuda hi mali ka'ana-ku, pai' tauna topesapuaka hi mali ki'ii-ku.

24044	40	25	35	Apa' nto'u-ku mo'oro', niwai' -a pongkoni'. Ngkamara-a, niwai' -a ue ininu. Liu-a hi tomi-ni, nipopehani-a.

24047	40	25	38	Nto'uma-ko liu hi tomi-kai, pai' kipopehani-ko? Nto'uma-ko kihilo uma ria pohea-nu, pai' kiwai' -ko pohea?
24048	40	25	39	Nto'uma-ko kihilo peda' ba hi rala tarungku', pai' tilou-kai mpencuai' -ko?'
24049	40	25	40	"Pai' Aku' Magau', kutompoi' -ra: `Bona ni'inca: napa to nibabehi mpotulungi ompi' -ku tohe'ira lau, nau' hadua ompi' -ku to kedi' lia katuwu' -na, batua-na, hibalia nibabehi hi Aku' -mi.'
24050	40	25	41	"Oti toe mpai', ku'uli' -raka to hi mali ki'ii-ku: `Malai-mokoi ngkai rei, koi' to natotowi Tuama-ku! Mesua' -mokoi hi rala apu to jela' ncuu, to raporodo ami' -miki Magau' Anudaa' pai' mala'eka to mpotuku' -i.
24051	40	25	42	Apa' nto'u-ku mo'oro', uma-a niwai' koni'. Ngkamara-a, uma-a niwai' ue ininu.
24052	40	25	43	Liu-a hi tomi-ni, uma-a nipopehani. Uma ria pohea-ku, uma-a niwai' pohea. Peda' -a, hi rala tarungku' -a, uma-a nipencuai'.'
24053	40	25	44	"Ra'uli' wo'o-mi-rawo mpai' mpo'uli' -ka: `Pue', nto'uma-ko kihilo mo'oro' ba ngkamara ba hewa tauna toliu, ba uma-ko moheai, ba peda' ba ratarungku', pai' uma-ko kitulungi?'
24054	40	25	45	"Pai' Aku' Magau', kutompoi' -ra: `Bona ni'inca: apa' uma-koina nitulungi-ra tauna to kedi' tuwu' -ra tohe'i-era lau, batua-na, Aku' -mi to uma nitulungi tetu-e.'"
24055	40	25	46	Napohudu Yesus lolita-na, na'uli': "Hawe'ea tauna to dada'a toera lau ratadi hi rala naraka pai' rahuku' duu' kahae-hae-na, pai' tauna to monoa' mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na."
24056	40	26	1	 Kahudu-na Yesus mpololita hawe'ea tohe'e, na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na:
24057	40	26	2	"Ni'inca wa karo'eo-na-damo eo bohe Paskah? Pai' Aku' Ana' Manusia' rapewai' hi pale bali' -ku bona raparika'."
24058	40	26	3	Nto'u toe, imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi morumpu hi tomi Imam Bohe to rahanga' Kayafas.
24059	40	26	4	Mohawa' -ramo, ra'uli': "Beiwa akala-ta mpolede pai' mpohoko' Yesus bona rapatehi-ie?
24060	40	26	5	Agina neo' ulu tahoko' -i nto'u eo bohe, nee-neo' mpai' bara' ntodea."
24061	40	26	6	 Nto'u Yesus hi ngata Betania, hilou-i hi tomi hadua tauna to rahanga' Simon topohaki' poko'.
24062	40	26	7	Bula-na hi ree, rata hadua tobine ngkeni hameha' butolo' ihia' lana honga to masuli' lia oli-na. Bula-na Yesus ngkoni', tumai tobine toei mpotua lana honga toe hi woo' -na tanda pebila' -na.
24063	40	26	8	Karahilo-na ana'guru-na napa to nababehi tobine toei, moroe-ramo, ra'uli': "Napa-hawo pai' rakerei lana to masuli' oli-na hewa tetu?
24064	40	26	9	Ke agina rapobalu' lau bona oli-na rawai' -raka tokabu."
24065	40	26	10	Na'inca Yesus pekiri-ra, toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' nipedahi nono-na tobine toei! To nababehi hi Aku' toe-le, lompe'.
24066	40	26	11	Apa' tokabu-hana, ria oa' loga-ni mpotulungi-ra apa' ria oa' -ra doo-ni. Aga Aku', uma-a mpai' ria oa' doo-ni.
24067	40	26	12	Natuai-a hante lana toe, mpakasadia ami' woto-ku hi karatana-ku mpai'.
24068	40	26	13	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hi humalili' dunia', hiapa-apa Kareba Lompe' rapalele, napa to nababehi tobine toei we'i bate ralolita, uma mpai' ralipo' -lipo'."
24069	40	26	14	 Nto'u toe, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, to rahanga' Yudas Iskariot, hilou hi imam pangkeni.
24070	40	26	15	Na'uli' -raka: "Ane kutonu Yesus hi rala pale-ni, napa to niwai' -ka?" Rabila' -mi doi pera' tolu mpulu', pai' rawai' -ki.
24071	40	26	16	Ngkai ree, Yudas mpopali' loga to lompe' mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na.
24072	40	26	17	 Hi eo to lomo' -na hi Posusa' Roti to Uma Raragii, rata-ramo ana'guru-na hi Yesus, ra'uli' -ki: "Hiapa konoa-nu kiporodo pongkoni' Paskah to takoni' -e mpai'?"
24073	40	26	18	Na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi rala ngata hi tomi ni'anu, uli' -ki hewa toi: `Na'uli' Guru: Rata-mi tempo-ku, doko' -a mo'eo bohe Paskah hi tomi-nu hante ana'guru-ku.'"
24074	40	26	19	Ana'guru Yesus toera, hilou mpu'u-ramo hewa to nahubui-raka, pai' -ra mporodo-mi pongkoni' Paskah.
24075	40	26	20	Kamobengi-na, Yesus hante ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua mohura ngkoni'.
24076	40	26	21	Bula-ra ngkoni' toe, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Pe'epei-koi: hadua ngkai olo' -ni mpobalu' -a mpai' hi bali' -ku."
24077	40	26	22	Mpo'epe tohe'e, peda' -mi nono-ra ana'guru-na, pai' mepekune' -ramo hadua bo hadua hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Bela-hawo aku' to nutoa' -e Pue'?"
24078	40	26	23	Na'uli' Yesus: "Tauna to mpololo' roti hi banga' uta hangkaa-ngkania hante Aku', hi'a-mi to mpobalu' -a.
24079	40	26	24	Makono mpu'u, Aku' Ana' Manusia' bate mate hewa to ralowa hi rala Buku Tomoroli' -e. Aga mpe'ahii' tauna to mpobalu' -a tetui. Ke lompe' lau-pi ane uma-i na'ote tina-na."
24080	40	26	25	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi-hawo Yudas, to mpobalu' -ie mpai': "Bela-hawo aku' to nutoa' -e Guru?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Hewa to nu'uli' tetu-midi!"
24081	40	26	26	 Bula-ra ngkoni', na'ala' -mi Yesus roti pai' naposampayai mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala. Oti toe, napihe-pihe pai' natonu-raka ana'guru-na, na'uli': "Ala' -mi, koni' -mi. Toi-mi woto-ku."
24082	40	26	27	Oti toe na'ala' wo'o sangkiri' to ihia' anggur, na'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala pai' natonu-raka, na'uli': "Nginu-mokoi omea,
24083	40	26	28	apa' toi-mi raa' -ku to rabowo ane mate-a mpai'. Raa' -ku toi mpai' mporohoi pojanci to mpoposidai' Alata'ala hante manusia', bona jeko' tauna to wori' ra'ampungi.
24084	40	26	29	Bona ni'inca: ntepu'u ngkai wae lau, uma-apa nginu anggur duu' -na rata tempo-na Tuama-ku jadi' Magau' hi dunia' bo'u. Nto'u toe mpai' mpo'inu-a anggur to bo'u hangkaa-ngkania hante koi' hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
24085	40	26	30	Oti toe morona' -ramo hanyala rona' pe'une'. Kahudu-ra morona', malai-ramo ngkai ngata hilou hi Bulu' Zaitun.
24086	40	26	31	 Na'uli' -mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Bengi toe mpai' lau, hawe'ea-ni, molengo pepangala' -ni hi Aku', apa' ria te'uki' Lolita Alata'ala to mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Kupatehi topo'ewu toei, pai' bima inewu-na pagaa' -gaa' -ramo.'
24087	40	26	32	Aga ane tuwu' nculii' -apa mpai', meri'ulu-a hilou hi tana' Galilea, bona hirua' hi ria-ta-damo mpai'."
24088	40	26	33	Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Petrus: "Nau' hawe'ea tauna molengo pepangala' -ra hi Iko Pue', aku' uma!"
24089	40	26	34	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -koko: kako'ia-na turua' manu' bengi toe mpai' lau, mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku."
24090	40	26	35	Na'uli' Petrus: "Nau' -a mate hangkaa-ngkania dohe-nu, uma mpu'u kusapu kaku'inca-nu!" Wae wo'o-rawo pololita-ra ana'guru-na to ntani' -na.
24091	40	26	36	 Oti toe, rata-ramo hi pampa to rahanga' Getsemani. Hi ree-i mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Koi', mohura hi rei-mokoi. Aku', lou hi ree-a mai ulu mosampaya."
24092	40	26	37	Aga Petrus pai' ana' Zebedeus to rodua, nabawai-ra hilou dohe-na. Nto'u toe, susa' pai' mokaratu-mi nono-na.
24093	40	26	38	Na'uli' -raka: "Susa' lia nono-ku, hewa to neo' mate-ama ku'epe. Rehe'i-mokoi ulu, dohei-a mojaga."
24094	40	26	39	Oti toe hilou-imi molaa hangkedi', pai' -i motumpa, mosampaya, na'uli': "Tuama-ku, ane ma'ala, pomolaa-ka-kuwo kaparia to neo' mporumpa' -a toi. Aga bela konoa-ku Aku' to jadi', agina konoa-nu Iko moto."
24095	40	26	40	Oti toe, nculii' -imi hi ana'guru-na to tolu toera, narata-ra bula-ra leta' moto. Na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Hilo! Hajaa-wadi uma nidadahi mojaga dohe-ku?
24096	40	26	41	Mojaga pai' mosampaya-mokoi bona neo' -koi mporata pesori. Hi rala nono-ni dota moto-koi mpobabehi to makono, aga uma nidadahi apa' manusia' bate lente."
24097	40	26	42	Ngkai ree, hilou wo'o-imi mosampaya, na'uli': "Tuama-ku, ane kaparia toi uma ma'ala rawi'iha-ka, bate konoa-numi to majadi'."
24098	40	26	43	Oti toe, nculii' wo'o-imi mporata ana'guru-na, leta' wo'o-ra-wadi apa' mopoke' mata-ra.
24099	40	26	44	Hangkani wo'o-ipi Yesus mpalahii-ra hilou mosampaya katolu ngkani-na. Posampaya-na toe hibalia hante posampaya-na to we'i.
24100	40	26	45	Ka'oti-na mosampaya toe, nculii' wo'o-imi hi ana'guru-na to tolu toera, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Turu pai' leta' oa' -pada-koi? Hilo-dile, rata-mi tempo-na Aku' Ana' Manusia' rapobalu' pai' ratonu hi tauna to dada'a.
24101	40	26	46	Memata-mokoi! Hilo, etu-imi tumai tauna to mpobalu' -a. Kita-mi lou."
24102	40	26	47	 Bula-na Yesus mololita-pidi, rata-imi Yudas, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua. Pai' dohe-na wori' wo'o tau ntani' -na to ngkeni piho' pai' sumampu. Hira' toe rapahawa' imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi.
24103	40	26	48	Yudas mpo'uli' ami' -miraka tanda bona ra'inca kato'uma-nai Yesus, na'uli': "Hema mpai' to ku'eki, Hi'a-mi Yesus. Hoko' -imi!"
24104	40	26	49	Jadi', karata-ra hi ree, kahilou-nami Yudas mpohirua' -ki Yesus, na'uli': "Wori' tabe, Guru!" pai' na'eki-i ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi.
24105	40	26	50	Na'uli' Yesus: "Toe-tanoe pai' tumai-koe, bale!" Katumai-rami tauna to wori' mpohoko' Yesus.
24106	40	26	51	Ngkai ree, hadua tauna to dohe Yesus mpowute' piho' -na natime-ki batua Imam Bohe, bela mpoholu tilinga-na.
24107	40	26	52	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Unco' nculii' piho' -nu! Apa' hema to mpohenta piho' mpopatehi doo, bate rapatehi wo'o-i-hawo mpai' hante piho'.
24108	40	26	53	Ha uma nu'incai, ane mpopetulungi-a hi Tuama-ku, napesahui mpahawa' tumai hampulu' rontuda tantara mala'eka-na, ba melabi tena!
24109	40	26	54	Aga ane ta'ewa-ra to mpohoko' -a toi-e, uma mpai' madupa' lolita to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' owi to mpo'uli' hawe'ea toe lau kana majadi' hi Aku'."
24110	40	26	55	Nto'u toe, na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka tauna to wori' toera: "Ha toperampaki-a toi-e, pai' mingki' tumai-koi ntali piho' pai' sumampu mpohoko' -ae! Butu eo-na mohura moto-a hi rala Tomi Alata'ala metudui', napa pai' uma-a nihoko' nto'u toe?
24111	40	26	56	Aga to hewa toi-le kana majadi', bona madupa' -mi napa to ra'uki' nabi-nabi owi hi rala Buku Tomoroli'." Oti toe, metibo' -ramo hawe'ea ana'guru-na mpalahii-i.
24112	40	26	57	 Ngkai ree, tauna to mpohoko' Yesus mpokeni-i hilou hi tomi Imam Bohe Kayafas. Hi ria morumpu-ramo guru-guru agama pai' totu'a to Yahudi.
24113	40	26	58	Petrus metuku' ngkawao-wadi, duu' -na rata hi berewe tomi Imam Bohe. Mesua' -i hi berewe pai' -i mohura dohe topojaga, apa' doko' na'inca ba napa mpai' to majadi' hi Yesus.
24114	40	26	59	Nto'u toe, imam pangkeni pai' hawe'ea topohura agama morumpu hi tomi Kayafas. Mpali' -ra sabi' boa' to mpakilu Yesus, bona ngalai' rahuku' mate-i.
24115	40	26	60	Aga nau' wori' sabi' boa' to mpo'uli' napa to nababehi Yesus, uma raruai' to masipato' rahuku' mate-ki. Ka'omea-na, ria rodua sabi' to tumai hi nyanyoa topohura to hibalia lolita-ra,
24116	40	26	61	ra'uli': "Tauna toii, ria-i-hana mpo'uli': `Tomi Alata'ala ma'ala kugero, pai' rala-na tolu eo kuwangu nculii'.'"
24117	40	26	62	Kamokore-nami Imam Bohe pai' -i mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ha uma nutompoi' -ra to mpakilu-ko toe-e?"
24118	40	26	63	Aga Yesus, uma-i winihi. Na'uli' wo'o-mi Imam Bohe: "Hante hanga' Alata'ala to Tuwu', uli' -kakai to makono! Makono mpu'u ka'Iko-na Magau' Topetolo', Ana' Alata'ala-e?"
24119	40	26	64	Na'uli' Yesus: "Io', hewa to nu'uli' tetu-e. Pai' ku'uli' tena: rata mpai' tempo-na nihilo-a Aku' Ana' Manusia', mohura pai' moparenta hi mali ka'ana Alata'ala to Mobaraka', pai' nihilo wo'o-a mpai' mana'u tumai ngkai suruga hi rala limu'."
24120	40	26	65	Mpo'epe toe we'i, Imam Bohe mpoheu' baju-na ngkai kamoroe-na, pai' na'uli': "Tau toii mpopohibalia woto-na hante Alata'ala! Uma-pi mingki' ria sabi'. Ni'epe moto-mi-koiwo lolita-na mpokedi' Alata'ala.
24121	40	26	66	Beiwa-mi-koiwo pompowile-nie?" Ratompoi' topohura: "Kana rahuku' mate-imile!"
24122	40	26	67	Ngkai ree, ra'uelikui lio-na pai' -i raweba'. Ria wo'o to mpohopo' -i, pai' ra'uli' -ki:
24123	40	26	68	"Ee Magau' Topetolo'! Pe'uli' pe' ba hema to mpohopo' -koe!"
24124	40	26	69	 Nto'u toe, Petrus mohura hi berewe. Nto'u pohura-na toe, tumai hadua tobine to mobago hi tomi Imam Bohe, na'uli' -ki Petrus: "Ba iko wo'o-di doo-na Yesus to Galilea toei-e mai?"
24125	40	26	70	Aga nasapu Petrus hi nyanyoa-ra omea, na'uli': "Uma-kuna ku'incai napa to nu'uli'!"
24126	40	26	71	Ngkai ree hilou wo'o-imi Petrus mokore mohu' hi wobo' wala. Ria wo'o hadua tobine mpohilo-i pai' mpo'uli' -raka tauna to hi ree: "Hi'a toi wo'o-le to dohe Yesus to Nazaret toei-e mai."
24127	40	26	72	Nasapu wo'o-wadi Petrus hante mosumpa, na'uli': "Uma-kuna ku'incai-i tau tetui!"
24128	40	26	73	Uma mahae ngkai ree, tauna to mokore hi ree mpomohui' Petrus, ra'uli' -ki: "Iko mpu'u-di hadua doo-nae! Incana ngkai kotu basa-nu Katogalilea-nu."
24129	40	26	74	Mosumpa tena-i Petrus mpotuna' woto-na, na'uli': "Uma mpu'u-kuwo ku'incai-i!" Nto'u toe turua' -mi manu'.
24130	40	26	75	Nakiwoi-mi Petrus lolita Yesus ngone to mpo'uli' -ki: "Kako'ia-na turua' manu', mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku." Kamalai-nami Petrus hilou hi mali-na, pai' -i geo' ngkai kapeda' nono-na.
24131	40	27	1	 Mepupulo ngkii, hawe'ea imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi mpobotuhi: Yesus kana rapatehi.
24132	40	27	2	Jadi', rahoo' -imi pai' rakeni hilou rabua' hi Gubernur Pilatus.
24133	40	27	3	Ane Yudas, to mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na toei, kana'inca-na karahuku' mate-na mpai' Yesus, soho' -mi nono-na. Kahilou-nami hi imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi, napoponculi' -raka doi pera' to tolu mpulu' mpepa',
24134	40	27	4	pai' na'uli': "Mojeko' -ama! Mpobalu' -a-kuna tauna to uma masala', alaa-na rahuku' mate-i!" Ratompoi' -i: "Napa ki'uli' kai'! Iko moto-kowo pue' sala'!"
24135	40	27	5	Ngkai ree, Yudas mpetadi doi tohe'e hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, pai' -i hilou mengkahunca'.
24136	40	27	6	Imam pangkeni mpotima' doi toe, pai' ra'uli': "Doi toi, doi posula' raa'. Ntuku' atura agama, doi to hewa tohe'e uma ma'ala rapuna' hi rala peti' pompunaa' doi pepue' hi Tomi Alata'ala."
24137	40	27	7	Hibalia-mi pohawa' -ra, doi toe ra'oli-ki tana' to rahanga' Tana' Topobabehi Kura, bona tana' toe rapontanai-raka tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi.
24138	40	27	8	Toe pai' tana' toe rahanga' Tana' Raa' duu' tempo toi.
24139	40	27	9	Hante babehia-ra toe, madupa' -mi napa to nalowa nabi Yeremia owi, hewa toi moni-na: "Ntuku' ada to Israel, oli hadua batua tolu mpulu' doi pera'. Jadi', ra'ala' -mi tolu mpulu' doi pera' toe,
24140	40	27	10	pai' ra'oli-ki tana' topobabehi kura. Tohe'e majadi' ntuku' hawa' Pue' Alata'ala hi aku'."
24141	40	27	11	 Ane Yesus we'i, karakeni-na hi Gubernur Pilatus, mokore-i hi nyanyoa-na. Pilatus mpekune' -i: "Ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' to Yahudi-e?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae mpu'u, hewa to nu'uli' tetu."
24142	40	27	12	Imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi mpodulu mpakilu-i. Aga uma-i winihi.
24143	40	27	13	Toe pai' Pilatus mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ha uma nu'epei hawe'ea to rapakilu-kokoe?"
24144	40	27	14	Uma hamelaa nahono' Yesus, alaa-na napokakonce lia Gubernur.
24145	40	27	15	Butu eo bohe Paskah, Gubernur biasa mpobahaka hadua tauna to ratarungku', ba hema konoa ntodea.
24146	40	27	16	Jadi', mpae toe, ria hadua to ratarungku' to ra'inca lia ntodea. Hanga' -na Yesus Barabas.
24147	40	27	17	Jadi', hi pohura-na Pilatus mpohurai kara-kara Yesus toe, wori' -mi tauna morumpu. Mepekune' Pilatus mpekune' -ra: "Hema to nipokono kubahaka-kokoi mpae tohe'i? Yesus Barabas, ba Yesus to rahanga' Kristus-di?"
24148	40	27	18	Pilatus mpo'uli' hewa toe, apa' na'inca ka'uma-na-hawo masala' -i Yesus; pangkeni to Yahudi mpotonu Yesus hi hi'a apa' kamohingi' -ra-wadi.
24149	40	27	19	Nto'u pohura-na Pilatus hi pohuraa pobotuhia toe, rata suro ngkai tobine-na to mpo'uli' -ki: "Neo' -konae' nuhuku' -i tauna to uma masala' tetui! Apa' ngkai Hi'a alaa-ku mo'ompo' to mekoroi' bengi ngone-e."
24150	40	27	20	Aga imam pangkeni pai' totu'a to Yahudi, kaliliu moto-ra mpo'ukei' ntodea, ra'uli' -raka: "Perapi' -koi hi Gubernur bona Barabas nabahaka, pai' Yesus to nahuku' mate!"
24151	40	27	21	Jadi', mepekune' Gubernur Pilatus hi ntodea, na'uli': "Ngkai hira' rodua tohe'i, hema to nipokono kubahaka-kokoi?" Ratompoi': "Barabas!"
24152	40	27	22	Napekune' tena Pilatus: "Ane wae, kupopai-imi Yesus to rahanga' Kristus?" Metompoi' -ra omea: "Raparika' -i!"
24153	40	27	23	Mepekune' tena-i-pidi Pilatus: "Hiaa' napa sala' -na?" Rapesukui lau-mi mejeu': "Parika' -imi!"
24154	40	27	24	Ka'omea-na nahilo Pilatus uma-pi ria kalaua-na mpololitai-ra, apa' kameroo-rodoa' lau-ramo. Toe pai' na'ala' ue napowano hi nyanyoa ntodea pai' na'uli': "Mowano-a! Bona nihilo, ka'uma-na-kuwo kugalo kanipatehi-na tau toii! Koi' moto-koiwo to mpotangku."
24155	40	27	25	Metompoi' ntodea, ra'uli': "Io', kai' moto-kaiwo pai' hante muli-kai to mpokolo kamate-na."
24156	40	27	26	 Ngkai ree, nabahaka-miraka Barabas, pai' nahubui tantara-na mpoweba' Yesus. Oti toe natonu-miraka bona raparika'.
24157	40	27	27	Oti toe, tantara Gubernur mpokeni Yesus mesua' hi rala tomi Gubernur, pai' -ra mpokio' hawe'ea doo-ra tumai mpotipuhi-i.
24158	40	27	28	Raroncu-ki pohea-na pai' rapasuai' -i baju to mperelei to hewa baju magau'.
24159	40	27	29	Rababehi hameha' songko ngkai walaa to morui to hewa songko magau', pai' rasongkoi-ki. Rawai' wo'o-i lua' hameha' hi pale ka'ana-na, hewa lua' to nakamu magau', pai' -ra mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na, ra'uli': "Wori' tabe, Magau' to Yahudi!"
24160	40	27	30	Ra'uelikui-i pai' ra'ala' lua' to hi pale-na rapao' -ki woo' -na.
24161	40	27	31	Ka'oti-na rapopo'ore' hewa toe, raroncu-mi baju to rabajui-ki we'i pai' ra'uncoi' nculii' -i pohea-na moto-mi. Oti toe rakeni-imi hilou hi mali ngata bona raparika'.
24162	40	27	32	Hi lengko ohea hirua' -ra hante hadua tauna to rahanga' Simon to Kirene. Tantara to Roma mpewuku Simon toe mpopaha'a kaju parika' -na Yesus.
24163	40	27	33	 Uma mahae rata-ramo hi po'ohaa' to rahanga' Golgota, batua-na Bulu' Banga'woo'.
24164	40	27	34	Hi ree, Yesus rapopo'inui anggur to ragalo hante pokuli' to mopai'. Ka'oti-na napemita, oja' -i mpo'inu.
24165	40	27	35	Raparika' -imi, pai' pohea-na rabagi-bagi hante ntene' undi hewa pompenoa' -ra.
24166	40	27	36	Oti toe, mohura-ramo hilau mojaga.
24167	40	27	37	Hi kaju parika' -na hi lolo woo' -na rapataka' hampepa' papan. Hi papan toe te'uki' napa to rapakilu-ki Yesus, hewa toi moni-na: TOI-MI YESUS MAGAU' TO YAHUDI.
24168	40	27	38	Ria wo'o rodua toperampaki raparika' dohe-na, hadua mali ka'ana-na hadua mali ki'ii-na.
24169	40	27	39	Tauna to liu hi ree, ngkololi-ra mpopo'ore' -i,
24170	40	27	40	ra'uli': "Nu'uli' -kona mpogero-ko Tomi Alata'ala pai' nuwangu nculii' rala-na tolu eo! Ane Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-ko, tulungi woto-nu moto! Mana'u-moko ngkai kaju parika' tetu!"
24171	40	27	41	Wae wo'o imam pangkeni, guru agama pai' totu'a to Yahudi mpopo'ore' -i, ra'uli':
24172	40	27	42	"Tau ntani' -na natulungi-ramo, woto-na moto-pi uma nakulei' ntulungi. Hiaa' bo Hi'a he'e Magau' to Israel! Agina mana'u-i ngkai kaju parika' -na toe, pai' lako' tapangala' -i.
24173	40	27	43	Ncarumaka Alata'ala-i, pai' na'uli' Ana' Alata'ala-i. Mai tahilo Alata'ala mpobahaka-i, ane dota-i."
24174	40	27	44	Ntahawe' toperampaki to raparika' dohe-na, meruge' wo'o-ra-rawo mporuge' -i hewa toe.
24175	40	27	45	Tebua' -mi eo, muu-mule' mobengi hobo' hi ngata toe rala-na tolu jaa.
24176	40	27	46	Jaa tolu ncimonou', mekio' -imi Yesus napasimuku mpo'uli': "Alata'ala-ku! Alata'ala-ku! Napa pai' nupalahii-a?" Hi rala basa Yahudi: "Eli! Eli! Lama sabakhtani?"
24177	40	27	47	Ba hangkuja dua to mokore mohu' hi kaju parika' -na mpo'epe pe'au-na toe, ra'uli': "Epe, mpokio' nabi Elia-i!"
24178	40	27	48	Ria hadua to mokeno hilou mpo'ala' hampu'u wunga to hewa lomo', nabangkahi hi rala ue anggur to mo'onco, natu'u hi wuntu hompea pai' napopoju'ui-ki Yesus bona na'inu.
24179	40	27	49	Ria wo'o to mpo'uli': "Popea ulu, tahilo ba tumai mpu'u-i Elia mpotulungi-i."
24180	40	27	50	 Oti toe me'au tena-i Yesus napesukui, pai' modupe' -mi inoha' -na.
24181	40	27	51	Nto'u toe, kain porini-olo' to tetoe hi rala Tomi Alata'ala muu-mule' mobika' ntongo' ngkai lolo-na rata hi une' -na. Ria wo'o linu, pai' watu bohe paheka' -heka'.
24182	40	27	52	Wori' daeo' mobea-mi, pai' wori' tauna to monoa' ingku-ra owi rapotuwu' nculii'.
24183	40	27	53	Ka'oti-na Yesus tuwu' nculii', mehupa' -ra ngkai daeo' -ra, pai' -ra mesua' -hi ngata Yerusalem, ngata to moroli' toe. Wori' tauna mpohilo-ra.
24184	40	27	54	Tadulako tantara hante tantara-tantara doo-na to mpojaga Yesus, me'eka' lia-ramo mpo'epe linu pai' mpohilo hawe'ea to jadi' toe. Ra'uli': "Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-i-tawo'!"
24185	40	27	55	Hi ree, wori' wo'o tobine to menaa ngkawao. Hira' toe tobine to mpotuku' pai' mpotulungi Yesus, ntepu'u ngkai pobago-na hi tana' Galilea.
24186	40	27	56	Hanga' -na to hadua, Maria Magdalena. To hadua wo'o, Maria tina-na Yakobus pai' Yusuf. Pai' hadua wo'o tobine-na Zebedeus.
24187	40	27	57	 Neo' limpa-mi eo, tumai hadua tauna to mo'ua' to ngkai ngata Arimatea, hanga' -na Yusuf. Yusuf toei, topetuku' Yesus wo'o-i-hawo.
24188	40	27	58	Hilou-i hi Pilatus mperapi' woto Yesus. Pilatus mpohubui tantara-na mpowai' -i Yusuf woto-na Yesus.
24189	40	27	59	Na'ala' mpu'u-mi, naputu' hante kain to bula,
24190	40	27	60	pai' napopoturu hi rala daeo'. Daeo' toe, daeo' to bo'u-pidi, daeo' pomporodoa-na Yusuf moto, to ratowi hi panapa bulu' watu. Oti toe, naluli' hameha' watu to bohe na'unca-ki daeo' toe, pai' -i malai-mi.
24191	40	27	61	Aga Maria Magdalena pai' Maria to ntani' -na, mohura-ra hi mai hi mali daeo'.
24192	40	27	62	Kamepulo-na hi Eo Sabat, imam-imam pangkeni pai' to Parisi hilou hangkaa-ngkania hi Pilatus,
24193	40	27	63	ra'uli': "Tua Gubernur, kikiwoi lolita topebagiu toei ngone lou, bula-na tuwu' -pidi na'uli': `Kaliu-na tolu eo, tuwu' nculii' -a.'
24194	40	27	64	Jadi', toe pai' kiperapi' bona Tua mpohubui tantara hilou mpojaga daeo' -na toe ria, radongo lompe' duu' -na rata hi eo katolu-na, bona neo' ria loga ana'guru-na lou mpanako woto-na. Ra'uli' mpai' hi ntodea tuwu' nculii' -i, duu' -na wori' -mi tauna to rabagiu. Helee, meliu lau-mi mpai' kawori' tauna to mpotuku' -i ngkai to mpotuku' -i bula-na tuwu' -pidi."
24195	40	27	65	Na'uli' Pilatus: "Ria moto tantara. Keni-ramo hilou mpodongo daeo' -na hudupakulea' -ni."
24196	40	27	66	Hilou mpu'u-ramo hi daeo'. Rasaa' watu po'unca-na, bona uma ma'ala raderu', pai' rahubui tantara mpodongo daeo' toe, bona neo' ria to mpokabiboi.
24197	40	28	1	 Timpaliu-mi eo pepuea', kako'ia-na mehupa' eo hi eo Mingku, Maria Magdalena pai' Maria to ntani' -na hilou mpokamata daeo'.
24198	40	28	2	Ncorobaa ria linu bohe, apa' hadua mala'eka Pue' mana'u ngkai suruga tumai mpoderu' watu po'unca daeo', pai' -i mohura hi lolo-na.
24199	40	28	3	Lence-na mekiroi' hewa kila', pai' pohea-na bula ngehe.
24200	40	28	4	Tantara to mpodongo hi ree, me'eka' lia-ramo, moridi' -ra, pai' uma-rapa tono mokore, hewa to mate-ramo.
24201	40	28	5	Na'uli' mala'eka mpo'uli' -raka tobine toera: "Neo' -koi me'eka', ku'inca moto mpali' -koi Yesus to mate raparika'.
24202	40	28	6	Uma-ipi-hana ria hi rehe'i. Tuwu' nculii' -imi, hewa to na'uli' -kokoie wengi. Mai hilo karatu'ua-na wengi.
24203	40	28	7	Wae-pi, hilou-mokoi pesahui, uli' -raka ana'guru-na katuwu' -na nculii' -mi. Hilou meri'ulu-i hi tana' Galilea. Hi ria-damo mpai', pai' -i nihilo. Kiwoi napa to ku'uli' -kokoi!"
24204	40	28	8	Rapesahui-mi-rawo tobine toera malai ngkai daeo'. Me'eka' moto-ra, aga goe' lia wo'o-ra. Pokeno-rami hilou apa' doko' raparata to jadi' toe hi ana'guru-na Yesus.
24205	40	28	9	Muu-mule' etu-imi Yesus mpohirua' -raka pai' natabe-ra. Tumai-ramo mpomohui' -i, rakupui witi' -na pai' ranyompa-i.
24206	40	28	10	Na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' me'eka'! Hilou-mokoi, uli' -raka ompi' -ku bona hilou-ra hi Galilea, hi ria mpai' rahilo-a."
24207	40	28	11	 Lingku' -ra tobine toera hilou, ba hangkuja dua tantara to mpodongo daeo' hilou hi rala ngata, pai' -ra mpoparata hi imam pangkeni hawe'ea to jadi' hi daeo' we'i.
24208	40	28	12	Mohawa' -ramo imam pangkeni toera hante totu'a to Yahudi to ntani' -na. Kabotu' lolita-ra, agina mpowai' -ra tantara wori' doi po'ompo wiwi-ra, bona neo' ra'uli' hilau.
24209	40	28	13	Ra'uli' imam pangkeni toera mpo'uli' -raka tantara: "Uli' -koi hewa toi: `Mentongo' bengi ngone, topetuku' Yesus tumai mpanako woto-na bula-kai leta'.'
24210	40	28	14	Ane na'epe Gubernur tohe'e, kai' -damo mpololitai-i bona neo' -koi rapoo-popai."
24211	40	28	15	Radoa-mi-rawo tantara doi toe, pai' ra'uli' hewa to oti ratudui' -raka. Duu' rata hi eo tohe'i, motote oa' lolita toe hi to Yahudi.
24212	40	28	16	 Ana'guru-na Yesus to hampulu' hadua toera hilou hi tana' Galilea, hi bulu' to natudo' ami' -raka Yesus.
24213	40	28	17	Rahilo mpu'u-imi hi ria, pai' ranyompa-i. Aga ria wo'o tauna to morara' -pidi nono-ra.
24214	40	28	18	Yesus mpomohui' -ra pai' na'uli' -raka: "Hawe'ea kuasa hi suruga pai' hi dunia' ratonu-maka.
24215	40	28	19	Jadi', hilou-mokoi hi humalili' dunia', tudui' hawe'ea tauna jadi' topetuku' -ku. Niu' -ra hi rala hanga' Alata'ala to Tuama, to Ana' pai' Inoha' Tomoroli'.
24216	40	28	20	Tudui' -ramo mpotuku' hawe'ea to kuhawai' -kokoi. Kiwoi-koi: kudohei moto-koi duu' -na hi kahudua dunia'."
24217	41	1	1	 Tohe'i-mi Kareba Lompe', tutura katuwu' -na Yesus Kristus, Ana' Alata'ala.
24218	41	1	2	Tutura-na ntepu'u ngkai karata-na Yohanes Topeniu'. Karata-na Yohanes toei, telowa ami' -mi hi rala sura nabi Yesaya. Hante wiwi nabi, Alata'ala mpo'uli' -ki Ana' -na hewa toi: Hi'a toi-mi suro-ku, kuhubui-i meri'ulu ngkai Iko, bona mporodo ohea-nu."
24219	41	1	3	"Mekio' -i hi papada to wao', na'uli': `Neo' rata-imi Pue'! Porodo ami' -miki ohea-na. Nipakalempe ami' -mi ohea to natara mpai'.'"
24220	41	1	4	Hewa to ra'uki' toe, mehupa' mpu'u-imi Yohanes Topeniu' hi papada to wao'. Mpoparata-i Lolita Alata'ala hi ntodea, na'uli': "Medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, pai' kana tumai-koi kuniu' bona Alata'ala mpo'ampungi jeko' -ni."
24221	41	1	5	Wori' tauna to hilou hi papada to wao' doko' mpo'epe lolita-na Yohanes. Ria-ra ngkai ngata Yerusalem pai' ngkai hawe'ea ngata hi tana' Yudea. Hilou-ra mpangaku' jeko' -ra, pai' naniu' -ra hi ue Yordan, tanda kamedea-ra ngkai jeko' -ra.
24222	41	1	6	Pohea-na Yohanes rababehi ngkai wulu porewua to rahanga' unta. Salepe' -na ngkai kuliba. Koni' -na lari pai' ue wani.
24223	41	1	7	Mpopalele-i kareba toi: "Ngkabokoa' ngkai aku', tumai mpai' to meliu kuasa-na ngkai aku'. Bangku' mowilingkudu mpobongka koloro sapatu' -na, uma-a-kuwo natao.
24224	41	1	8	Aku' mponiu' -koi hante ue tanda kamedea-ni ngkai jeko' -ni. Aga Hi'a mpai' mponiu' -koi hante Inoha' Tomoroli'."
24225	41	1	9	 Rala-na ha'eo, Yesus me'ongko' ngkai ngata Nazaret hi tana' Galilea, tumai mpopeniu' hi Yohanes. Yohanes mponiu' -i hi ue Yordan.
24226	41	1	10	Wae ka'oti-na raniu', mencore-imi ngkai ue, pai' mpohilo-imi langi' mobea pai' Inoha' Tomoroli' mana'u tumai molence mpo-danci mangkebodo hompo hi Hi'a.
24227	41	1	11	Alata'ala mololita ngkai langi' mpo'uli' -ki: "Iko toi-mi Ana' -ku to kupe'ahi'. Iko-mi to mpakagoe' nono-ku."
24228	41	1	12	Oti toe, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpakeni Yesus lou hi papada to wao'.
24229	41	1	13	Opo' mpulu' eo-i hi ria. Bula-na hi papada toe, Magau' Anudaa' mposori-i. Binata to me'ila dohe-na, pai' mala'eka mpomawai-i.
24230	41	1	14	 Ko'ia mahae ngkai ree, Yohanes Topeniu' rahoko' pai' -i ratarungku'. Nto'u toe, hilou-imi Yesus hi tana' Galilea, pai' -i mpopalele Kareba Lompe' to ngkai Alata'ala,
