24231	41	1	15	na'uli': "Neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'! Medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, pangala' -mi Kareba Lompe'."
24232	41	1	16	Bula-na momako' hi wiwi' rano Galilea, mpohilo-i rodua tauna. Hanga' -ra: Simon hante Andreas ompi' -na. Nto'u toe, bula-ra mebau' hi rano mojala', apa' toe-mi-rawo bago-ra.
24233	41	1	17	Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Mai-mokoi ntuku' -a! Uma-pokoi mebau' mpali' uru. Ngkai wae lau, kuwai' -koi pobago mpotudui' tauna mepangala' hi Aku'."
24234	41	1	18	Karapalahii-nami jala' -ra, pai' ntepu'u eo toe mpotuku' Yesus-ramo.
24235	41	1	19	Napaliliu-mi Yesus momako', ko'ia molaa ngkai ree mpohilo wo'o-imi rodua to ntali ompi': Yakobus pai' Yohanes, ana' -na Zebedeus. Hira' toe, bula-ra mpokolompehii jala' -ra hi rala sakaya.
24236	41	1	20	Nakio' -ramo mpotuku' -i. Jadi', rapalahii-mi tuama-ra hi rala sakaya hante tauna to dohe-ra to ngkoni' gaji', pai' mpotuku' Yesus-ramo.
24237	41	1	21	Ngkai ree, Yesus hante topetuku' -na hilou hi ngata Kapernaum. Hi eo pepuea' to Yahudi, mesua' -imi hi rala tomi posampayaa pai' natepu'u-mi metudui'.
24238	41	1	22	Konce-ramo tauna to mpo'epe tudui' -na. Apa' uma-i metudui' hewa guru-guru agama. Petudui' -na, hewa tauna to mokuasa mpu'u.
24239	41	1	23	 Nto'u toe, ria hadua tauna to nahawi' anudaa', mesua' wo'o-i-hawo hi tomi posampayaa toe, pai' -i mejeu':
24240	41	1	24	"Ee Yesus to Nazaret! Doko' nupopai-dakaie? Ba doko' nuropuhi-dakaie? Ku'inca moto-kole, ka'Iko-na Suro to moroli' ngkai Alata'ala-e."
24241	41	1	25	Yesus mpo'uli' -ki anudaa' toei: "Ngkaba'i-ko! Palai-ko ngkai tauna tetui!"
24242	41	1	26	Tauna toei moridi' sabana anudaa', pai' -i me'au, pai' malai-mi anudaa' to mpohawi' -i.
24243	41	1	27	Konce omea-ramo tauna to mpohilo, alaa-na momepololitai-ramo ra'uli': "Uma mowo-e'! Toi-e tudui' to bo'u, ria mpu'u baraka' -na! Mpopalai-i anudaa', bo ratuku' mpu'u-diki-hana hawa' -nae!"
24244	41	1	28	Ngkai ree, kamolele-nami kareba to mpotompo'wiwi Yesus hobo' hi tana' Galilea.
24245	41	1	29	 Kanculii' -ra Yesus hante ana'guru-na ngkai tomi posampayaa toe, hilou-ramo hi tomi-ra Simon pai' Andreas. Yakobus pai' Yohanes hilou wo'o dohe-ra.
24246	41	1	30	Hi ria, piniana-na Simon tobine ntora turu apa' ngkelengi' -i. Rapesahui mpo'uli' -ki Yesus kapeda' -na.
24247	41	1	31	Ngkai ree, hilou-imi Yesus hi poturua-na, nakamu pale-na pai' napopemata-i. Ncaliu mo'uri' -imi, pai' -i mpolayani-ra.
24248	41	1	32	Ncimonou' toe, limpa-mi eo, wori' tauna tumai hi Yesus mpokeni hawe'ea to peda' ba to nahawi' seta.
24249	41	1	33	Wori' pue' ngata tumai morumpu hi berewe tomi Simon.
24250	41	1	34	Wori' tauna to napaka'uri' ngkai haki' -ra to wori' nyala. Wori' wo'o seta to mpesuai' tauna napopalai. Aga seta toera, uma-ra napiliu mololita, apa' ra'inca moto Kahi'a-na Ana' Alata'ala.
24251	41	1	35	Kamepulo-na parabaja-pidi, memata-imi Yesus pai' -i malai ngkai ngata hilou hi kawaoa' -na, lou mosampaya.
24252	41	1	36	Simon hante doo-na hilou mpali' -i. Kararua' -na, ra'uli' -ki:
24253	41	1	37	"Wori' tauna mpali' -ko Guru."
24254	41	1	38	Na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-tamo hi ngata ntani' -na to mohu' bona mpokeni Lolita Alata'ala hi ria wo'o-a. Apa' toe-mi patuju-ku tumai hi dunia'."
24255	41	1	39	Ngkai ree, kahilou-nami Yesus hante ana'guru-na mpokeni Lolita Alata'ala hi hawe'ea ngata hi tana' Galilea. Metudui' -i hi rala tomi-tomi posampayaa, pai' -i mpopalai seta to mpesuai' tauna.
24256	41	1	40	 Ria hadua tauna to mohaki' poko' rata hi Yesus. Powingkotu' -nami mpopetulungi, na'uli': "Ane ma'ala, paka'uri' -a-kuwo!"
24257	41	1	41	Metumu' -mi ahi' -na Yesus mpohilo-i. Toe pai' najama-i pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ma'ala moto, kupaka'uri' -moko!"
24258	41	1	42	Hampinisi mata, moronto-mi haki' -na, mo'uri' -imi.
24259	41	1	43	Oti toe, Yesus mpohubui-i hilou, na'uli' -ki: "Kutagi mpu'u-ko,
24260	41	1	44	neo' nulolita hi hema-hema napa to jadi' tohe'i-e. Hilou-moko ulu mpopehuwu woto-nu hi imam, bona nahilo kamo'uri' -numi, pai' keni pepue' -nu ntuku' parenta to te'uki' hi rala Atura Musa, bona monoa' hi hawe'ea tauna kamo'uri' -nu mpu'u-mi."
24261	41	1	45	Ntaa' we'i, kahilou-na tauna toei, ntora nalolita lau-mi hiapa-apa kanapaka'uri' -na Yesus. Alaa-na, Yesus uma-ipi bisa mesua' hi rala ngata apa' wori' rahi tauna mpotipuhi-i. Mo'oha' hi mali ngata-i-damo hi kawaoa' -na. Aga nau' wae, uma oa' ria kaputua-na tauna tumai ngkai wori' ngata doko' mpohirua' -ki.
24262	41	2	1	 Ba hangkuja kahae-na ngkai toe, Yesus nculii' hilou hi ngata Kapernaum. Motolele-mi karia-na Yesus hi rala tomi,
24263	41	2	2	toe pai' wori' tauna himuhu doko' mpohilo-i. Kahimuhu-ra toe, alaa-na bihi' -mi hi rala tomi, rata-rata hi wobo' bihi' tauna. Naparata-raka Lolita Alata'ala.
24264	41	2	3	Bula-na mololita tohe'e, tumai opo' tauna mpokowa' doo-ra to pungku.
24265	41	2	4	Uma ria ohea-ra mpomohui' Yesus apa' bihi' rahi tauna. Toe pai' ngkahe' tuka' -ramo hilou hi lolo tomi, ratangka' ata' to hintoto Yesus, pai' ra'ulu doo-ra ntali ali' -na hilou hi rala tomi.
24266	41	2	5	Nahilo Yesus kabohe pepangala' -ra toe, na'uli' -mi hi topungku toei: "Ana' -ku, te'ampungi-mi jeko' -nu."
24267	41	2	6	Ria wo'o-ra-rawo ba hangkuja dua guru agama Yahudi to mohura hi rala tomi toe. Kedi' nono-ra mpo'epe lolita-na Yesus toe, ra'uli' hi rala nono-ra:
24268	41	2	7	"Daho' rahi-i-hana tauna toei mololita hewa tetu! Ha na'uli' -hana hibalia tuwu' -na hante tuwu' -na Alata'ala? Uma ria ntani' -na to ma'ala mpo'ampungi jeko', hadua Alata'ala-wadi."
24269	41	2	8	Ntaa' na'inca moto-di Yesus napa to hi pekiri-rae. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa-di pai' hewa tetu pekiri-nie?
24270	41	2	9	
24271	41	2	10	Aku' Ana' Manusia', ria mpu'u kuasa-ku hi dunia' mpo'ampungi jeko'. Tapi' ane ku'uli' -ki topungku toei: `Te'ampungi-mi jeko' -nu,' uma ni'incai ba te'ampungi mpu'u-di jeko' -na ba uma-di. Aga ane ku'uli': `Memata-moko, lulu-mi ali' -nu pai' momako' -moko,' nihilo mpai' kadupa' -na ba ka'uma-na. Jadi', kupopohiloi-koi karia-na kuasa-ku mpo'ampungi jeko'." Ngkai ree, kamewili' -nami hi topungku toei,
24272	41	2	11	na'uli' -ki: "Memata-moko, lulu-mi ali' -nu, pai' -ko nculii' -mi!"
24273	41	2	12	Pemata-na mpu'u-mi topungku toei, nalulu ali' -na, pai' -i momako' hilou rasabii' tauna to wori'. Karahilo-na tauna to wori' napa to jadi' toe, konce omea-ramo, pai' -ra mpo'une' Alata'ala, ra'uli': "Ko'ia ria tahiloi hewa to jadi' tohe'i!"
24274	41	2	13	 Oti toe, hilou wo'o-imi Yesus hi wiwi' rano. Wori' lia tauna morumpu, pai' natudui' -ra.
24275	41	2	14	Bula-na momako', mpohilo-i hadua topesingara' paja' to rahanga' Lewi ana' -na Alfeus, bula-na mohura hi kantoro' -na. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Tuku' -ama!" Kamokore-nami Lewi kaliliu mpotuku' -i.
24276	41	2	15	Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na ngkoni' hi tomi Lewi, pai' wori' wo'o-ra topesingara' paja' pai' tau ntani' -na to ra'uli' ntodea dada'a kehi-ra tumai ngkoni' dohe-ra, apa' wori' -ra to mpotuku' Yesus.
24277	41	2	16	Ria wo'o hi ree ba hangkuja dua guru agama to mpotuku' tudui' Parisi. Kampohilo-ra Yesus ngkoni' dohe tauna to dada'a kehi-ra toe, ra'uli' -mi mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Napa pai' guru-ni ngkoni' hangkaa-ngkania hante topesingara' paja' pai' tauna topojeko' -e!"
24278	41	2	17	Yesus mpo'epe lolita-ra toe, toe pai' napololitai-ra hante lolita rapa' toi, na'uli': "Tauna to uma peda', uma mingki' rapokulii'. Tauna to peda' -wadi-hawo to paraluu rapokulii'. Uma-a tumai mpokio' tauna to monoa' ingku-ra. Katumai-ku toi-le, mpokio' topojeko' -a-kuna bona medea-ra ngkai jeko' -ra."
24279	41	2	18	 Rala-na hangkani, topetuku' Yohanes Topeniu' pai' to Parisi bula-ra mopuasa'. Ria-mi tauna rata hi Yesus mpekune' -i: "Topetuku' -na Yohanes Topeniu' mopuasa', wae wo'o topetuku' to Parisi, mopuasa' wo'o-ra. Hiaa' topetuku' -nu Iko, napa pai' uma-ra mopuasa'?"
24280	41	2	19	Yesus mpotompoi' -ra hante lolita rapa' toi, na'uli' -raka: "Ane tauna hi posusaa' poncamokoa, ha mopuasa' -ra-rana bula-ra mpo'ema' topemua'? Uma-hawo. Bula-na ria-pidi topemua' dohe-ra, uma-ra mopuasa'.
24281	41	2	20	Tapi' rata mpai' tempo-na, topemua' ra'ala' ngkai laintongo' -ra. Nto'u toe-damo, pai' lako' mopuasa' -rada."
24282	41	2	21	Oti toe Yesus mpo'uli' lolita rapa' to ronyala-pi, na'uli': "Uma ria haduaa tauna to mpotelepei baju to hae hante pontaia' to bo'u. Apa' pontaia' to bo'u mongkuru' mpai', duu' -na mpoheu' baju to hae toe, alaa-na kaboo-bohea lau-mi heu' -na.
24283	41	2	22	Wae wo'o uma ria tauna to mpotua anggur to bo'u hi rala pontu'ua to hae. Apa' ane dede' -ipi mpai', mopengka lau-mi pontu'ua to hae toe, alaa-na mobowo lau-mi anggur, pai' mpadaa' -mi pontu'ua-na. Jadi', anggur to bo'u kana ra'ihii' hi pontu'ua to bo'u wo'o-hawo."
24284	41	2	23	Hangkani hi eo pepuea', Yesus pai' ana'guru-na ntara rala bonea. Bula-ra mpotara bonea toe, ana'guru-na mpotepo' wua' gandum pai' raru'a.
24285	41	2	24	To Parisi to hi ree mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Napa-di-rana pai' ana'guru-nu mpotiboki atura agama-tae? Mobago-ra-rana hi eo pepuea'."
24286	41	2	25	
24287	41	2	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ha uma ria nibasa napa to nababehi Magau' Daud owi nto'u Abyatar jadi' Imam Bohe-e? Nto'u-na Daud hante ema' -na mo'oro' pai' uma ria anu rakoni', mesua' -imi hi rala tomi pepuea', pai' -i mpokoni' roti to rapopepue' hi Alata'ala, pai' nabagi wo'o-raka doo-na. Ntuku' ada agama-ta, imam-wadi-hana to ma'ala mpokoni' roti toe. Aga nau' wae, gau' -na Daud toe uma-hawo naposala'."
24288	41	2	27	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Alata'ala mpobabehi eo pepuea' bona mpotulungi manusia'. Bela manusia' to rababehi bona napari'une' ada eo pepuea'.
24289	41	2	28	Jadi', Aku' Ana' Manusia', ria kuasa-ku mpo'uli' napa to ma'ala rababehi hi eo pepuea'."
24290	41	3	1	 Rala-na hangkani, mesua' wo'o-imi Yesus hi rala tomi posampayaa. Hi ree, ria hadua tauna to mate pale-na hamali.
24291	41	3	2	Ria wo'o-ra hi ree to Parisi to tungkai' doko' mpali' kasalaa' Yesus meka' mobago-i hi eo pepuea', apa' doko' rapakilu-i. Jadi', ralelemata-i meka' ba mepaka'uri' mpu'u-i hi eo pepuea'.
24292	41	3	3	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki tauna to mate pale-na hamali: "Mai-ko mokore hi laintongo' rehe'i."
24293	41	3	4	Oti toe, na'uli' -raka to Parisi: "Ntuku' ada agama-ta, to'uma to ma'ala tababehi hi eo pepuea': mpobabehi to lompe' -di ba to dada'a? Mpotulungi doo ba mpatehi doo?" Tapi' to Parisi toera, oja' -ra mpotompoi' -i, ngkaba'i-ra-wadi.
24294	41	3	5	Mogolili Yesus mponaa-ra. Moroe-i pai' peda' nono-na apa' motu'a rahi nono-ra. Toe pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki tauna to mate pale-na hamali toei: "Tanoa pale-nu!" Kanatanoa-nami pale-na, mo'uri' -imi.
24295	41	3	6	Palai-ra to Parisi ngkai tomi posampayaa toe, pai' -ra morumpu hante tauna to tono' hi Magau' Herodes. Mpali' akala-ra bona Yesus rapatehi.
24296	41	3	7	Yesus hante ana'guru-na malai ngkai ree hilou hi wiwi' rano. Wori' to Galilea ntuku' -i. Wori' wo'o to tumai ngkai tana' Yudea,
24297	41	3	8	ngkai Yerusalem, ngkai tana' Idumea, ngkai dipo ue Yordan, ria wo'o ngkai ngata Tirus pai' Sidon. Wori' rahi tauna to tumai hi Yesus apa' ra'epe hawe'ea to nababehi.
24298	41	3	9	
24299	41	3	10	Wori' tauna to mohaki' napaka'uri', alaa-na mome'upi' -ra tauna lou mpomohui' -i doko' mpoganga-i. Ngkai kawori' tauna, toe pai' nahubui ana'guru-na mporodo sakaya nahawi', nee-neo' mpai' ra'upi' -i ntodea.
24300	41	3	11	Rata wo'o-ra tauna to napesuai' anudaa'. Kampohilo-ra Yesus kaliliu mowingkotu' -ra hi nyanyoa-na, pai' -ra mejeu', ra'uli': "Iko-mi Ana' Alata'ala!"
24301	41	3	12	Aga natagi mpu'u-ra, bona neo' ra'uli' kahema-nai.
24302	41	3	13	 Oti toe, Yesus manake' hilou hi bulu' -na, pai' -i mpokio' tauna hema-hema to napokono. Rata mpu'u-ramo,
24303	41	3	14	pai' napelihi hampulu' rodua-ra, na'uli' -raka: "Kupelihi-koi bona nipodohe-a, pai' bona kusuro-koi mpopalele Kareba Lompe'.
24304	41	3	15	Pai' kuwai' -koi kuasa mpopalai seta."
24305	41	3	16	
24306	41	3	17	
24307	41	3	18	
24308	41	3	19	Tohe'i-mi hanga' -ra to hampulu' rodua toera: Simon (Yesus mpohanga' -i Petrus); oti toe, Yakobus ana' Zebedeus; pai' Yohanes ompi' -na Yakobus (Yesus mpohanga' -ra Boanerges-- batua-na: tauna to hewa berese); oti toe, Andreas; Filipus; Bartolomeus; Matius; Tomas; Yakobus ana' Alfeus; Tadeus; Simon to Zelot; pai' Yudas Iskariot (hi'a mpai' to mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na).
24309	41	3	20	Oti toe, Yesus nculii' hilou hi tomi. Aga wori' wo'o-wadi tauna to tumai mpotipuhi-i, alaa-na Yesus pai' ana'guru-na uma-ra tepongkoni'.
24310	41	3	21	Toe pai' ria tauna to mpo'uli': "Wuli-imile!" Kara'epe-na ompi' -na Yesus tohe'e, hilou-ramo ke mpo'ala' -i.
24311	41	3	22	 Ria wo'o hi ree guru agama Yahudi to lako' rata ngkai Yerusalem. Ra'uli' guru agama toera: "Ah, napesuai' Beelzebul-i-hanale, magau' hawe'ea seta. Magau' seta toe-mile to mpowai' -i kuasa mpopalai seta-e."
24312	41	3	23	Toe pai' Yesus mpokio' -ra bona mpomohui' -i, pai' napololitai-ra hante ba hangkuja nyala lolita rapa', na'uli': "Ha beiwa-hawo seta mpopalai hingka seta-na?
24313	41	3	24	Ane rapa' -na ria hadua magau', pai' ntodea hi rala kamagaua' -na ntora mosisala, uma mpai' ntaha mahae kamagaua' -na toe.
24314	41	3	25	Ane tau hantina ntora motuda', bate pagaa' -gaa' mpai' posantinaa-ra.
24315	41	3	26	Wae wo'o hi kamagaua' seta. Ane hi rala kamagaua' seta ria posisalaa pai' potudaa', kamagaua' -na toe uma ntaha mahae, kahudua-nami mpai' toe.
24316	41	3	27	"Seta ma'ala rarapai' -ki tauna to parimuku. Ane mesua' -ta hi rala tomi tauna to parimuku doko' mpo'ala' ihi' tomi-na, kana tahoo' ncala' -i, pai' lako' ma'ala tapatau' rewa-na. Wae wo'o, ane Aku' mpopalai seta, batua-na, meliu kuasa-ku ngkai seta.
24317	41	3	28	"Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Hawe'ea jeko' manusia' pai' lolita pesapuaka-ra ma'ala ra'ampungi.
24318	41	3	29	Aga hema to mposapuaka Inoha' Tomoroli', uma ria ampungia-ra duu' kahae-hae-na. Pesapuaka-ra toe raposala' duu' kahae-hae-na."
24319	41	3	30	Pai' hewa toe lolita-na Yesus, apa' ria to mpo'uli' kanahawi' -na anudaa' -i, uma rapangalai' kangkai Inoha' Tomoroli' kuasa-na.
24320	41	3	31	 Ngkai ree, rata-mi tina-na pai' ompi' -na Yesus mokore hi mali tomi. Mpohubui-ra tauna mpokio' -i tumai hi mali-na bona rapololitai.
24321	41	3	32	Nto'u toe, wori' tauna mpotololiki Yesus. Ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, tina-nu pai' ompi' -nu, oe-ra ria hi mali-na mpali' -ko."
24322	41	3	33	
24323	41	3	34	Yesus mponaa tauna to mpotololiki-i, pai' na'uli': "Ane tina-ku pai' ompi' -kule, hira' toe-ramo lau.
24324	41	3	35	Apa' hema-hema to mpobabehi konoa Alata'ala, hira' -mi ompi' -ku pai' hira' -mi tina-ku."
24325	41	4	1	 Rala-na hangkani, metudui' wo'o-imi Yesus hi wiwi' rano. Wori' lia tauna morumpu mpotololiki-i. Ngkai kawori' tauna, toe-mi pai' hilou-i mohawi' sakaya to hi lolo ue, mohura-i hi rala-na pai' tauna to wori' mokore hi talinti.
24326	41	4	2	Wori' nyala to natudui' -raka hante lolita rapa'. Hewa tohe'i na'uli' -raka:
24327	41	4	3	"Pe'epei! Ria hadua topohawu' hilou mohawu'.
24328	41	4	4	Rala mpohawu' -na toe, ria hawua' -na to monawu' hi mata ohea. Rata danci mpotilo' hawua' toe duu' -na oti.
24329	41	4	5	Ria wo'o to monawu' hi tana' to watua, hangkedi' -wadi tana' -na. Hinawu' -na toe sohi' lia tuwu', apa' moreni' tana' -na.
24330	41	4	6	Kamorani' -na eo, molaju-imi duu' -na bangi, apa' uma monala rali' -na.
24331	41	4	7	Ria wo'o to monawu' hi laintongo' rui. Tuwu' rui mpo'upi' hinawu' toe, alaa-na uma-i mowua', mate lau-idi.
24332	41	4	8	Ria wo'o hawua' to monawu' hi tana' to morudu'. Tuwu' lompe' hawua' toe kakaa-kamaa, alaa-na mowua'. Ria to nte tolu mpulu' ngkani ngkai hinawu' -na, ria to ono mpulu', ria wo'o to ha'atu ngkani ngkai hinawu' -na."
24333	41	4	9	Ka'oti-na mpololita lolita rapa' toe, na'uli' -miraka: "Hema-koi to tilingaa, pe'epei lompe'!"
24334	41	4	10	Oti toe, nto'u-na Yesus hadudua-na, ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua pai' topetuku' -na to ntani' -na tumai mpekune' -i: "Napa-die batua-na lolita rapa' toe-e we'i?"
24335	41	4	11	Na'uli' Yesus: "Owi, Alata'ala ko'ia mpopo'incai manusia' beiwa-i mpai' jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Aga hewa toe lau, napopo'incai-mokoi tudui' toe. Tapi' ane tauna to bela topetuku' -ku, kutudui' -ra hante lolita rapa',
24336	41	4	12	bona madupa' -mi lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': `Pe'epe moto-ra, aga uma oa' ra'incai batua-na. Pehilo moto-ra, aga hewa to uma oa' monoto rahiloi. Jadi', uma oa' -ra nculii' hi Alata'ala, pai' jeko' -ra uma te'ampungi.'"
24337	41	4	13	Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane uma ni'incai batua lolita rapa' toe we'i, beiwa kani'inca-na batua lolita rapa' to ntani' -na?
24338	41	4	14	Topohawu', hira' -mi tauna to mpoparata Lolita Alata'ala.
24339	41	4	15	Ria tauna to ma'ala rarapai' -ki hawua' to monawu' hi mata ohea. Ra'epe moto Lolita Alata'ala, aga Magau' Anudaa' mpohilingai' nono-ra, alaa-na uma-pi rapoinono lolita toe.
24340	41	4	16	"Ria wo'o tauna to ma'ala rarapai' -ki hawua' to monawu' hi tana' to watua. Kara'epe-na Lolita Alata'ala, ncaliu goe' nono-ra.
24341	41	4	17	Aga uma morali' mpu'u Lolita Alata'ala hi rala nono-ra, toe pai' uma-ra ntaha mahae. Ane rabalinai' -ra ba rapakasusa' sabana pepangala' -ra hi Lolita Alata'ala, kamo'ungkere' -rami.
24342	41	4	18	"Ria wo'o tauna to rarapai' -ki hawua' to monawu' hi olo' rui. Ra'epe moto Lolita Alata'ala,
24343	41	4	19	aga sese' -ra ntora mpenonoi katuwu' -ra hi rala dunia' toi, doko' -ra mporumpu rewa dunia' -wadi, pai' wori' nyala kahinaa hi rala nono-ra. Hawe'ea toe mposesei' -ra, alaa-na uma ria po'ohaa' Lolita Alata'ala hi rala nono-ra, pai' uma ria kalaua-na lolita toe hi katuwu' -ra.
24344	41	4	20	"Ria wo'o tauna to rarapai' -ki hawua' to monawu' hi tana' to morudu'. Mpo'epe-ra Lolita Alata'ala, kaliliu ratarima. Hi tauna toe-ramo Lolita Alata'ala mowua' mpu'u. Ria to mowua' hangkedi', ria to mowua' wori', ria to mowua' wori' lia."
24345	41	4	21	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Ha ria-ta to mpokeni palita hi rala tomi pai' tapopoi' hante kura ba tatu'u hi une' poturua? Tantu uma-hawo ria. Palita bate ratu'u hi pontu'ua-na bona nahinii hobo'.
24346	41	4	22	Apa' hawe'ea to tewuni kana rapopehuwu, pai' hawe'ea to kalerua kana jadi' kahiloa.
24347	41	4	23	Hema-koi to tilingaa, pe'epei lompe'!"
24348	41	4	24	Na'uli' tena Yesus: "Penotohi mpu'u-koi napa to ni'epe tohe'i-e. Apa' kawoo-woria' Lolita Alata'ala to nibagi-ki doo, kawoo-woria' wo'o to nanotohi-kokoi Alata'ala-- ba melabi tena-pi ngkai ree.
24349	41	4	25	Tauna to mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala, ranotohi nono-ra bona kawoo-woria' to ra'inca. Aga tauna to uma dota mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala, nau' ria hangkedi' to ra'inca, ra'alai' lau-ra."
24350	41	4	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia', kajadi' -na hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i: Hadua tauna mpotujai' bonea-na.
24351	41	4	27	Hi bengi-na turu-i, hi eo-na memata-i. Kahae-na toe, tinuja' -na tuwu' kaboo-bohea. Aga beiwa tinuja' -na tuwu' pai' jadi' bohe, uma-hawo na'incai.
24352	41	4	28	Ngkai tana' moto-hawo pehupaa' wua' -na. Lomo' -na rau-na pai' kaho-na to mehupa', ngkai ree huwu-mi, duu' -na mo'ihi.
24353	41	4	29	Kataha' -na pae, hilou-imi pue' -na ngkeni are' nasoe-ki, apa' tempo-nami mepae."
24354	41	4	30	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia', beiwa kajadi' -na? Kajadi' -nale hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i:
24355	41	4	31	Ria tauna to mpohawu' unto' hawi hi tana'.
24356	41	4	32	Unto' toe monete' lia, meliu kakedi' -na ngkai hawe'ea unto' to ria hi dunia'. Aga ane rahawu' -i-damo pai' -i tuwu', meliu kabohe-na ngkai ngkojo to ntani' -na. Ra'a-na mopanga molanga, duu' -na rapopetai danci pai' rapengkamoui."
24357	41	4	33	Wae-mi Yesus mpoparata Lolita Alata'ala hi ntodea hante wori' nyala lolita rapa', ntuku' pakulea' -ra mpopaha.
24358	41	4	34	Uma ria to natudui' -raka ane uma hante lolita rapa'. Aga ane Hi'a-damo pai' ana'guru-na, nanotohi-miraka omea.
24359	41	4	35	 Ncimonou' toe wo'o, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Hilou-tamo hi dipo rano."
24360	41	4	36	Jadi', apa' hi rala sakaya ami' -imi Yesus, pe'ongko' -rami mpalahii ntodea to hi wiwi' rano. Ria wo'o sakaya ntani' -na hi ree to mpotuku' -ra.
24361	41	4	37	Ko'ia mahae, rata-mi ngolu' bohe. Ntepu'u-mi balumpa mporumpa' sakaya-ra, alaa-na neo' ponu' -mi sakaya-ra hante ue.
24362	41	4	38	Yesus leta' moto-i molunai hi wuntu sakaya. Kahilou-rami ana'guru-na mpolike-i, ra'uli' -ki: "Guru! Napa-di pai' nupelele' moto-ta neo' matala-tamoe?"
24363	41	4	39	Pemata-nami Yesus pai' -i mpotagi ngolu' pai' balumpa, na'uli': "Mento'o-ko ngolu'! Rodo-moko balumpa!" Mento'o mpu'u-mi-hawo ngolu', pai' muu-mule' molino nculii' -mi rano.
24364	41	4	40	Na'uli' -mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' me'eka' rahi-koie? Ha uma ria pepangala' -nie?"
24365	41	4	41	Me'eka' lia-ramo ana'guru-na, pai' momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Hema mpu'u-idi-hana tau toii-e? Ngolu' pai' rano molino-di-hana ntuku' hawa' -na!"
24366	41	5	1	 Ngkai ree, rata-ramo hi dipo rano, hi tana' Gerasa.
24367	41	5	2	
24368	41	5	3	
24369	41	5	4	
24370	41	5	5	Hi tana' Gerasa toe, ria hadua tauna to nahawi' anudaa'. Hi daeo' -wadi po'ohaa' -na. Uma-i tono rahoo' nau' hante rante, apa' uma mowo karoho-na. Pontu-na witi' -na pai' pale-na rahoo', aga koloro pai' rante ma'ala oa' nadupe'. Ngkai kamoroho-na toe, pai' uma ria haduaa to daho' mpodongo-i. Hi eo-na hi bengi-na ntora dao' -dao' -na hi daeo' pai' hi bulu' -na, pai' kakakio' -kio', pai' -i mposerohi woto-na hante watu. Jadi', wae pana'u-na Yesus ngkai rala sakaya, mehupa' -mi tauna to kahawia' toei ngkai daeo'.
24371	41	5	6	Kampohilo-na Yesus ngkai molaa, pokeno-nami hilou mperapai-i, pai' -i mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na mponyompa-i.
24372	41	5	7	
24373	41	5	8	Yesus mpohubui anudaa' malai, na'uli': "Malai-moko ngkai tauna tetui!" Mejeu' tau toei na'uli': "Ee Yesus Ana' Alata'ala to hi suruga! Napa-di-kona pai' tumai-koe? Hante hanga' Alata'ala merapi' -a bona neo' -a-kuwo nusesa'."
24374	41	5	9	Yesus mpekune' -i: "Hema hanga' -nu?" Na'uli': "Hanga' -ku Legion, apa' wori' -kai hampo'emaa' to mesua' hi tau toii." (Hanga' Legion tohe'e, batua-na: moncobu.)
24375	41	5	10	Rajojo seta toera merapi' hi Yesus bona neo' -ra napopalai ngkai ngata toe.
24376	41	5	11	Uma molaa ngkai ree, ria wori' wawu mojume hi panapa bulu'.
24377	41	5	12	Anudaa' toera merapi' hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Hubui-kai mesua' hi wawu toera mai."
24378	41	5	13	Napiliu moto-ra Yesus. Ngkai ree, malai mpu'u-ramo anudaa' toera kaliliu mesua' hi wawu. Pesua' -ra hi wawu toe, mparampuli-ramo-rawo wawu hilou mengkajuala' hi rano, mate bonga-ramo hi rala ue-- kawori' -ra ria nte roncobu ma'a.
24379	41	5	14	Karahilo-na tauna to mpodoo wawu toera napa to jadi', pokeno-rami hilou hi rala ngata pai' hi bonea to mohu' mpoparata kajadia' toe. Toe pai' tumai-ramo pue' ngata doko' mpohilo napa to jadi'.
24380	41	5	15	Karata-ra hi Yesus, rahilo-rawo tauna to kahawia' toei, mohura rodo-imi, moheai-i, pai' monoto-mi nono-na. Mpohilo toe, me'eka' -ramo.
24381	41	5	16	Tauna to mpohilo kajadia' toe mpotutura napa to jadi' hi tauna to kahawia', pai' napa to jadi' hi wawu-ra.
24382	41	5	17	Ngkai ree, pue' ngata merapi' hi Yesus bona malai-i ngkai ngata-ra. Jadi', mohawi' nculii' -imi hi rala sakaya.
24383	41	5	18	Bula-na Yesus mohawi' toe, tauna to kahawia' -e ngone merapi' bona ma'ala-i hilou dohe-na.
24384	41	5	19	Tapi' uma-i napiliu, na'uli' -ki: "Nculii' -moko hilou hi tomi-nu, uli' -raka hingka ngata-nu napa to nababehi Pue' Ala hi iko, pai' ahi' -na hi iko."
24385	41	5	20	Hilou-imi-hawo hi tana' Dekapolis (batua-na: Hampulu' Ngata), mpopalele napa to nababehi Yesus hi woto-na. Konce hawe'ea tauna to mpo'epe.
24386	41	5	21	 Nculii' wo'o-imi Yesus hilou hi dipo rano. Karata-na hi dipo-na, wori' wo'o-mi tauna mpotipuhi-i. Bula-na hi wiwi' rano-pidi,
24387	41	5	22	rata hadua pangkeni tomi posampayaa to Yahudi, hanga' -na Yairus. Kampohilo-na Yesus, powingkotu' -nami hi nyanyoa-na
24388	41	5	23	mpopetulungi, na'uli': "Neo' mate lia-imi dei' -ku hi tomi. Lou-ta hi tomi-ku, nujama-ka-kuwo bona mo'uri' -i, bona neo' -i-hawo mate."
24389	41	5	24	Hilou mpu'u-imi Yesus dohe-na, pai' mo'iko wo'o tauna ntuku' -ra. Wori' tauna mpo'upi' Yesus.
24390	41	5	25	Hi olo' ntodea, ria hadua tobine, hampulu' rompae-imi moraa', uma ria kantotoa' -na.
24391	41	5	26	Mompae-mpae-imi mpopepokulii' hi dokter, duu' -na oti-mi ihi' tomi-na napobalu' bona ria napobayari-raka. Aga uma oa' ria kamo'uria' -na, tedonihii lau-di haki' -na.
24392	41	5	27	
24393	41	5	28	Wori' -mi to na'epe to mpotompo'wiwi Yesus. Toe pai' na'uli' hi rala nono-na: "Nau' baju-na-wadi kureo, mo'uri' -ale mpai'!" Jadi' mengkahipi' -imi-hawo hilou hi olo' tauna to wori' mpomohui' Yesus ngkai tilingkuria-na, pai' naganga mpu'u-mi-hawo baju-na.
24394	41	5	29	Wae kanaganga-na, hampinisi mata mentoda' -mi poraa' -na. Ncaliu na'inca kamo'uri' -nami.
24395	41	5	30	Nto'u toe wo'o-hawo, Yesus mpo'inca karia-na baraka' malai ngkai Hi'a. Kame'ili' -nami hi tauna to wori', na'uli': "Hema to mpoganga baju-kue?"
24396	41	5	31	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Guru, nuhilo moto-kowole kawori' tauna to mpo'upi' -koe. Beiwa-kona pai' nupekune' hema to mpoganga-ko?"
24397	41	5	32	Aga Yesus menaa ntololikia-na mpali' tauna to mpoganga-i.
24398	41	5	33	Na'inca tobine toei napa to jadi' hi woto-na. Kamoridi' -nami-hawo me'eka', pai' tumai-i mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa Yesus mpangaku' hawe'ea-na.
24399	41	5	34	Yesus mpo'uli' -ki tobine toei: "Ana' -ku, mo'uri' -moko sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'. Nculii' -moko hante kalompea' tuwu' -nu. Mo'uri' -moko, uma-pi ria haki' -nu."
24400	41	5	35	 Bula-na Yesus mololita-pidi, rata-mi ba hangkuja dua suro ngkai tomi Yairus mpo'uli' -ki Yairus: "Mate-imi-hana ana' -nu. Neo' -pi mposusai' Guru."
24401	41	5	36	Pe'epe moto-i Yesus napa to ra'uli' suro toera. Na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yairus: "Neo' mere' nono-nu! Pangala' moto-mi-hana!"
24402	41	5	37	Kakaliliu-nami Yesus mako', aga uma napiliu tauna to wori' mpodohei-i mesua' hi rala tomi Yairus, muntu' Petrus, Yakobus pai' Yohanes ompi' -na Yakobus-wadi.
24403	41	5	38	Karata-na hi tomi Yairus, na'epe-hawo merodo' -ra-damo tauna, hangaa pogeo' -ra-damo pai' motantangi' rahuduwukui.
24404	41	5	39	Kamesua' -na hi rala tomi, na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' merodo' rahi-koi geo' -e! Uma-i-hawo-le mate-e. Leta' -i-wadi."
24405	41	5	40	Mpo'epe toe we'i, rapotawai-i-wadi. Ngkai ree, Yesus mpohubui-ra omea malai ngkai rala tomi, pai' -i mesua' hi kamar poturua ana' toei, hante tina pai' tuama-na, pai' ana'guru-na to tolu.
24406	41	5	41	Nakamu pale-na ana' toei, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Memata-moko ana'!" Hi rala basa-ra to Yahudi, moni-na hewa toi: "Talita kum!"
24407	41	5	42	Pemata-nami ana' toei kaliliu momako'. (Umuru-na hampulu' rompae.) Uma mowo kakonce-ra tauna to mpohilo.
24408	41	5	43	Aga Yesus mpotagi-ra, na'uli': "Neo' mpu'u nilolita napa to lako' jadi' toi." Pai' na'uli' wo'o: "Wai' -imi ana' tetui koni' -na."
24409	41	6	1	 Oti toe, Yesus me'ongko' ngkai ngata toe hilou hi ngata-na moto hante ana'guru-na.
24410	41	6	2	Hi eo pepuea', hilou-i hi tomi posampayaa mpotudui' tauna. Wori' tauna hi ree. Kampo'epe-ra tudui' Yesus, konce-ra ra'uli': "Hema-di to mpotudui' -i hawe'ea toe-e? Kapantea napa-di to ria hi Hi'a-e? Beiwa pai' ma'ala-i mpobabehi anu mekoncehi?
24411	41	6	3	Bo topowangu tomi-i-wadi, ana' Maria. Ompi' -na, hira' Yakobus, Yoses, Yudas pai' Simon. Ompi' -na tobine, ria moto wo'o-ra dohe-ta hi rehe'i." Toe pai' oja' -ra mepangala' hi Yesus.
24412	41	6	4	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Hadua nabi bate rabila' hiapa kahilouaa-na. Aga hi ngata-na pai' tomi-na, pai' dohe ompi' -na moto, uma lau-i rabila'."
24413	41	6	5	
24414	41	6	6	Jadi', Yesus mpokehele-ra apa' uma-ra mepangala'. Toe pai' uma-i bisa mpobabehi wori' anu mekoncehi hi ria. Sampale to nababehi, mpojama ba hangkuja dua topeda' bona mo'uri' -ra.
24415	41	6	7	 Mpokio' -i ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, nasuro-ra rodua-rodua hampo'emaa', pai' nawai' -ra kuasa mpopalai anudaa'.
24416	41	6	8	Kako'ia-ra me'ongko', natudui' -ra hewa toi: "Neo' -koi ngkeni napa-napa hi pomakoa' -ni, muntu' lua' -wadi. Neo' ngkeni pongkoni' ba boku ba doi hi rala karepe'.
24417	41	6	9	Ma'ala moto-koi mpake' lihi witi', aga neo' ngkeni rontonga' baju."
24418	41	6	10	Na'uli' wo'o-mi: "Ane rata-koi hi hameha' ngata pai' ratarima-koi hi tomi hantomi, mo'oha' hi ree-mokoi duu' -ni kaliliu hilou mpai' hi ngata ntani' -na.
24419	41	6	11	Ane ria pue' ngata to uma dota mpotarima-koi, ane oja' -ra mpo'epe lolita to nikeni, wae kanipalahii-na ngata-ra, tonta awu to mentaka' hi palanta' witi' -ni, tanda kanahuku' -ra mpai' Alata'ala."
24420	41	6	12	Ka'oti-na Yesus mpotudui' ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua toera, me'ongko' -ramo hilou mpotudui' tauna bona medea-ra ngkai jeko' -ra.
24421	41	6	13	Wori' seta to rapopalai. Pai' wori' wo'o tauna to peda' ragelai' hante lana pai' rapaka'uri'.
24422	41	6	14	 Nto'u toe, Magau' Herodes Antipas mpo'epe kareba napa to nababehi Yesus, apa' hanga' Yesus rapotompo'wiwi hiapa-apa. Ria to mpo'uli': "Yesus toei lou, Yohanes Topeniu' -ile tuwu' nculii'! Toe-hana pai' ria baraka' -na mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi toe-e."
24423	41	6	15	Aga ria wo'o to mpo'uli': "Yesus toei, nabi Elia to owi-i." Hiaa' ria wo'o to mpo'uli': "Nabi mpu'u-i, hewa nabi to owi."
24424	41	6	16	Kana'epe-na Magau' Herodes tohe'e, na'uli' -mi: "Yohanes Topeniu' mpu'u-i-tano Yesus toei lou-e! Kupehubui wengi rapata' wuroko' -na, aga tuwu' nculii' -imi."
24425	41	6	17	
24426	41	6	18	Hewa toi tutura kamate-na Yohanes Topeniu'. Magau' Herodes mpo'ago pai' mpotobine Herodias, tobine ompi' -na moto to rahanga' Filipus. Wori' ngkani Yohanes mpokamaro Herodes ngkai gau' -na toe, na'uli' -ki: "Uma-ko ma'ala mpotobine era-nu tetui! Gau' -nu tetu mpotiboki Atura Musa." Ngkai ree, Herodes mpohubui tantara-na hilou mpohoko' Yohanes. Rahoko' mpu'u-imi, rahoo' pai' -i ratarungku'.
24427	41	6	19	Ane Herodias-e, mowuku-damo nono-na hi Yohanes, doko' napatehi. Aga uma-i mologa mpopadupa' roe-na toe,
24428	41	6	20	apa' Herodes mpohubui tantara-na mpojaga-i hi rala tarungku'. Me'eka' -i mpatehi Yohanes apa' na'inca, tauna to monoa' -i pai' moroli' wo'o-i. Ane Herodes mpo'epe Yohanes mpololitai-i, mokarara' nono-na, aga goe' wo'o-i mpo'epe-i mololita.
24429	41	6	21	Hi eo pompokiwoia kaputua Magau' Herodes, ria-mi loga-na Herodias. Hi eo toe, Magau' Herodes mpobabehi posusa' mpokiwoi eo kaputua-na. Mpokio' -i wori' maradika, tadulako pai' pangkeni to ngkai tana' Galilea.
24430	41	6	22	Bula posusa' toe, ana' -na Herodias tobine mesua' pai' modero'. Goe' lia-i Magau' Herodes mpohilo podero' toronaa toei, wae wo'o torata-na. Na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki toronaa toei: "Ane ria ba napa to nupokono, perapi' -mi, bate kuwai' -ko."
24431	41	6	23	Mosumpa wo'o-i, na'uli': "Nau' ba napa mpu'u-mi to nuperapi', nau' hantanga' ngkai poparenta-ku, bate kuwai' -ko!"
24432	41	6	24	Palai-nami toronaa toei hilou mpekune' tina-na, na'uli': "Ina', napa to kuperapi' -e?" Na'uli' tina-na: "Perapi' -mi woo' -na Yohanes Topeniu'!"
24433	41	6	25	Kanculii' -nami hilou hi Magau', kaliliu na'uli': "Merapi' -a woo' -na Yohanes Topeniu' wae lau, ratu'u hi lolo dula."
24434	41	6	26	Mpo'epe pomperapia' toe-di, soho' lia-mi nono-na Magau'. Aga uma-pi ma'ala nadii' nculii' lolita-na hi toronaa toe, apa' mpolia' mosumpa-imi we'i ra'epe torata-na.
24435	41	6	27	Kaliliu napahawa' hadua tantara-na hilou mpo'ala' woo' Yohanes Topeniu'. Kahilou-nami-hawo tantara toe hi tarungku' mpopata' wuroko' -na.
24436	41	6	28	Woo' -na toe nakeni tumai natu'u hi lolo dula pai' natonu-ki toronaa toei, pai' toronaa toei mpowai' tina-na.
24437	41	6	29	Kara'epe-na topetuku' -na Yohanes kamate-nami, hilou-ramo-rawo mpo'ala' woto-na, pai' ratana.
24438	41	6	30	 Suro to nahubui Yesus mpopalele Lolita Alata'ala wengi, nculii' -ramo ngkai pomakoa' -ra, pai' ratutura-miki Yesus hawe'ea to rababehi pai' to ratudui' -raka ntodea.
24439	41	6	31	Nto'u toe, wori' lia tauna to hilou-tumai, alaa-na ntahawe' ngkoni' neo' uma-pi ria loga-ra. Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus hi topetuku' -na: "Kita hilou hi kawaoa' -na mpalahii tauna to wori', bona ma'ala-ta mento'o hampai'."
24440	41	6	32	Jadi', mohawi' sakaya-ramo hilou hi kawaoa' -na.
24441	41	6	33	Ntaa' pehilo moto-di-hana tauna pe'ongko' -rae, pai' ra'inca wo'o toaa' -ra. Jadi', wori' tauna ngkai hawe'ea ngata to mohu', pokeno-rami hilou hi wiwi' rano, rata meri'ulu lau-ra ngkai Yesus hante ana'guru-na.
24442	41	6	34	Pehompo-na Yesus ngkai sakaya, nahilo-hawo wori' tauna mpopea-i. Metumu' -mi ahi' -na mpohilo-ra, apa' hiloa-ra hewa bima to uma te'ewu. Kanatudui' -rami wori' nyala.
24443	41	6	35	Neo' solo-mi eo, tumai-ramo ana'guru-na mpomohui' -i, ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, wao' -hana hi rehe'i lau, pai' neo' limpa-mi eo.
24444	41	6	36	Agina tahubui-ramo tauna toera lau hilou hi ngata pai' tomi hi bonea to mohu' bona mpo'oli pongkoni' -ra."
24445	41	6	37	Na'uli' Yesus: "Koi' -mi to mpopokoni' -ra." Hampetompoi' ana'guru-na: "Ei'! Ha napa-mi-kaina to kiwai' -rakae? Nau' ro'atu doi pera' kipope'oli-ki roti, uma-le hono' mpopokoni' tauna to hewa toe lau kadea-ra."
24446	41	6	38	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kamata pe', hangkuja meha' roti to ria hi koi' -e." Ka'oti-na rapehiloi, ra'uli': "Ria-le, lima meha' -wadi, pai' rongkaju bau' uru."
24447	41	6	39	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpohubui tauna to wori' mohura omea mopantuda-ntuda hi kowo', apa' wori' kowo' to mata' nto'u toe.
24448	41	6	40	Pohura-rami pantuda-ntuda, butu ntuda-na ria nte ha'atu, ria wo'o to nte lima mpulu'.
24449	41	6	41	Oti toe, na'ala' -mi roti to lima meha' pai' uru to rongkaju, pai' -i ngkongoa' hi langi' mosampaya. Oti toe, napihe-pihe-mi roti, pai' nawai' -raka ana'guru-na bona rabagi hi ntodea. Pai' uru to rongkaju, nabagi wo'o-raka omea.
24450	41	6	42	Ngkoni' omea-ramo duu' -ra bohu.
24451	41	6	43	Ka'oti-ra ngkoni', rarumpu-mi toro-na roti pai' bau', hampulu' roluncu-pi.
24452	41	6	44	Kawori' -ra to ngkoni' roti toe, ba ria nte lima ncobu paka' tomane.
24453	41	6	45	 Oti toe Yesus mpohubui ana'guru-na mosakaya meri'ulu hilou hi dipo rano hi ngata Betsaida, pai' -i mpohubui tauna to wori' nculii' hilou hi tomi-ra.
24454	41	6	46	Ponculi' -ra ntodea, manake' -imi hilou hi bulu' -na lou mosampaya.
24455	41	6	47	Mobengi-mi, hi laintongo' rano-ramo ana'guru-na. Hiaa' Hi'a, hi role-nai-pidi hadudua-na.
24456	41	6	48	Nahilo-hawo kawuhe-ramo mowose, apa' ngolu' mewui mpotomu sakaya-ra. Parabaja-mi, momako' -imi hilou hi lolo ue mpototoaka-ra, ntani' naliu-ra.
24457	41	6	49	Karahilo-na to momako' hi lolo ue, pe'au-rami me'eka', ra'uli': "Etu tope'ekahi!"
24458	41	6	50	Wilingkoroa omea-ramo mpohilo-i. Ncaliu na'uli' -raka Yesus: "Pakaroho nono-ni! Neo' me'eka'! Aku' -mile toi-e."
24459	41	6	51	Kangkahe' -nami hi rala sakaya dohe-ra, ngolu' wo'o haliu ora-mi. Uma mowo kakonce-ra, apa' kuyu-ramo.
24460	41	6	52	Apa' nau' ko'ia-ra mahae mpohilo tanda mekoncehi to nababehi hante roti-e ngone, ko'ia oa' monoto hi rala nono-ra kahema-na mpu'u-i Yesus. Morara' oa' -pidi nono-ra mepangala'.
24461	41	6	53	Karata-ra hi dipo rano, mencore-ramo hi tana' to rahanga' Genesaret.
24462	41	6	54	Pehompo-ra ngkai sakaya, rahilo-rawo pue' ngata Kayesus-na to rata hi ngata-ra.
24463	41	6	55	Pokeno-rami hilou hi ngata-ngata to mohu', pai' -ra tumai mpokowa' doo-ra to peda'. Hiapa-apa kara'epea-na ria-i, hi ree wo'o-mi tauna mpokeni doo-ra topeda'.
24464	41	6	56	Hiapa kahiloua-na Yesus hi rala ngata bohe ba ngata kedi', rakeni tumai doo-ra topeda' pai' rapopoturu hi wiwi' karajaa, pai' -ra merapi' hi Yesus bona napiliu-ra mporeo nau' kampa' wuntu baju-na-wadi. Hawe'ea to mporeo baju-na, haliu mo'uri' -ramo.
24465	41	7	1	 Hangkani ria-ra to Parisi pai' guru agama Yahudi to ngkai Yerusalem mpohirua' -ki Yesus.
24466	41	7	2	Mpohilo-ra ba hangkuja dua topetuku' Yesus ngkoni' hante uma-ra mowano ncala' ntuku' ada agama Yahudi.
24467	41	7	3	Apa' hawe'ea to Yahudi, mo'ipi lia-ra mpotuku' ada totu'a-ra, hangkedia' -nami hira' to mpotuku' tudui' -ra to Parisi. Ko'ia-ra ngkoni' ane ko'ia-ra mowano ntuku' ada.
24468	41	7	4	Ane nculii' -ra ngkai pomako' -ra hi rala ngata, kana moniu' -ra ulu ntuku' ada kako'ia-ra mpoganga pongkoni'. Pai' wori' wo'o-pi ada to ratarima ngkai totu'a-ra to ratuku' lia, hewa rapa' -na ada mpobohoi' sangkiri', kura pai' rewa to rababehi ngkai ngkala.
24469	41	7	5	Toe pai' to Parisi nte guru-guru agama toera we'i mpokamaro Yesus, ra'uli': "Napa pai' ana'guru-nu, uma-ra mpotuku' ada totu'a-tae? Ngkoni' -ra, uma-ra mowano ncala'."
24470	41	7	6	Na'uli' Yesus: "Koi' -le, hi mali-na-wadi petuku' -ni hi Alata'ala! Makono mpu'u lolita to na'uki' nabi Yesaya owi to mpolowa-koi, hewa toi moni-na: Na'uli' Alata'ala: `Tauna tohe'era mpobila' -a hi wiwi-ra-wadi, nono-ra molaa ngkai Aku'.
24471	41	7	7	Uma ria kalaua-ra mpopue' -a, apa' tudui' -ra tudui' manusia' -wadi, bela tudui' ngkai Aku'.'
24472	41	7	8	Jadi', hawa' Alata'ala nikalempei' moto, hiaa' moroho lia-damo pongkakamu-ni ada manusia'."
24473	41	7	9	Ngkai ree, na'uli' tena-raka Yesus: "Koi' -le, pante lia-koi mpelelii' hawa' Alata'ala bona mpotuku' ada-ni moto.
24474	41	7	10	Hi rala Atura Musa te'uki' hewa toi: `Kana tabila' tuama pai' tina-ta.' Pai' `hema to mpotipo' tuama-na ba tina-na kana rapatehi.'
24475	41	7	11	
24476	41	7	12	Hiaa' koi' metudui' hewa toi: uma-pi mingki' tabila' tina pai' tuama-ta, asala ta'uli' -raka hewa toi: `Napa to masipato' kuwai' -kokoi totu'a, oti-mi kupajadi' pepue' hi Alata'ala.' Tauna to mpo'uli' hewa toe, nibahaka-imi ngkai kinolo-na mpotulungi tina pai' tuama-na.
24477	41	7	13	Jadi', Lolita Alata'ala uma nisaile', ada to nitarima ngkai totu'a-ni, tetu lau-mi to nitudui' -raka ntodea. Wori' -pidi to hewa tohe'i to nibabehi."
24478	41	7	14	Oti toe Yesus mpokio' wo'o-mi tauna to wori' bona mpomohui' -i, na'uli' -raka: "Epe omea-koi bona ni'inca:
24479	41	7	15	Nau' ba napa-napa to takoni', uma-hawo toe to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala. Kehi to mehupa' ngkai rala nono-ta, toe-die to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala-e. ((
24480	41	7	16	Jadi', hema-koi to tilingaa, pe'epei lompe'!))"
24481	41	7	17	Oti toe, Yesus mpalahii tauna to wori', pai' -i mesua' hi rala tomi. Ana'guru-na mpekune' -i ba napa patuju tudui' -na toe we'i.
24482	41	7	18	Na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Ha uma wo'o-koiwo nipaha-e? Pongkoni' to mesua' hi rala nganga-ta ngkai mali-na, bela-hawo toe to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala.
24483	41	7	19	Apa' pongkoni' toe, uma mesua' hi rala nono-ta. Mesua' hi ta'i-ta-wadi, pai' ngkai ree kaliliu tatadi." Hante lolita-na toe, Yesus mpakanoto ka'uma-na ria pongkoni' to rapalii'.
24484	41	7	20	Na'uli' tena-raka: "Aga kehi pai' gau' -ta, toe-dile to mpakada'a-ta hi poncilo Alata'ala-e, apa' kehi pai' gau' -ta toe mehupa' ngkai nono-ta.
24485	41	7	21	Ngkai nono manusia' mehupa' pekiri to dada'a, pai' alaa-na ria to mogau' sala' hi tobine ba hi tomane, manako, mepatehi,
24486	41	7	22	mobualo', mebagiu, metipo', pai' mpobabehi wori' nyala to dada'a. Mpokahina anu doo, mohingi', molangko nono, nakeni hina nono to dada'a, uma tuduia'.
24487	41	7	23	Hawe'ea gau' dada'a to hewa toe-mi lau mehupa' ngkai nono manusia'. Toe-mi to mpakada'a tauna hi poncilo Alata'ala-e."
24488	41	7	24	 Ngkai ree, hilou-imi Yesus hi tana' to mohu' hi ngata Tirus, pai' -i mesua' hi rala tomi. Patuju-na bona ke neo' ra'incai tauna karata-na. Aga karata-na uma ma'ala wuniia'.
24489	41	7	25	
24490	41	7	26	Hi ngata toe, ria wo'o hadua totina, ana' -na tobine kahawia'. Kana'epe-na totina toei karia-na Yesus hi ngata, katumai-nami mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na mpopetulungi, na'uli': "Popalai-ka-kuwo seta to mpohawi' ana' -ku!" Hiaa' tobine toei, bela-i to Yahudi, to Fenisia-i-hana ngkai tana' Siria.
24491	41	7	27	Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Aku', mpotulungi to Yahudi-a-kuna ulu. Uma lompe' mpo'ala' koni' ana', pai' rarora-ki dike'."
24492	41	7	28	Na'uli' -mi-hawo tobine toei: "Makono moto-di Pue'. Aga dike' to hi une' meja' wo'o-hawo-le, biasa-ra ngkoni' koni' ana' to mohewu' ngkai lolo meja'."
24493	41	7	29	Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Kono wo'o-kowo petompoi' -nu! Wae-pi, nculii' -moko, malai-mi seta to mpesuai' ana' -nu."
24494	41	7	30	Kanculii' -nami totina toei. Rata hi tomi, nahilo ana' -na rodo-imi hi poturua-na, apa' malai mpu'u-mi seta.
24495	41	7	31	 Ngkai ree, Yesus mpalahii ngata Tirus mpokaliliu pomako' -na ntara hi ngata Sidon, pai' nculii' wo'o-imi hilou hi rano Galilea, rata hi tana' Dekapolis.
24496	41	7	32	Hi ree, ria to mpokeni hadua tauna to wongo pai' to neo' uma howa' mololita. Merapi' -ra bona najama-i-hawo.
24497	41	7	33	Yesus mpokeni tauna toei ngkai laintongo' ntodea. Ka'oti-na napatani' -i, nape'uso karawe-na hi tilinga-na ntimalia, mpetiliku-i, pai' -i mpojama jila' -na tauna toei.
24498	41	7	34	Oti toe, ngkongoa' -imi hi langi' mpo'osu' inoha' -na pai' mpo'uli': "Mobea-mi!" (Hi rala basa-ra to Yahudi, moni-na hewa toi: "Efata!")
24499	41	7	35	Pe'epe mpu'u-imi-hawo, pai' jila' -na molengkue' -mi. Lonto' -mi-hawo pololita-na.
24500	41	7	36	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpotagi-ra tauna to wori' bona neo' ra'uli' hi hema-hema napa to jadi' tohe'e. Aga nau' wae kanatagi-ra, hangkedi' -na lau-mi karatolele-na.
24501	41	7	37	Uma mowo kakonce-ra ntodea, ntora ra'uli' -mi: "Hawe'ea to nababehi, lompe'. Tauna to wongo napaka'uri', pe'epe-ramo! Tauna to uma howa' mololita, howa' -ramo mololita!"
24502	41	8	1	 Uma mahae ngkai ree, wori' wo'o-mi tauna morumpu dohe Yesus. Apa' uma-hawo ria pongkoni' -ra, nakio' -ra ana'guru-na pai' na'uli' -raka:
24503	41	8	2	"Tuna-kuna nono-ku mpohilo tauna to wori' toera lau. Tolu eo-ramo dohe-ku, uma ria pongkoni' -ra.
24504	41	8	3	Hiaa' ane kuhubui-ra nculii' hilou hi tomi-ra ntali oro' -ra, meka' molinga' -ra mpai' hi ohea. Apa' ria-ra to ngkai kalaa-na."
24505	41	8	4	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Ngkaiapa-tana mpai' tarata pongkoni' tapokoni' -raka, bo wao' -hana hi rehe'i lau?"
24506	41	8	5	Napekune' -ra: "Hangkuja roti to ria hi koi' -e?" Ra'uli' -ki: "Pitu meha'."
24507	41	8	6	Ngkai ree, nahubui-ramo tauna to wori' mohura hi tana'. Na'ala' -mi roti pai' -i mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala. Oti toe, napihe-pihe-mi pai' nawai' -raka ana'guru-na mpobagi-bagi-raka tauna to wori'.
24508	41	8	7	Ria wo'o-raka bau' uru to kedi' ba hangkuja ma'a. Naposampayai wo'o pai' nahubui ana'guru-na mpobagi hi ntodea.
24509	41	8	8	
24510	41	8	9	Ngkoni' -ramo duu' -ra bohu. Kawori' -ra to ngkoni' nto'u toe, ba opo' ncobu. Ka'oti-ra ngkoni', rarumpu-mi toro-na, pitu luncu-pi. Oti toe, Yesus mpohubui-ra nculii' hilou hi tomi-ra,
24511	41	8	10	 pai' Hi'a hante ana'guru-na mohawi' sakaya hilou hi ngata Dalmanuta.
24512	41	8	11	Ba hangkuja dua to Parisi rata hi Yesus, pai' ratepu'u-mi mpomehono' -ki doko' mposori-i. Ra'uli' -ki: "Babehi-mi anu mekoncehi bona monoto ki'inca kangkai Alata'ala-na mpu'u-ko."
24513	41	8	12	Kana'epe-na Yesus lolita-ra, na'osu' -mi inoha' -na pai' na'uli': "Napa-di pai' tauna to tuwu' tempo toi merapi' tanda mekoncehi-e? Uma-a dota! Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: uma-koi kupopohiloi tanda mekoncehi hewa to niperapi'."
24514	41	8	13	Kanapalahii-rami, mehawi' -imi hi sakaya hilou hi dipo rano.
24515	41	8	14	Hi pomako' -ra tohe'e, ana'guru-na Yesus uma mpokiwoi ngkeni boku, muntu' hameha' roti to ria hi rala sakaya.
24516	41	8	15	Yesus mpololitai-ra hante hanyala walatu, na'uli': "Pelompehi-koi, mo'inga' -inga' hi ragi-ra to Parisi pai' ragi Magau' Herodes!"
24517	41	8	16	Aga uma ra'incai batua-na walatu toe, helee momepololitai moto-ramo, ra'uli': "Pai' na'uli' hewa toe-le, apa' uma ria roti-ta."
24518	41	8	17	
24519	41	8	18	Ntaa' na'inca-di Yesus napa to ra'uli' ana'guru-nae, toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' ntora mpololita ka'uma-na ria roti-nie? Ko'ia oa' -tano nipaha-e? Ha uma oa' monoto nono-ni, jau-mi ni'epe tudui' -ku, jau nihilo kabaraka' -ku? Mataa pai' tilingaa moto-koi, hiaa' uma oa' nipaha napa to nihilo pai' to ni'epe? Ha uma nikiwoi,
24520	41	8	19	roti to lima meha' kupihe-pihe kupokoni' -raka tauna to lima ncobu? Hangkuja luncu-pi toro-na to nirumpu?" Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Hampulu' roluncu."
24521	41	8	20	Napekune' tena Yesus: "Pai' roti to pitu meha' kupokoni' -raka to opo' ncobu, hangkuja luncu wo'o-pi toro-na to nirumpu?" Ra'uli': "Pitu luncu-pi."
24522	41	8	21	Na'uli' tena-raka: "Hiaa' uma oa' nipaha toe?"
24523	41	8	22	 Ngkai ree, rata-ramo hi ngata Betsaida. Hi ngata toe, ria to ngkeni hadua towero hi Yesus. Merapi' -ra bona najama-i-hawo.
24524	41	8	23	Yesus mpokamu pale-na, pai' natete' -i hilou hi mali bola'. Na'uelikui mata-na pai' naganga. Oti toe, napekune' -i: "Ria to nuhilo ba napa-napa?"
24525	41	8	24	Towero toe menaa-naa pai' na'uli': "Kuhilo tauna, mokao' hewa kaju to mako' hilou tumai."
24526	41	8	25	Oti toe, naganga tena mata-na, pai' nahubui-i menaa. Mo'uri' mpu'u-miki mata-na. Hawe'ea to nahilo, monoto-mi.
24527	41	8	26	Oti toe, Yesus mpohubui-i nculii' hilou hi tomi-na, na'uli' -ki: "Nculii' -moko hilou hi tomi-nu, aga neo' -ko mesua' hi rala ngata mpo'uli' -raka pue' ngata napa to jadi' toi."
24528	41	8	27	 Yesus hante ana'guru-na hilou hi ngata to mohu' Kaisarea Filipi. Hi lengko ohea, napekune' -ra, na'uli': "Ntuku' ponguli' ntodea, hema-a Aku' toi-e?"
24529	41	8	28	Ra'uli' -ki: "Ria to mpo'uli' Yohanes Topeniu' -ko tuwu' nculii'. Ria wo'o to mpo'uli' nabi Elia-ko. Ria wo'o-ra to mpo'uli' Iko hadua nabi to owi tuwu' nculii'."
24530	41	8	29	Napekune' tena-ra, na'uli': "Hiaa' koi' -koiwo mpo'uli' hema-a Aku' toi-e?" Natompoi' Petrus: "Iko-mi Magau' Topetolo'!"
24531	41	8	30	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' ulu ni'uli' hi hema-hema ka'Aku' -na Magau' Topetolo'."
24532	41	8	31	Oti toe, natepu'u-mi Yesus mpotudui' ana'guru-na napa to kana jadi' hi woto-na. Na'uli' -raka: "Aku' Ana' Manusia' kana mporata wori' kaparia. Rasapuaka-a mpai' totu'a ngata, imam pangkeni hante guru agama. Rapatehi-a mpai', aga tolu eo oti toe, tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
24533	41	8	32	Hawe'ea toe napolonto' mpo'uli' -raka. Aga Petrus mpo'ai' -i hi ncori-na pai' nakorai' -i.
24534	41	8	33	Yesus me'ili' pai' mponaa ana'guru-na, pai' -i ngkaroe Petrus, na'uli' -ki: "Palai-ko topesori! Pekiri-nu tetu-le pekiri manusia', bela pekiri Alata'ala."
24535	41	8	34	Oti toe, Yesus mpokio' tauna to wori' bona morumpu hangkaa-ngkania hante Hi'a pai' ana'guru-na. Na'uli' -raka: "Hema to doko' mpotuku' -a kana mpobahaka konoa-na moto, pai' kana napaha'a kaju parika' -na-- batua-na: kana natuku' hawa' -ku nau' napomate-ki. Oti toe-di pai' lako' ma'ala-i mpotuku' -a.
24536	41	8	35	Hema to mpentaei konoa-na moto, uma-i mpai' mporatai katuwua' to lompe'. Aga hema to mpobahaka konoa-na moto sabana petuku' -na hi Aku' pai' sabana Kareba Lompe', nau' napomate-ki, hi'a mpai' to mporata katuwua' to lompe'.
24537	41	8	36	Napa kalaua-na tarumpu hawe'ea ka'uaa' dunia', ane uma taratai katuwua' to lompe' hi eo mpeno-na.
24538	41	8	37	Apa' uma ria napa-napa to ma'ala tasula' -ki katuwua' to lompe' toe.
24539	41	8	38	"Mo'oha' -koi hi laintongo' tauna to dada'a pai' to uma mpotuku' -a. Aga hema to me'ea' mpangaku' petuku' -na hi Aku' pai' mpoka'ea' tudui' -ku, Aku' wo'o mpai' me'ea' mpangaku' kahi'a-na topetuku' -ku ane rata-apa mpai' ngkai suruga. Nto'u toe mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia' mana'u tumai hante mala'eka-mala'eka to moroli', mehini-a hante baraka' -na Tuama-ku."
24540	41	9	1	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Ngkai olo' -ni koi' toi, ria-koi mpai' to ko'ia mate kako'ia-na nihilo Alata'ala moparenta hante baraka' -na."
24541	41	9	2	Ono mengi ngkai ree, Yesus mpobawai tolu ana'guru-na hilou dohe-na hi bulu' to molangko. Ana'guru to tolu toera: Petrus, Yakobus pai' Yohanes. Muntu' Yesus hante ana'guru-na to tolu toera-wadi to hi ria. Bula-ra hi ria, mobali' -mi lence-na.
24542	41	9	3	Pohea-na hangaa mengea' meringkila', uma ria haduaa hi rala dunia' tohe'i to ma'ala mo'uja' duu' -na mengea' hewa toe.
24543	41	9	4	Rahilo-rawo ana'guru-nae, ria rodua nabi to owi mpololitai Yesus. Nabi toera, Elia pai' Musa.
24544	41	9	5	Ngkai ree Petrus mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, lompe' lia-ta mo'oha' hi rehe'i. Agina kibabehi-damo tolu bamaru': hameha' bagia-nu Pue', hameha' bagia-na Musa, pai' hameha' wo'o bagia-na Elia."
24545	41	9	6	Kakono-na, uma-hawo na'incai Petrus napa to na'uli' toe, apa' nto'u toe bula-ra me'eka' lia.
24546	41	9	7	Nto'u toe wo'o, rata-mi limu' mpokamoui-ra, pai' ngkai rala limu' ra'epe topololita to mpo'uli': "Hi'a toi-mi Ana' -ku to kupe'ahi'. Pe'epei lolita-na!"
24547	41	9	8	Hampegoli we'i, ranaa-rawo ntololikia-ra, uma-pi ria tau ntani' -na dohe-ra, hadua Yesus-damo.
24548	41	9	9	Pana'u-ra ngkai lolo bulu' toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' ulu nilolita hi hema-hema napa to nihilo we'i, duu' -na Aku' Ana' Manusia' memata ngkai kamatea."
24549	41	9	10	Ratuku' mpu'u-miki hawa' -na toe, uma mpu'u-rawo ralolita kajadia' toe hi hema-hema. Aga hi himpau hira' moto bate ntora rapomepekunei' ba napa patuju-na Yesus mpo'uli' kamemata-na mpai' ngkai kamatea.
24550	41	9	11	Mepekune' -ramo hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Napa pai' guru agama mpo'uli' nabi Elia ncala' -di to ri'ulu rata, pai' lako' rata-idi Magau' Topetolo' -e?"
24551	41	9	12	Na'uli' -raka: "Makono mpu'u-di. Elia kana rata mperi'ulu, apa' hi'a to mporodo hawe'ea-na. Aga beiwa-ama Aku' Ana' Manusia'? Napa pai' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' te'uki' kamporata-ku wori' kaparia pai' -a raruge' tauna?
24552	41	9	13	Aga ane nabi Elia, ku'uli' -kokoi, mpolia' rata-imile Elia-e, aga pangkeni ngata-ta mpo'ewa-i ntuku' konoa-ra, hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'."
24553	41	9	14	 Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na to tolu toera, mana'u-ramo ngkai lolo bulu' mpohirua' -raka ana'guru to ntani' -na. Rata hi ria, rahilo-rawo wori' tauna mpotipuhi ana'guru-na, pai' ba hangkuja dua guru agama bula-ra mpomehono' -raka.
24554	41	9	15	Pehilo-ra tauna to wori' toera etu-mi tumai Yesus. Wae kampohilo-ra, konce-ramo. Pokeno-rami hilou mpohirua' -ki.
24555	41	9	16	Yesus mpekune' -ra: "Napa to nipomepekunei' hante guru agama toera?"
24556	41	9	17	Hadua ngkai tauna to wori' toera mpo'uli': "Guru, oi-kuwo ana' -ku, kukeni bona nupaka'uri' -i. Uma-i howa' mololita apa' napesuai' anudaa' -i.
24557	41	9	18	Ane napesuai' wo'o-ipi anudaa' -e, modungka-i hi tana', mowura' nganga-na, kakakeji' -keji' ngihi' -na, pai' mokadu hudu woto-na. Kuperapi' -ramo ana'guru-nu mpopalai anudaa' -na, aga uma rakulei'."
24558	41	9	19	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma mowo-koie'. Ko'ia oa' -tano mepangala' -koie! Ni'uli' -koina hangkuja tena-pi kahae-ku dohe-ni, hangkuja tena-pi kahae-na kupengkatarii kalente pepangala' -nie! Keni tumai ana' tetui!"
24559	41	9	20	Rakeni mpu'u-mi ana' toei hi Yesus. Wae pehilo-na anudaa' toei mpohilo Yesus, napakako'o wo'o-mi woto ana' toei duu' -na modungka-i pai' -i ngkawulela' hi tana', nganga-na mowura'.
24560	41	9	21	Mepekune' -i Yesus hi tuama-na ana' toei, na'uli': "Hangkuja-mi hae-na narata haki' toi-e?" Na'uli' tuama-na: "Ngkai kakedia' -nami-hana.
24561	41	9	22	Wori' ngkani-mi anudaa' mpodungka-i hi rala apu ba hi rala ue doko' napatehi. Ane ma'ala Guru, poka'ahi' pai' tulungi-ka-kaiwo!"
24562	41	9	23	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa pai' nu'uli' `ane ma'ala-e?' Hawe'ea ma'ala jadi' hi tauna to mepangala'."
24563	41	9	24	Hampetompoi' tuama-na ana' toei napesukui: "Mepangala' -ama Pue'! Tulungi-a-kuwo, apa' aku' toi kura' rahi pepangala' -ku."
24564	41	9	25	Nahilo Yesus kawoo-woria' tauna to mokeno tumai morumpu. Kanahawai' -nami anudaa' toe, na'uli': "Ee anudaa' to mepakawongo pai' mepakawojo tetu-ko! Petibo' -ko ngkai ana' tetui, pai' neo' -pi nupesuai' nculii'."
24565	41	9	26	Pe'au-nami ana' toei, kakapadi-padi woto-na, pai' malai-mi anudaa'. Kamalai-na anudaa', uma-pi molengo ana' toei, hewa tomate-imi, alaa-na wori' to mpo'uli': "Mate-imi!"
24566	41	9	27	Aga Yesus mpokamu pale-na mpotulungi-i memata. Memata mpu'u-imi-hawo ana' toei.
24567	41	9	28	Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na malai ngkai ree mesua' hi rala tomi. Pesua' -ra hi rala tomi, mepekune' -ramo hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Guru, napa pai' uma kipakulei' mpopalai anudaa' toei-e we'i?"
24568	41	9	29	Na'uli' -raka: "Anudaa' to hewa tohe'e uma-hana ma'ala rapopalai hante inca napa-napa, muntu' hante mosampaya."
24569	41	9	30	 Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na malai ngkai ree mpokaliliu pomako' -ra ntara hi tana' Galilea. Patuju-na Yesus bona neo' ra'incai ntodea kahiapa-na,
24570	41	9	31	apa' nto'u toe bula-na mpotudui' ana'guru-na. Na'uli' -raka: "Aku' Ana' Manusia', ratonu-a mpai' hi kuasa manusia'. Rapatehi-a mpai', aga tolu eo oti toe, tuwu' nculii' -a."
24571	41	9	32	Aga ana'guru-na uma mpo'incai patuju-na Yesus. Hiaa' uma wo'o-ra daho' mpekune' -i.
24572	41	9	33	Rata-ramo hi ngata Kapernaum. Hi rala tomi-ramo, mepekune' -i Yesus hi ana'guru-na, na'uli': "Napa-die to ntora nilolita hi lengko ohea-e we'i?"
24573	41	9	34	Uma-ra winihi, apa' to rapomehonoi' hi lengko ohea we'i, ba hema-ra to meliu kabohe tuwu' -ra.
24574	41	9	35	Jadi', mohura-imi Yesus pai' -i mpokio' ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, na'uli' -raka: "Hema to doko' meliu bohe tuwu' -na, kana tuwu' mengkadingki' -i, meliu kadingki' -na ngkai hawe'ea doo-na, pai' kana jadi' pahawaa' hi hawe'ea doo-na."
24575	41	9	36	Oti toe, na'ala' hadua ana' to kedi', napopokore hi laintongo' -ra. Nakupui ana' toei pai' na'uli' -raka ana'guru-na:
24576	41	9	37	"Hema to mpotarima hadua ana' to kedi' hewa ana' toii sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', batua-na Aku' -mi to natarima. Pai' hema to mpotarima-a, uma muntu' Aku' to natarima, mpotarima wo'o-i Alata'ala to mposuro-a."
24577	41	9	38	Na'uli' Yohanes mpo'uli' -ki: "Guru, ria kihilo hadua tauna mpopalai seta hante hanga' -nu, aga kitagi-i apa' bela-i topetuku' -ta."
24578	41	9	39	Na'uli' Yesus: "Neo' -i ratagi, apa' tauna to mpobabehi anu mobaraka' hante hanga' -ku, uma-ra mpai' kaliliu mporuge' -a.
24579	41	9	40	Tauna to uma mpo'ewa-ta, batua-na hira' -mi to tono' hi kita'.
24580	41	9	41	 "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: ane ria to mpotulungi-koi apa' topetuku' Kristus-koi, bate mporata-i hiwili-na hi eo mpeno. Nau' ue mara-wadi nawai' -koi ni'inu sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku', bate mporata-i mpai' hiwili-na.
24581	41	9	42	"Aga hema to mpopanawu' hadua ana' to kedi' hewa ana' toii alaa-na uma-ipi mepangala' hi Aku', bohe mpu'u mpai' pehuku' -na Alata'ala hi tauna tetui. Agina lau-pi hameha' watu po'ahaa' to bohe ratoe hi wuroko' -na pai' -i ratene' hi rala tahi'.
24582	41	9	43	"Ane rapa' -na pale-ta hamali mpakeni-ta mojeko', pua' lau-imi. Agina hamali-damo pale-ta, asala mporata-ta katuwua' to lompe' dohe Alata'ala. Agina lau-pi toe, ngkai palea ntimalia-ta, hiaa' ka'omea-na mesua' naraka-tamo hi rala apu to jela' ncuu. ((
24583	41	9	44	Apa' hi ria mpai', tauna nakoni' ule ncuu pai' rasesa' hi rala apu.))
24584	41	9	45	Ane rapa' -na witi' -ta hamali mpakeni-ta mojeko', pua' lau-imi. Agina hamali-damo witi' -ta, asala mporata-ta katuwua' to lompe' dohe Alata'ala. Agina lau-pi toe, ngkai witia' ntimalia-ta, hiaa' ka'omea-na ratadi-ta hi rala naraka. ((
24585	41	9	46	Hi ria mpai', tauna nakoni' ule ncuu pai' rasesa' hi rala apu.))
24586	41	9	47	Pai' ane rapa' -na mata-ta hamali mpakeni-ta mojeko', jungki' lau-mi. Agina hamali-wadi mata-ta pai' -ta jadi' ntodea Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na. Agina lau-pi toe, ngkai mataa ntimalia-ta, hiaa' ka'omea-na ratadi-ta hi rala apu naraka.
24587	41	9	48	Hi ria mpai', tauna nakoni' ule ncuu pai' rasesa' hi rala apu.
24588	41	9	49	Ntuku' Atura Musa, hawe'ea pongkoni' to rapopepue' hi Alata'ala kana rapoii'. Wae wo'o butu dua tauna kana rapomoroli' hante apu.
24589	41	9	50	"Poi' wori' kalaua-na. Aga ane mobali' -mi kapoi' -na alaa-na mononto, napa tena to ma'ala mpakapoi' -i? Wae wo'o, koi' to mpotuku' -a kana hewa poi': Neo' nipelele' pepangala' -ni jadi' lente. Kana tuwu' hintuwu' -koi."
24590	41	10	1	 Malai-imi Yesus ngkai ree hilou hi tana' Yudea pai' hi dipo ue Yordan. Wori' wo'o-mi tauna tumai mpotipuhi-i, pai' hewa to lalaua natudui' wo'o-ramo.
24591	41	10	2	Ria ba hangkuja dua to Parisi rata mpali' kedo'. Rapekune' -i: "Ntuku' atura agama-ta, ba ma'ala moto-hawo tomane mpogaa' -ki tobine-nae?"
24592	41	10	3	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa parenta to nawai' -kokoi nabi Musa?"
24593	41	10	4	Ratompoi' to Parisi: "Musa mpiliu tomane mpogaa' -ki tobine-na, asala nababehi ncala' sura mpogaa'."
24594	41	10	5	Na'uli' Yesus: "Musa mpo'uki' pai' mpoparata-kokoi parenta toe-le, apa' ngkai kamotu'a maga-ni, uma tuduia'.
24595	41	10	6	Aga ngkai lomo' kajadi' dunia', nto'u Alata'ala mpajadi' manusia', napajadi' -ra hadua tomane pai' hadua tobine.
24596	41	10	7	`Toe pai' tomane kana mpalahii tina pai' tuama-na, pai' kana tuwu' hintuwu' hante tobine-na,
24597	41	10	8	bona hira' tau rodua toe jadi' hewa hadua lau-ra-damo.' Jadi', hi poncilo Alata'ala, tau hancamoko uma-pi rodua, hadua lau-ramo.
24598	41	10	9	Toe pai' ku'uli' -kokoi: ane ntoa' Alata'ala mpoposidai' -ra, manusia' uma ma'ala mpogaa' -ra."
24599	41	10	10	Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na mesua' hi rala tomi. Bula-ra hi rala tomi ana'guru-na mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Beiwa mpu'u-hawo gau' pogaa' tohe'e we'i-e?"
24600	41	10	11	Na'uli' -raka: "Hema to mpogaa' -ki tobine-na pai' -i ncamoko hante tobine to ntani' -na, mobualo' -i-hana, mpobualohi tobine-na to lomo' -na.
24601	41	10	12	Wae wo'o tobine to mpogaa' -ki tomane-na pai' -i ncamoko hante tomane to ntani' -na, mobualo' wo'o-i-wadi-hawo."
24602	41	10	13	 Hangkani, ria tauna to mpokeni ana' -ra hi Yesus bona najama pai' nagane' -ra. Aga ana'guru-na mpokaroe tauna toera.
24603	41	10	14	Mpohilo toe-di, kamoroe-nami Yesus mpokaroe ana'guru-na, na'uli' -raka: "Pelele' moto-ra ana' tetura tumai hi Aku', neo' -ra nitagi. Apa' tauna to hewa toe-ramo to jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na.
24604	41	10	15	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Ane uma-koi mengkoru hi Alata'ala hewa ana', uma-koi mpai' jadi' ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
24605	41	10	16	Ka'oti-na mpo'uli' toe, nakupui-ramo ana' toera, najama-ra pai' -ra nagane'.
24606	41	10	17	 Neo' me'ongko' wo'o-imi Yesus mpokaliliu pomako' -na, muu-mule' mokeno tumai hadua tauna mperapai-i, kaliliu mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na, pai' -i mepekune', na'uli': "Guru to lompe', napa-kuwo to kana kubabehi bona mporata-a-kuwo katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na?"
24607	41	10	18	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa pai' nu'uli' tauna to lompe' -a? Uma ria ntani' -na to lompe', hadua Alata'ala-wadi.
24608	41	10	19	Nu'inca moto parenta to te'uki' hi rala Atura Pue': `Neo' mepatehi, neo' mobualo', neo' manako, neo' mosabi' boa', neo' mebagiu, pai' kana tabila' tina pai' tuama-ta.'"
24609	41	10	20	Na'uli' tauna toei: "Guru, hawe'ea parenta tetu lau, kutuku' omea-mi ngkai kakedia' -ku."
24610	41	10	21	Yesus mpomonaa-i hante ahi' -na, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Hanyala-pi to kana nubabehi. Lou-moko ulu mpobalu' rewa-nu, pai' doi oli-na wai' -raka tokabu. Ane nubabehi hewa toe, bohe mpai' rasi' to nurata hi rala suruga. Oti toe, pai' tumai-moko mpotuku' -a."
24611	41	10	22	Kana'epe-na lolita-na Yesus tohe'e, peda' -mi nono-na. Kamalai-nami ngkai ree hante susa' nono-na, apa' wori' rewa-na.
24612	41	10	23	Yesus mpomonaa ana'guru-na to mokore ntololikia-na, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Mokoro rahi tauna to wori' rewa-ra mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra."
24613	41	10	24	Rapokakonce ana'guru-na mpo'epe lolita-na tohe'e. Toe pai' na'uli' tena-raka: "Ana' -ana' -ku, mokoro mpu'u manusia' mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra.
24614	41	10	25	Mojoli-pi hama'a unta ntara hi wulou' jaru, ngkai tauna to mo'ua' mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra."
24615	41	10	26	Mpo'epe toe-di, hangkedi' kakonce-ra ana'guru-na, ra'uli': "Ei', ane wae-di, hema lau-damo to ma'ala mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae!"
24616	41	10	27	Yesus mponaa-ra pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ane hante pakulea' manusia' -le, uma ami' hema. Aga ane Alata'ala, ma'ala oa' madupa', apa' hi Alata'ala uma ria to uma madupa'."
24617	41	10	28	Ngkai ree, na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Hiaa' kai', kipalahii omea-mi-kaina bona mpotuku' -ko."
24618	41	10	29	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Hema-hema to mpalahii ompi' -na, tina-na ba tuama-na, ana' -na ba tomi-na ba bonea-na sabana mpotuku' -a pai' sabana Kareba Lompe',
24619	41	10	30	bate mporata-i mpai' hiwili to bohe. Hi dunia' toi mporata-i ha'atu ngkani kawori' tomi, ompi', tina, ana', bonea-- pai' mporata wo'o-i pebalinai'. Pai' hi eo mpeno-na mpai', mporata wo'o-i katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
24620	41	10	31	Aga wori' tauna to bohe tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' kedi' tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno. Pai' wori' wo'o tauna to kedi' tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' bohe tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno."
24621	41	10	32	 Yesus hante ana'guru-na mpokaliliu pomako' -ra hilou hi Yerusalem. Yesus momako' ri'ulu, ana'guru-na hi boko'. Koro' ana'guru-na mpohilo-i, pai' tauna to metuku' hi boko' wo'o me'eka' omea-ramo. Toe pai' nakio' wo'o-mi ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua mopahantani', pai' na'uli' -raka napa to kana jadi' mpai' hi woto-na.
24622	41	10	33	Na'uli': "Epe-koi! Hilou-tamo tohe'i-e mpotoa' Yerusalem. Hi ria mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia' ratonu hi imam pangkeni pai' guru agama, pai' rabotuhi bona rapatehi-a. Oti toe ratonu-a hi tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi.
24623	41	10	34	Rapopo'ore' -a, ra'uelikui, raweba', pai' rapatehi. Aga tolu eo oti toe tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
24624	41	10	35	Oti toe, Yakobus pai' Yohanes, ana' -na Zebedeus, mpomohui' Yesus, ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, ria hanyala to doko' kiperapi' ngkai Iko."
24625	41	10	36	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa to niperapi' kuwai' -koi?"
24626	41	10	37	Ra'uli': "Ane nupopehuwu mpai' baraka' -nu pai' -ko jadi' Magau', piliu-kai mohura pai' moparenta dohe-nu, hadua hi mali ka'ana-nu, hadua hi mali ki'ii-nu."
24627	41	10	38	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Uma ni'incai napa to niperapi' tetu. Ha nipakule' mpai' mpokolo kaparia to kana kukolo Aku' -e? Ha nipakule' mpotodohaka to kutodohaka-e mpai'?"
24628	41	10	39	Ra'uli': "Kipakule' moto!" Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono, bate nikolo mpu'u mpai' kaparia hewa to kukolo, pai' nitodohaka napa to kutodohaka.
24629	41	10	40	Aga ane hema to mohura hi mali ka'ana-ku ba hi mali ki'ii-ku, bela Aku' to mpakatantu tetu. Alata'ala-hana to mpakatantu hema to mporata bagia tetu."
24630	41	10	41	Kara'epe-na ana'guru-na to hampulu' pomperapia' Yakobus pai' Yohanes toe, moroe-ramo.
24631	41	10	42	Toe pai' Yesus mpokio' -ra omea, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ni'inca moto kasoa-ra topoparenta to uma mpo'incai Alata'ala mpoparentai ntodea-ra. Tauna to bohe pangka' -ra mpewuku ntodea-ra mpotuku' hawa' -ra.
24632	41	10	43	Aga koi', neo' hewa toe kehi-ni! Hema-koi to doko' bohe pangka' -na kana jadi' pahawaa'.
24633	41	10	44	Pai' hema to doko' bohe hanga' -na kana jadi' batua hi hawe'ea doo-na.
24634	41	10	45	Bangku' Aku' Ana' Manusia' -e', patuju-ku tumai hi dunia', uma bona jadi' topohawa'. Pai' -a tumai-le, bona jadi' pahawaa', duu' -na mpewai' woto-ku rapatehi mpotolo' sala' tauna to wori'."
24635	41	10	46	 Yesus pai' ana'guru-na rata hi ngata Yerikho. Nto'u-ra malai ngkai ngata, wori' tauna mpotuku' -ra. Hi wiwi' ohea mohura hadua tauna to wero kakarapi' -rapi'. Hanga' -na Bartimeus (batua-na: ana' Timeus).
24636	41	10	47	Kana'epe-na Bartimeus Kayesus to Nazaret to liu, kamekio' -nami na'uli': "Yesus, muli Magau' Daud! Poka'ahi' -a-kuwo!"
24637	41	10	48	Wori' tauna mpokaroe-i, ra'uli': "Ngkalino-ko!" Aga hangkedi' kanapesukui-na mekio': "Muli Magau' Daud, poka'ahi' -a-kuwo!"
24638	41	10	49	Mentoda' -imi Yesus pai' na'uli': "Kio' -i tumai!" Karakio' -nami towero toei, ra'uli' -ki: "Pakaroho nono-nu! Mokore-moko, apa' nakio' -moko!"
24639	41	10	50	Kamokore-nami towero toei, nabahaka abe' -na hi ohea pai' napesahui hilou hi Yesus.
24640	41	10	51	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Napa to nupokono kubabehi-koko?" Natompoi' towero toei: "Guru, bona pehilo-a-kuwo!"
24641	41	10	52	Na'uli' Yesus: "Hilou-moko. Kupaka'uri' -moko sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'." Ncaliu pehilo-imi, pai' -i mpotuku' Yesus.
24642	41	11	1	 Kamohu' -ra hi ngata Yerusalem, rata-ramo hi ngata Betfage pai' Betania hi Bulu' Zaitun. Hi ree, Yesus mpohubui rodua ana'guru-na hilou meri'ulu,
24643	41	11	2	na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi ngata to tanyanyohi toe mai. Wae pesua' -ni mpai' rala ngata, nihilo mpai' hama'a ana' keledai tehoo', to ko'ia hangkania rahawi'. Bongka koloro-na pai' keni-i tumai.
24644	41	11	3	Ane ria to mpekune' -koi napa pai' nibongka-i, uli' -raka hewa toi: `Apa' naparaluu Pue', napebolo ulu pai' napoponculi' moto mpai'.'"
24645	41	11	4	Kahilou-rami ana'guru-na to rodua toera, rarata mpu'u-mi hama'a ana' keledai tehoo' hi wiwi' ohea mohu' wobo' tomi. Karabongka-nami-rawo.
24646	41	11	5	Tauna to mokore hi ree mpekune' -ra: "Napa pai' nibongka keledai tetu-e?"
24647	41	11	6	Ratompoi' hewa to na'uli' -raka Yesus we'i. Mpo'epe toe, rapelele' wae-ramo mpokeni keledai toe.
24648	41	11	7	Karata-ra nculii', ralampii-mi keledai toe hante baju-ra, pai' mehawi' -imi Yesus.
24649	41	11	8	
24650	41	11	9	Hilou-ramo mpotoa' Yerusalem. Wori' tauna mpotuku' -ra. Ria-ra to meri'ulu, ria wo'o-ra to hi boko'. Wori' -ra mpokodo pohea-ra hi mata ohea to natara Yesus, pai' hantongo' wo'o-ra hilou mpo'ala' rau-rau kaju hi pampa pai' rakodo hi mata ohea, bona mpobila' -i. Tauna to wori' toera, ntora mogora-ra mpo'uli': Une' -imi Pue' Ala!" Pue' mpogane' Magau' to tumai mpokeni hanga' -na!"
24651	41	11	10	"Pue' mpogane' poparenta-na. Moparenta-i mpai' hewa ntu'a-ta owi, Magau' Daud." Une' -imi Pue' Ala to hi rala suruga!"
24652	41	11	11	Karata-na Yesus hi ngata Yerusalem, kaliliu mesua' -i hi rala Tomi Alata'ala. Napomonaa ntololikia-na mponaa omea. Oti toe, apa' neo' mobengi-mi, nculii' wo'o-imi hante ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua hilou turu hi ngata Betania.
24653	41	11	12	 Kamepulo-na, me'ongko' wo'o-ramo ngkai Betania lou hi Yerusalem. Hi ohea, mo'oro' -i Yesus.
24654	41	11	13	Molaa-pidi, nahilo-hawo hangkaju kaju ara to mobumu-damo rau-na-- hiaa' ko'ia tempo powuaa' -na. Hilou-imi hi kaju toe, pai' nanaa meka' ba ria wua' -na. Aga uma ria nau' hantakua.
24655	41	11	14	Toe pai' natotowi kaju toe, na'uli': "Ngkai eo toe lau, uma-pi ria mpai' haduaa tauna to mpokoni' wua' ngkai kaju toi!" Ana'guru-na mpo'epe lolita-na toe.
24656	41	11	15	Rata wo'o-ramo hi Yerusalem, hilou-imi Yesus hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala. Hi ree-i mpopalai tauna to mobabalu'. Nabilingko-raka meja' -meja' posulaa' -ra doi, pai' nabilingko wo'o pohuraa topobabalu' danci mangkebodo.
24657	41	11	16	Uma napiliu tauna mpokeni rewa ntara berewe Tomi Alata'ala toe.
24658	41	11	17	Natudui' -ra, na'uli': "Ha uma ni'incai napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'? Alata'ala mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Tomi-ku mpai' jadi' tomi posampayaa to rapake' tauna humalili' dunia'.' Hiaa' koi' -koina, niponcawa tomi toperampaki-di!"
24659	41	11	18	Kara'epe-na imam pangkeni pai' guru agama napa to nababehi Yesus toe, rapali' -mi akala-ra doko' mpopatehi-i. Koro' -ra, apa' hawe'ea tauna goe' mpo'epe tudui' -na.
24660	41	11	19	Neo' mobengi-mi, Yesus hante ana'guru-na malai ngkai ngata, lou turu hi Bulu' Zaitun.
24661	41	11	20	Kamepulo-na mepupulo ngkii-pidi, hilou wo'o-ramo hi Yerusalem. Hi lengko ohea, rahilo-rawo kaju ara to natotowi Yesus wengi, mate-mi, bangi rata hi rali' -na.
24662	41	11	21	Nakiwoi-mi Petrus lolita-na Yesus. Toe pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru! Hilo-dile kaju ara to nutotowi wengi-e, molaju-mi!"
24663	41	11	22	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mepangala' -mokoi hi Alata'ala!
24664	41	11	23	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Ane rapa' -na ria tauna to mpo'uli' -ki bulu' tohe'i: `Te'ongko' -moko, mengkanawu' hi rala tahi'!' bate majadi', asala neo' morara' nono-na pai' mepangala' mpu'u-i napa to na'uli' bate madupa'.
24665	41	11	24	Jadi', pe'epei lolita-ku toi: Ane mosampaya-koi mperapi' napa-napa, pangala' -mi-hana kanawai' -nimi Alata'ala napa to niperapi', pai' bate nitarima.
24666	41	11	25	"Pai' ane mosampaya-koi, ane ria to nipodaa' -ki doo-ni, ampungi-i ulu, bona Tuama-ni to hi suruga wo'o mpo'ampungi sala' -ni. ((
24667	41	11	26	Aga ane uma-di ni'ampungi doo-ni, wae wo'o Tuama-ni to hi suruga uma mpo'ampungi sala' -ni.))"
24668	41	11	27	 Rata wo'o-ramo Yesus pai' ana'guru-na hi Yerusalem. Nto'u-ra momako' -mako' hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala, rata-ra imam pangkeni, guru agama pai' pangkeni to Yahudi to ntani' -na.
24669	41	11	28	Mepekune' -ra hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Uli' -kakai, ngkaiapa huraa-nu mpobabehi hawe'ea tetu hi Tomi Alata'ala! Hema to mpowai' -ko kuasa hewa tetu-e?"
24670	41	11	29	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' wo'o, ria pompekunea' -ku hi koi'. Tompoi' -ka ulu, pai' lako' ku'uli' wo'o-kuwo kangkaiapa kuasa-ku mpobabehi hawe'ea toe lau.
24671	41	11	30	Ngkaiapa kuasa-na Yohanes Topeniu' mponiu' tauna? Ngkai Alata'ala-di, ba ngkai manusia' -di?"
24672	41	11	31	Momepololitai-ramo pangkeni to Yahudi toera, ra'uli': "Beiwa-tale' mpotompoi' -ie? Ane ta'uli' ngkai Alata'ala kuasa-na, na'uli' -taka mpai': `Ane wae, napa pai' uma-i nipangala'?'
24673	41	11	32	Hiaa' mokoro wo'o ane ta'uli' ngkai manusia' -wadi kuasa-na." Pangkeni to Yahudi toera me'eka' mporuge' Yohanes Topeniu', apa' mpoka'eka' -ra ntodea, apa' hawe'ea ntodea mpo'uli' Yohanes toe hadua nabi mpu'u.
24674	41	11	33	Jadi', ratompoi' -i: "Uma ki'incai." Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane wae, uma wo'o-kuwo ku'uli' -kokoi kangkaiapa kuasa-ku mpobabehi toe lau."
24675	41	12	1	 Oti toe Yesus mpololitai pangkeni to Yahudi toera hante lolita rapa', na'uli': "Ria hadua tauna to mpohu'ai bonea-na hante anggur. Nawala ntololikia-na, nakae tana' mpobabehi torobo' pompeaa' anggur, pai' natunya' pongko pompodooa. Oti toe, napewai' bonea-na rapobago hi ba hangkuja dua tauna, pai' hilou-imi hi ngata to molaa.
24676	41	12	2	Rata-mi tempo pohopua' wua' anggur, napahawa' hadua batua-na hilou mperapi' bagia-na hi to mpodoo bonea-na toera.
24677	41	12	3	Tapi' to mpodoo bonea toera mpohoko' batua-na, rapao' pai' rapopalai mara.
24678	41	12	4	Oti toe, pue' bonea mpahawa' tena hadua batua-na. Rata ria, rapao' wo'o-i-wadi-hawo, weho woo' -na, ralibui' ntarurua' pai' -i rapopalai.
24679	41	12	5	Ngkai ree, nahubui tena hadua batua-na. Rata ria, rapatehi lau-imi. Bate hewa toe-mi kehi-ra hi butu dua batua to napahawa': ria to raweba', ria to rapatehi.
24680	41	12	6	"Uma-pi hema to napahawa' pue' bonea toei, metoro hadua ana' woto-na to nape'ahi' -damo. Ka'omea-na napahawa' ana' -na toe hilou hi to mpodoo bonea-na, na'uli': `Bate rapengkorui-ile mpai'.'
24681	41	12	7	"Ntaa' we'i, to mpodoo bonea toera, mohawa' -ramo ra'uli': `Etu-mi tumai ana' -na, hi'a mpai' to jadi' pue' bonea toi-e. Kita tapatehi-i, bona bonea-na toi kita' -mi pue' -na.'
24682	41	12	8	Karahoko' -nami ana' toei, rapatehi pai' ratadi hi mali bonea."
24683	41	12	9	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka pangkeni to Yahudi: "Jadi', napa-mi to nababehi pue' bonea toei? Bate tumai-ile mpopatehi-ra to mpodoo bonea-na, pai' bonea-na nawai' -raka tau ntani' -na.
24684	41	12	10	Tantu nibasa-mi lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpolowa pesapuaka-ni hi Aku', hewa toi moni-na: `Watu to ratadi topowangu tomi, watu toe lau-mi to jadi' poko parawatu.
24685	41	12	11	Tohe'e majadi' ntuku' konoa Pue' Ala, uma mowo kalompe' -na hi poncilo-ta.'"
24686	41	12	12	Kara'epe-na pangkeni to Yahudi lolita-na Yesus tohe'e, doko' rahoko' -i apa' ra'inca kahira' -na to natoa' hante lolita rapa' toe. Aga uma-ra daho' mpohoko' -i, apa' mpoka'eka' -ra ntodea. Jadi', malai-ramo mpalahii-i.
24687	41	12	13	 Ngkai ree, pangkeni to Yahudi mpohubui ba hangkuja dua to Parisi pai' tauna to tono' hi Magau' Herodes hilou hi Yesus. Patuju-ra doko' mpahala'nawu' -i hante pompekunea' -ra.
24688	41	12	14	Karata-ra hi Yesus, ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, ki'inca Guru tau monoa'. Metudui' -ko hante kalonto' -lonto' -na mpo'uli' napa konoa Alata'ala hi manusia'. Uma nupengkorui ba hema-hema, apa' uma-ko mpelence tauna. Toe pai' kipekune' -ko: ntuku' atura agama-ta, ba ma'ala moto-ta mpobayari paja' hi Kaisar, ba uma-di? Kana tabayari, ba uma mingki' tabayari?"
24689	41	12	15	Na'inca Yesus patuju nono-ra to tewunii'. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' nipali' kahala'kedoa' pololita-kue? Keni pe' tumai doi to biasa nibayari-ki paja', doko' kuhilo."
24690	41	12	16	Ngkai ree, ratonu-miki hampepa' doi pera'. Na'uli': "Lence hema pai' hanga' hema to hi doi toi?" Ra'uli': "Lence pai' hanga' Kaisar."
24691	41	12	17	Na'uli': "Ane wae-di, wai' -ki Kaisar napa to masipato' rawai' -ki Kaisar. Pai' wai' -ki Alata'ala napa to masipato' rawai' -ki Alata'ala." Konce-ramo mpo'epe tompoi' -na toe.
24692	41	12	18	 Oti toe, ba hangkuja dua to Saduki rata hi Yesus. To Saduki toera, pangkeni agama Yahudi to mposapuaka tauna to mate tuwu' nculii' hi eo mpeno. Karata to Saduki toera, ra'uli' -ki Yesus:
24693	41	12	19	"Guru, nabi Musa mpo'uki' hi rala buku atura hewa toi: ane hadua tomane mate hiaa' uma-ki ria ana' -na, pudupuhe-na kana mpotobine balu-na bona ria-ki-hawo muli-na.
24694	41	12	20	Jadi', ria pitu to ntali ompi' paka' tomane. To ulumua' motobinei, mate-i uma ria ana' -na.
24695	41	12	21	Tu'ai-na mpotobine balu-na. Mate wo'o-i-wadi-hawo, hiaa' ko'ia-i mo'anai'. Wae wo'o to majadi' hi katolu-na,
24696	41	12	22	duu' rata hi kapitu-na. Mate omea-ramo hante uma ria ana' -ra. Ka'omea-na, mate wo'o-imi-hawo tobine toei.
24697	41	12	23	Jadi', hi eo mpeno, ane tuwu' nculii' mpu'u-di hawe'ea tomate-e, hema-ramo mpai' pue' tobine toei, apa' pitu-ramo to mpotobine-i."
24698	41	12	24	Na'uli' Yesus: "Sala' mpu'u pekiri-ni tetu-e, apa' uma nipaha ihi' Buku Tomoroli', uma wo'o ni'incai baraka' -na Alata'ala.
24699	41	12	25	Apa' ane tuwu' nculii' -ramo tauna to mate, katuwu' -ra hewa katuwu' mala'eka hi rala suruga, uma-rapa motobinei ba motomanei.
24700	41	12	26	Ha ko'ia ria nibasa lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpakanoto katuwu' -ra nculii' tomate-e? Hi rala buku Atura Musa, tabasa tutura-na beiwa Alata'ala mpololitai nabi Musa ngkai rala julumpu to jela'. Nto'u toe, Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub mahae-ramo mate. Aga nau' wae, Alata'ala mpo'uli' -ki Musa hewa toi: `Aku' toi-mi Alata'ala to napue' Abraham, Alata'ala to napue' Ishak, Alata'ala to napue' Yakub.'
24701	41	12	27	Jadi', ngkai lolita-na Alata'ala toe, monoto-mi ta'inca katuwu' -ra moto Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub. Apa' bela tauna to mate to mepue' hi Alata'ala, tauna to tuwu' -hana to mpopue' -i. Sala' rahi-koina pekiri-ni tetu-e."
24702	41	12	28	 Nto'u toe, hadua guru agama Yahudi rata hi Yesus. Na'epe pomehono' -ra to Saduki hante Yesus we'i, pai' na'uli' hi rala nono-na: "Lompe' mpu'u tompoi' -na Yesus tetui!" Toe pai' mepekune' wo'o-imi-hawo hi Yesus, na'uli': "Parenta to'uma to poko-na ngkai hawe'ea parenta?"
24703	41	12	29	Na'uli' Yesus: "Toi-mi parenta to poko-na: `Pe'epei-koi to Israel! Pue' -ta Pue' Alata'ala hadua-na-wadi.
24704	41	12	30	Kana tapoka'ahi' -i hante nono-ta mpu'u, tatonu hawe'ea katuwu' -ta hi Hi'a, tapoka'ahi' -i hudu inca-ta pai' hudu pakulea' -ta.'
24705	41	12	31	Pai' tohe'i-mi parenta karonyala-na: `Kana tapoka'ahi' doo-ta hewa pompoka'ahi' -ta woto-ta moto.' Uma ria parenta ntani' -na to meliu kabohe-na ngkai to ronyala tohe'i."
24706	41	12	32	Na'uli' -mi guru agama toei hi Yesus: "Makono mpu'u-di Guru! Makono lia to nu'uli' tetu-e. Pue' Ala bate hadua-na-wadi, uma ria ntani' -na.
24707	41	12	33	Pai' kana tapoka'ahi' -i hante nono-ta mpu'u, hante hawe'ea pekiri-ta pai' hudu pakulea' -ta. Pai' kana tapoka'ahi' doo-ta hewa woto-ta moto. Toe to meliu kalompe' -na ngkai hawe'ea porewua pai' rewa ntani' -na to tapopepue' hi Alata'ala."
24708	41	12	34	Na'epe Yesus kamonoto tompoi' -na tauna toei. Toe pai' na'uli' -ki: "Neo' jadi' ntodea hi rala Kamagaua' Alata'ala mpu'u-moko!" Ngkai ree, uma-pi hema to daho' mpekune' ba napa-napa hi Yesus.
24709	41	12	35	 Nto'u-na Yesus metudui' hi Tomi Alata'ala, na'uli': "Napa pai' guru agama mpo'uli' Magau' Topetolo' muli-na Magau' Daud?
24710	41	12	36	
24711	41	12	37	Hiaa' bo Daud moto mpokahangai' -i Pue' -na. Hante petete' Inoha' Tomoroli' Daud mpotompo'wiwi Magau' Topetolo' hewa toi: Pue' Ala mpo'uli' -ki Pue' -ku: `Mohura-moko hi mali ngka'ana-ku duu' -na kupopengkoru hawe'ea bali' -nu hi Iko.'
24712	41	12	38	Nto'u-na Yesus mpotudui' ntodea, na'uli' -raka: "Pelompehi-koi, neo' -koi mpenau' kehi-ra guru agama. Goe' -ra modao' mpopake' baju to moloe, pai' goe' -ra ane tauna hi wiwi' karajaa motingkua' mpotabe-ra.
24713	41	12	39	Goe' -ra rapopohura hi pohuraa karabilaa' hi tomi posampayaa. Goe' -ra ane rapopohura-ra hi pohuraa to lompe' hi posusaa'.
24714	41	12	40	Mpobagiu-ra tobine tobalu, pai' -ra mpohagoi tomi-ra. Rawunii' kadada'a gau' -ra tohe'e hante mosampaya rapomoloe-loe. Motomo lia mpai' huku' -ra."
24715	41	12	41	 Yesus mohura mohu' peti' pompunaa' doi pepue', pai' -i mponaa tauna to mpopuna' doi pepue' -ra hi rala-na. Wori' tauna to mo'ua' mpopuna' doi uma hangke-ngkedi'.
24716	41	12	42	Nto'u toe, rata wo'o-hawo hadua tobine tobalu to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -na, napuna' wo'o-hawo doi pepue' -na. To napuna' tohe'e, rompepa' doi ngkala, hangkedi' lia oli-na.
24717	41	12	43	Yesus mpokio' ana'guru-na pai' na'uli' -raka: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: tobalu to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -na tohe'e mai, meliu pewai' -na ngkai pewai' to rapuna' hawe'ea tau ntani' -na.
24718	41	12	44	Apa' hira' mewai' ngkai labi ka'uaa' -ra. Tapi' tobine toei, nau' hewa apa-mi kampe'ahii' -na, napewai' omea-mi to ria hi hi'a, nau' kakono-na to naparaluu-hawo hi katuwu' -na eo-eo-na."
24719	41	13	1	 Oti toe, malai-imi Yesus ngkai rala Tomi Alata'ala. Ria hadua ngkai ana'guru-na mpo'uli' -ki: "Guru, hilo mpu'u-konae' tomi toe-e! Hilo watu-na! Uma mowo kancola-na!"
24720	41	13	2	Na'uli' Yesus: "Nuhilo wa tomi to bohe toe-e lau? Uma mpai' ria hamehaa' watu to bate pomeduncu-na. Bate ragero omea mpai'."
24721	41	13	3	Oti toe, hilou-imi Yesus hi Bulu' Zaitun pai' -i mohura mposinyanyohi-ki Tomi Alata'ala. Petrus, Yakobus, Yohanes pai' Andreas tumai mpololitai-i nto'u uma ria tau ntani' -na.
24722	41	13	4	Ra'uli': "Uli' -kakai ba nto'uma kadupa' -na to nu'uli' toe-e we'i, pai' napa mpai' to jadi' tanda ane hawe'ea toe neo' madupa' -pi."
24723	41	13	5	 Na'uli' Yesus: "Pelompehi, neo' -koi ma'ala rabagiu.
24724	41	13	6	Apa' wori' mpai' tauna to mehupa' to mpo'uli' kahira' -na Magau' Topetolo', alaa-na wori' mpai' tauna to rabagiu.
24725	41	13	7	Mpo'epe-koi mpai' kareba panga'ea ngkai kalaa-na, ni'epe wo'o moni panga'ea to mohu'. Aga neo' me'eka', apa' hawe'ea toe kana jadi' ulu, tapi' kajadia' toe uma mpobatuai karata-nami kahudua dunia'.
24726	41	13	8	Nto'u toe mpai', wori' ngata mosipanga'ei, magau' hadua mpo'ewa magau' kahadua-na. Hiapa-apa ria linu pai' oro'. Aga hawe'ea toe lau lako' pontepu'ua-na-pidi, hewa pontodohaka hadua tobine to neo' mo'ana'.
24727	41	13	9	"Aga koi' tohe'i, mo'inga' -inga' -koi! Apa' koi' mpai' bate rahoko' pai' rakeni hi topohura agama. Raweba' -koi hi rala tomi posampayaa. Rabua' -koi hi topoparenta pai' hi magau' sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku'. Nto'u toe mpai', ria loga-ni mpo'uli' -raka pepangala' -ni hi Aku'.
24728	41	13	10	Pai' Kareba Lompe' kana raparata hi humalili' dunia' kako'ia-na Eo Kiama.
24729	41	13	11	Ane rahoko' -koi pai' rakeni hi topohura, neo' -koi me'eka' ba napa mpai' petompoi' -ni. Ane rata-damo tempo-ni mololita, uli' -mi-hana napa to natu'u Pue' Ala hi rala nono-ni. Apa' napa to ni'uli' nto'u toe, bela ngkai pekiri-ni moto. Lolita-ni tetu mehupa' ngkai Inoha' Tomoroli'.
24730	41	13	12	
24731	41	13	13	"Rata mpai' tempo-na hawe'ea tauna mpokahuku' -koi sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku'. Ria mpai' tauna to mpewai' ompi' -ra ba ana' -ra moto bona rapatehi sabana petuku' -ra hi Aku'. Ria wo'o ana' to mpo'ewa totu'a-ra pai' mpopatehi-ra. Aga tauna to tida mepangala' hi Aku' duu' hi ka'omea-na, mporata-ra kalompea' hi eo mpeno.
24732	41	13	14	 "Owi nabi Daniel mpolowa karata-na to rahanga' `Topegerohi to dada'a.' (Hema to mpobasa lolita pelowa toe, penotohi mpu'u batua-na!) Jadi', ane nihilo to nalowa Daniel toe mokore hi pokorea to ratagi-ki, agina tauna to mo'oha' hi Yudea metibo' hilou hi bulu' -na.
24733	41	13	15	Tauna to mohura hi parawa-na neo' -pi leba' mesua' hi rala tomi-na mpo'ala' ba napa-napa.
24734	41	13	16	Tauna to hi bonea, neo' -pi nculii' hi ngata mpo'ala' pohea-na. Kaliliu metibo'!
24735	41	13	17	Mpe'ahii' -ra mpai' tobine to nto'u-ra motina'i pai' to mpentii' ana' -ra nto'u toe, apa' mokoro mpai' petibo' -ra.
24736	41	13	18	Mekakae-koi hi Alata'ala bona eo petiboa' -ni toe neo' nto'u tempo lengi'.
24737	41	13	19	Apa' nto'u toe mpai' rata pesesa' to ko'ia ria hangkania jadi' ngkai lomo' -na Alata'ala mpajadi' dunia' rata tempo tohe'i, pai' uma wo'o-pi-hawo mpai' ria jadi' hi eo boko' -na.
24738	41	13	20	Aga naredehi moto mpai' Pue' Ala tempo kaparia toe, apa' ane uma naredehi tempo-na, bate uma ria haduaa to tuwu'. Jadi', apa' napoka'ahi' -ra tauna to napelihi pai' to napobagia, toe pai' naredehi mpai' tempo kaparia toe.
