24739	41	13	21	"Nto'u toe mpai', ane ria to mpo'uli' -kokoi: `Hilo, Magau' Topetolo' ohe'i-imi,' ba `Hilo, ohe'e-i mai Magau' Topetolo',' neo' nipangalai'.
24740	41	13	22	Apa' mehupa' mpai' wori' tauna to boa' to mpo'uli' kahira' -na Magau' Topetolo', ba to mpo'uli' kahira' -na nabi. Mpobabehi-ra tanda mekoncehi pai' tanda to mobaraka', bona mpobagiu-ra wori' tauna. Ane ke ma'ala, ntahawe' tauna to napelihi Alata'ala rabagiu wo'o.
24741	41	13	23	Aga koi' tohe'i, mo'inga' -inga' -koi! Ku'uli' ami' -mikokoi hawe'ea tohe'e kako'ia-na jadi'.
24742	41	13	24	
24743	41	13	25	"Jadi', nto'u toe mpai', ane timpaliu-pi tempo kaparia toe, hawe'ea anu to mobaraka' hi langi' ralengo. Eo mobali' mobengi, wula uma-pi mehini, betue' roda' ngkai langi'.
24744	41	13	26	Nto'u toe-damo mpai', hawe'ea tauna mpohilo-a, Aku' Ana' Manusia', mana'u tumai hi rala limu'. Uma mowo kabaraka' -ku pai' pehini-ku nto'u toe.
24745	41	13	27	Kuhubui mala'eka-ku hilou mporumpu tauna to kupobagia ngkai humalili' dunia', ngkai wuntu dunia' pai' ngkai wuntu langi'.
24746	41	13	28	 "Petonoi-koi napa to kutudui' -kokoi hante lolita rapa' kaju ara. Ane nihilo rau-na mela' pai' mohulu-i, ni'inca-mi kaneo' -na mara eo.
24747	41	13	29	Wae wo'o ane nihilo-damo kajadia' toe we'i lou, ni'inca-mi neo' madupa' mpu'u-mi to ku'uli' we'i.
24748	41	13	30	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hawe'ea toe we'i bate madupa' kako'ia-na mate omea tauna to tuwu' tempo toi.
24749	41	13	31	Langi' pai' dunia' mogero mpai', tapi' lolita-ku bate-bate-na duu' kahae-hae-na.
24750	41	13	32	"Aga ane eo pai' jaa kadupa' -na hawe'ea toe, muntu' Tuama-ku-wadi to mpo'inca. Uma ria to ntani' -na to mpo'inca. Bangku' mala'eka to hi suruga-hawoe', uma wo'o-rawo ra'incai. Bangku' Aku' Ana' -nae', uma wo'o-kuwo ku'incai.
24751	41	13	33	Toe pai' kana mo'inga' -inga' pai' mojaga-koi, apa' uma ni'incai tempo kadupa' -na.
24752	41	13	34	Ane rata nculii' -apa mpai', kajadi' -na hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i. Hadua pue' tomi mopatuju hilou hi ngata to molaa. Kako'ia-na me'ongko', nahubui pahawaa' -na mpewili' tomi-na, hore-hore nawai' -ra bago-ra. Hi tompodoo wobo' na'uli' -ki: `Mo'inga' -inga' -koe'!'
24753	41	13	35	
24754	41	13	36	Jadi', kana mo'inga' mpu'u-ra, apa' uma ra'incai ba nto'uma karata-na pue' tomi, ba ncimonou' -di ba ntongo' bengi-di ba mepulo ngkii ba nto'u eo mehupa'. Nee-neo' mpai' rata ncorobaa-imi pai' narata-ra bula-ra leta'. Wae wo'o kana mo'inga' -inga' -koi, apa' uma ni'incai nto'uma-a rata.
24755	41	13	37	Napa to ku'uli' -kokoi tohe'i, ku'uli' wo'o hi hawe'ea tauna: Mo'inga' -inga' -hawoe'!"
24756	41	14	1	 Ro'eo-damo rata-mi Eo Paskah pai' Posusa' Roti to uma Raragii. Imam pangkeni pai' guru agama bula-ra mpali' akala-ra mpolede Yesus bona rapatehi bongo-i.
24757	41	14	2	Ra'uli': "Aga neo' ulu tababehi nto'u eo bohe, nee-neo' mpai' bara' ntodea."
24758	41	14	3	Nto'u Yesus hi ngata Betania, hilou-i hi tomi hadua tauna to rahanga' Simon topohaki' poko'. Bula-na hi ree, rata hadua tobine ngkeni hameha' butolo' ihia' lana honga to masuli' lia oli-na, to rababehi ngkai rali' kaju to mohonga. Bula-na Yesus ngkoni', tobine toei mpopengka butolo' toe pai' natua hi woo' Yesus bona mpobila' -i.
24759	41	14	4	Ba hangkuja dua to hi ree, moroe-ra mpohilo napa to nababehi tobine toei. Momepololitai-ramo ra'uli': "Napa-mi-hawo kalaua-na lana honga rakerei mara hewa toe!
24760	41	14	5	Ke agina lau-pi-hawo rapobalu' nte oli tolu atu labi doi pera', pai' doi oli-na rawai' -raka tokabu." Toe pai' moroe-ra mpokaroe tobine toei.
24761	41	14	6	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Pelele' moto-i-hana. Napa pai' nipedahi nono-na? To nababehi hi Aku' toe-le, lompe'.
24762	41	14	7	Apa' tokabu-hana, ria oa' -ra dohe-ni. Ane dota-koi ntulungi-ra, ria oa' loga-ni. Aga Aku', uma-a mpai' ria oa' dohe-ni.
24763	41	14	8	Tobine toei mpobabehi napa to nakule' mpobabehi. Natuai-a hante lana honga mporodo ami' -mi woto-ku hi karatana-ku mpai', kako'ia-na rata tempo-na.
24764	41	14	9	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hi humalili' dunia', hiapa-apa Kareba Lompe' rapalele, napa to nababehi tobine toei bate ralolita, uma mpai' ralipo' -lipo'."
24765	41	14	10	Nto'u toe, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, to rahanga' Yudas Iskariot, hilou hi imam pangkeni, mpo'uli' -raka patuju-na mpobalu' Yesus hi hira'.
24766	41	14	11	Goe' -ramo mpo'epe patuju-na toe, pai' rajanci-ki rawai' -i doi. Ngkai ree, Yudas mpopali' loga to lompe' mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na.
24767	41	14	12	 Rata-mi eo to lomo' -na hi Posusa' Roti to Uma Raragii, nto'u bima Paskah rasumale'. Nto'u toe, ana'guru-na Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Hiapa-kai mporodo pongkoni' Paskah to takoni' -e mpai'? Hiapa konoa-nu?"
24768	41	14	13	Yesus mpohubui rodua ana'guru-na, na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi rala ngata. Ria mpai' to mpohirua' -kokoi hadua tomane to ngkeni pontomua' -na oti ntomu'. Tuku' -imi.
24769	41	14	14	Ane mesua' -i hi rala tomi, uli' -ki pue' tomi: `Na'uli' Guru: Hiapa-kuwo pobabehia-ku Posusa' Paskah hante ana'guru-ku?'
24770	41	14	15	Pue' tomi toe mpai' mpotudo' -kokoi hameha' kamar to hi lolo-na to bohe. Kamar toe teporodo ami' -mi, hono' -mi rewa-na. Hi retu-mokoi mpai' mporodo-taka pongkoni' Paskah-ta."
24771	41	14	16	Hilou mpu'u-ramo ana'guru-na to rodua toera mesua' rala ngata. Rarata mpu'u-mi hewa to na'uli' -raka, pai' -ra mporodo-mi pongkoni' Paskah.
24772	41	14	17	Mobengi-mi, rata-imi Yesus hante ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua.
24773	41	14	18	Bula-na mohura ngkoni', na'uli' -mi: "Pe'epei-koi: Ria hadua ngkai koi', to ngkoni' hante Aku' toe lau, to mpobalu' -a mpai' hi bali' -ku."
24774	41	14	19	Mpo'epe tohe'e, kapeda' -nami nono-ra ana'guru-na, pai' mepekune' -ramo hadua bo hadua hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Bela-hawo aku' to nutoa' -e Pue'?"
24775	41	14	20	Na'uli' Yesus: "To mpobalu' -ale, hadua ngkai koi' to hampulu' rodua tohe'i-e, to mpodulu' -ka.
24776	41	14	21	Makono mpu'u, Aku' Ana' Manusia' bate mate hewa to ralowa hi rala Buku Tomoroli' -e. Aga mpe'ahii' tauna to mpobalu' -a tetui. Ke lompe' lau-pi ane uma-i na'ote tina-na."
24777	41	14	22	Bula-ra ngkoni', na'ala' -mi Yesus roti pai' naposampayai, mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala. Oti toe, napihe-pihe pai' natonu-raka, na'uli': "Ala' -mi, koni' -mi. Toi-mi woto-ku."
24778	41	14	23	Oti toe na'ala' wo'o sangkiri' to ihia' anggur, na'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala pai' natonu-raka. Nginu omea-ramo ngkai sangkiri' toe.
24779	41	14	24	Na'uli' -raka: "Toi-mi raa' -ku to rabowo ane mate-a mpai' bona mpotolo' wori' tauna. Raa' -ku toi mporohoi pojanci to mpoposidai' Alata'ala hante manusia'.
24780	41	14	25	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: ntepu'u ngkai wae lau, uma-apa nginu anggur duu' -na rata tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Nto'u toe-damo mpai', pai' lako' ku'inu anggur to bo'u hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
24781	41	14	26	Oti toe, morona' -ramo hanyala rona' pe'une'. Kahudu-ra morona', malai-ramo ngkai ngata hilou hi Bulu' Zaitun.
24782	41	14	27	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Hawe'ea-ni mpai', molengo pepangala' -ni hi Aku', apa' ria te'uki' Lolita Alata'ala to mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Kupatehi topo'ewu toei, alaa-na bima-na pagaa' -gaa' -ramo.'
24783	41	14	28	Aga ane tuwu' nculii' -apa mpai', meri'ulu-a hilou hi tana' Galilea, bona hirua' hi ria-ta-damo mpai'."
24784	41	14	29	Na'uli' Petrus: "Nau' hawe'ea tauna molengo pepangala' -ra hi Iko Pue', aku' uma!"
24785	41	14	30	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -koko: Bengi toe mpai' lau, kako'ia-na turua' manu' karongkani-na, mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku."
24786	41	14	31	Aga hangkedi' kanaperohoi-na Petrus lolita-na, na'uli': "Nau' -a mate hangkaa-ngkania dohe-nu, uma mpu'u kusapu kaku'inca-nu!" Wae wo'o-rawo lolita-ra ana'guru-na to ntani' -na.
24787	41	14	32	 Rata-ramo hi pampa to rahanga' Getsemani. Hi ree na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Koi', mohura hi rei-mokoi mpopea-a, bula-ku hilou mosampaya."
24788	41	14	33	Aga Petrus, Yakobus pai' Yohanes nabawai hilou dohe-na. Nto'u toe pepa-mi na'epe pai' mokaratu-mi nono-na.
24789	41	14	34	Na'uli' -raka: "Susa' lia nono-ku, hewa to neo' mate-ama ku'epe. Rehe'i-mokoi ulu mojaga."
24790	41	14	35	Oti toe, hilou-imi molaa hangkedi', pai' -i motumpa hi tana' mosampaya. Rala posampaya-na merapi' -i bona ane ma'ala uma-i-hawo mporata kaparia toe.
24791	41	14	36	Na'uli': "Tuama-ku! Uma ria to uma majadi' ane Iko Mama mpo'uli'. Wi'iha-ka-kuwo kaparia to neo' mporumpa' -a toi. Aga bela konoa-ku Aku' to jadi', agina konoa-nu Iko moto."
24792	41	14	37	Oti toe, nculii' -imi hi ana'guru-na to tolu, narata-ra bula-ra leta' moto. Na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Simon! Ba leta' -dako-konae! Hajaa-wadi uma nudadahi mojaga?
24793	41	14	38	Mojaga pai' mosampaya-mokoi, bona neo' -koi mporata pesori. Hi rala nono-ni dota moto-koi mpobabehi to makono, aga uma nidadahi apa' manusia' bate lente."
24794	41	14	39	Ngkai ree, hilou wo'o-imi mosampaya. Posampaya-na toe hibalia hante posampaya-na to lomo' -na.
24795	41	14	40	Oti toe, nculii' wo'o-imi mporata ana'guru-na, leta' wo'o-ra-wadi apa' mopoke' rahi mata-ra. Nakehele-ra, aga uma-ra winihi apa' uma ra'incai ba napa to ra'uli' -ki.
24796	41	14	41	Hilou wo'o-imi mosampaya katolu ngkani-na, pai' oti toe, nculii' wo'o-imi hi ana'guru-na, na'uli' -raka: "Turu pai' leta' oa' -pada-koi? Naporae' -mi! Rata-mi tempo-na Aku' Ana' Manusia' rapobalu' pai' ratonu hi tauna to dada'a.
24797	41	14	42	Memata-mokoi! Hilo, etu-imi tumai to mpobalu' -a. Kita-mi lou."
24798	41	14	43	 Bula-na Yesus mololita-pidi, rata mpu'u-imi Yudas, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua. Pai' dohe-na wori' wo'o tau ntani' -na to ngkeni piho' pai' sumampu. Hira' toe rapahawa' imam pangkeni, guru agama pai' totu'a to Yahudi.
24799	41	14	44	Yudas mpo'uli' ami' -miraka tanda bona ra'inca kato'uma-nai Yesus, na'uli': "Hema mpai' to ku'eki, Hi'a-mi. Hoko' -imi, keni-i hilou, jaga lompe' -i."
24800	41	14	45	Jadi', karata-ra hi ree, kahilou-nami Yudas mpohirua' -ki Yesus, na'uli': "Guru!" pai' -i na'eki ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi.
24801	41	14	46	Katumai-rami tauna to wori' mpohoko' Yesus.
24802	41	14	47	Ngkai ree, hadua tauna to mokore mohu' Yesus mpowute' piho' -na natime-ki batua Imam Bohe, bela mpoholu tilinga-na.
24803	41	14	48	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka tauna to mpohoko' -i: "Ha toperampaki-a toi-e, pai' mingki' tumai-koi ntali piho' pai' sumampu mpohoko' -ae!
24804	41	14	49	Butu eo-na ria moto-a dohe-ni hi Tomi Alata'ala metudui', napa pai' uma-a nihoko' nto'u toe? Aga tohe'i kana jadi', bona madupa' -mi to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'."
24805	41	14	50	Ngkai ree, metibo' -ramo hawe'ea ana'guru-na mpalahii-i.
24806	41	14	51	Ria wo'o hadua kabilasa mpotuku' Yesus nto'u toe, motapui' -i-wadi hante abe' to bula. Ria-ra to doko' mpohoko' -i,
24807	41	14	52	toe pai' naroncu-mi abe' -na, pai' -i metibo' molawa.
24808	41	14	53	 Ngkai ree, Yesus rakeni hilou hi tomi Imam Bohe. Hi ria, morumpu-ramo hawe'ea imam pangkeni, guru agama pai' totu'a to Yahudi to ntani' -na.
24809	41	14	54	Petrus metuku' ngkawao-wadi, duu' -na rata hi berewe tomi Imam Bohe. Hi ria mohura-i moneru dohe topojaga.
24810	41	14	55	Nto'u toe, imam pangkeni pai' hawe'ea topohura agama mpali' sabi' to mpakilu Yesus, bona ngalai' rahuku' mate-i. Aga uma raruai' sala' -na.
24811	41	14	56	Wori' moto sabi' to mpopakilu-i, aga uma hibalia lolita-ra.
24812	41	14	57	Ria ba hangkuja dua to mokore pai' to mosabi' boa', ra'uli':
24813	41	14	58	"Tauna toii, ki'epe-i-kaina mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Kugero Tomi Alata'ala to nawangu manusia', pai' rala-na tolu eo kuwangu to ntani' -na, to bela manusia' mpowangu.'"
24814	41	14	59	Hiaa' posabi' -ra toe, uma wo'o-wadi hibalia.
24815	41	14	60	Kamokore-nami Imam Bohe hi nyanyoa hawe'ea topohura, pai' na'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ha uma nutompoi' -ra to mpakilu-ko toe-e?"
24816	41	14	61	Aga Yesus, uma-i winihi, uma-i metompoi' nau' hamelaa. Hangkani-pi Imam Bohe mpekune' -i: "Ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' Topetolo', Ana' Alata'ala to Moroli'?"
24817	41	14	62	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' -mi, pai' nihilo moto-a mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia', mohura pai' moparenta hi mali ka'ana Alata'ala to Mobaraka', pai' nihilo wo'o-a mana'u tumai ngkai suruga hi rala limu'."
24818	41	14	63	Mpo'epe toe we'i, Imam Bohe mpoheu' baju-na ngkai kamoroe-na, pai' na'uli': "Uma-pi mingki' ria sabi'!
24819	41	14	64	Ni'epe moto-mi-koiwo lolita-na mpokedi' Alata'ala. Beiwa-mi-koiwo kabotu' -ni?" Hibalia-mi kabotu' -ra omea, ra'uli': "Bate masala' -imile, kana rahuku' mate-i!"
24820	41	14	65	Ngkai ree, ria-ra to mpo'uelikui-i, ria wo'o to mpopo'ore' -i: rakaramuai lio-na, raweba' -i, pai' ra'uli' -ki: "Ee nabi! Pe'uli' pe' ba hema to mpoweba' -koe!" Topojaga wo'o-hawo, mehopo' wo'o-ramo-rawo.
24821	41	14	66	 Nto'u toe, Petrus hi berewe-pidi. Bula-na hi berewe toe, tumai hadua tobine topobago hi tomi Imam Bohe.
24822	41	14	67	Kampohilo-na Petrus moneru, nanaa-i pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ba iko wo'o-di hadua doo-na Yesus to Nazaret toei-e mai?"
24823	41	14	68	Aga nasapu Petrus, na'uli': "Uma ku'incai-i, pai' uma kupaha ba napa to nu'uli'!" Ngkai ree moderu' -imi hilou mohu' hi wobo' wala. Turua' -mi manu'.
24824	41	14	69	Pehilo wo'o-imi tobine toei, na'uli' -raka tauna to hi ree: "Hi'a tetu wo'o-di doo-na Yesus toei-e mai."
24825	41	14	70	Aga nasapu mperii wo'o-wadi Petrus. Uma mahae ngkai ree, tauna to mokore hi ree mpo'uli' wo'o-miki: "Iko mpu'u-di doo-nae! Apa' to Galilea wo'o-ko-kowo."
24826	41	14	71	Kamosumpa-nami Petrus mpotuna' woto-na, na'uli': "Uma mpu'u ku'incai tauna to ni'uli' tetui!"
24827	41	14	72	Nto'u toe, turua' -mi manu' karongkani-na. Nakiwoi-mi Petrus lolita-na Yesus ngone to mpo'uli' -ki: "Kako'ia-na turua' manu' karongkani-na, mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku." Kageo' -nami Petrus kaka'utu-utu.
24828	41	15	1	 Mepupulo ngkii, hawe'ea topohura agama nte imam pangkeni pai' guru agama pai' totu'a to Yahudi to ntani' -na, mohawa' wo'o-ramo. Rahoo' -imi Yesus, rakeni hilou rabua' hi Gubernur Pilatus.
24829	41	15	2	Mepekune' -i Pilatus: "Ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' to Yahudi-e?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae mpu'u, hewa to nu'uli' tetu."
24830	41	15	3	Wori' nyala pepakilu to raparata imam pangkeni hi Pilatus.
24831	41	15	4	Toe pai' mepekune' wo'o-i-pidi: "Uma-ko dota metompoi' -e? Wori' nyala-mi to raparata kehi-nu."
24832	41	15	5	Aga Yesus bate uma-pi winihi, alaa-na napokakonce mpu'u Pilatus.
24833	41	15	6	Butu eo bohe Paskah, Pilatus biasa-na mpobahaka hadua tauna to ratarungku', ba hema to raperapi' ntodea.
24834	41	15	7	Hi mpae toe, ria hi rala tarungku' hadua to me'ewa hi topoparenta, to rahanga' Barabas. Barabas pai' doo-na, ria-ramo mpopatehi tauna rala pe'ewa-ra hi topoparenta.
24835	41	15	8	Jadi', morumpu-ramo ntodea, raperapi' hi Pilatus bona nabahaka hadua to ratarungku' hewa to biasa nababehi butu mpae-na.
24836	41	15	9	Napekune' -ra: "Beiwa, dota-koi ane kubahaka-kokoi Magau' to Yahudi toii?"
24837	41	15	10	Pilatus mpo'uli' hewa toe, apa' na'inca ka'uma-na-hawo masala' -i Yesus; imam pangkeni mpotonu Yesus hi hi'a ngkai kamohingi' -ra-wadi.
24838	41	15	11	Aga imam pangkeni mpo'ukei' ntodea, ra'uli' -raka: "Perapi' -koi bona nabahaka-taka Barabas!" Merapi' Barabas mpu'u-ramo.
24839	41	15	12	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi Pilatus mpo'uli' -raka ntodea: "Ane rapa' -na Barabas to kubahaka-kokoi, kupopai-imi tauna to ni'uli' magau' -ni to Yahudi-e?"
24840	41	15	13	Pejeu' -rami ntodea, ra'uli': "Parika' -i!"
24841	41	15	14	Napekune' Pilatus: "Hiaa' napa sala' -na?" Rapesukui lau-mi mejeu': "Parika' -imi!"
24842	41	15	15	 Pilatus doko' ngala' nono ntodea, toe pai' nabahaka-miraka Barabas. Oti toe, nahubui-mi tantara-na mpoweba' Yesus pai' natonu-miraka bona raparika'.
24843	41	15	16	Oti toe, tantara mpokeni Yesus hilou hi po'ohaa' -ra to hi rala tomi Gubernur, pai' -ra mpokio' hawe'ea doo-ra tumai.
24844	41	15	17	Ra'uncoi' -imi hante baju to mperelei to hewa baju magau'. Rababehi hameha' songko ngkai walaa to morui to hewa songko magau', pai' rasongkoi-ki.
24845	41	15	18	Oti toe, pai' -i rapopo'ore', ra'uli' -ki: "Wori' tabe, Magau' to Yahudi!"
24846	41	15	19	Woo' -na rapao' hante lua', ra'uelikui-i, pai' motingkua' -ra ntani' hewa to mpobila' -i.
24847	41	15	20	Ka'oti-na rapopo'ore' hewa toe, raroncu-mi baju to mperelei-e we'i, pai' ra'uncoi' nculii' -imi pohea-na ami'. Oti toe, rakeni-imi hilou hi mali ngata bona raparika'.
24848	41	15	21	Hi lengko ohea, hirua' -ra hante hadua tauna to lako' rata hi ngata, pai' rapewuku-ki hi'a-mi mpopaha'a kaju parika' -na Yesus. Hanga' -na Simon to Kirene, tuama-ra hira' Aleksander pai' Rufus.
24849	41	15	22	 Ko'ia mahae, rata-ramo hi po'ohaa' to rahanga' Golgota, batua-na Bulu' Banga'woo'.
24850	41	15	23	Hi ree, Yesus rapopo'inui anggur to ragalo pokuli' to rahanga' mur, aga uma-i dota mpo'inu.
24851	41	15	24	Oti toe, tantara mpoparika' -i, pai' -ra mpobagi-bagi pohea-na hante mpotene' undi hewa pompenoa' -ra, ba hema-ra to mporata.
24852	41	15	25	Nto'u karaparika' -na toe, jaa sio mepulo.
24853	41	15	26	Hi kaju parika' -na hi ntoto woo' -na, ria ukia' to mpo'uli' napa to rapakilu-ki, hewa toi moni-na: MAGAU' TO YAHUDI.
24854	41	15	27	Ria wo'o rodua toperampaki raparika' dohe-na, hadua mali ka'ana-na hadua mali ki'ii-na. ((
24855	41	15	28	Jadi', napa to rababehi toe, madupa' -mi lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': "Magau' Topetolo' rapohewa tauna to dada'a."))
24856	41	15	29	Tauna to liu hi ree, ngkololi-ra mpopo'ore' -i, ra'uli': "Hahi Nu'uli' -kona mpogero-ko Tomi Alata'ala pai' nuwangu nculii' rala-na tolu eo!
24857	41	15	30	Ane wae-di, tulungi moto-mi woto-nu! Mana'u-moko ngkai kaju parika' tetu!"
24858	41	15	31	Wae wo'o imam pangkeni hante guru agama ntora mpopo'ore' -i. Momepololitai-ramo ra'uli': "Tau ntani' -na natulungi-ramo. Woto-na moto-pi uma nakulei' ntulungi.
24859	41	15	32	Hiaa' bo ra'uli' Hi'a Magau' Topetolo', Magau' to Israel! Ane tahilo mpu'u-i mana'u ngkai kaju parika' -na toe mai, lako' tapangala' -idi." Ntahawe' tauna to raparika' dohe-na, meruge' wo'o-ra-rawo.
24860	41	15	33	 Tebua' -mi eo, muu-mule' mobengi hobo' hi ngata toe rala-na tolu jaa.
24861	41	15	34	Jaa tolu ncimonou', mekio' -imi Yesus napasimuku mpo'uli': "Alata'ala-ku, Alata'ala-ku! Napa pai' nupalahii-a?" Hi rala basa Yahudi hewa toi moni-na: "Eloi, Eloi, lama sabakhtani?"
24862	41	15	35	Ba hangkuja dua to mokore mohu' hi kaju parika' -na mpo'epe pe'au-na toe, ra'uli': "Epe-dile! Mpokio' nabi Elia-i."
24863	41	15	36	Hadua mokeno hilou mpo'ala' hampu'u wunga to hewa lomo', nabangkahi hi rala ue anggur to mo'onco, natu'u hi wuntu hompea pai' napopoju'ui-ki Yesus bona na'inu. Na'uli': "Popea, tahilo ba tumai mpu'u-i Elia mpopana'u-i ngkai kaju parika'!"
24864	41	15	37	Ngkai ree, kame'au-nami Yesus napesukui, pai' modupe' -mi inoha' -na.
24865	41	15	38	Nto'u toe, kain porini-olo' to tetoe hi rala Tomi Alata'ala mobika' ntongo' ngkai lolo-na rata hi une' -na.
24866	41	15	39	Tadulako tantara to mokore mponyanyohi kaju parika' toe mpohilo beiwa kamate-na Yesus. Na'uli': "Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-i-tawo'!"
24867	41	15	40	Ria wo'o hi ree ba hangkuja dua tobine to menaa ngkawao. Hanga' -na to hadua, Maria Magdalena. To hadua wo'o, Maria tina-ra Yakobus to tu'ai pai' Yoses. Pai' hadua wo'o, Salome.
24868	41	15	41	Tobine toe-ramo to mpotuku' pai' mpotulungi Yesus bula-na hi tana' Galilea. Pai' wori' wo'o-pidi tobine to ntani' -na to mpotuku' Yesus tumai ngkai Galilea rata hi Yerusalem.
24869	41	15	42	 Eo karaparika' -na Yesus toe, eo pomporodoa, batua-na, eo kako'ia-na eo pepuea', pai' ntuku' ada to Yahudi ntepu'u ncimonou' toe, rapalii' -mi mobago. Jadi', neo' limpa-mi eo,
24870	41	15	43	tumai-mi hadua tauna to rahanga' Yusuf to Arimatea. Yusuf toei, hadua topohura agama Yahudi to rabila', mahae moto-imi-hana mpopea tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Yusuf mpedahoi' hilou hi Pilatus mperapi' woto-na Yesus.
24871	41	15	44	Konce-i Pilatus mpo'epe kasohi' -na mate Yesus. Toe pai' nakio' -mi tadulako tantara napompekunei' ba mahae-imi Yesus mate.
24872	41	15	45	Kana'epe-na Pilatus lolita tadulako tohe'e, napiliu-imi Yusuf mpo'ala' woto Yesus.
24873	41	15	46	Yusuf mpo'oli kain to bula bona nahompui' -ki. Napopana'u-mi woto-na ngkai kaju parika' pai' naputu' hante kain toe. Oti toe natu'u hi rala daeo' to ralonga' hi panapa bulu' watu, pai' naluli' hameha' watu na'unca-ki wobo' daeo' toe.
24874	41	15	47	Maria Magdalena pai' Maria tina-na Yoses mpetonoi kahiapa-na woto-na Yesus ratu'u.
24875	41	16	1	 Katimpaliu-na eo pepuea', Maria Magdalena, Maria tina-na Yakobus, pai' Salome, hilou-ra mpo'oli anu mohonga. Patuju-ra, doko' hilou mpolanai woto-na Yesus hante to mohonga toe.
24876	41	16	2	Jadi', mepupulo ngkii eo Mingku, lako' moweka', hilou-ramo hi daeo'.
24877	41	16	3	
24878	41	16	4	Hi lengko ohea momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Hema-mi-tawo to mpotulungi-ta mpoderu' watu po'unca wobo' daeo'?" Apa' watu toe ria bohe lia. Ntaa' we'i, karata-ra hi daeo', rahilo-rawo tederu' -mi watu.
24879	41	16	5	Pesua' -rami hi rala daeo', mpohilo-ra hadua kabilasa mohura tono' mali ka'ana-na, moheai hante pohea to bula. Konce tobine toera mpohilo-i.
24880	41	16	6	Na'uli' kabilasa toei: "Neo' -koi konce! Mpali' Yesus to Nazaret-koi, to mate raparika'. Tuwu' nculii' -imi! Uma-ipi ria hi rehe'i. Hilo karatu'ua-na wengi.
24881	41	16	7	Wae-e lau, hilou-mokoi, uli' -raka Petrus pai' ana'guru-na to ntani' -na katuwu' -na nculii' -mi. Uli' -raka hewa toi: Hilou meri'ulu-i hi tana' Galilea. Hi ria-damo mpai', pai' -i nihilo, hewa to oti na'uli' -kokoi wengi."
24882	41	16	8	Pehupa' -ra tobine toera ngkai rala daeo', pokeno-rami metibo', apa' wulunga pai' moridi' -ramo. Uma-ra ulu mpololitai hema-hema, apa' ngkai kame'eka' -ra.
24883	41	16	9	 Pemata-na Yesus ngkai kamatea mepupulo ngkii hi eo Mingku, lomo' -na mpopehuwu-i woto-na hi Maria Magdalena. Maria tohe'ei, ria-i Yesus mpopalai pitu seta to mpohawi' -i.
24884	41	16	10	
24885	41	16	11	Hilou-imi Maria hi topetuku' -na Yesus, narata-ra bula-ra geo' pai' peda' nono-ra. Na'uli' -raka: "Tuwu' nculii' -imi-hana Pue', kuhilo-imi we'i!" Aga uma raparasaya hawe'ea to najarita Maria toe.
24886	41	16	12	Oti toe, Yesus mpopehuwu wo'o-mi woto-na hi rodua topetuku' -na bula-ra mako' hilou hi mali ngata. Nto'u toe, lence-na mobali', alaa-na uma ra'incai Kayesus-na.
24887	41	16	13	Ponculi' -rami to rodua toera mpo'uli' -raka doo-ra kampohilo-ra Yesus. Aga uma wo'o raparasaya.
24888	41	16	14	 Ngkai ree, mehupa' wo'o-imi hi ana'guru-na to hampulu' hadua bula-ra ngkoni'. Nakamaro-ra apa' kura' pepangala' -ra pai' motu'a nono-ra. Nau' ria-mi tauna to mpohilo-i, uma oa' -ra dota mparasaya katuwu' -na nculii' mpu'u-imi.
24889	41	16	15	Na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi humalili' dunia', mpopalele Kareba Lompe' hi hawe'ea tauna.
24890	41	16	16	Hema to mepangala' pai' raniu', tehore-ra ngkai huku' jeko' -ra. Aga hema to uma mepangala' bate rahuku'.
24891	41	16	17	Pai' hema to mepangala', kuwai' -ra kuasa mpobabehi tanda-tanda to hewa toi: Hante hanga' -ku mpopalai-ra seta. Mololita-ra hante basa to uma ra'incai ngkai baraka' Inoha' Tomoroli'.
24892	41	16	18	Ria-ra to ngkamu ule, ba paia-na nginu rasu, aga uma moto-ra moapa. Mpojama-ra tauna to peda', bona mo'uri' -ra topeda'."
24893	41	16	19	 Ka'oti-na Pue' Yesus mpololitai-ra, te'ongko' -imi hilou hi suruga, pai' -i mohura hi mali ka'ana Alata'ala.
24894	41	16	20	Ngkai ree, topetuku' -na hilou mpopalele Kareba Lompe' hiapa-apa. Pue' mobago hangkaa-ngkania dohe-ra, pai' nawai' -ra kuasa mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi bona mporohoi kamakono-na Kareba to rakeni.
24895	42	1	1	 Teofilus to rabila': Wori' -mi tauna mperao mpo'uki' dala ngkatuwu' -na Yesus, hewa to jadi' ba hangkuja mpae to liu hi laintongo' -ta.
24896	42	1	2	To ra'uki' tohe'e, hibalia hante tutura to raparata-taka tauna to mpohilo mata moto-mi hawe'ea to jadi' toe ngkai lomo' -na pai' to jadi' pangkeni Lolita Pue'.
24897	42	1	3	Jadi', ka'oti-ku mpewulihi' hawe'ea-na ngkai tawu-na hante kanoto-noto-na, ku'uli' agina aku' wo'o-kuwo mpo'uki' tutura-na ntuku' pomeduncu-na.
24898	42	1	4	Patuju-ku, bona nu'inca kamakono-na mpu'u napa to oti-mi ratudui' -koko.
24899	42	1	5	 Nto'u Magau' Herodes moparenta hi tana' Yudea, ria hadua imam to rahanga' Zakharia. Zakharia toei, ngkai posantina imam muli Abia. Hanga' tobine-na, Elisabet, muli imam wo'o-i-hawo.
24900	42	1	6	Tau hancamoko toera, monoa' ingku-ra hi poncilo Alata'ala, apa' ratuku' hawe'ea parenta pai' atura Pue' hante uma ria kasalaia' -na.
24901	42	1	7	Aga uma-ra mo'anai', apa' Elisabet lalo, pai' tu'a-ramo roduaa-ra.
24902	42	1	8	Hangkani, megoli-mi tempo-na imam-imam muli Abia to mpokamu bago Alata'ala, pai' Zakharia mpobago bago imam hi Tomi Alata'ala.
24903	42	1	9	Ntuku' ada-ra, mpenoa' -ra ba hema-ra to rapelihi mesua' hi rala Tomi Alata'ala mpotunu dupa'. Zakharia-mi to mpela pompenoa' -ra.
24904	42	1	10	Jadi', bula ntodea mosampaya hi mali-na, Zakharia mesua' hi rala Tomi Alata'ala mpotunu dupa'.
24905	42	1	11	Nto'u toe, mehupa' -mi hadua mala'eka Pue' hi mali ngka'ana meja' pontunua dupa'.
24906	42	1	12	Kanahilo-na Zakharia mala'eka toei, konce pai' me'eka' lia-imi.
24907	42	1	13	Na'uli' mala'eka toei: "Zakharia, neo' -ko me'eka', apa' Pue' Ala mpo'epe pomperapia' -nu. Elisabet tobine-nu mo'ana' mpai', hadua ana' tomane. Ana' tetui kana nuhanga' Yohanes.
24908	42	1	14	Uma mpai' mowo kagoe' -nu mpokagoe' ana' -nu tetui. Wori' tauna mpokagoe' kaputu-na.
24909	42	1	15	Hi'a jadi' tau bohe hi poncilo Pue'. Uma-i ma'ala nginu anggur ba napa-napa to melanguhi, pai' Inoha' Tomoroli' mpokuasai-i ngkai lomo' kaputu-na.
24910	42	1	16	Wori' muli Israel natete' nculii' bona mepangala' -ra hi Alata'ala to rapue' ntu'a-ra owi.
24911	42	1	17	Ana' -nu tetui mpai' jadi' suro to mako' meri'ulu ngkai Pue' hante kuasa pai' kabaraka' -na nabi Elia owi. Napopohintuwu' ana' -ana' hante tuama-ra. Pai' tauna to uma mpotuku' Pue' natete' nculii' hi ohea to monoa' bona monoto nono-ra. Hawe'ea toe nababehi bona mporodo nono ntodea, bona sadia-ramo mpotarima Pue'."
24912	42	1	18	Na'uli' Zakharia mpo'uli' -ki mala'eka: "Hiaa', beiwa kaku'inca-na kamakono-na to nu'uli' tetu-e? Apa' tu'a-amadie, pai' tobine-ku tu'a wo'o-imi-hawo."
24913	42	1	19	Natompoi' mala'eka toei: "Aku' toi Gabriel, pahawaa' Alata'ala to ngkai suruga. Alata'ala mposuro-a tumai mpoparata-koko kareba toe.
24914	42	1	20	Napa to ku'uli' -koko toe we'i, bate madupa' ane rata-pi mpai' tempo-na. Aga iko-kona, apa' uma nuparasaya lolita-kue, wae-pi ngkai wae lau, uma-poko howa' mololita duu' -na madupa' mpu'u lolita-ku."
24915	42	1	21	Bula-na Zakharia hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, kapea-pea-ramo ntodea hi mali-na. Ingu' -ra apa' mahae rahi-i.
24916	42	1	22	Pehupa' -na hi mali-na, uma-ipi howa' mpololitai-ra. Muntu' mohuka' -i-damo pai' bate uma-i howa' mololita. Toe pai' ra'inca-mi ntodea karia-na to nahilo hi rala Tomi Alata'ala.
24917	42	1	23	Hudu-mi pobago-na Zakharia hi Tomi Alata'ala, nculii' -imi hilou hi tomi-na.
24918	42	1	24	Ko'ia mahae ngkai ree, motina'i mpu'u-imi Elisabet. Lima mula kahae-na Elisabet uma mehupa' -hupa' ngkai rala tomi-na, pai' na'uli':
24919	42	1	25	"Tohe'i-e ahi' -na Pue' hi aku'. Natulungi-a mo'anai', bona uma-apa me'ea' sabana kalalo-ku."
24920	42	1	26	 Kahono' -na ono mula Elisabet motina'i, Alata'ala mpohubui mala'eka Gabriel hilou hi tana' Galilea, hi ngata to rahanga' Nazaret,
24921	42	1	27	bona mpohirua' -ki hadua toronaa to rahanga' Maria. Toronaa toei, bula-na mokamae' hante hadua kabilasa to rahanga' Yusuf, muli Magau' Daud owi.
24922	42	1	28	Karata-na mala'eka hi ria, na'uli' -ki Maria: "Wori' tabe! Pue' mpogane' -ko pai' mpodohei-ko!"
24923	42	1	29	Konce-i Maria mpo'epe lolita mala'eka toei, pai' -i mopekiri ba napa batua petabe-na toe.
24924	42	1	30	Na'uli' wo'o-mi mala'eka: "Neo' -ko me'eka' Maria, apa' iko-mi to napokono Alata'ala bona mporata pegane' -na.
24925	42	1	31	Motina'i-ko mpai', pai' -ko mo'ana', hadua ana' tomane. Ana' tetu mpai' kana nuhanga' Yesus.
24926	42	1	32	Hi'a mpai' jadi' tauna to bohe tuwu' -na, pai' -i rahanga' Ana' Alata'ala to hi suruga. Pai' Pue' Alata'ala mpo'ongko' -i jadi' Magau', hewa Magau' Daud, ntu'a-na owi.
24927	42	1	33	Hi'a jadi' magau' to mpoparentai hawe'ea muli Yakub duu' kahae-hae-na, pai' poparenta-na uma ria kahudua-na."
24928	42	1	34	Na'uli' Maria mpo'uli' -ki mala'eka: "Beiwa-hawo kajadi' -na to nu'uli' tetu-e? Apa' ko'ia-a-kuwo motomanei."
24929	42	1	35	Na'uli' mala'eka: "Inoha' Tomoroli' mpai' mana'u hi iko, pai' kabaraka' Alata'ala to hi suruga ngkamoui-ko. Toe pai' ana' to putu toe mpai' rahanga' moroli', Ana' Alata'ala.
24930	42	1	36	Epe-dile: ompi' -nu Elisabet-ele, to tu'a lia-imi pai' to ra'uli' doo lalo-ie, motina'i ono mula-imi-hawo! Mo'ana' -i mpai', hadua ana' tomane.
24931	42	1	37	Apa' napa-napa to na'uli' Alata'ala bate kana madupa'."
24932	42	1	38	Na'uli' Maria: "Aku' toi batua-na Pue', mengkoru-ama hi hawa' -na, bona napadupa' patuju-na hi aku', hewa to nu'uli' -ka tetu." Oti toe, malai-imi mala'eka mpalahii Maria.
24933	42	1	39	 Ngkai ree, pe'ongko' -nami Maria hilou hi ngata to hi bulu' -na hi tana' Yudea.
24934	42	1	40	Karata-na hi tomi Zakharia, pesua' -nami pai' -i mpotabe Elisabet.
24935	42	1	41	Kana'epe-na Elisabet petabe-na Maria toe, pongkale-nami ana' to hi rala puanaka-na, pai' Elisabet, nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli' -imi.
24936	42	1	42	Mekio' -imi napesukui mpo'uli' -ki Maria: "Iko-mi-kona to nagane' Alata'ala meliu ngkai hawe'ea tobine ntani' -na, pai' Alata'ala mpogane' ana' to nupotina'i-ki tetu.
24937	42	1	43	Ha hema-a-kuwo aku' toi-e, pai' iko tina-na Pue' -ku tumai mpokinomo-a!
24938	42	1	44	Wae kaku'epe-na petabe-nu, ana' to hi rala-ku ncaliu mongkale nakeni kagoe' -na.
24939	42	1	45	Morasi' mpu'u-ko, apa' nupangala' lolita Pue', apa' napa to na'uli' -koko bate madupa'."
24940	42	1	46	Na'uli' Maria: Mpo'une' -a Pue' hante nono-ku mpu'u.
24941	42	1	47	Goe' lia-a, apa' Alata'ala Magau' Tompohore-a ngkai huku' jeko' -ku.
24942	42	1	48	Nakiwoi-awa-kuwo, aku' batua-na to mpe'ahii'. Ngkai wae lau, hawe'ea tauna mpo'uli' ka'aku' -na tobine to nagane' Alata'ala.
24943	42	1	49	Apa' Alata'ala to mokuasa mpopehuwu kabaraka' -na hi aku'. Moroli' hanga' -na!
24944	42	1	50	Ma'ahi' -i hi hawe'ea tauna to mengkoru hi Hi'a, duu' rata hi muli-muli-ra.
24945	42	1	51	Nababehi anu mobaraka' hante kuasa-na: Tauna to molangko nono-ra nagaro' bona uma oko patuju-ra.
24946	42	1	52	Magau' -magau' napohu ngkai pangka' -ra. Tauna to dingki' tuwu' -ra napomolangko.
24947	42	1	53	Tauna to mo'oro' nabohui hante pongkoni' to lompe'. Tauna topo'ua' napopalai hante ngkeni woto mara.
24948	42	1	54	
24949	42	1	55	Napopohiloi ahi' -na hi kita' muli Israel, batua-na owi. Natulungi-ta hewa to najanci hi ntu'a-ta owi. Uma nalipo' pojanci-na hi Abraham pai' hi muli-na duu' kahae-hae-na."
24950	42	1	56	Ba tolu mula kahae-na Maria mo'oha' hante Elisabet, pai' lako' nculii' -idi hilou hi tomi-na.
24951	42	1	57	 Rata-mi tempo-na Elisabet mo'ana'. Mo'ana' mpu'u-imi, hadua ana' tomane.
24952	42	1	58	Tongki-ra pai' ompi' -ra mpo'epe beiwa Pue' mpopohiloi ahi' -na hi Elisabet hi kanawai' -na ana' -na toe, toe pai' goe' wo'o-ramo-rawo hangkaa-ngkania hante Elisabet.
24953	42	1	59	Ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi, kahono' -na walu eo umuru-na ana' toei, tumai-ramo tongki pai' ompi' -ra mpotini' -i ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi. Patuju-ra doko' mpohanga' -i Zakharia, mpongkona' -ki tuama-na moto, ntuku' ada-ra.
24954	42	1	60	Tapi' na'uli' Elisabet mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' waetu! Bate Yohanes hanga' -na."
24955	42	1	61	Hampetompoi' -ra: "Hiaa' bo uma-hanale ria ompi' -ni to rahanga' tetu-e!"
24956	42	1	62	Ngkai ree, rahuka' -ki Zakharia rapompekunei' ba napa to doko' nahanga' -ki ana' -na.
24957	42	1	63	Zakharia mperapi' hameha' po'ukia' pai' na'uki': "Hanga' -na Yohanes." Konce omea-ramo.
24958	42	1	64	Nto'u toe, muu-mule' howa' nculii' -imi mololita, pai' -i mpo'une' -une' Alata'ala.
24959	42	1	65	Me'eka' omea-ramo tongki-ra, pai' kareba toe molele hobo' hi bulu' -na Yudea.
24960	42	1	66	Hawe'ea to mpo'epe kareba toe mokanono, ra'uli': "Ha jadi' napa-i mpai' ana' toei?" Apa' Pue' mpodohei-i hante baraka' -na.
24961	42	1	67	 Ane Zakharia, tuama ana' toei, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpokuasai-i, pai' -i mpohowa' lolita Alata'ala, na'uli':
24962	42	1	68	"Mai-tamo kita' muli Israel, mpo'une' Alata'ala Pue' -ta! Apa' hompo-imi tumai mpotulungi-ta kita' ntodea-na. Tumai-i mpobahaka-ta ngkai bali' -ta.
24963	42	1	69	Nawai' -tamo Tadulako to mobaraka' to mpokeni kalompea'. Tadulako toei, muli Magau' Daud, batua-na owi.
24964	42	1	70	Ngkai owi hante wiwi nabi-nabi to moroli', Pue' mpojanci
24965	42	1	71	kanabahaka-ta mpai' ngkai bali' -ta, nabahaka-ta ngkai kuasa-ra to mpokahuku' -ta.
24966	42	1	72	Napopohiloi mpu'u-mi ahi' -na hi ntu'a-ta owi. Napadupa' -mi janci-na to moroli'.
24967	42	1	73	
24968	42	1	74	Mojanci pai' mosumpa-i hi Abraham ntu'a-ta owi, kanabahaka-ta ngkai kuasa bali' -ta, bona ma'ala-ta mpopue' -i hante uma ria ka'ekaa' -ta,
24969	42	1	75	bona kita' jadi' topetuku' -na to moroli' pai' to monoa' hi poncilo-na, duu' kahae-hae-na.
24970	42	1	76	Hiaa' ane iko, ana' -ku, iko mpai' rahanga' nabi Pue' Ala to hi suruga. Apa' iko-mi mpai' to mako' meri'ulu ngkai Pue', bona mporodo ohea-na.
24971	42	1	77	Iko mpai' to mpopo'incai ntodea-na ohea bona Alata'ala mpowai' -ra kalompea' pai' mpo'ampungi jeko' -ra.
24972	42	1	78	Apa' ma'ahi' lia Alata'ala Pue' -ta. Toe pai' hompo-imi tumai mpotulungi-ta. Tumai-i ngkai suruga hewa eo mebere'.
24973	42	1	79	Tumai-i mpobajahi nono tauna to hi rala kabengia-na pai' to me'eka' mpoka'eka' kamatea. Natete' -ta hi ohea to mpotoa' kalompea' tuwu'."
24974	42	1	80	Ana' Zakharia toei, kaboo-bohea kamonoo-notoa nono-na. Mo'oha' -i hi papada to wao', duu' -na rata tempo-na natepu'u-mi mpokeni Lolita Pue' hi muli Israel.
24975	42	2	1	 Nto'u toe, rata hawa' ngkai Kaisar Agustus, mpohawai' bona hawe'ea tauna hi humalili' kamagaua' Roma ra'uki' hanga' -ra bona ra'inca kadea-ra.
24976	42	2	2	Pobilaa' tauna to lomo' -na tohe'i rababehi nto'u-na Kirenius jadi' gubernur hi tana' Siria.
24977	42	2	3	Hawe'ea tauna hilou mpope'uki' hanga' -ra, hore-hore hi ngata totu'a-ra.
24978	42	2	4	
24979	42	2	5	Wae wo'o Yusuf me'ongko' ngkai ngata Nazaret, mpo'ema' Maria kamae' -na to bula-na motina'i-mi. Me'ongko' -ramo ngkai tana' Galilea, manake' hilou hi tana' Yudea, mpotoa' ngata Betlehem, ngata kaputua Magau' Daud owi. Yusuf kana mpope'uki' hanga' -na hi ria, apa' hi'a muli Magau' Daud.
24980	42	2	6	Nto'u-ra hi Betlehem toe, rata-mi tempo-na Maria mo'ana'.
24981	42	2	7	Mo'ana' mpu'u-imi, hadua ana' tomane, ana' ulumua' -na. Ana' -na toei naputu' pai' napopoturu hi rala paiwa', apa' ihia' -mi tomi torata.
24982	42	2	8	 Hi mali ngata Betlehem, ria ba hangkuja dua topo'ewu. Bula-ra mpodoo bima-ra hi papada ngkabengia toe,
24983	42	2	9	muu-mule' mehupa' -mi hadua mala'eka Pue' mpohirua' -raka, pai' kabaraka' Pue' mehini mpohinii-ra, alaa-na me'eka' lia-ramo.
24984	42	2	10	Na'uli' mala'eka toei mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' -koi me'eka', apa' katumai-ku toi mpokeni kareba lompe' hi koi', kareba to mpakagoe' lia hawe'ea tauna.
24985	42	2	11	Eo toe lau hi ngata Magau' Daud, putu-mi Magau' Tompohore-koi ngkai huku' jeko' -ni, Hi'a-mi Kristus, Pue'.
24986	42	2	12	Toi-mi pompetonoi-na bona ni'inca kamakono-na lolita-ku: mporua' -koi mpai' hadua ana'lei raputu' pai' rapopoturu hi rala paiwa'."
24987	42	2	13	Hampinisi mata mehupa' wo'o-mi wori' mala'eka to ngkai suruga dohe mala'eka to lomo' -na we'i. Mpo'une' -ra Alata'ala, ra'uli':
24988	42	2	14	"Mai-tamo mpo'une' Alata'ala to hi suruga! Pai' hi dunia', tauna to napokono mporata kalompea' tuwu'."
24989	42	2	15	Ngkai ree, nculii' -ramo mala'eka hilou hi suruga, pai' mohawa' -ramo topo'ewu toera, ra'uli': "Kita-mi hilou hi Betlehem mpohilo kajadia' to na'uli' -taka Pue'."
24990	42	2	16	Kahilou-rami, pai' rarua' mpu'u-mi Maria pai' Yusuf, hante ana'lei-ra to turu hi rala paiwa'.
24991	42	2	17	Karahilo-na ana' toei, ralolita-mi napa to na'uli' -raka mala'eka mpotompo'wiwi-i.
24992	42	2	18	Konce omea tauna to mpo'epe lolita topo'ewu toera.
24993	42	2	19	Aga Maria mpotimamahi hawe'ea to jadi' toe hi rala nono-na, pai' ntora napenonoi.
24994	42	2	20	Nculii' -ramo topo'ewu toera, pai' halengko ohea mpo'une' pai' mpobila' Alata'ala-ramo, apa' hawe'ea to ra'epe pai' to rahilo, bate hewa to na'uli' -raka mala'eka.
24995	42	2	21	 Ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi, kahono' -na walu eo umuru-na, Ana' toei ratini' pai' rahanga' -i Yesus, hanga' to nahanga' -ki mala'eka kako'ia-na napotina'i-ki tina-na.
24996	42	2	22	Oti toe, rata-mi tempo-na Yusuf pai' Maria kana mpobabehi ada ka'oti-na mo'ana', ntuku' Atura Pue' to na'uki' Musa. Nto'u toe, ana'lei-ra toe rakeni hilou hi Yerusalem bona ratonu hi Pue',
24997	42	2	23	hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Atura Pue': "Butu dua ana' tomane to ulumua' kana ratonu hi Pue' bona jadi' bagia-na."
24998	42	2	24	Rakeni wo'o pepue' -ra, ntuku' hawa' to te'uki' hi rala Buku Atura Pue': hamoko korokou ba roma'a ana' mangkebodo.
24999	42	2	25	 Hi Yerusalem nto'u toe, ria hadua tauna to rahanga' Simeon. Simeon toei, tau monoa' to mengkoru hi Alata'ala. Inoha' Tomoroli' mpodohei-i, pai' -i ncarumaka kaneo' -na rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala mpotulungi muli Israel.
25000	42	2	26	Hangkani, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpo'uli' -ki hewa toi: "Ko'ia-ko mate ane ko'ia nuhiloi Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Pue' Ala."
25001	42	2	27	Jadi', nto'u-na Yusuf pai' Maria mpokeni Yesus ana'lei-ra hi Tomi Alata'ala bona ratonu hi Alata'ala ntuku' Atura Musa, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpopakeni Simeon mesua' hi Tomi Alata'ala.
25002	42	2	28	Kana'ala' -nami ana'lei toei, napanawi pai' -i mpo'une' Alata'ala, na'uli':
25003	42	2	29	"O Pue', nau' mate-ama, uma-pi beiwa. Oha-mi nono-ku, apa' madupa' -mi janci-nu.
25004	42	2	30	Hante mata-ku moto-mi mpohilo Topetolo' to ngkai Iko Pue',
25005	42	2	31	to nuporodo hi hawe'ea manusia'.
25006	42	2	32	Topetolo' toei, hewa baja to mponotohi nono tauna to bela-ra muli Israel. Pai' -i mpokeni karabilaa' hi kai' muli Israel to nupobagia."
25007	42	2	33	Tina pai' tuama ana' toei konce mpo'epe lolita Simeon mpotompo'wiwi ana' -ra.
25008	42	2	34	Simeon mpogane' -ra, pai' na'uli' -ki Maria: "Ngkai Ana' -nu toii, wori' mpai' muli Israel monawu' mporata silaka, aga wori' wo'o to tehore bona mporata kalompea'. Hi'a-mi to napelihi pai' nasuro tumai Pue' Ala, aga wori' tauna mposapuaka-i mpai',
25009	42	2	35	alaa-na telohu-mi ihi' nono-ra. Hiaa' iko Maria, narumpa' -ko-hana mpai' kasusaa' nono, hewa to rajalo piho'."
25010	42	2	36	
25011	42	2	37	Nto'u karata-ra Yusuf pai' Maria hi Tomi Alata'ala toe, ria wo'o-hawo hi ree hadua nabi tobine to tu'a lia-mi. Hanga' -na Hana, ana' Fanuel, ngkai posantina-na Asyer. Nto'u toe, umuru-na walu mpulu' opo' mpae. Pitu mpae-i-wadi motomanei. Ngkai ree, balu-imi pai' uma-ipi motomanei. Tida oa' -i hi Tomi Alata'ala, hi eo-na hi bengi-na ntora mosampaya pai' mopuasa' -i mepue' hi Pue' Ala.
25012	42	2	38	Jadi', nto'u Yusuf pai' Maria hi Tomi Alata'ala toe, rata wo'o-imi-hawo Hana, mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala, pai' ntora mpotompo'wiwi Ana' toei hi hawe'ea tauna to mpopea tempo-na Alata'ala mpobahaka to Yerusalem ngkai bali' -ra.
25013	42	2	39	Ka'oti-ra Yusuf pai' Maria mpobabehi hawe'ea to ratuntu' hi rala Buku Atura Pue', nculii' -ramo hilou hi ngata Nazaret hi tana' Galilea.
25014	42	2	40	Ana' -ra toei, kaboo-bohea pai' karoo-rohoa. Monoto lia nono-na, pai' Alata'ala mpogane' -i.
25015	42	2	41	 Butu mpae-na, tina pai' tuama-na Yesus hilou hi Yerusalem mpokaralai eo bohe to Yahudi to rahanga' Eo Paskah.
25016	42	2	42	Hono' -mi hampulu' rompae umuru-na Yesus, hilou wo'o-ramo ngkaralai eo bohe toe hewa kabiasaa-ra.
25017	42	2	43	Katimpaliu-na eo bohe toe, nculii' -ramo hilou mpotoa' ngata-ra. Aga Yesus-hana, uma-i mpotuku' -ra. Hi ria-i-pidi hi Yerusalem, aga uma ra'incai totu'a-na.
25018	42	2	44	Ra'uli' -rawo, metuku' moto-i dohe doo hampomakoa' -ra. Ha'eo-ramo momako', lako' rapali' -idi hi doo-ra pai' ompi' -ra.
25019	42	2	45	Aga uma-i raruai'. Toe pai' nculii' -ra hi Yerusalem mpopali' -i.
25020	42	2	46	Tolu eo-ramo mepali', lako' rarua' -idi hi Tomi Alata'ala. Mohura-i hi laintongo' guru agama, mpe'epei pai' mepekune'.
25021	42	2	47	Hawe'ea tauna to mpo'epe-i mpo'uli': "Uma mowo kapante-nae'! Uma mowo kamonoto tompoi' -na!"
25022	42	2	48	Konce tina pai' tuama-na mpohilo-i. Na'uli' tina-na: "Uto', napa-di-kona pai' nupohewa toe-kaie! Kai' tuama-nu, sese' -kai mpopali' -ko!"
25023	42	2	49	Na'uli' -raka: "Ha napa pai' nipali' -a? Ha uma ni'incai kana hi rala tomi Tuama-kua?"
25024	42	2	50	Tapi' uma rapaha batua lolita-na.
25025	42	2	51	Oti toe, hidohea-ramo nculii' hilou hi Nazaret, pai' bate mengkoru-i hi hawa' tina pai' tuama-na. Tina-na mpotimamahi hawe'ea to jadi' toe hi rala nono-na.
25026	42	2	52	Yesus kaboo-bohea pai' kamonoo-notoa nono-na. Alata'ala mpokono-i, wae wo'o manusia'.
25027	42	3	1	 Hi kahampulu' lima mpae-na poparenta Kaisar Tiberius hi ngata Roma, Pontius Pilatus jadi' gubernur hi tana' Yudea pai' Herodes Antipas to moparenta hi Galilea. Filipus ompi' -na Herodes moparenta hi Iturea pai' hi Trakhonitis, pai' Lisanias moparenta hi Abilene.
25028	42	3	2	To jadi' Imam Bohe nto'u toe, Hanas pai' Kayafas. Hi mpae tohe'e, Alata'ala mpoparata lolita-na hi Yohanes ana' Zakharia hi papada to wao'.
25029	42	3	3	Jadi', momako' -imi Yohanes mure' -nca'u ue Yordan mpoparata Lolita Alata'ala hi ntodea, na'uli': "Medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, pai' kana tumai-koi kuniu', bona Alata'ala mpo'ampungi jeko' -ni."
25030	42	3	4	Yohanes toei mpopadupa' napa to te'uki' hi rala sura nabi Yesaya owi, moni-na hewa toi: Ria tauna to mekio' hi papada to wao', na'uli': `Neo' rata-imi Pue'! Porodo ami' -miki ohea-na! Nipakalempe ami' -mi ohea to natara mpai'!
25031	42	3	5	To lobu' -na kana ra'ihii', to molangko pai' to pabulu' -bulu' kana rapohimpaya'. To pahiku-hiku rapomonoa', pai' to moloke' -loke' rapokalempe.
25032	42	3	6	Oti toe, hawe'ea manusia' mpohilo Alata'ala mpohore ntodea-na ngkai jeko' -ra.'"
25033	42	3	7	Wori' tauna tumai mpopeniu' hi Yohanes. Na'uli' Yohanes mpo'uli' -raka: "He koi' to bengku' gau' -ni! Napa pai' tumai-koie? Ba ni'uli' -koina, ma'ala mpai' nipasalewa roe Pue' Ala to neo' mporumpa' -koi?
25034	42	3	8	Ane bongko medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, babehi-mokoi gau' to lompe'. Pai' neo' nipoperaha kamuli-na Abraham-koi! Bona ni'inca: muli Abraham bisa napajadi' Alata'ala ngkai watu-watu toe lau.
25035	42	3	9	Neo' rata-mi pehuku' Alata'ala! Pehuku' -na hewa pati to rodo ami' -mi hi tawu kaju. Butu ngkaju-na to uma lompe' wua' -na, bate ratoki pai' ratene' hi rala apu."
25036	42	3	10	Ntodea mpekune' Yohanes, ra'uli': "Ane wae, napa-kaiwo to kana kibabehi?"
25037	42	3	11	Na'uli' Yohanes: "Hema-koi to rontonga' baju-ni, hantonga' wai' -raka-rawo to uma nakariai. Pai' tauna to ria pongkoni' -ra, bagii-ra-rawo to uma ria pongkoni' -ra."
25038	42	3	12	Rata wo'o-ra-rawo topesingara' paja' mpopeniu' hi Yohanes. Mepekune' -ra, ra'uli': "Guru, napa-kaiwo to kana kibabehi-e?"
25039	42	3	13	Natompoi' -ra: "Neo' -koi mesingara' melabi ngkai to rapakatantu topoparenta."
25040	42	3	14	Rata wo'o-ra-rawo tantara mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Hiaa' beiwa wo'o-ka-kaiwo kai'! Napa-kaiwo to kana kibabehi-e?" Na'uli' -raka: "Neo' -koi mporampaki rewa doo, pai' neo' mpo'ekahi ntodea bona rawai' -koi doi. Hangkuja-mi-hawo gaji' -ni, tarima-mi hante kagoea' nono."
25041	42	3	15	 Nto'u toe, ntodea ntora mpopea karata-na Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Alata'ala. Hawe'ea-ra mepekune' hi rala nono-ra, meka' ba lue' Yohanes lau-mi Magau' Topetolo' to rapopea toe.
25042	42	3	16	Toe pai' Yohanes mpo'uli' -raka omea: "Ane aku' -le, mponiu' -koi hante ue-wadi, tanda kamedea-ni ngkai jeko' -ni. Tapi' tumai-i mpai' to meliu kuasa-na ngkai aku'. Bangku' jadi' pahawaa' -na to mpobongka koloro sapatu' -na, uma-a-kuwo natao. Hi'a mpai' to mponiu' -koi hante Inoha' Tomoroli' pai' hante apu.
25043	42	3	17	Hi'a ma'ala rarapai' -ki tauna to mpowiri' pae. Nagaa' pae to mo'ihi ngkai to lopa' -na duu' -na me'itu'. Pae to mo'ihi napuna' hi rala wilulu-na, pai' to lopa' -na nasuwe hi rala apu to jela' ncuu duu' kahae-hae-na."
25044	42	3	18	Hewa toei Yohanes mpokeni Kareba Lompe' hi ntodea, pai' naparesai' -ra nte wori' nyala tudui' -na.
25045	42	3	19	Pai' nakamaro wo'o kasalaa' -na Herodes Antipas, topoparenta hi tana' Galilea, apa' Herodes mpo'ago pai' mpotobine Herodias, tobine ompi' -na moto. Yohanes mpokamaro-i sabana gau' -na toe, pai' sabana hawe'ea gau' -na to dada'a ntani' -na.
25046	42	3	20	Jadi', kana'epe-na Herodes pekamaro Yohanes toe, uma-di nabalii' gau' -na to dada'a, nadonihii lau-di: nahoko' lau-imi Yohanes pai' -i natarungku'.
25047	42	3	21	 Kako'ia-na Yohanes ratarungku', bula-na meniu' -pidi mponiu' ntodea, Yesus wo'o-hawo tumai mpopeniu'. Ka'oti-nai raniu', bula-na mosampaya, muu-mule' tebea-mi langi',
25048	42	3	22	pai' Inoha' Tomoroli' mana'u tumai dungku hi Yesus, lence-na hewa danci mangkebodo. Pai' Alata'ala mololita ngkai suruga mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Iko toi-mi Ana' -ku to kupe'ahi'. Iko-mi to mpakagoe' nono-ku."
25049	42	3	23	Nto'u umuru Yesus kira-kira tolu mpulu' mpae, natepu'u-mi pobago-na. Ntuku' pomporataa tauna, Yesus ana' Yusuf, Yusuf ana' Eli,
25050	42	3	24	Eli ana' Matat, Matat ana' Lewi, Lewi ana' Malkhi, Malkhi ana' Yanai, Yanai ana' Yusuf,
25051	42	3	25	Yusuf ana' Matica, Matica ana' Amos, Amos ana' Nahum, Nahum ana' Hesli, Hesli ana' Nagai,
25052	42	3	26	Nagai ana' Maat, Maat ana' Matica, Matica ana' Simei, Simei ana' Yosekh, Yosekh ana' Yoda,
25053	42	3	27	Yoda ana' Yohanan, Yohanan ana' Resa, Resa ana' Zerubabel, Zerubabel ana' Sealtiel, Sealtiel ana' Neri,
25054	42	3	28	Neri ana' Malkhi, Malkhi ana' Adi, Adi ana' Kosam, Kosam ana' Elmadam, Elmadam ana' Er,
25055	42	3	29	Er ana' Yesua, Yesua ana' Eliezer, Eliezer ana' Yorim, Yorim ana' Matat, Matat ana' Lewi,
25056	42	3	30	Lewi ana' Simeon, Simeon ana' Yehuda, Yehuda ana' Yusuf, Yusuf ana' Yonam, Yonam ana' Elyakim,
25057	42	3	31	Elyakim ana' Melea, Melea ana' Mina, Mina ana' Matata, Matata ana' Natan, Natan ana' Daud,
25058	42	3	32	Daud ana' Isai, Isai ana' Obed, Obed ana' Boas, Boas ana' Salmon, Salmon ana' Nahason,
25059	42	3	33	Nahason ana' Aminadab, Aminadab ana' Admin, Admin ana' Arni, Arni ana' Hezron, Hezron ana' Peres, Peres ana' Yehuda,
25060	42	3	34	Yehuda ana' Yakub, Yakub ana' Ishak, Ishak ana' Abraham, Abraham ana' Terah, Terah ana' Nahor,
25061	42	3	35	Nahor ana' Serug, Serug ana' Rehu, Rehu ana' Peleg, Peleg ana' Eber, Eber ana' Salmon,
25062	42	3	36	Salmon ana' Kenan, Kenan ana' Arpakhsad, Arpakhsad ana' Sem, Sem ana' Nuh, Nuh ana' Lamekh,
25063	42	3	37	Lamekh ana' Metusalah, Metusalah ana' Henokh, Henokh ana' Yared, Yared ana' Mahalaleel, Mahalaleel ana' Kenan,
25064	42	3	38	Kenan ana' Enos, Enos ana' Set, Set ana' Adam, Adam ana' Alata'ala.
25065	42	4	1	 Pe'ongko' -na Yesus ngkai ue Yordan, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpokuasai-i pai' mpakeni-i hilou hi papada to wao'.
25066	42	4	2	Mo'oha' -i hi ria opo' mpulu' bengi, pai' -i nasori Magau' Anudaa'. Kahae-na toe, uma ria hanyalaa to nakoni'. Timpaliu opo' mpulu' bengi toe, mo'oro' -imi.
25067	42	4	3	Na'uli' Magau' Anudaa' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ane Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-ko, wae-pi hubui watu toe mewali pongkoni'!"
25068	42	4	4	Natompoi' Yesus: "Hi rala Buku Tomoroli' te'uki' hewa toi: `Manusia' uma tuwu' ngkai pongkoni' -wadi.'"
25069	42	4	5	Oti toe, Magau' Anudaa' mpokeni-i hilou hi kalangkoa-na. Hampinisi mata-wadi napopohiloi-i hawe'ea kamagaua' hi dunia',
25070	42	4	6	pai' na'uli' -ki: "Kuasa mpoparentai hawe'ea kamagaua' toera lau pai' hawe'ea ka'uaa' -na, kuwai' -koko Iko omea-mi mpai', apa' aku' omea pue' -na, pai' ma'ala kupewai' hi hema konoa-ku.
25071	42	4	7	Jadi', ane mepue' -ko hi aku', kuwai' -koko Iko omea-mi toe lau."
25072	42	4	8	Natompoi' Yesus: "Hi rala Buku Tomoroli' te'uki' hewa toi: `Kana mepue' -ta hi Pue' -ta, Pue' Ala. Muntu' Hi'a-wadi to natao tapengkorui.'"
25073	42	4	9	Oti toe, Magau' Anudaa' mpopakeni-i hilou hi Yerusalem, napopokore-i hi lolo wumu Tomi Alata'ala, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ane Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-ko, mengkanawu' -ko pe' ngkai rei!
25074	42	4	10	Uma-ko mpai' moapa, apa' ria te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli': `Pue' Ala mpohubui mala'eka-na mpetalawai' -ko, bona neo' -ko silaka.
25075	42	4	11	Rahorongko-ko, bona witi' -nu uma dungku hi watu.'"
25076	42	4	12	Natompoi' Yesus: "Te'uki' wo'o hewa toi: `Neo' tasori Pue' -ta, Pue' Ala.'"
25077	42	4	13	Ka'oti-na Magau' Anudaa' mposori Yesus hante hawe'ea pesori toe, malai-imi mpopea loga to lompe'.
25078	42	4	14	 Oti toe, Yesus nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' -i nculii' hilou hi tana' Galilea. Hi humalili' Galilea, molele-mi kareba to mpo'uli' napa to nababehi.
25079	42	4	15	Metudui' -i hi tomi-tomi posampayaa to Yahudi, pai' hawe'ea tauna mpo'une' -i.
25080	42	4	16	Hilou-imi Yesus hi Nazaret, ngata kabohea-na. Pai' hewa kabiasaa-na, mesua' -imi hi tomi posampayaa hi Eo Sabat, eo pepuea' -ra to Yahudi. Mokore-imi bona mpobasa Buku Tomoroli'.
25081	42	4	17	Ratonu-ki sura nabi Yesaya. Napali' duu' -na mporua' lolita tohe'i:
25082	42	4	18	"Inoha' Pue' Ala hompo hi Aku', apa' nawati' -ama mpokeni Kareba Lompe' hi tauna to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -ra. Nasuro-a mpo'uli' -raka to ratawani: `Tebahaka-mokoi!' Nasuro-a mpo'uli' -raka towero: `Pehilo-mokoi!' Nahubui-a mpobahaka-ra to rapobatua.
25083	42	4	19	Nahubui-a mpopalele kareba-na, karata-nami tempo-na Pue' mpopohiloi ahi' -na hi ntodea-na."
25084	42	4	20	Ka'oti-na nabasa toe we'i, nalulu nculii' -mi sura toe, natonu-ki pue' bago, pai' -i mohura bona metudui'. Hawe'ea tauna to hi rala tomi posampayaa toe mpodulu mponaa-i doko' mpo'epe lolita-na.
25085	42	4	21	Na'uli' -miraka: "Eo toe lau, madupa' -mi lolita Buku Tomoroli' toe, nto'u kani'epe-na kubasa we'i."
25086	42	4	22	Konce omea-ramo to mpo'epe-i, ra'uli': "Lompe' lia pololita-na! Uma mowo kanoto-na! Hiaa' bo ana' Yusuf-i-wadi-hawo."
25087	42	4	23	Ngkai ree, na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Bate ria-koi mpai' to mpo'uli' -ka walatu tohe'i: `Ee dokter, paka'uri' moto-mi-kowo woto-nu! Ane bongko nabi mpu'u-ko, anu mekoncehi to ki'epe nubabehi hi Kapernaum, babehi wo'o hi rehe'i hi ngata-nu moto.'"
25088	42	4	24	Na'uli' tena-raka Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi, uma ria nabi to rabila' hi ngata-na moto.
25089	42	4	25	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: napa to jadi' tempo toi, bate hewa to jadi' hi tempo-na nabi Elia owi. Nto'u toe, tolu mpae ono mula hangaa mara eo, alaa-na rata oro' bohe hi hawe'ea ngata. Wori' moto tobine tobalu hi tana' Israel to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -ra nto'u toe.
25090	42	4	26	Tapi' Pue' Ala uma mpohubui Elia mpotulungi haduaa ngkai tobalu toera. To nahubui-ki hilou hi ngata Sarfat, mpotulungi hadua tobine tobalu to Sidon, bela-i-hana to Israel.
25091	42	4	27	Wae wo'o nto'u nabi Elisa owi, wori' moto topohaki' poko' hi tana' Israel. Aga uma-ra haduaa to napaka'uri' nabi Elisa. Muntu' Naaman, tauna to Siria."
25092	42	4	28	Mpo'epe lolita-na Yesus toe we'i, moroe lia-ramo hawe'ea tauna to hi rala tomi posampayaa.
25093	42	4	29	Pokore-rami mpopalai-i hilou hi mali ngata, pai' rakeni hilou hi bingke-na, apa' ngata-ra hi lolo bulu'. Patuju-ra ke mpotulaka-i hi bingke-na bona mate-i.
25094	42	4	30	Ntaa' we'i, Yesus mako' mpe'olo' tauna to wori', pai' nculi' palai-nami.
25095	42	4	31	 Oti toe, Yesus hilou hi ngata Kapernaum hi tana' Galilea. Karata-na hi ree, metudui' wo'o-i hi tomi posampayaa hi Eo Sabat.
25096	42	4	32	Konce-ramo tauna to mpo'epe tudui' -na, apa' mololita-i hewa tauna to mokuasa.
25097	42	4	33	Ria wo'o hi ree hadua tauna to napesuai' seta to dada'a lia. Mejeu' -imi na'uli':
25098	42	4	34	"Ee Yesus to Nazaret Doko' nupopai-dakaie? Ba doko' nuropuhi-dakaie? Ku'inca moto-kole, ka'Iko-na Suro to moroli' ngkai Alata'ala-e."
25099	42	4	35	Yesus mpo'uli' -ki seta toei: "Ngkaba'i-ko! Palai-ko ngkai tauna tetui!" Seta to mpesuai' tau toei mpodungka-i hi laintongo' ntodea, pai' -i malai, aga uma-i napopai-pai.
25100	42	4	36	Konce omea-ramo tauna to mpohilo, pai' momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Uma mowo kabaraka' lolita-nae'! Napake' kuasa-na mpopalai anudaa', malai mpu'u-ramo-rana."
25101	42	4	37	Ngkai ree, molele-mi kareba hiapa-apa hi tana' Galilea, to mpo'uli' napa to nababehi Yesus.
25102	42	4	38	Oti toe, malai-imi Yesus ngkai rala tomi posampayaa, hilou hi tomi Simon. Nto'u toe, piniana-na Simon tobine ngkelengi' gaga. Jadi' merapi' -ra hi Yesus bona natulungi-i-hawo.
25103	42	4	39	Lou-imi Yesus mokore hi ncori poturua-na, pai' na'uli': "Palai-ko haki'!" Ncaliu mo'uri' -imi, pai' memata-i mpolayani-ra.
25104	42	4	40	Limpa-mi eo, wori' tauna tumai hi Yesus, mpokeni hawe'ea ompi' -ra to peda' hante wori' nyala haki' -ra. Naganga-ra butu dua-na pai' napaka'uri' -ra.
25105	42	4	41	Pai' wori' wo'o seta napopalai ngkai tauna to rapesuai'. Seta to napopalai toera, kaka'au-au-ra, ra'uli': "Iko-mi Ana' Alata'ala!" Aga natagi mpu'u-ra bona neo' -ra mololita, apa' ra'inca Kahi'a-na Magau' Topetolo'.
25106	42	4	42	Kamepulo-na, malai-imi Yesus ngkai ngata toe, hilou hi kawaoa' -na. Wori' tauna mpali' -i, duu' -na rarua' -i. Merapi' -ra bona neo' -ipi mpalahii-ra.
25107	42	4	43	Tapi' na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Kana hilou wo'o-a hi ngata-ngata ntani' -na, mpoparata-raka kareba lompe' to mpo'uli' neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Apa' toe-mi patuju-na Alata'ala mposuro-a tumai."
25108	42	4	44	Ngkai ree, Yesus hilou mpokeni Lolita Pue' hi tomi posampayaa hobo' hi tana' Yudea.
25109	42	5	1	 Hangkani, bula-na Yesus mokore hi wiwi' rano Genesaret, wori' tauna mome'upi' doko' mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala.
25110	42	5	2	Mpohilo-i romeha' sakaya hi wiwi' rano. Nto'u toe, topebau' mencore ngkai sakaya-ra hilou hi role-na mpobohoi' jala' -ra.
25111	42	5	3	Hilou-imi Yesus mpohawi' sakaya to hameha', sakaya-na Simon, pai' naperapi' bona Simon mpotoko sakaya ngkai wiwi' rano hangkedi'. Oti toe, pai' mohura-imi hi rala sakaya mpotudui' ntodea.
25112	42	5	4	Kahudu-na metudui', na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Simon: "Toko tena hilou hi kanalaa-na, pai' tene' jala' -ni bona mporata-koi bau'."
25113	42	5	5	Na'uli' Simon: "Guru, hamengia-makai ngone mobago, aga uma hama'aa ihi' jala' -kai. Aga nau' wae, kutene' moto, lawi' nuhubui-kai."
25114	42	5	6	Ngkai ree, karatene' -na jala' -ra, wori' mpu'u-mi bau' to mesua' hi rala-na, alaa-na ntepu'u morenta-mi jala' -ra.
25115	42	5	7	Mekawe-ra hi doo-ra to hi rala sakaya kahameha' -na bona tumai mengawa'. Tumai mpu'u-ramo-rawo pai' ra'ihii' -mi sakaya romehaa', duu' -na neo' matala nakeni katomo-na.
25116	42	5	8	Kanahilo-na Simon Petrus kabaraka' -na Yesus toe, powingkotu' -nami hi nyanyoa-na, na'uli': "Neo' -apa numohui', Pue'! Apa' aku' toi tauna topojeko'."
25117	42	5	9	Simon mololita hewa toe, apa' hi'a pai' hawe'ea doo-na wilingkoroa mpohilo kawori' bau' to nawoko' jala' -ra.
25118	42	5	10	Wilingkoroa wo'o-ra-rawo Yakobus pai' Yohanes, rodua ana' Zebedeus to mobago dohe Simon. Ngkai ree, na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Simon: "Neo' me'eka'. Ntepu'u wae lau, uma-poko mebau'. Kuwai' -moko pobago to bo'u: mpotudui' tauna jadi' topetuku' -ku."
25119	42	5	11	Oti toe, radii' sakaya-ra hi role-na, rapalahii omea-mi, pai' mpotuku' Yesus-ramo.
25120	42	5	12	 Hangkani, bula-na Yesus hi rala ngata, rata hadua tauna to mohaki' poko' hobo' woto-na. Kampohilo-na Yesus, powingkotu' -nami, lio-na dungku hi tana'. Merapi' -i hi Yesus, na'uli': "Pue', ane ma'ala, paka'uri' -a-kuwo!"
25121	42	5	13	Yesus mpojama-i pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ma'ala moto. Kupaka'uri' -moko!" Hampinisi mata, mo'uri' -imi.
25122	42	5	14	Oti toe, Yesus mpotagi-i, na'uli': "Neo' nulolita to jadi' tohe'i hi hema-hema. Hilou-moko ulu mpopehuwu woto-nu hi imam, bona nahilo kamo'uri' -numi, pai' keni pepue' -nu ntuku' parenta to na'uki' Musa, bona monoa' hi hawe'ea tauna kamo'uri' -nu mpu'u-mi."
25123	42	5	15	Ntaa' molele lau-midi kareba-na hiapa-apa-e, alaa-na mo'iko tauna mpotuku' Yesus doko' mpo'epe lolita-na pai' mpopepaka'uri'.
25124	42	5	16	Tapi' Yesus biasa hilou hi kawaoa' -na pai' mosampaya.
25125	42	5	17	 Rala-na ha'eo nto'u Yesus metudui', ria ba hangkuja dua to Parisi pai' guru agama mohura hi ree. Ria-ra ngkai ngata-ngata hi tana' Galilea, Yudea, pai' ngkai ngata Yerusalem wo'o. Baraka' ngkai Pue' Ala ria hi Yesus bona mepaka'uri'.
25126	42	5	18	Nto'u toe, tumai-ra ba hangkuja tauna mpokowa' hadua topungku to turu hi rala pokowaa'. Rapali' ohea-ra mesua' hi tomi doko' mpokeni doo-ra hi Yesus.
25127	42	5	19	Aga uma-ra teliu mesua', apa' bihi' rahi tauna. Toe pai' ngkahe' tuka' -ramo mpokeni doo-ra hilou hi lolo tomi, rahungka' ata' pai' ra'ulu-i ntali pokowaa' -na hilou hi nyanyoa Yesus hi laintongo' ntodea.
25128	42	5	20	Kanahilo-na Yesus kabohe pepangala' -ra, na'uli' -mi hi topungku toei: "Ompi', te'ampungi-mi jeko' -nu."
25129	42	5	21	Mololita-ramo guru agama pai' to Parisi toera hi rala nono-ra, ra'uli': "Hema rahi-idi tauna toei mai, pai' daho' -i mpo'uli' hibalia tuwu' -na hante Alata'ala-e? Uma ria haduaa to ma'ala mpo'ampungi jeko', muntu' Alata'ala-wadi."
25130	42	5	22	Na'inca moto Yesus napa to hi rala nono-ra. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' nipekiri hewa tetu-e?
25131	42	5	23	Aku' Ana' Manusia', ria mpu'u kuasa-ku hi dunia' mpo'ampungi jeko'. Tapi' ane ku'uli' -ki topungku toei mai: `Te'ampungi-mi jeko' -nu,' uma ni'incai ba te'ampungi mpu'u-di jeko' -nae ba uma-di. Aga ane ku'uli': `Memata pai' mako' -moko,' nihilo mpai' kadupa' -na ba ka'uma-na.
25132	42	5	24	Jadi', kupopohiloi-koi karia-na kuasa-ku mpo'ampungi jeko'." Ngkai ree, kamewili' -na hi topungku toei, na'uli' -ki: "Ku'uli' -koko, memata-moko, ongko' -mi pokowaa' -nu, pai' nculii' -moko."
25133	42	5	25	Pemata-na mpu'u-mi topungku toei, rasabii' tauna to wori', na'ongko' poturua-na, pai' -i nculii' hilou hi tomi-na. Pai' hi lengko ohea ntora mpo'une' Alata'ala-imi.
25134	42	5	26	Konce lia hawe'ea tauna mpohilo tohe'e, pai' -ra mpo'une' Alata'ala. Hante mogalo me'eka' wo'o-ra, ra'uli': "Uma mowo kajadia' to tahilo eo toe we'i lau!"
25135	42	5	27	 Oti toe, malai-imi Yesus, pai' hi lengko ohea mpohilo-i hadua topesingara' paja' bula-na mohura hi kantoro' -na, hanga' -na Lewi. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Tuku' -ama."
25136	42	5	28	Pokore-nami mpalahii omea, pai' -i mpotuku' Yesus.
25137	42	5	29	Lewi mpobabehi karamea bohe hi tomi-na, mpotorata Yesus. Wori' wo'o topesingara' paja' pai' tau ntani' -na rakio' ngkoni' dohe-ra.
25138	42	5	30	Mpohilo toe, ba hangkuja dua pangkeni agama pai' guru agama to mpotuku' tudui' Parisi, ntora ngkunuti. Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na Yesus: "Napa pai' ngkoni' pai' nginu-ko-koina hangkaa-ngkania hante topesingara' paja' pai' topojeko' -e?"
25139	42	5	31	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Tauna to uma peda', uma mingki' rapokulii'. Tauna to peda' -wadi-hawo to paraluu rapokulii'.
25140	42	5	32	Uma-a tumai mpokio' -ra to monoa' ingku-ra. Katumai-ku toi-le, mpokio' topojeko' -a bona medea-ra ngkai jeko' -ra."
25141	42	5	33	Nto'u toe, ria to mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Topetuku' -na Yohanes Topeniu', jau-ra-hana mopuasa' pai' mosampaya. Wae wo'o topetuku' -ra to Parisi. Hiaa' topetuku' -nu Iko-kona, ngkoni' pai' nginu oa' -ra-wadi. Napa pai' uma-ra mopuasa' -e?"
25142	42	5	34	Yesus mpotompoi' -ra hante lolita rapa' toi, na'uli': "Tauna hi posusaa' poncamokoa, ha mopuasa' -ra-rana bula-ra mpo'emai' topemua'? Uma-hawo.
25143	42	5	35	Tapi' rata mpai' tempo-na, topemua' ra'ala' ngkai laintongo' -ra. Nto'u toe-damo, pai' lako' mopuasa' -rada."
25144	42	5	36	Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' lolita rapa' toi, na'uli' -raka: "Uma ria tauna to mpotai' hanceu' pontaia' ngkai baju to bo'u pai' natelepei-ki baju to hae. Apa' ane wae, narenta lau-mi baju to bo'u. Pai' uma wo'o mpai' lompe' lence-na pontaia' to bo'u toe hi baju to hae.
25145	42	5	37	Wae wo'o, uma ria tauna to mpotua anggur to bo'u hi rala pontu'ua to hae. Apa' ane dede' -i mpai', mopengka lau-mi pontu'ua to hae toe, alaa-na mobowo anggur, pai' mpadaa' wo'o-mi pontu'ua-na.
25146	42	5	38	Anggur to bo'u bate kana ra'ihii' hi pontu'ua to bo'u wo'o-wadi-hawo.
25147	42	5	39	"Uma ria tauna to dota nginu anggur to bo'u ane oti-i-damo mpo'inu to hae. Apa' na'uli' mpai': `Anggur to hae to motomo'.'"
25148	42	6	1	 Hangkani Yesus pai' ana'guru-na ntara rala bonea nto'u Eo Sabat, eo pepuea' -ra to Yahudi. Bula-ra mpotara bonea toe, ana'guru-na mpotepo' wua' gandum, raporo bona molepa' kuluma-na, pai' raru'a.
25149	42	6	2	To Parisi to hi ree mpokamaro-ra, ra'uli': "Napa pai' nitiboki atura agama-ta? Mobago-dako-koina hi eo pepuea'!"
25150	42	6	3	Na'uli' -raka Yesus: "Ha uma ria nibasa napa to nababehi Magau' Daud pai' doo-doo-na owi nto'u-ra mo'oro' -e?
25151	42	6	4	Mesua' -i hi rala tomi pepuea', pai' nakoni' roti to rapopepue' hi Alata'ala, pai' nabagi wo'o-raka doo-na. Ntuku' ada agama-ta, imam-wadi-hana to ma'ala mpokoni' roti toe. Aga nau' wae, gau' -na Daud toe uma-hawo naposala'."
25152	42	6	5	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Aku' Ana' Manusia', ria kuasa-ku mpo'uli' napa to ma'ala rababehi hi eo pepuea'."
25153	42	6	6	Hangkani wo'o nto'u Eo Sabat, hilou-i metudui' hi tomi posampayaa. Hi tomi posampayaa toe, ria hadua tauna to mate pale ka'ana-na.
25154	42	6	7	Ba hangkuja dua to Parisi pai' guru agama to hi ree mpolelemata-i Yesus, meka' ba mepaka'uri' -i mpai' hi Eo Sabat. Patuju-ra, mpali' kedo' bona rapakilu-i mobago hi Eo Sabat.
25155	42	6	8	Aga na'inca moto Yesus anu hi nono-ra. Toe pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki tauna to mate pale-na hamali toei: "Mai-moko mokore hi laintongo' rei!" Hilou mpu'u-imi-hawo mokore hi ree.
25156	42	6	9	Ngkai ree, na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Kupekune' -koi ulu. Ntuku' atura agama-ta, to'uma to ma'ala tababehi hi Eo Sabat: mpobabehi to lompe' -di ba to dada'a? Mpotulungi doo ba mpatehi doo?"
25157	42	6	10	Mogolili Yesus mponaa-ra omea, pai' na'uli' -ki topeda' toei: "Tanoa pale-nu!" Kanatanoa-na pale-na, mo'uri' -imi.
25158	42	6	11	Ngkai ree, uma mowo karoe-ra guru agama pai' to Parisi. Toe pai' mohawa' -ramo mpali' reke-ra, ba rapopai-i Yesus.
25159	42	6	12	 Nto'u toe, Yesus hilou hi bulu' -na, pai' mosampaya-i hamengia hi Alata'ala.
25160	42	6	13	Kabaja-na, nakio' -ramo topetuku' -na pai' napelihi hampulu' rodua ngkai laintongo' -ra. To hampulu' rodua toera, nahanga' suro-na.
25161	42	6	14	
25162	42	6	15	
25163	42	6	16	Hanga' -ra: Simon (Yesus mpohanga' -i Petrus); pai' Andreas ompi' -na Simon; Yakobus; Yohanes; Filipus; Bartolomeus; Matius; Tomas; Yakobus ana' Alfeus; Simon to rahanga' to Zelot; Yudas ana' Yakobus; pai' Yudas Iskariot, to mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -nae mpai'.
25164	42	6	17	Oti toe, mana'u-imi Yesus ngkai lolo bulu' hante ana'guru-na, pai' -ra mento'o hi lempe-na. Hi ree, wori' -mi topetuku' -na mpopea-i, pai' wori' lia tauna morumpu. Tauna toera ngkai humalili' tana' Yudea, ngkai ngata Yerusalem pai' ngkai ngata Tirus pai' Sidon to hi wiwi' tahi'.
25165	42	6	18	Patuju-ra tumai, doko' mpo'epe lolita Yesus pai' mpopepaka'uri'. To napesuai' seta tumai wo'o pai' napaka'uri' -ra.
25166	42	6	19	Wori' tauna mpali' ohea doko' mpoganga Yesus, apa' ria baraka' to mehupa' ngkai woto-na to mpaka'uri' -ra omea.
25167	42	6	20	 Yesus mponaa topetuku' -na pai' na'uli' -raka: Morasi' -koi tokabu, apa' koi' to jadi' ntodea Alata'ala, pai' Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ni.
25168	42	6	21	Morasi' -koi to mo'oro' tempo toi, apa' rabohui moto-koi mpai'. Morasi' -koi to geo' tempo toi, apa' goe' moto-koi mpai'.
25169	42	6	22	"Morasi' -koi ane rapokahuku' -koi, rapopalai-koi, raruge' pai' rapomohoa hanga' -ni sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku' Ana' Manusia'.
25170	42	6	23	Apa' wae wo'o gau' ntu'a-ra mpobalinai' nabi-nabi to owi. Jadi', ane rapohewa toe-koi, mohajo-koi pai' pakagoe' moto nono-ni, apa' bohe mpai' rasi' to nirata hi rala suruga.
25171	42	6	24	"Aga silaka-koi topo'ua' tempo toi, apa' mpolia' nirata-mi-koina kagoea' -ni.
25172	42	6	25	Silaka-koi to bohu tempo toi, apa' mo'oro' -koi mpai'. Silaka-koi to goe' tempo toi, apa' susa' pai' geo' -koi mpai'.
25173	42	6	26	Silaka-koi ane hawe'ea tauna mpo'une' -koi, apa' wae wo'o ntu'a-ra owi mpo'une' nabi-nabi to boa'.
25174	42	6	27	 "Aga hi koi' to mpo'epe lolita-ku wae-e lau, ohe'i hawa' -ku: Kana tapoka'ahi' bali' -ta, mo'ingku lompe' hi tauna to mpokahuku' -ta.
25175	42	6	28	Gane' -ra to mpokamo-ta, posampayai-ra to dada'a hi kita'.
25176	42	6	29	Ane ria tauna to mpohopo' kulimpi-ta hamali, neo' rapehawai. Tonu lau wo'o-ki to hamali. Ane ria to mpo'agoi-ta abe' -ta, wai' wo'o lau-i baju-ta.
25177	42	6	30	Ane ria to mperapii' -ta, wai' -ra-rawo. Ane ria to mpo'agoi ba napa-napa rewa-ta, neo' raperapi' nculii'.
25178	42	6	31	Napa po'ingku to tapokono rababehi doo hi kita', toe wo'o to kana tababehi hi doo.
25179	42	6	32	"Ane tapoka'ahi' muntu' tauna to mpoka'ahi' -ta-wadi, uma mpai' nagane' -ta Alata'ala. Bangku' tauna to dada'a gau' -ra, ma'ahi' moto-ra hi tauna to mpoka'ahi' -ra.
25180	42	6	33	Ane lompe' po'ingku-ta muntu' hi tauna to lompe' po'ingku-ra hi kita', uma mpai' nagane' -ta Alata'ala. Bangku' tauna to dada'a, bate lompe' po'ingku-ra hi tauna to lompe' po'ingku-ra hi hira'.
25181	42	6	34	Ane kita' mpewai' doi-ta rahenta muntu' hi tauna to ta'inca bisa mpoponculi' -taka, uma mpai' nagane' -ta Alata'ala. Bangku' tauna to dada'a, dota wo'o-ra-rawo rapohentai doi hingka todada'a-ra, apa' ncarumaka-ra rapoponculi' moto-raka mpai'.
25182	42	6	35	"Neo' hewa tetu! Kana tapoka'ahi' bali' -ta, mo'ingku lompe' hi hira'. Wai' -ra hema to doko' mpohentai-ta, pai' neo' ncarumaka ponculia' -na. Ane wae po'ingku-ta, bohe mpai' rasi' to tarata hi eo mpeno, pai' tatuku' -mi po'ingku Pue' Ala to hi suruga. Apa' manara-i Pue' hi tauna to uma mpo'incai mpo'uli' tarima kasi pai' hi tauna to dada'a.
25183	42	6	36	Kana ma'ahi' -ta, hewa kama'ahi' -na Pue' Ala Tuama-ta.
25184	42	6	37	 "Neo' -ta mpotudo' sala' doo, bona uma wo'o mpai' Pue' Ala mpotudo' sala' -ta. Neo' mpo'uli' tauna to masala' kana rahuku', bona uma wo'o mpai' Pue' Ala mpohuku' -ta. Ampungi sala' doo, Pue' Ala wo'o mpai' mpo'ampungi sala' -ta.
25185	42	6	38	Kana tawai' doo-ta, Pue' Ala wo'o mpowai' -ta. Nawai' -ta pewai' to lompe' lia, to oti-mi ralengo pai' ra'oo', duu' -na moloju'. Apa' pohuka' to tapake' hi doo, tetu wo'o-hawo mpai' to rapopohuka' -taka."
25186	42	6	39	Pai' na'uli' wo'o Yesus lolita rapa' tohe'i: "Ane towero mpotete' hingka towero-na, bate moluli' -ra mpai' hi rala kinali.
25187	42	6	40	Pai' uma ria ana' sikola to meliu karabila' -na ngkai guru-na. Ane hudu-miki posikola-na, pai' lako' hibalia-idi hante guru-na.
25188	42	6	41	"Napa pai' mponaa-ta gege' hi mata doo, hiaa' wince' kaju to hi mata-ta moto uma ta'incai karia-na!
25189	42	6	42	Beiwa-ta ma'ala mpo'uli' -ki doo: `Ompi', mai kulali gege' -nu,' bo uma moto tahiloi wince' kaju to hi mata-ta. Neo' mpetolompei' kehi! Kana talali ulu wince' kaju to hi mata-ta, bona monoto mata-ta mpolali gege' doo.
25190	42	6	43	"Uma ria kaju to lompe' mowua' to dada'a. Wae wo'o uma ria kaju to dada'a mowua' to lompe'.
25191	42	6	44	Butu nyala kaju ra'inca kalompe' -na hi powua' -na. Wua' ara uma rahopu' ngkai walaa to morui. Wua' anggur uma rahopu' ngkai jilata.
25192	42	6	45	Wae wo'o manusia'. Tauna to lompe', bate mpohowa' lolita to lompe' -ra, apa' lawi' nono-ra ihia' to lompe'. Tauna to dada'a, dada'a wo'o lolita-ra, apa' nono-ra ihia' to dada'a. Apa' napa ihi' nono-ta, toe wo'o-mi to howa' hi wiwi-ta.
25193	42	6	46	"Napa pai' nikio' -a `Pue'! Pue'!' bo uma-di nituku' hawa' -kue!
25194	42	6	47	Tauna to tumai hi Aku' mpo'epe pai' mpotuku' tudui' -ku, hira' hewa tauna hi rala lolita rapa' tohe'i:
25195	42	6	48	Hadua tauna mpowangu tomi, nakae tana' napomonala pai' nahu'a parawatu to moroho. Rata uda bohe pai' ue mowo' mporumpa' tomi toe, aga uma-i molengo apa' moroho parawatu-na.
25196	42	6	49	Aga tauna to mpo'epe lolita-ku pai' uma ratuku', hira' hewa hadua tauna to mpowangu tomi hi lolo tana' -wadi hante uma ria parawatu-na. Rata ue mowo' mporumpa' tomi toe, kamodungka-nami, pai' gaga kagero-na."
25197	42	7	1	 Kahudu-na Yesus mpotudui' ntodea hawe'ea toe, hilou-imi hi ngata Kapernaum.
25198	42	7	2	Hi ngata toe, ria hadua tadulako tantara to Roma, ria-ki batua-na to napoka'ahi' lia. Batua-na toei peda' danca, neo' mate.
25199	42	7	3	Kana'epe-na tadulako toei karia-na Yesus hi ngata-na, nahubui ba hangkuja dua pangkeni to Yahudi hilou mpopetulungi hi Yesus, bona tumai-i mpaka'uri' batua-na.
25200	42	7	4	Karata-ra hi Yesus, merapi' mpu'u-ra, ra'uli': "Tadulako toei ria, natao lia nutulungi,
25201	42	7	5	apa' napoka'ahi' -ta kita' to Yahudi, pai' ria-i mpowai' -kai doi mpowangu tomi posampayaa-kai."
25202	42	7	6	Ngkai ree, hilou mpu'u-imi Yesus dohe-ra. Kamohu' -na Yesus hi tomi-na, tadulako toei mpohubui wo'o-ramo ba hangkuja dua doo-na hilou mpohirua' -ki Yesus mpo'uli' -ki hewa toi: "Tuama, uma-ko mingki' tumai hi tomi-ku, apa' aku' toi bela-a to Yahudi, uma-a natao nupencuai'.
25203	42	7	7	Toe pai' uma-a daho' tilou hi Iko Tuama, apa' uma-a natao mpohirua' -koko. Nau' lolita hamela-wadi nu'uli', bate mo'uri' -i mpai' batua-ku.
25204	42	7	8	Apa' aku' toi-e, pahawaa' wo'o-a-wadi-kuwo, pai' ria wo'o-ra-kuwo to kuhawai'. Ane rapa' -na ria hawa' -ku hi hadua tantara mpo'uli' -ki: `Hilou-ko!' bate hilou-i. Ane mekio' -a hi tantara kahadua-na: `Mai-ko!' bate tumai-i. Ane ku'uli' -raka batua-ku: `Babehi toe!' bate rababehi. Wae wo'o-kowo Iko Tuama, napa to nu'uli' hi retu, bate madupa' hi rei."
25205	42	7	9	Konce-i Yesus mpo'epe lolita ngkai tadulako toei. Toe pai' me'ili' -imi hi ntodea to mpotuku' -i, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Uma mowo pepangala' -na tau toei ria! Nau' hi to Yahudi muli Israel, ko'ia ria haduaa kurata to bohe pepangala' -na hewa tauna toei ria."
25206	42	7	10	Oti toe, nculii' -ramo suro toera hi tomi tadulako. Karata-ra hi ria, mpolia' mo'uri' -imi batua-na.
25207	42	7	11	 Uma mahae ngkai toe, hilou-imi Yesus hi ngata to rahanga' Nain, hante ana'guru-na pai' wori' tau ntani' -na dohe-ra.
25208	42	7	12	Mohu' -ramo hi wobo' wuntu ngata, rahilo-rawo wori' tauna mehupa' ngkai rala ngata, mpokowa' tomate. Tomate toei, hadua kabilasa, ana' hadudua, tina-na balu-mi. Wori' pue' ngata mpodohei tina-na hilou hi daeo'.
25209	42	7	13	Kanahilo-na Pue' Yesus tobine toei, metumu' -mi ahi' -na pai' na'uli' -ki: "Neo' -pi-hawo geo'!"
25210	42	7	14	Hilou-imi mpoganga pokowa', mentoda' -ramo to mokowa'. Na'uli' Yesus: "Kabilasa! Kuhubui-ko memata!"
25211	42	7	15	Kabilasa to mate toei we'i, kaliliu mohura-imi pai' -i mololita. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki tina-na: "Oi-mi ana' -nu, totina."
25212	42	7	16	Tauna to mpohilo kajadia' toe, me'eka' omea-ramo, pai' -ra mpobila' Alata'ala, ra'uli': "Hadua nabi to mobaraka' mehuwu-mi hi laintongo' -ta! Hompo mpu'u-imi Alata'ala tumai mpotulungi ntodea-na!"
25213	42	7	17	Kareba toe molele hobo' hi tana' Yudea pai' ntololikia-na.
25214	42	7	18	Ana'guru-na Yohanes Topeniu' mpoparata-ki hawe'ea to nababehi Yesus toe. Toe pai' mpokio' -i rodua ana'guru-na,
25215	42	7	19	 pai' nahubui-ra hilou hi Pue' Yesus, na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi Yesus pai' uli' -ki retu: `Ba Iko-mi Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Alata'ala, ba ria-pidi to ntani' -na to kipopea?'"
25216	42	7	20	Hilou mpu'u-ramo suro to rodua toera, pai' ra'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pai' -kai tumai Guru, nahubui-kai Yohanes mpekune' -ta, ba kita' -midi Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Pue' Ala, ba ria-pidi to ntani' -na to kipopea."
25217	42	7	21	Nto'u toe wo'o-hawo, Yesus mpaka'uri' wori' topeda' ngkai haki' -ra, napopalai anudaa' ngkai tauna to rahawi', pai' napaka'uri' towero bona pehilo-ra.
25218	42	7	22	Na'uli' -mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka suro Yohanes toera hewa toi: "Nculii' -mokoi, uli' -ki Yohanes hi retu napa to nihilo pai' to ni'epe: towero pehilo-mi, tokejo momako' monoa' -mi, topohaki' poko' mo'uri', towongo pe'epe, tomate kupotuwu' nculii', pai' Kareba Lompe' kuparata-raka to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -ra.
25219	42	7	23	Marasi' -ra tauna to uma morara' nono-ra hi Aku'."
25220	42	7	24	Palai-ra suro Yohanes toera, mololita-imi Yesus hi ntodea, mpotompo'wiwi Yohanes. Na'uli': "Napa patuju-ni hilou mpohirua' -ki Yohanes Topeniu' hi tana' to wao'? Ba doko' -koi mpohilo tauna to morara' nono-na, to hewa pimpi to molue nawui ngolu' hilou tumai? Uma-hawoe'.
25221	42	7	25	Jadi', hilou doko' mpohilo napa-dikoie? Ba doko' mpohilo tauna to ncola pohea-na? Uma wo'o, apa' po'ohaa' tauna to ncola pohea-ra pai' to mo'ua' katuwu' -ra, hi tomi magau' -ra-wadi-hana.
25222	42	7	26	Jadi', hilou doko' mpohilo napa-dikoie? Ba doko' mpohilo nabi-dikoi? Ane tetu, makono lia. Apa' Yohanes tetui meliu ngkai nabi to ntani' -na.
25223	42	7	27	Apa' hi'a tetu-mi to mporodo nono-ra ntodea mpotarima-a, hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' owi. Na'uli' Alata'ala: `Hi'a toi-mi suro-ku, kuhubui-i meri'ulu ngkai Iko, bona mporodo ohea-nu.'"
25224	42	7	28	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Pe'epei lompe': ngkai hawe'ea tauna to putu hi rala dunia' toi, uma ria haduaa to meliu kabohe tuwu' -na ngkai Yohanes. Aga ngkai wae lau, marasi' mpu'u-ra tauna to jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na. Nau' to kedi' lia tuwu' -ra, meliu kamarasi' -ra ngkai Yohanes."
25225	42	7	29	Hawe'ea tauna, nte to mpesingarai' paja', mpo'epe lolita Yesus toe mpotompo'wiwi Yohanes. Mpo'epe toe, ratarima-mi Lolita Alata'ala, apa' oti-ramo mpopeniu' hi Yohanes.
25226	42	7	30	Hiaa' to Parisi pai' guru agama-rana, oja' -ra mpotarima patuju Alata'ala hi tuwu' -ra, bo oja' -ra mpopeniu' hi Yohanes.
25227	42	7	31	Na'uli' wo'o Yesus: "Uma mowo tauna to tuwu' tempo toi! Toi-mi lolita rapa' -ku to kurapai' -raka:
25228	42	7	32	Hira' hewa ana' to mohura hi wiwi' karajaa, to ntora momekio' hi doo-ra, ra'uli': `Kibawai-koi molalowe, uma-koi dota goe' dohe-kai. Kibawai-koi motantangi', uma wo'o-koi dota geo' dohe-kai.'
25229	42	7	33	
25230	42	7	34	Batua-na: Yohanes Topeniu' uma nipokonoi, Aku' wo'o uma nipokonoi. Katumai-na Yohanes, mopuasa' -i pai' uma-i nginu to melanguhi. Nipoka'oja' -i, ni'uli': `Kahawia' -i-hanale!' Hiaa' katumai-ku Aku' Ana' Manusia', nginu-a, ngkoni' -a. Nipoka'oja' wo'o-a-wadi, ni'uli': `Hilo-i! Tojampa, topalangu-langu, bale-ra topesingara' paja' pai' doo-ra topojeko'!'
25231	42	7	35	Aga nau' wae, ta'inca kamonoto-na patuju Alata'ala ane tanaa gau' hawe'ea topetuku' -na."
25232	42	7	36	 Ria hadua to Parisi, hanga' -na Simon, mpohinta' Yesus ngkoni' hi tomi-na. Hilou mpu'u-imi Yesus hi tomi-na, mohura pai' -ra ngkoni'.
25233	42	7	37	Hi rala ngata toe, ria hadua tobine topojeko', uma tumotoa gau' -na. Kana'epe-na karia Yesus ngkoni' hi tomi to Parisi toei, tumai-i ngkeni hameha' butolo' ihia' lana honga.
25234	42	7	38	Tumai-imi mpomohui' witi' Yesus, pai' -i geo'. Nasiii' witi' -na Yesus hante ue mata-na. Oti toe nabongka wuluwoo' -na, napomporihi-ki witi' -na, na'eki pai' natuai hante lana honga.
25235	42	7	39	Nahilo to Parisi babehia tobine toei. Mololita bongo-imi hi rala nono-na, na'uli': "Ane bongko nabi mpu'u-i tau toei, ke na'inca kahema-na tobine to mpoganga-i toe, ka'uma-na tumotoa gau' -na."
25236	42	7	40	Ngkai ree, na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki to Parisi toei: "Simon, ria to doko' ku'uli' -koko." Na'uli' Simon: "Uli' -mile Guru."
25237	42	7	41	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ria rodua tauna to mo'inta hi tauna to ma'ala rapohentai doi. Hadua mpohenta lima atu doi pera', to hadua lima mpulu' -wadi.
25238	42	7	42	Ngkai ka'uma-napi rakulei' mpobayari inta-ra, na'uli' -mi tauna to rapohentai toei: `Uma-pi mingki' nibayari inta-ni.' Jadi', hema ngkai hira' to rodua toera to meliu ahi' -ra hi popa'intaa-ra?"
25239	42	7	43	Natompoi' Simon: "Ba tauna to wori' inta-na tu?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono tompoi' -nu."
25240	42	7	44	Oti toe, pai' me'ili' -imi hi tobine toei pai' na'uli' -ki Simon: "Ha nuhilo tobine toei-e? Karata-ku hi tomi-nu we'i, uma nuporodo ue pobohoi' witi' -ku, ntuku' ada-ta hi torata. Hiaa' tobine toei, nabohoi' -hana witi' -ku hante ue mata-na pai' naporihi hante wuluwoo' -na.
25241	42	7	45	Iko, uma-a nutabe hante pe'eki ntuku' ada-ta. Hiaa' tobine toei, uma nabahakai mpo'eki witi' -ku ngkai lomo' -ku rata duu' toe lau.
25242	42	7	46	Iko, uma nulanai woo' -ku ntuku' ada-ta hi torata. Hiaa' tobine toei mpobowohi witi' -ku hante lana honga to masuli' oli-na.
25243	42	7	47	Jadi', bo ma'ahi' lia-ie, toe pai' monoa' -mi kata'inca-na, jeko' -na to wori' te'ampungi-mi. Aga tauna to hangkedi' -wadi te'ampungi jeko' -na, hangkedi' wo'o-wadi-hawo ahi' -na."
25244	42	7	48	Oti toe na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki tobine toei: "Te'ampungi-mi jeko' -nu."
25245	42	7	49	Mpo'epe toe, momepololitai-ramo tauna to mpohimpongkoni' -raka, ra'uli': "Hema-idie tau tetui-e, pai' daho' -i mpo'ampungi jeko' -e?"
25246	42	7	50	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus hi tobine toei: "Tebahaka-moko ngkai huku' jeko' -nu sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'. Hilou-moko hante kalompea' tuwu' -nu."
25247	42	8	1	 Oti toe, Yesus mpodaoi' wori' ngata mpopalele Kareba Lompe', na'uli': "Neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'." Ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua mpodohei-i.
25248	42	8	2	Ria wo'o ba hangkuja dua tobine to mpodohei-ra. Tobine toera, tobine to napaka'uri' Yesus ngkai haki' -ra ba ngkai anudaa' to mpohawi' -ra. To hadua, Maria to biasa-na rahanga' Magdalena. Ria-i hangkani Yesus mpopalai pitu anudaa' ngkai Maria toei.
25249	42	8	3	To hadua wo'o, Yohana tobine-na Khuza, topohawa' hi rala tomi Magau' Herodes. Ria wo'o Susana, pai' wori' -pidi tobine ntani' -na. Tobine toera mpake' doi-ra moto mpotulungi Yesus pai' ana'guru-na.
25250	42	8	4	 Uma ria kaputua tauna ngkai ngata ntani' -na tumai hi Yesus. Wori' -mi tauna to morumpu, Yesus mpololitai-ra hante lolita rapa' toi, na'uli':
25251	42	8	5	"Ria hadua topohawu' hilou mohawu'. Rala mpohawu' -na toe, ria hawua' -na monawu' hi mata ohea, alaa-na rapopongko tauna pai' natilo' danci.
25252	42	8	6	Ria wo'o to monawu' hi tana' to watua. Tuwu' moto hinawu' toe, aga kaliliu molaju apa' bangi tana' -na.
25253	42	8	7	Ria wo'o to monawu' hi laintongo' rui. Tuwu' rui hangkaa-ngkania hante hinawu', alaa-na rui mpo'upi' hinawu' duu' -na mate.
25254	42	8	8	Ria wo'o hawua' to monawu' hi tana' to morudu'. Tuwu' hinawu' toe, morudu' lia, wua' -na ha'atu ngkani ngkai hinawu' -na." Oti lolita rapa' -na toe, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Hema-koi to tilingaa, pe'epei lompe'!"
25255	42	8	9	Ana'guru-na mpekune' Yesus ba napa-i batua lolita rapa' toe.
25256	42	8	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Owi, Alata'ala ko'ia mpopo'incai manusia' beiwa-i mpai' jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Aga hewa toe lau, napopo'incai-mokoi tudui' toe. Aga ane ntodea-hana, kutudui' -ra hante lolita rapa', bona madupa' lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': `Pe'epe moto-ra, aga uma oa' ra'incai batua-na. Pehilo moto-ra, aga hewa to uma oa' monoto rahilo.'
25257	42	8	11	"Tohe'i-mi batua lolita rapa' -ku we'i: Hawua' to rahawu', tetu-mi Lolita Alata'ala.
25258	42	8	12	Hawua' to monawu' hi mata ohea mpobatuai tauna to mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala, aga Magau' Anudaa' mpohilingai' nono-ra, alaa-na uma-ra mepangala', pai' uma-ra tebahaka ngkai huku' jeko' -ra.
25259	42	8	13	"Hawua' to monawu' hi watu mpobatuai tauna to mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala pai' ratarima hante goe' nono-ra. Mepangala' moto-ra, aga pepangala' -ra tetu uma moroho, hewa hinu'a to uma morali'. Toe pai' ane rata-damo pesori, mo'ungkere' -ramo, uma-rapa mepangala'.
25260	42	8	14	"Hawua' to monawu' hi laintongo' rui mpobatuai tauna to mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala, aga ntora mpenonoi katuwu' -ra hi rala dunia', doko' mo'ua' pai' doko' mporata kagoea'. Hawe'ea toe mposesei' -ra, alaa-na uma-ra kaliliu mpotuku' Lolita Alata'ala, pai' uma ria kalaua-na hi katuwu' -ra.
25261	42	8	15	"Hawua' to monawu' hi tana' to morudu' mpobatuai tauna to mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala, pai' lolita toe rakakamu hante kanoa' pai' karoli' nono-ra. Ntaha-ra mpotuku' Lolita Alata'ala, duu' -na ria kalaua-na hi katuwu' -ra.
25262	42	8	16	"Uma ria tauna to mposuwe palita pai' napopoi' ba natu'u hi une' poturua. Palita bate natu'u hi pontu'ua-na bona hini-na rahilo tauna to mesua'.
25263	42	8	17	Apa' hawe'ea to tewuni kana rapopehuwu. Pai' hawe'ea to kalerua kana rahungke pai' jadi' kahiloa.
25264	42	8	18	"Toe pai' ku'uli', pelompehi-koie' beiwa-koi mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala. Apa' tauna to mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala, ranotohi nono-ra bona kawoo-woria' to ra'inca. Aga tauna to uma dota mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala, nau' ria hangkedi' to ra'inca, ra'alai' lau-ra."
25265	42	8	19	Hangkani, tina pai' ompi' -na Yesus tumai doko' mpohirua' -ki, aga uma-ra teliu apa' wori' rahi tauna.
25266	42	8	20	Ria hadua to mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, tina-nu pai' ompi' -nu, oe-ra ria hi mali-na, doko' mpohirua' -koko."
