25267	42	8	21	Tapi' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane to kupotina pai' to kupo'ompi' -le, tauna to mpo'epe pai' mpotuku' Lolita Alata'ala."
25268	42	8	22	 Rala-na ha'eo, Yesus hante ana'guru-na mohawi' sakaya. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Hilou-tamo hi dipo rano." Me'ongko' -ramo.
25269	42	8	23	Bula-ra mosakaya, leta' -imi Yesus. Muu-mule' rata-mi ngolu' bohe hi rano mporumpa' -ra. Sakaya-ra napesua' ue, alaa-na neo' matala-ramo.
25270	42	8	24	Ana'guru-na hilou hi Yesus mpolike-i, ra'uli': "Guru! Guru! Mate-ta toi-e!" Pemata-nami Yesus pai' -i mpotagi ngolu' pai' balumpa to mekoroi' toe. Mento'o-mi ngolu', pai' rano molino nculii'. Rodo omea-mi.
25271	42	8	25	Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Yesus hi ana'guru-na: "Napa pai' uma-a nipangala' -e?" Konce pai' me'eka' -ramo, pai' momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Hema mpu'u-idi tau toii-e? Bangku' ngolu' pai' balumpa nahawai', ratuku' mpu'u-diki-hana hawa' -nae!"
25272	42	8	26	Kaliliu-ramo mosakaya, duu' -na rata hi tana' Gerasa to hi dipo rano ngkai tana' Galilea.
25273	42	8	27	
25274	42	8	28	
25275	42	8	29	Ria hi ree hadua pue' ngata to rapesuai' seta to wori'. Mahae-imi tauna toei uma moheai pai' uma-i mo'oha' hi tomi. Hi daeo' -wadi po'ohaa' -na. Jau-i kahawia'. Nau' rahilu' -i hante koloro pai' rante pai' radongo ncuu, ma'ala oa' nadupe' pohilu' -na pai' metibo' hilou hi kawaoa' -na, apa' nakeni karoho seta to mpohawi' -i. Nto'u Yesus mehompo ngkai sakaya hilou hi role-na, tumai-imi tauna to kahawia' toei mpohirua' -ki. Kampohilo-na Yesus, pe'au-nami pai' -i mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa-na. Yesus mpohubui seta toera malai. Na'uli' tau toei mpesukui: "Ee Yesus, Ana' Alata'ala to hi suruga! Napa-di-kona pai' tumai-koe? Kuperapi' bona neo' -a-kuwo nusesa'!"
25276	42	8	30	Yesus mpekune' -i: "Hema hanga' -nu?" Natompoi': "Legion." ("Legion" tohe'e, batua-na "moncobu," apa' wori' seta to mpohawi' -i.)
25277	42	8	31	Raperapi' mpu'u seta toera bona neo' -ra nawuso hilou hi rala wulou'laa to uma tepetudu kanala-na.
25278	42	8	32	Uma molaa ngkai ree, ria wori' wawu mojume hi panapa bulu'. Seta toera merapi' hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Piliu-ka-kaiwo mesua' hi wawu toera mai." Napiliu moto-ra.
25279	42	8	33	Malai mpu'u-ramo seta ngkai rala tauna toei, kaliliu mesua' hi wawu. Pesua' -ra hi wawu toe, mparampuli-ramo-rawo wawu hilou mengkajuala' hi rano, mate bonga-ramo hi rala ue.
25280	42	8	34	Karahilo-na to mpodoo wawu kajadia' toe, mokeno-ramo hilou hi ngata pai' bonea to mohu' mpoparata kajadia' toe.
25281	42	8	35	Toe pai' tumai-ramo pue' ngata doko' mpohilo napa to jadi'. Karata-ra hi Yesus, rahilo-rawo tauna to biasa-na napesuai' seta, mohura rodo-imi hi ncori Yesus. Moheai-i pai' monoto-mi nono-na. Me'eka' -ramo.
25282	42	8	36	Tauna to mpohilo kajadia' toe mpotutura beiwa Yesus mpaka'uri' tauna to kahawia'.
25283	42	8	37	Ngkai ree, hawe'ea tauna hi tana' Gerasa toe merapi' hi Yesus bona malai-imi ngkai ngata-ra, apa' me'eka' lia-ra. Jadi' mohawi' sakaya-imi nculii' hilou hi dipo-na.
25284	42	8	38	Ane tauna to napaka'uri' Yesus, merapi' -i bona ma'ala-i hilou dohe-na. Tapi' uma-i napiliu, na'uli' -ki:
25285	42	8	39	"Nculii' -moko hilou hi tomi-nu pai' uli' -raka retu napa to nababehi Alata'ala hi iko." Hilou mpu'u-imi mpopalele hi rala ngata napa to nababehi Yesus hi woto-na.
25286	42	8	40	 Karata-na Yesus nculii' hi dipo rano, goe' -ramo tauna to wori' mpotomu-i, apa' hawe'ea-ra ntora mpopea-i.
25287	42	8	41	Nto'u toe, rata hadua pangkeni tomi posampayaa hi ngata toe, hanga' -na Yairus. Mowingkotu' -i hi nyanyoa Yesus, naperapi' bona hilou-i hi tomi-na.
25288	42	8	42	Apa' ria ana' -na tobine hadudua-wadi, umuru-na hampulu' rompae, peda' neo' mate. Hilou mpu'u-i Yesus dohe-na. Bula-ra momako' hilou hi tomi-na Yairus, mome'upi' -damo tauna to wori' mpo'upi' Yesus.
25289	42	8	43	Hi olo' ntodea, ria hadua tobine, hampulu' rompae-imi ntora moraa', pai' uma ria katontoa' -na, nau' wori' -mi to mpokulii' -i.
25290	42	8	44	Tumai-imi tobine toei mpomohui' Yesus ngkai tilingkuria-na pai' naganga wuntu baju-na. Hampinisi mata mentoda' -mi poraa' -na.
25291	42	8	45	Mepekune' -imi Yesus: "Hema to mpoganga-ae?" Mancapu omea-ra. Na'uli' Petrus: "Guru, apa' wori' rahi tauna mpotipuhi-ta, mome'iho' -ra-damo mpo'upi' -ko."
25292	42	8	46	Na'uli' Yesus: "Bate ria-di to mpoganga-ae! Ku'inca-le, apa' ria kabaraka' to malai ngkai woto-ku."
25293	42	8	47	Na'inca tobine toei ka'uma-na tewunii' babehia-na. Jadi' moridi' -i tumai mowingkotu' hi nyanyoa Yesus. Napangaku' hi ntodea kahi'a-na to mpoganga baju Yesus pai' kamo'uri' -nami ngkai haki' -na.
25294	42	8	48	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Ana' -ku, mo'uri' -moko sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'. Nculii' -moko hante kalompea' tuwu' -nu."
25295	42	8	49	Bula-na Yesus mololita-pidi, rata-mi suro ngkai tomi Yairus to mpo'uli' -ki Yairus: "Mate-mi ana' -nu. Neo' -pi mposusai' Guru."
25296	42	8	50	Kana'epe-na Yesus lolita toe, na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yairus: "Neo' mere' nono-nu. Pangala' -mi-hana, mo'uri' moto-i mpai' ana' -nu."
25297	42	8	51	Karata-ra hi tomi Yairus, Yesus uma mpiliu kabua' -bua' tauna mesua' dohe-na. Muntu' Petrus, Yohanes, Yakobus hante tina pai' tuama ana' toei-wadi to ma'ala mesua'.
25298	42	8	52	Hawe'ea tauna to morumpu hi tomi Yairus geo' pai' motantangi', mpotantangii' ana' to mate toei. Na'uli' Yesus: "Neo' -pi-hawo geo'. Uma-ile mate-e, leta' -i-wadi-hawo."
25299	42	8	53	Mpo'epe toe, rapotawai-i-wadi, apa' ra'inca kamate-na mpu'u-mi.
25300	42	8	54	Oti toe, Yesus mpokamu pale-na ana' toei pai' na'uli' -ki: "Memata-moko ana'!"
25301	42	8	55	Mo'inoha' nculii' -imi ana' toei, pai' kaliliu memata-imi. Na'uli' Yesus: "Wai' -i pongkoni'."
25302	42	8	56	Konce mpu'u-ramo totu'a-na. Aga Yesus mpotagi-ra, bona neo' ra'uli' hi hema-hema napa to jadi' toe.
25303	42	9	1	 Yesus mpokio' ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua morumpu, pai' nawai' -ra kuasa pai' kabaraka' mpopalai hawe'ea seta pai' mpaka'uri' topohaki'.
25304	42	9	2	Napahawa' -ra hilou mpaka'uri' topeda' pai' mpopalele kareba-na: "Neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'."
25305	42	9	3	Kako'ia-ra me'ongko', na'uli' -raka: "Neo' -koi ngkeni napa-napa hi pomakoa' -ni. Neo' ngkeni boku ba pongkoni' ba doi. Neo' ngkeni rontonga' baju ba lua'.
25306	42	9	4	Ane ratarima-koi hi rala tomi hantomi, mo'oha' hi ree-mokoi duu' -ni kaliliu hilou hi ngata ntani' -na.
25307	42	9	5	Ane rata-koi hi ngata pai' uma-koi ratarima, wae kanipalahii-na ngata tetu, tonta awu to mentaka' hi palanta' witi' -ni, tanda kanahuku' -ra mpai' Alata'ala."
25308	42	9	6	Ka'oti-na Yesus mpotudui' -ra, me'ongko' -ramo hilou hi ngata-ngata. Hiapa pomakoa' -ra, mpokeni-ra Kareba Lompe' pai' mpaka'uri' topeda'.
25309	42	9	7	Nto'u toe, topoparenta hi Galilea, Herodes Antipas. Kana'epe-na Herodes hawe'ea to nababehi Yesus toe, napoka'ingu' lau-mi. Apa' ria to mpo'uli': "Yesus toei lou, Yohanes Topeniu' tuwu' nculii' -imi."
25310	42	9	8	Ria wo'o to mpo'uli' Yesus toei nabi Elia owi mehupa' nculii'. Ria wo'o to mpo'uli' Yesus toei hadua nabi to owi memata nculii'.
25311	42	9	9	Na'uli' Herodes: "Ane Yohanes Topeniu', kuhubui-mi wengi tauna mpopata' wuroko' -na. Hiaa' Yesus toe-e lou, hema mpu'u-i-hawo? Wori' -mi ku'epe to mpotompo'wiwi-i." Toe pai' Herodes doko' mpohirua' -ki Yesus.
25312	42	9	10	 Rata nculii' -ramo suro Yesus to hampulu' rodua toera, pai' ratutura-ki Yesus hawe'ea to rababehi. Oti toe, Yesus mpo'ema' -ra hilou hi kawaoa' -na mohu' hi ngata Betsaida.
25313	42	9	11	Ntaa' ra'inca-di ntodea kahilou-rae. Toe pai' metuku' -ramo mpotuku' Yesus. Karata-ra hi Yesus, natarima moto-ra pai' natudui' -ra tudui' to mpotompo'wiwi Kamagaua' -na Alata'ala. Pai' hema-hema to mohaki' napaka'uri'.
25314	42	9	12	Neo' limpa-mi eo, rata-ramo ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, agina tahubui-ramo ntodea toera lau hilou mpali' pongkoni' -ra pai' poturua-ra hi ngata pai' bonea to mohu'. Apa' wao' -hana hi rehe'i lau."
25315	42	9	13	Na'uli' Yesus: "Koi' -mi to mpopokoni' -ra." Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Beiwa-mi-kaina! Apa' muntu' lima meha' roti pai' rongkaju bau' uru-wadi to ria hi kai' -e. Ha kana hilou-kai mpo'oli pongkoni' to rapokoni' -raka tauna to wori' toera lau?"
25316	42	9	14	(Kawori' -ra kira-kira lima ncobu paka' tomane-pidi.) Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Hubui-ra mohura mopantuda-ntuda, nte lima mpulu' tauna hantuda."
25317	42	9	15	Ratuku' -mi ana'guru-na napa to nahubui-raka Yesus.
25318	42	9	16	Mohura-ra omea, na'ala' -mi Yesus roti to lima meha' pai' uru to rongkaju, pai' -i ngkongoa' hi langi' mosampaya. Oti toe napihe-pihe-mi roti pai' nabibe' -bibe' bau', pai' nawai' -raka ana'guru-na bona rabagi hi ntodea.
25319	42	9	17	Ngkoni' omea-ramo duu' -ra bohu. Ka'oti-ra ngkoni', ana'guru-na mporumpu toro koni'. Metoro-pi hampulu' roluncu.
25320	42	9	18	 Rala-na ha'eo, Yesus mosampaya hadudua-na, pai' rata ana'guru-na dohe-na. Napekune' -ra, na'uli': "Ntuku' ponguli' ntodea, hema-a Aku' toi-e?"
25321	42	9	19	Ratompoi': "Ria to mpo'uli' Yohanes Topeniu' -ko tuwu' nculii'. Aga ria wo'o to mpo'uli' nabi Elia-ko. Ria wo'o to mpo'uli' Iko hadua nabi to owi tuwu' nculii'."
25322	42	9	20	Napekune' tena-ra: "Hiaa' koi' -koiwo mpo'uli', hema-a Aku' toi-e?" Natompoi' Petrus: "Iko-mi Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Alata'ala!"
25323	42	9	21	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpotagi mpu'u-ra, na'uli': "Neo' ulu ni'uli' hi hema-hema ka'Aku' -na Magau' Topetolo'."
25324	42	9	22	Na'uli' wo'o-mi: "Aku' Ana' Manusia' kana mporata wori' kaparia. Rasapuaka-a mpai' totu'a ngata, imam pangkeni hante guru agama. Rapatehi-a mpai', aga hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
25325	42	9	23	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpololitai hawe'ea tauna, na'uli': "Hema to doko' mpotuku' -a kana mpobahaka konoa-na moto, pai' kana napaha'a kaju parika' -na butu eo-na-- batua-na: kana natuku' hawa' -ku nau' napopate-ki. Oti toe-di pai' lako' ma'ala-i mpotuku' -a.
25326	42	9	24	Hema to mpentaei konoa-na moto, uma-i mpai' mporatai katuwua' to lompe'. Aga hema to mpobahaka konoa-na moto sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', nau' napopate-ki, hi'a-mi mpai' to mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
25327	42	9	25	Napa kalaua-na tarumpu hawe'ea ka'uaa' dunia', tapi' kao' -ta moto morugi apa' uma taratai katuwua' to lompe' hi eo mpeno-na.
25328	42	9	26	"Hema to me'ea' mpangaku' petuku' -na hi Aku' pai' mpoka'ea' tudui' -ku, Aku' wo'o mpai' me'ea' mpangaku' kahi'a-na topetuku' -ku ane rata-apa mpai' ngkai suruga. Nto'u toe mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia' mana'u tumai hante mala'eka-mala'eka to moroli', mehini-a hante baraka' -ku pai' hante baraka' -na Tuama-ku.
25329	42	9	27	Pe'epei to ku'uli' -kokoi tohe'i: ria-koi mpai' hi rehe'i to ko'ia mate kako'ia-na nihilo Alata'ala jadi' Magau'."
25330	42	9	28	 Kira-kira hamingku ngkai pololita-na toe, Yesus mpobawai Petrus, Yohanes pai' Yakobus manake' hilou hi lolo bulu', lou mosampaya.
25331	42	9	29	Bula-na Yesus mosampaya, mobali' -mi lence-na, pai' pohea-na mewali mengea' meringkila'.
25332	42	9	30	Muu-mule' ria rodua tauna to mpololitai-i, hira' nabi Musa pai' Elia.
25333	42	9	31	Mehini pai' ncola wo'o-ra-rawo to rodua toera. Mololita-ra, mpotompo'wiwi kamate-na Yesus to napadupa' mpai' hi ngata Yerusalem.
25334	42	9	32	Nto'u toe, Petrus pai' doo-na leta' luru'. Kamolike-ra, rahilo-rawo Yesus mehini ncola hante tauna to rodua to dohe-na.
25335	42	9	33	Kaneo' -ra me'ongko' -mi to rodua toera, na'uli' Petrus: "Guru, lompe' lia-ta mo'oha' hi rehe'i! Agina kibabehi-damo tolu bamaru' hi rehe'i. Hameha' bagia-nu Guru, hameha' bagia-na Musa, pai' hameha' wo'o bagia-na Elia." (Aga uma-hawo na'incai kahompoa lolita-na.)
25336	42	9	34	Bula-na mololita-pidi Petrus, rata-mi limu' mpokamoui-ra. Me'eka' -ramo mpohilo limu' to mpoputu' -ra.
25337	42	9	35	Mpo'epe-ra topololita ngkai rala limu' to mpo'uli': "Hi'a toi-mi Ana' -ku to kupelihi. Pe'epei-mi lolita-na!"
25338	42	9	36	Kamolino-na topololita, rahilo-rawo ana'guru-na, hadudua-na Yesus-damo. Pana'u-ra ngkai bulu' toe, ana'guru-na to tolu toera mengkalino-wadi, uma-ra ulu mpololita hi hema-hema napa to rahilo hi lolo bulu' toe.
25339	42	9	37	 Kamepulo-na mana'u-ramo ngkai lolo bulu', pai' wori' tauna mpohirua' -ki Yesus.
25340	42	9	38	Ria hadua tomane hi laintongo' tauna to wori' to mekio', na'uli': "Guru! Tulungi-a! Pehiloi-ka-kuwo ana' -ku. Hadudua hi'a-wadi-ka-kuwo ana' -ku.
25341	42	9	39	Ane napesuai' anudaa' -i, kaka'au-au-i pai' kakapadi-padi-i, duu' -na mowura' nganga-na. Neo' uma ria palaia-na anudaa' toe mpopedahi-i.
25342	42	9	40	Kuperapi' -ramo ana'guru-nu mpopalai anudaa' toe, aga uma rakulei'."
25343	42	9	41	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma mowo-koie'! Ko'ia oa' -tano mepangala' -koie! Mesapuaka oa' -pidi-koi mposapuaka konoa Alata'ala! Ni'uli' -koina hangkuja tena-pi kahae-ku dohe-ni, hangkuja tena-pi kahae-na kupengkatarii kalente pepangala' -nie! Keni tumai ana' -nu!"
25344	42	9	42	Bula-na ana' toei momako' hilou hi Yesus, modungka-imi napakeni seta to mpohawi' -i, pai' kakapadi-padi woto-na. Yesus mpopetibo' anudaa', pai' mpaka'uri' ana' toei. Oti toe na'uli' -ki tuama-na: "Ala' -mi ana' -nu. Mo'uri' -imi."
25345	42	9	43	 Konce omea-ramo tauna mpohilo baraka' Alata'ala to bohe tohe'e.
25346	42	9	44	"Penonoi lompe' -e' lolita-ku toi: Aku' Ana' Manusia' bate ratonu mpai' hi kuasa manusia'."
25347	42	9	45	Aga ana'guru-na uma mpo'incai patuju-na, apa' tewunii' -raka batua-na, alaa-na uma rapaha. Hiaa' uma wo'o-ra daho' mpekune' -i ba napa batua lolita-na toe.
25348	42	9	46	Ana'guru-na Yesus momehono', ba hema-ra to meliu kabohe tuwu' -ra.
25349	42	9	47	Na'inca Yesus napa to hi rala nono-ra. Toe pai' na'ala' hadua ana' to kedi' napopokore hi ncori-na,
25350	42	9	48	pai' na'uli' -raka: "Hema to mpotarima ana' to kedi' toi sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', batua-na Aku' -mi to natarima. Pai' hema to mpotarima-a, mpotarima wo'o-imi Pue' Ala to mposuro-a. Hema-koi to tuwu' mengkadingki', hi'a-mi to bohe mpu'u tuwu' -na."
25351	42	9	49	Na'uli' Yohanes: "Guru, ria kihilo hadua tauna mpopalai seta hante hanga' -nu, aga kitagi-i apa' bela-i topetuku' -ta."
25352	42	9	50	Na'uli' Yesus: "Neo' -i ratagi, apa' tauna to uma mpo'ewa-ta, batua-na hira' -mi to tono' hi kita'."
25353	42	9	51	 Mohu' -mi tempo-na Yesus me'ongko' hilou hi suruga, napomonoa' -mi bate mpotoa' -i Yerusalem.
25354	42	9	52	Nahubui ba hangkuja dua topetuku' -na meri'ulu ngkai Hi'a. Mesua' -ra to rahubui toera hi ngata to Samaria bona mporodo hawe'ea-na kako'ia-na Yesus rata.
25355	42	9	53	Aga pue' ngata toera, oja' -ra mpotarima Yesus, apa' ra'inca kampotoa' -na Yerusalem.
25356	42	9	54	Yakobus pai' Yohanes mpo'epe karapoka'oja' -ra pue' ngata toera. Toe pai' ra'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pue', ane nupokono, kiperapi' apu ngkai langi' mpomampuhi pue' ngata toera lau!"
25357	42	9	55	Tapi' Yesus mpe'ili' -ra pai' mpotagi-ra.
25358	42	9	56	Oti toe, kaliliu-ramo hilou hi ngata ntani' -na.
25359	42	9	57	 Hi pomakoa' -ra toe, ria hadua tauna to mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Hiapa kahiloua-nu Pue', doko' kutuku' -ko."
25360	42	9	58	Yesus mpotompoi' -i, na'uli': "Bangko' ria pulo'u-ra, pai' danci ria peta-ra, aga Aku' Ana' Manusia' uma-kuna ria tomi-ku kupoturui."
25361	42	9	59	Oti toe, pai' na'uli' Yesus hi kahadua-na: "Tuku' -a." Aga natompoi' tau toei: "Pue', piliu-a-kuwo ulu nculii' hi tomi-ku. Ane mate-damo tuama-ku pai' -i ratana, bo kutuku' -moko."
25362	42	9	60	Yesus mpotompoi' -i hante walatu toi, na'uli': "Pelele' moto-ramo tomate mpotana hingka tomate-ra. Aga iko-kona, hilou-moko mpopalele kareba Kamagaua' Alata'ala."
25363	42	9	61	Ria wo'o kahadua-na mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pue', dota moto-a mpotuku' -ko. Aga piliu-a ulu nculii' mpalakana hi ompi' -ku."
25364	42	9	62	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Tauna to ntepu'u-mi mopajeko', uma-hawo lompe' ane kaka'ili' -ili' -i. Tauna to hewa toe kehi-ra, uma-ra natao jadi' topobago hi rala Kamagaua' -na Alata'ala."
25365	42	10	1	 Oti toe, Pue' Yesus mpelihi wo'o-mi pitu mpulu' topetuku' to ntani' -na pai' nahubui-ra momako' rodua-rodua meri'ulu ngkai Hi'a hilou hi butu-butu ngata to natara mpai'.
25366	42	10	2	Na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Tauna to doko' mpo'epe Kareba Lompe' ma'ala rarapai' -ki pae to taha'. Wori' pae to kana rapepae, aga topepae uma-ra wori'. Toe pai' kana mekakae-koi hi pue' bonea, niperapi' bona nahubui tauna hilou mepae hi bonea-na.
25367	42	10	3	"Hilou-mokoi, aga pelompehi, apa' kuhubui-koi hilou hi olo' tauna to dada'a. Koi' mpai' hewa bima hi olo' serigala.
25368	42	10	4	Neo' ngkeni karepe' doi ba boku ba sapatu' ropasa. Neo' mengkahae mpololitai tauna hi lengko ohea.
25369	42	10	5	"Ane mesua' -koi hi rala tomi hantomi, ncaliu ni'uli': `Kalompea' ngkai Pue' rata hi koi' pue' tomi!'
25370	42	10	6	Ane lompe' nono-ra pue' tomi mpotarima-koi, bate nagane' mpu'u-ra mpai' Pue' Ala. Aga ane uma-rada dota mpotarima-koi, uma-ra mpai' mporata rasi' ngkai pegane' -ni tetu.
25371	42	10	7	Hantomi lau-wadi po'ohaa' -ni, neo' -koi pantoli-ntoli hi kahantomi-na bula-ni mpokeni Kareba Lompe' hi ngata tetu. Pongkoni' napa to rawai' -kokoi, koni' -mi-hana, apa' topobago masipato' mpotarima gaji' -na.
25372	42	10	8	"Ane mesua' -koi hi rala ngata pai' -koi ratarima, koni' -mi-hana napa to ratonu-kokoi.
25373	42	10	9	Paka'uri' topeda' to hi rala ngata, pai' uli' -raka pue' ngata: `Rata-mi tempo-na, Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi laintongo' -ni.'
25374	42	10	10	Aga ane mesua' -koi hi rala ngata pai' uma-koi ratarima, hilou-mokoi hi karajaa pai' mpo'uli':
25375	42	10	11	`Nau' awu ngata-ni to mentaka' hi palanta' witi' -kai, kitonta bona nihilo. Aga kiwoi-koie': neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau'!'"
25376	42	10	12	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus hi topetuku' -na: "Ku'uli' -kokoi, hi Eo Kiama, meliu pehuku' -na Alata'ala mpohuku' pue' ngata toera ngkai pehuku' -na hi pue' ngata Sodom owi.
25377	42	10	13	"Silaka-koi to Yahudi to mo'oha' hi ngata Korazim pai' hi Betsaida! Wori' moto-mi tanda mekoncehi kubabehi hi ngata-ni, aga uma oa' -koi medea ngkai jeko' -ni. Ane rapa' -na tanda mekoncehi toe rababehi hi rala ngata Tirus pai' Sidon, ke mahae-ramo-rana medea ngkai jeko' -ra, nau' bela-ra to Yahudi. Ke mpo'ala' karu' -ramo rapohea, pai' mohura-ra mpohawui' woto-ra hante awu, tanda kasoho' nono-ra.
25378	42	10	14	Jadi', hi Eo Kiama mpai', meliu-pi pehuku' -na Alata'ala hi koi' ngkai pehuku' -na hi to Tirus pai' to Sidon.
25379	42	10	15	"Pai' koi' wo'o to Kapernaum! Ha ni'uli' -koina na'ongko' napomolangko-koi mpai' Alata'ala-e? Uma-e'! Natadi pai' nahuku' lau-dakoi mpai'."
25380	42	10	16	Oti toe, Yesus mololita tena hi topetuku' -na, na'uli': "Tauna to mpotarima lolita-ni, batua-na lolita-ku Aku' to ratarima. Tauna to mposapuaka-koi, batua-na Aku' to rasapuaka. Pai' tauna to mposapuaka-a, mposapuaka wo'o-ra Pue' Ala to mposuro-a."
25381	42	10	17	 Ba hangkuja kahae-na ngkai toe, nculii' -ramo topetuku' to pitu mpulu' toera. Goe' mpu'u-mi nono-ra, ra'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pue', bangku' seta wo'o mengkoru hi kai' pai' metibo' -ra, ane kipopalai-ra hante hanga' -nu."
25382	42	10	18	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kuhilo-di Magau' Anudaa' -e monawu' ngkai langi' hewa kila'!
25383	42	10	19	Jadi', bona ni'inca: kuwai' -mokoi kuasa, bona ma'ala-koi mpolisa ule ba lipa pai' mpodagi hawe'ea karohoa bali' -ta. Uma hema to mposerohi-koi.
25384	42	10	20	Aga nau' wae, neo' nipokagoe' kamengkoru-ra seta hi koi'. Agina mpokagoe' -koi kate'uki' -nami hanga' -ni hi rala suruga."
25385	42	10	21	Nto'u toe Yesus nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' -i mololita ngkai kagoe' nono-na, na'uli': "O Mama, Pue' langi' pai' dunia'! Mpo'uli' -a tarima kasi, apa' hawe'ea toe lau nupopohiloi-raka tauna to uma pe'incai, tapi' nuwunii' -raka tauna to nginca pai' tauna to pante. Apa' wae-mi konoa-nu Mama.
25386	42	10	22	"Hawe'ea-na natonu-maka Tuama-ku. Uma ria haduaa to mpo'inca kahema-ku Aku' Ana' Alata'ala, muntu' Tuama-ku to mpo'inca-a. Wae wo'o uma ria to mpo'incai hema-i Tuama-ku, muntu' Aku' Ana' -na to mpo'inca-i, pai' hema-hema to kupopo'incai kahema-nai Tuama-ku."
25387	42	10	23	Ngkai ree, bona neo' ra'epe doo, me'ili' -imi hi ana'guru-na, na'uli' -raka: "Morasi' mpu'u-koi, apa' nihilo-mi-koina hawe'ea tohe'i.
25388	42	10	24	Apa' wori' moto nabi pai' magau' owi to doko' mpohilo napa to nihilo koi' toi, aga uma-rana rahiloi. Doko' lia-ra mpo'epe napa to ni'epe-mi koi', aga uma-rana ra'epei."
25389	42	10	25	 Ria hadua guru agama Yahudi to doko' mpemai-mai kasala' petompoi' Yesus. Napekune' -i: "Guru, napa-hawo to kana kubabehi bona mporata-a katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na?"
25390	42	10	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa to te'uki' hi rala Atura Pue'? Beiwa to nubasa?"
25391	42	10	27	Natompoi' guru agama toei: `Kana tapoka'ahi' Pue' -ta Pue' Alata'ala hante nono-ta mpu'u, tatonu hawe'ea katuwu' -ta hi Hi'a, tapoka'ahi' -i hudu pakulea' -ta, pai' hudu inca-ta.' Pai' `Kana tapoka'ahi' doo-ta hewa pompoka'ahi' -ta woto-ta moto.'"
25392	42	10	28	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kono-mi petompoi' -nu. Babehi-mi hewa tetu, mporata moto-ko mpai' katuwua' to lompe'."
25393	42	10	29	Aga guru agama toei uma dota radagi, mpoperaha-i kamonoa' po'ingku-na. Toe pai' na'uli': "Hiaa' hema doo-ku to kana kupoka'ahi' -e?"
25394	42	10	30	Natompoi' Yesus: "Ria hadua tomane to mako' ngkai Yerusalem mana'u hilou hi ngata Yerikho. Hi lengko ohea-i mpohirua' -ki toperampaki. Ra'agoi-i rewa-na pai' pohea-na, pai' -i rapao' duu' -na neo' mate, pai' rapalahii moto-imi hi ohea.
25395	42	10	31	Ko'ia mahae ngkai ree, ria wo'o-hawo hadua imam ntara hi ohea toe. Kanahilo-na tauna to weho toei, napelelii' pai' kaliliu moto-i.
25396	42	10	32	Wae wo'o, hadua topobago hi Tomi Alata'ala liu hi ree. Kanahilo-na tauna to weho toei, napelelii' wo'o-i-wadi-hawo pai' -i kaliliu.
25397	42	10	33	"Uma mahae ngkai ree, liu wo'o-hawo hadua to Samaria to bula-na hi pomakoa' -na. Kanahilo-na tauna to weho toei, metumu' -mi ahi' -na.
25398	42	10	34	Kahilou-nami mpomohui' -i, nabohoi' weho-na hante lana pai' anggur pai' nawewe. Oti toe napopehawi' -i hi keledai-na pai' nakeni-i hilou hi tomi torata, pai' napodoo-i hi ree.
25399	42	10	35	Kamepulo-na na'ala' rompepa' doi pera', nawai' -ki pue' tomi pai' na'uli' -ki: `Pewili' -i-hawo ulu tauna toei hi rehe'i. Nculii' moto-a mpai' pai' kubayari omea ongkoso' -nu ane ria pelabia-na ngkai tetu.'"
25400	42	10	36	Hudu-mi jarita-na toe, napekune' Yesus hi guru agama toei, na'uli': "Ntuku' pomporataa-nu, ngkai to tolu toera, hema-ra to ma'ahi' hi doo to rarampaki toei?"
25401	42	10	37	Natompoi' guru agama toei: "Tauna to mpotulungi-i." Na'uli' Yesus: "Koi' -moko, babehi wo'o-kowo hewa tetu."
25402	42	10	38	 Rala pomakoa' -ra toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na mehani hi ngata. Hi rala ngata toe, ria hadua tobine to rahanga' Marta to mpotorata Yesus.
25403	42	10	39	Ria wo'o ompi' -na Marta, tobine wo'o-wadi, hanga' -na Maria. Maria toei mohura mohu' hi witi' -na Yesus ntora mpe'epei lolita-na.
25404	42	10	40	Hiaa' Marta-hana, sese' -i-damo mpo'urusi torata. Kahilou-nami Marta hi Yesus pai' na'uli' -ki: "Pue', ha nupokono ompi' -ku tetui mpelele' -a mobago hadudua-ku! Uli' -ki pe' mpongawa' -ae."
25405	42	10	41	Na'uli' Pue' Yesus: "Ee' Marta! Sese' pai' kawuhe rahi-ko mpenonoi to wori' nyala.
25406	42	10	42	Hiaa' kakono-na, to paraluu nubabehi hanyala lau-wadi, toe-mi mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala. Ane Maria, napelihi-mi bagia to lompe', pai' bagia toe uma mpai' ra'alai' ngkai hi'a."
25407	42	11	1	 Hangkani Yesus mosampaya. Kahudu-na mosampaya, hadua ana'guru-na mpo'uli' -ki: "Pue', tudui' wo'o-ka-kaiwo mosampaya, hewa Yohanes Topeniu' mpotudui' ana'guru-na."
25408	42	11	2	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane mosampaya-koi, uli' hewa tohe'i: Mama, pomperapia' -kai bona hawe'ea tauna mpobila' hanga' -nu to moroli', bona Iko jadi' Magau' hi dunia'.
25409	42	11	3	Wai' -kai pongkoni' to kiparaluu eo-eo-na.
25410	42	11	4	Ampungi jeko' -kai, apa' kai' wo'o mpo'ampungi hawe'ea tauna to masala' hi kai'. Pai' neo' -kai nupelele' rasori."
25411	42	11	5	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Rapa' -na hilou-ta hi doo-ta mentongo' bengi pai' ta'uli' -ki: `Bale, wai' -a-kuwo pongkoni' tolu mputu'.
25412	42	11	6	Apa' ria bale-ku to lako' rata, hiaa' uma-kuna ria napa-napa to kuwai' -ki.'
25413	42	11	7	"Ha natompoi' -ta mpai' hewa tohe'i: `Neo' -a nusaleroi. Wobo' tehohoki-mi. Ana' -ku leta' omea-ramo dohe-ku. Uma-a bisa memata mpowai' -ko ba napa-napa.'
25414	42	11	8	Uma mpai' hewa toe tompoi' -na. Nau' bale-ta uma dota memata pai' mpowai' -ta napa-napa, aga apa' uma tabahakai pai' uma-ta me'ea' mperapii' -i, memata oa' -i mpowai' -ta napa to taparaluu.
25415	42	11	9	"Jadi' ku'uli' -kokoi: Perapi' -mi hi Alata'ala, nawai' moto-ta mpai'. Pali' kaparaluua-ta hi Alata'ala, tarata moto mpai'. Neo' tabahakai mpopebea wobo', Alata'ala mpobea moto-taka mpai' wobo' -na.
25416	42	11	10	Apa' hema to merapi' bate rawai'. Hema to mpali' bate mporata. Hema to mpopebea wobo', bate rabea-ki wobo'.
25417	42	11	11	Ha ria-koi to mpowai' ule hi ana' -ni ane merapi' -i bau'?
25418	42	11	12	Ba mpowai' -i pehede' ane merapi' -i ntolumanu'? Tantu uma.
25419	42	11	13	Nau' hewa apa-mi kadada'a-nie, ni'inca moto mpowai' to lompe' hi ana' -ni. Peliu-liu-nami Tuama-ni to ria hi rala suruga! Bate nawai' Inoha' Tomoroli' hi tauna to merapi' hi Hi'a."
25420	42	11	14	 Rala-na ha'eo, Yesus mpopalai seta ngkai hadua tauna to uma howa' mololita. Wae kanawuso-na seta toe, howa' -imi tauna toei mololita. Konce-ramo ntodea.
25421	42	11	15	Aga ria wo'o-ra to mpo'uli': "Kuasa-na tetu-le ngkai Beelzebul, magau' hawe'ea seta. Toe-hawo pai' ria baraka' -na mpopalai seta-e."
25422	42	11	16	Ria wo'o-ra hantongo' to doko' mposori Yesus. Merapi' -ra hi Yesus bona napopohiloi-ra anu mekoncehi bona monoa' ra'inca kangkai Alata'ala-na mpu'u-i.
25423	42	11	17	Ntaa' na'inca-di Yesus napa to hi rala nono-rae. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ane rapa' -na ria hadua magau', pai' ntodea hi rala kamagaua' -na ntora mome'ewa, bate mogero mpai' kamagaua' -na toe. Wae wo'o tau hantomi to ntora motuda', bate pagaa' -gaa' -ra mpai'.
25424	42	11	18	Wae wo'o hi kamagaua' -na seta. Ane seta mpo'ewa hingka seta-na, bate mogero mpai' kamagaua' -na seta. Hiaa' ni'uli' -koina, mpopalai-a seta hante baraka' Beelzebul, magau' seta.
25425	42	11	19	Aga ria wo'o doo-ni moto to mpopalai seta. Hante kuasa napa doo-ni tetu mpopalai seta? Tantu hante kuasa Alata'ala. Jadi', ngkai pobabehi doo-ni moto, monoto-mi kamasala' pebalihi-ni tetu.
25426	42	11	20	Tapi' Aku', mpopalai-a seta hante baraka' Alata'ala. Ngkai toe, monoa' -mi ni'inca karata-nami tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi laintongo' -ni.
25427	42	11	21	"Seta ma'ala rarapai' -ki tauna to parimuku. Ane tauna to parimuku mpodongo tomi-na hante rewa panga'e-na, uma moapa ihi' tomi-na.
25428	42	11	22	Aga ane tumai hadua to meliu karoho-na mpo'ewa-i pai' mpodagi-i, nahagoi-i hawe'ea rewa panga'e-na to nasarumaka pai' nabagi-bagi ihi' tomi-na hi doo-doo-na. Jadi', ane Aku' mpopalai seta, batua-na meliu kuasa-ku ngkai seta.
25429	42	11	23	"Hema to uma tono' hi Aku', kakono-na bali' -ku-imi. Hema to uma mpotulungi-a mobago, hi'a to mpobalinai' bago-ku.
25430	42	11	24	"Rapa' -na ria anudaa' to mpohawi' tauna. Malai-imi anudaa' toei, pai' -i modao' -dao' hi kawaoa' -na mpali' po'ohaa' -na. Apa' uma ria naruai', na'uli' -mi: `Agina nculii' lau-ama hi po'ohaa' to kupalahii-mi toe wengi ria.'
25431	42	11	25	Ponculi' -na hilou hi tauna to napalahii-e wengi, nahilo-hawo uma ria to mpo'ohai' -i. Tauna toei hewa tomi to molela' tepehaii, hinapa' hiloa-na.
25432	42	11	26	Toe pai' hilou ncala' -i mpokio' pitu hingka anudaa' -na to meliu kadada'a-ra ngkai hi'a. Tumai-ramo mesua' hi tauna to napalahii toe-e wengi, pai' mo'oha' -ramo hi ree. Ka'omea-na tampai kampe'ahii' tauna toei ngkai lomo' -na."
25433	42	11	27	 Bula-na Yesus mololita, hadua tobine hi laintongo' ntodea mpo'uli' mpesukui: "Morasi' mpu'u-i-hana tobine to mpo'ote pai' to mpentii' -ko!"
25434	42	11	28	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aga to morasi' mpu'u-le, tauna to mpo'epe pai' mpotuku' Lolita Alata'ala."
25435	42	11	29	 Nto'u tauna to wori' mpotipuhi Yesus, napokaliliu lolita-na, na'uli': "Dada'a lia tauna to tuwu' tempo toi. Merapi' -ra bona kupopohiloi-ra tanda mekoncehi. Aga uma hanyalaa tanda mekoncehi to rapopohiloi-raka. Sampale to rapopohiloi-raka mpai', tanda hewa to jadi' hi nabi Yunus owi.
25436	42	11	30	Hewa Yunus jadi' tanda to rapokakonce pue' ngata Niniwe owi, wae wo'o Aku' Ana' Manusia' jadi' tanda to rapokakonce tauna to tuwu' tempo toi.
25437	42	11	31	Hi Eo Kiama mpai', raja bine ngkai Selatan rapotuwu' nculii' hangkaa-ngkania hante koi' to tuwu' tempo toi, pai' -i mpotudo' sala' -ni. Apa' momako' -i tumai ngkai ngata to molaa lia, doko' mpu'u-i mpo'epe lolita Magau' Salomo to pante lia. Hiaa' ria-mi hi laintongo' -ni to meliu kabohe tuwu' -na ngkai Salomo, aga uma oa' nipangalai' lolita-na.
25438	42	11	32	Wae wo'o hi Eo Kiama mpai', pue' ngata Niniwe rapotuwu' nculii' hangkaa-ngkania hante koi' to tuwu' tempo toi, pai' -ra mpotudo' sala' -ni. Apa' hira', medea-ramo-rana ngkai jeko' -ra kampo'epe-ra pololita nabi Yunus. Hiaa' ria-mi hi laintongo' -ni to meliu kabohe tuwu' -na ngkai Yunus, aga uma oa' nipangalai' lolita-na.
25439	42	11	33	"Uma ria tauna mposuwe palita pai' nawuni ba napopoi' hante kura. Palita bate ratu'u hi pontu'ua-na bona hini-na rahilo tauna to mesua'.
25440	42	11	34	Mata-ta ma'ala rarapai' -ki hulu'. Ane lompe' mata-ta, monoto pehilo-ta. Aga ane mogawu mata-ta, hewa mobengi pehilo-ta.
25441	42	11	35	Wae wo'o-hawo hante nono-ta. Kana tapelompehi mpu'u: ane Pue' mpobajahi nono-ta, neo' tapomobengi nculii'.
25442	42	11	36	Ane Pue' mpobajahi nono-ta duu' -na uma-pi ria kabengia-na, mobaja mpu'u katuwu' -ta omea, hewa tomi to nabajahi palita."
25443	42	11	37	 Hudu-mi Yesus mololita, ria hadua to Parisi mpokio' -i lou ngkoni' hi tomi-na. Hilou mpu'u-imi ngkoni'.
25444	42	11	38	Konce to Parisi toei mpohilo Yesus ngkoni', apa' uma-i leba' mowano ntuku' ada agama-ra.
25445	42	11	39	Toe pai' Pue' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Koi' to Parisi-le hewa tauna to mpobohoi' sangkiri' pai' piri hi mali-na-wadi, hiaa' hi rala-na babo' moto. Ada agama to kahiloa hi mali-na nituku' lia, hiaa' hi rala nono-ni, dada'a-koi pai' mpokahina anu doo-koi.
25446	42	11	40	Wojo mpu'u-koi! Ha woto-ta-wadi to napajadi' Pue'? Ha uma napajadi' wo'o nono-ta?
25447	42	11	41	Napa to hi rala sangkiri' pai' piri-ni wai' -raka to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -ra. Ane hewa toe-mi po'ingku-ni, hawe'ea jadi' moroli' hi koi'.
25448	42	11	42	"Silaka-koi to Parisi! Ntahawe' hinu'a to kedi' hewa tarangkada' pai' kula' pai' hinu'a ntani' -na nipopepue' hampobagiahampulu' hi Alata'ala. Hiaa' parenta to bohe, hewa po'ingku to monoa' hi doo-ni pai' ahi' hi Pue' Ala, uma nisaile'. Kakoo-kono-na, ke parenta to bohe toe-hanale to kana nituku' -e, pai' neo' wo'o nilipo' mpotuku' parenta to kedi'.
25449	42	11	43	"Silaka-koi to Parisi! Apa' goe' -koi mohura hi pohuraa karabilaa' hi tomi posampayaa, pai' goe' -koi ane tauna hi wiwi' karajaa motingkua' mpotabe-koi.
25450	42	11	44	Silaka-koi, apa' koi' hewa daeo' to uma ka'incanaa, to uma ria pompetonoi-na. Tauna mpolisa daeo' toe, aga uma ra'incai karia-na anu pope hi rala-na. Lompe' -koi hi mali-na, tapi' dada'a hi rala nono-ni."
25451	42	11	45	Hadua guru agama Yahudi mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, hante lolita-nu tetu, kai' wo'o to nusalai'!"
25452	42	11	46	Mehono' Yesus: "Silaka wo'o-dakoi guru agama! Apa' nipopokoloi ntodea hante parenta pai' ada to motomo. Hiaa' uma-koi dota mpotulungi-ra ngkolo kinolo toe. Nau' hangkaju karawe-ni uma nihuko-raka.
25453	42	11	47	Silaka-koi! Nipenasa-damo mpakalompe' daeo' -ra nabi to owi, hiaa' ntu'a-ni moto-mi to mpatehi nabi toera.
25454	42	11	48	Hante pobabehi-ni tetu, nipangaku' moto-mi kanipokono-na kehi ntu'a-ni tetu. Hira' mpatehi nabi to owi, pai' koi' mpakalompe' daeo' -ra.
25455	42	11	49	Aga monoto lia patuju-na Alata'ala, na'uli' hewa toi: `Kupahawa' mpai' nabi-ku pai' suro-ku hilou hi tauna toera. Hantongo' -ra mpai' rapatehi, hantongo' -ra rasesa'.'
25456	42	11	50	Ka'omea-na mpai', koi' to tuwu' tempo toi rahuku' sabana hawe'ea nabi to rapatehi ngkai lomo' kajadi' dunia',
25457	42	11	51	ntepu'u ngkai karapatehi-na Habel owi, rata-rata hi karapatehi-na nabi Zakharia, to rapatehi hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala hi olo' meja' pontunua pepue' pai' tomi to moroli'. Wae mpu'u-di! Koi' to tuwu' tempo toi bate rahuku' sabana hawe'ea kasalaa' totu'a-ni toe.
25458	42	11	52	"Silaka-koi guru agama! Kakoo-kono-na, ke koi' -di to mpotudui' ntodea ohea bona mpo'inca Alata'ala. Ntaa' koi' moto uma dota mpotuku' ohea toe, pai' nilawa' lau wo'o-di tauna to doko' mpotuku' -e."
25459	42	11	53	Malai-imi Yesus ngkai ree. Pai' ntepu'u tempo toe, gigi mpu'u-mi nono-ra guru agama pai' to Parisi. Toe pai' rapemai-mai-i hante wori' nyala pompekunea' -ra,
25460	42	11	54	pai' ralelemata ncuu-i, mpali' kasalaa' hi pololita-na.
25461	42	12	1	 Ngkai kamoncobu-ncobu-ra tauna to morumpu doko' mpohilo Yesus, mome'upi' -ra alaa-na momepopongko ngkawiti'. Nto'u toe, Yesus mpololitai ana'guru-na, na'uli': "Mo'inga' -inga' -koi hi ragi-ra to Parisi. Batua-na, neo' nituku' kehi-ra. Apa' hira' toe lompe' hi mali-na-wadi dada'a moto hi rala nono-ra.
25462	42	12	2	Tapi' hawe'ea kehi-ra to tewunii' bate kahiloa mpai'. Pai' hawe'ea to hi rala nono-ra bate telohu mpai'.
25463	42	12	3	Jadi', napa to ni'uli' hi bengi-na bate ralohu hi eo-na. Pai' napa to niwara' -ki doo hi rala tomi to tehohoki, bate ratolele hobo' hi rala ngata.
25464	42	12	4	"Ompi' -ompi', pe'epei lompe' lolita-ku: neo' -koi mpoka'eka' manusia' to doko' mpopatehi-koi, apa' hudu ree-wadi pakulea' -ra.
25465	42	12	5	Sampale-di to kana nipoka'eka', Alata'ala. Apa' mokuasa-i mpatehi-koi, pai' mokuasa wo'o-i mpotadi-koi hi rala naraka. Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi, Hi'a-mi to kana nipoka'eka'.
25466	42	12	6	"Lima ma'a rone biasa-na rapobalu' nte rompepa' doi see-wadi. Aga nau' wae, uma ria hama'aa to uma nakiwoi Pue' Ala.
25467	42	12	7	Peliu-liu-nami koi'. Bangku' kawori' wuluwoo' -ni nabila' pai' na'inca omea. Jadi' neo' -koi me'eka'. Meliu-pi pompewili' -na Alata'ala hi koi' ngkai pompewili' -na rone to wori'.
25468	42	12	8	"Pe'epei lompe' lolita-ku: hema to mpangaku' hi doo kahi'a-na topetuku' -ku, hi'a wo'o mpai' kupangaku' hi nyanyoa hawe'ea mala'eka Alata'ala, ku'uli': `Tau toei topetuku' -ku.'
25469	42	12	9	Aga hema to mposapu-a hi doo, hi'a wo'o mpai' kusapu hi nyanyoa mala'eka Alata'ala, ku'uli': `Bela-i topetuku' -ku.'
25470	42	12	10	"Tauna to ncapuaka-a, Aku' Ana' Manusia', ma'ala-pidi te'ampungi sala' -na. Aga tauna to mporuge' Inoha' Tomoroli', uma-pi ma'ala ampungia sala' -na.
25471	42	12	11	"Ane rakeni-koi hi tomi posampayaa pai' rapakilu-koi hi topohura agama ba topoparenta sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku', neo' -koi me'eka' ba beiwa mpai' tompoi' -ni ba napa mpai' to kana ni'uli'.
25472	42	12	12	Apa' hinto'u toe mpai', Inoha' Tomoroli' moto mpotudui' -koi napa to kana ni'uli'."
25473	42	12	13	 Ria hadua ngkai laintongo' ntodea mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, uli' -ki ompi' -ku bona nawai' -a-kuwo bagia-ku ngkai sosora totu'a-kai."
25474	42	12	14	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ompi', hema to mpo'ongko' -a jadi' topohura to mpobagi-kokoi sosora totu'a-ni?"
25475	42	12	15	Oti toe na'uli' -raka tauna to wori': "Mo'inga' -inga' -koi pai' pelompehi, bona neo' -koi mpokahina ba apa-apa rewa dunia'. Apa' nau' wori' rewa-ta, uma ngkai rewa toe pai' lompe' tuwu' -ta."
25476	42	12	16	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpololitai-ra hante hanyala lolita rapa', na'uli': "Ria hadua topo'ua' to tebua' lompe' -ki polia' -na.
25477	42	12	17	Na'uli' -mi hi rala nono-na: `Napa-le' to kubabehi-e? Uma-pi liu poropo' -ku kupontimamahii wua' polia' -ku.
25478	42	12	18	Aa, kurata reke! Kukero lau-di poropo' -ku, pai' kuwangu to meliu kabohe-na, bona hi retu-mi mpai' pontimamahia hawe'ea pae-ku pai' rewa-ku.
25479	42	12	19	Oti toe mpai', uma-apa mobago, apa' wori' -mi timamahia-ku, hono' nte ba hangkuja mpae kupake'. Wae-pi, ntora-ama, ngkoni', nginu, pai' ntora goe' -a-damo!'
25480	42	12	20	"Ntaa' we'i Alata'ala mpo'uli' -ki tauna toei: `He towojo! Bengi toe mpai' lau, ra'alai' -moko inoha' -nu. Jadi', hawe'ea to nurumpu tetu, hema-mi mpai' pue' -na?'
25481	42	12	21	"Wae-mi katuwu' tauna to doko' mporumpu ka'uaa' hi dunia', tapi' mpe'ahii' tuwu' -ra hi poncilo Alata'ala."
25482	42	12	22	 Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Toe pai' ku'uli' -kokoi, neo' -koi sese' mpopekiri tuwu' -ni. Neo' ni'uli': `Napa-le' to takoni' -e? Napa-le' to tapohea-e?'
25483	42	12	23	Apa' katuwu' -ni meliu ngkai pongkoni' pai' pohea.
25484	42	12	24	Penonoi-dile danci kaa' -e. Uma-ra molia', uma-ra mepae, uma ria poropo' -ra ba wilulu-ra. Aga nau' wae, Alata'ala mpowai' moto-ra pongkoni'. Peliu-liu-nami koi', apa' hi poncilo Alata'ala meliu tuwu' -ni ngkai katuwu' danci, pai' meliu pompewili' -na hi koi' ngkai pompewili' -na hi danci.
25485	42	12	25	Napa wo'o kalaua-na wori' rahi pekiri-ni? Apa' nau' sese' ncuu-ta mpopekiri, uma-ta bisa mpodonihii umuru-ta nau' kampa' hamengi.
25486	42	12	26	Jadi', ane to kedi' toe uma nipakulei' mpobabehi, napa pai' wori' rahi pekiri-ni?
25487	42	12	27	Penonoi-dile katuwu' wunga-e. Uma-ra mobago, uma-ra mpobabehi pohea-ra. Tapi' ku'uli' -kokoi, bangku' Magau' Salomo-hawoe' hante hawe'ea ka'uaa' -na, pohea-na uma hewa kancola wunga toera lau.
25488	42	12	28	Kowo' hi papada tuwu' eo toe lau, mepulo rasuwe oti. Aga nau' wae, Alata'ala mpakancola moto kowo' toe. Peliu-liu-nami koi'! Meliu pompewili' Alata'ala hi koi'. Jadi', napa pai' uma nipangala' pompewili' -nae?
25489	42	12	29	Jadi' neo' -koi sese' rahi mpenonoi napa to nikoni' ba napa to ni'inu. Neo' -koi me'eka'.
25490	42	12	30	Hawe'ea tetu lau to ntora rapali' tauna to uma mpo'incai Alata'ala. Hiaa' Tuama-ni hi suruga mpo'inca kaparaluua-ni.
25491	42	12	31	Kana mengkoru-ta hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ta. Ane toe tababehi, to ntani' -ntani' -na nawai' moto-ta mpai'.
25492	42	12	32	"Koi' to mpotuku' -a, uma-koi hangkuja-na. Aga nau' wae, neo' -koi me'eka'. Apa' Alata'ala Tuama-ni mpopelihi-mokoi ngkai kabula rala-na, napajadi' -koi ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na.
25493	42	12	33	Toe pai' ku'uli', pobalu' -mi rewa-ni, pai' oli-na wai' -raka tokabu. Babehi-mokoi karepe' to uma bisa moheu'. Batua-na, babehi kehi to lompe'. Apa' kehi to lompe' toe ma'ala rarapai' -ki rewa to nitimamahi hi suruga, to uma ria karontoa-na, apa' uma ria to mpanako pai' uma ria anutuwu' to mposerohi.
25494	42	12	34	Apa' hiapa pontimamahia rewa-ta, retu wo'o nono-ta.
25495	42	12	35	
25496	42	12	36	"Neo' -koi lempe', mo'inga' -inga' oa' -koi mpopea karata-ku. Agina-koi hewa batua to mpopea karata-na maradika-ra ngkai posusaa' poncamokoa. Batua toera, sadia-mi pohea-ra, pai' palita-ra rapobaa ncuu, bona ane rata-ipi mpai' maradika-ra pai' -i mpopebea wobo', kaliliu rabea-ki.
25497	42	12	37	Morasi' batua to narata maradika-ra bula-ra mojaga pai' mpopea karata-na. Apa' maradika toei mpai' mpehoo' abe' hi hope' -na, napopohura-ra pai' natonui-ra.
25498	42	12	38	Morasi' mpu'u-ra batua to narata maradika-ra rodo moto-ra mpopea-i, nau' mentongo' bengi ba paia-na liu mentongo' bengi.
25499	42	12	39	"Poinono lolita rapa' -ku toi: Ane na'inca ami' -mi pue' tomi jaa hangkuja topanako rata, bate mojaga-i bona neo' -ra mesua'.
25500	42	12	40	Hewa toe wo'o kana rodo ami' -mokoi mpopea-a, apa' uma ni'incai tempo karata-ku Aku' Ana' Manusia'."
25501	42	12	41	 Napekune' Petrus hi Yesus: "Pue', ba hi kai' -wadi lolita rapa' tetu-e, ba hi ntodea wo'o-di?"
25502	42	12	42	Na'uli' Pue': "Rapa' -na ria hadua batua to monoto nono-na pai' to tida mpobago bago maradika-na. Batua toei na'ongko' maradika-na jadi' topohawa' to mpohawai' batua ntani' -na pai' mpobagi-raka pongkoni' -ra butu eo-na.
25503	42	12	43	Uma mowo kamorasi' -na ane maradika-na rata nculii' ngkai pomakoa' -na pai' mporata-i bula-na mpobago bago-na.
25504	42	12	44	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi, maradika-na mpo'ongko' -i pai' mpowai' -i kuasa mpewili' hawe'ea ka'uaa' -na.
25505	42	12	45	Aga silaka mpai' batua to mpo'uli': `Uma-ile sohi' rata maradika-e.' Natepu'u-mi mpoweba' hingka batua-na ba tobine ba tomane, pai' -i ntora ngkoni' pai' nginu duu' -na palangu-langu.
25506	42	12	46	Ntaa' we'i, bula-na lempe' moto hewa toe, muu-mule' rata-mi maradika-na hi eo pai' hi jaa to uma na'incai. Batua toei raweba' ntarurua' pai' rapetadi hi mali-na, raponcawa tauna to uma mepangala' hi Alata'ala.
25507	42	12	47	"Batua to mpo'inca moto konoa maradika-na, tapi' uma-i mo'inga' -inga' pai' uma nababehi konoa maradika-na, batua toei bate raweba' mperegea.
25508	42	12	48	Aga batua to uma-hawo mpo'incai konoa maradika-na, pai' -i mpobabehi to natao raweba' -ki, raweba' moto-i, aga huka' -na-wadi. Apa' hema to rawai' wori', wori' wo'o to ratuntu' ngkai hi'a. Hema to ratonui wori', rapomperapii' wori' wo'o-i.
25509	42	12	49	"Katumai-ku toi, tumai mpobaa apu hi dunia'. Pai' konoa-ku bona apu toe sohi' rapobaa-mi.
25510	42	12	50	Ria-pidi pontodohakaa to kana kutodohaka, pai' uma oa' rodo nono-ku ane pontodohakaa toe ko'ia madupa'.
25511	42	12	51	Ha ni'uli' -koina katumai-ku toi, tumai mpopohintuwu' tauna? Uma-e'! Katumai-ku toi, tumai mpoposisala tauna.
25512	42	12	52	Ntepu'u ngkai tempo toi, tau hantina to nte lima rala-na hantomi mosisala: tolu hamali, rodua hamali.
25513	42	12	53	To tuama mpo'ewa ana' -na tomane, ana' tomane mpo'ewa tuama-na. To tina mpo'ewa ana' -na tobine, pai' ana' tobine mpo'ewa tina-na. To piniana mpo'ewa minia-na, pai' to minia mpo'ewa piniana-na."
25514	42	12	54	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus hi tauna to wori': "Ane nihilo limu' mehupa' tono' hi kasoloa, ni'uli' udaa mpai'. Udaa mpu'u.
25515	42	12	55	Ane mewui ngolu' ngkai tono' selatan, ni'uli' mara eo mpai', pai' bate wae mpu'u.
25516	42	12	56	He koi' to lompe' hi mali-na-wadi! Ni'inca lia mpelence tanda hi langi' pai' hi dunia'. Napa-di pai' uma ni'incai mpelence napa to nababehi Pue' Ala tempo toi!
25517	42	12	57	"Napa pai' uma oa' nipakanoto nono-ni pai' mpangaku' napa to monoa'!
25518	42	12	58	Ane rapa' -na ria to doko' mpakilu-ta hi totu'a ngata, agina tahuduwukui mpo'oti kara-kara-ta bula-ta hi lengko ohea-pidi. Nee-neo' mpai' nakeni mpu'u-ta hi topohura, pai' topohura mpai' mpotonu-ta hi polisi, pai' polisi mpopesua' -ta hi rala tarungku'.
25519	42	12	59	Mpu'u ku'uli': uma-tapa tebahaka ngkai rala tarungku' ane da koo-ko'ia oti tabayari waya' -ta."
25520	42	13	1	 Nto'u toe wo'o-hawo, ria tauna mpololitai Yesus, mpololita ba hangkuja dua to Galilea to rapatehi ntuku' hawa' Pilatus bula-ra mpotonu pepue' -ra hi Pue' Ala.
25521	42	13	2	Mpotompoi' lolita toe, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Ba ni'uli' -koina wae, pai' hewa toe rahi kamate-ra to Galilea toera, apa' meliu jeko' -ra ngkai hawe'ea to Galilea to ntani' -na?
25522	42	13	3	Uma-e' waetu! Ku'uli' -kokoi: ane uma-koi medea ngkai jeko' -ni, bate rahuku' wo'o-koiwo mpai' omea.
25523	42	13	4	Wae wo'o to hampulu' walu to mate nadungkahi tomi to molangko hi Siloam. Apa' oo-raka kamate-rae, meka' ba lue' ni'uli' melabi-rana sala' -ra ngkai hawe'ea to Yerusalem?
25524	42	13	5	Uma-e' waetu! Ku'uli' -kokoi: ane uma-koi medea ngkai jeko' -ni, bate rahuku' wo'o-koiwo mpai' omea."
25525	42	13	6	 Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka lolita rapa' toi. Na'uli': "Ria hadua tauna to mpohu'a kaju ara hi pampa-na. Hangkani hilou-imi mpongoa' -ngoa' ba ria wua' -na. Ntaa' uma-di ria hamehaa' -e.
25526	42	13	7	Toe pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki tompodoo pampa-na: `Hilo, tolu mpae-mi ntora tumai-a mpehiloi kaju toei ba ria wua' -na, uma oa' ria. Toki lau-mi! Napa kalaua-na tuwu' hi rehe'i mpe'oti mara rudu' tana'.'
25527	42	13	8	"Na'uli' tompodoo pampa toei: `Pelele' -mi ulu tuwu' hampae toi-pi Maradika. Kukawahi-damo, pai' kutaui' tana' to morudu' ngkai mali-na.
25528	42	13	9	Meka' ba lue' mowua' -i-hawo mpai' mpae boko'. Ane uma oa' -i mowua', tatoki-imi.'"
25529	42	13	10	 Hangkani, Yesus metudui' hi tomi posampayaa nto'u Eo Sabat, eo pepuea' -ra to Yahudi.
25530	42	13	11	Hi ree, ria hadua tobine, hampulu' walu mpae-imi peda', apa' napesuai' seta-i. Tobine toei bungku', uma nakulei' mokore monoa'.
25531	42	13	12	Kanahilo-na Yesus tobine toei, nakio' -i pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ina', mo'uri' -moko, uma-pi ria haki' to mpohoo' -ko."
25532	42	13	13	Oti toe najama tobine toei, kaliliu mokore monoa' -imi, pai' -i mpo'une' Alata'ala.
25533	42	13	14	Ngkai ree, kamoroe-nami pangkeni tomi posampayaa toei, apa' Yesus mpaka'uri' tauna hi Eo Sabat. Toe pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka tauna to wori': "Ono eo, eo pobagoa-ta. Hi eo toe, ma'ala-koi tumai mpopepaka'uri', neo' hi Eo Sabat!"
25534	42	13	15	Na'uli' Pue' Yesus: "He koi' to lompe' hi mali-na-wadi! Hi Eo Sabat, hema-ta to uma mpobahaka japi ba jara' -ta, takeni hilou hi mali gimpu pai' tapoponginu?
25535	42	13	16	Hiaa' hi rehe'i, ria hadua tobine muli Abraham, hampulu' walu mpae-imi nahoo' Magau' Anudaa'. Ha uma-hana ma'ala tabahaka-i ngkai pohoo' -na hi Eo Sabat?"
25536	42	13	17	Lolita-na Yesus tohe'e mpo'eai' bali' -na. Tapi' ane ntodea, goe' -ra-rana mpohilo hawe'ea anu mekoncehi to nababehi.
25537	42	13	18	 Ngkai ree, na'uli' Yesus: "Ane Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia', beiwa kajadi' -na? Kajadi' -nale, hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i:
25538	42	13	19	Ria hadua tauna ngala' unto' hawi, lou nahawu' hi pampa-na. Unto' toe tuwu' kaboo-bohea, duu' -na jadi' hangkaju kaju, pai' danci mpobabehi peta-ra hi ra'a-na."
25539	42	13	20	Oti toe, na'uli' wo'o-mi: "Ane Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia', kajadi' -na hewa lolita rapa' tohe'i:
25540	42	13	21	Hadua tobine mpo'ala' ragi hangkedi', nagalo hante lunu to wori'. Mahae-hae, woke' -mi omea."
25541	42	13	22	Rala pomakoa' -na hilou hi Yerusalem, Yesus mpotara ngata to bohe pai' ngata to kedi', mpotudui' tauna.
25542	42	13	23	 Ria hadua tauna mpekune' -i: "Pue', ba hangkedi' -wadi tauna to mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae?" Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ntodea:
25543	42	13	24	"Mporata katuwua' to lompe' -le, ma'ala rarapai' -ki tauna to mesua' ntara hi wobo' to jopi'. Pari-pari-koi mesua' ntara wobo' to jopi' toe. Apa' wori' -hana mpai' to mpali' ohea-ra mesua', aga uma-rapa ma'ala mesua'.
25544	42	13	25	Apa' rata mpai' tempo-na, mokore-imi pue' tomi toe hilou mpo'unca wobo'. Ane rapa' -na mokore hi mali-na-pidi-koi nto'u toe, mpopebea wobo' -koi, ni'uli': `Pue', bea-kaka-kaiwo!' "Natompoi' -koi mpai': `Uma-koi ku'incai, ba to ngkaiapa-koi.'
25545	42	13	26	"Ni'uli' -ki: `Ei'! Ngkoni' pai' nginu-madakaie dohe-nue Pue'! Ria-moko metudui' hi rala ngata-kai!'
25546	42	13	27	"Na'uli' -kokoi mpai': `Uma-koi ku'incai ba to ngkaiapa-koi. Palai-koi ngkai rei, koi' paka' to mo'ingku dada'a.'
25547	42	13	28	"Nto'u toe mpai', geo' pai' ntodohaka-mokoi, apa' nihilo Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub hante hawe'ea nabi, mohura goe' -goe' -ra hi rala Kamagaua' Alata'ala, hiaa' koi' ra'uncahi hi mali-na.
25548	42	13	29	Wori' wo'o mpai' tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi to jadi' ntodea Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na. Tumai-ra ngkai tono' mata'eo pai' ngkai kasoloa pai' ngkai humalili' dunia', mohura goe' -goe' omea-ra mpai' mpokaralai posusaa' hi rala Kamagaua' Alata'ala.
25549	42	13	30	Ka'omea-na mpai', wori' tauna to kedi' tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' bohe tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno. Pai' wori' tauna to bohe tuwu' -ra tempo toi jadi' kedi' tuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno."
25550	42	13	31	 Nto'u toe wo'o, ria ba hangkuja dua to Parisi rata hi Yesus pai' mpo'uli' -ki: "Malai-moko ngkai rei, apa' Magau' Herodes doko' mpopatehi-ko."
25551	42	13	32	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Koi', uli' -ki tope'akalai tetui hewa tohe'i: Eo toe lau pai' mepulo, mobago-a-pidi, mpopalai seta pai' mpaka'uri' topeda'. Pai' hi eo katolu-na, kupohudu-mi pobago-ku.
25552	42	13	33	Aga eo toe mpai' lau, mepulo pai' romengi mpai', bate kana kaliliu-ama mpotoa' Yerusalem. Apa' uma-hawo masipato' hadua nabi rapatehi hi ngata ntani' -na, kana hi ngata Yerusalem.
25553	42	13	34	"Ee to Yerusalem! to Yerusalem! Nipatehi-ra-koina nabi-nabi, pai' nipana' watu-ra-koina tauna to nasuro-kokoi Alata'ala. Wori' ngkani-mi kupehuka' ngkupui-koi, hewa hama'a manu' tina mpo'urui ana' -na hi une' pani' -na, aga uma-koi dota.
25554	42	13	35	Jadi', bona ni'inca: Tomi pepuea' -ni napalahii-kokoi mpai' Pue' Ala. Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi, uma-apa nihiloi, duu' -na rata tempo-na ni'uli': `Une' -imi to rata mpokeni hanga' Pue' Ala!'"
25555	42	14	1	 Hangkani nto'u Eo Sabat, Yesus hilou ngkoni' hi tomi hadua pangkeni to Parisi. Bula-na hi ree, ralelemata-i mpopali' sala' -na.
25556	42	14	2	Muu-mule' rata hadua tauna to mohaki' ngkumowu, mowoto witi' pai' pale-na.
25557	42	14	3	Yesus mpekune' -ra guru agama pai' to Parisi, na'uli': "Ntuku' atura agama-ta, ma'ala-ta mpaka'uri' topeda' hi Eo Sabat, ba uma-di?"
25558	42	14	4	Guru agama pai' to Parisi toera, oja' -ra mpotompoi' -i. Ngkai ree, Yesus mpojama topeda' toei, napaka'uri' pai' nahubui-i hilou.
25559	42	14	5	Oti toe na'uli' -raka: "Ane rapa' -na ria ana' -ta ba japi-ta monawu' hi rala buwu hi Eo Sabat, ha uma sahu ta'ore' -i tumai, nau' hi eo pepuea' -e?"
25560	42	14	6	Aga uma hema to daho' mpohono' -i.
25561	42	14	7	 Hi tomi to Parisi toe, Yesus mpohilo ria torata to doko' mohura hi pohuraa karabilaa'. Toe pai' natudui' -ra hante lolita rapa' toi.
25562	42	14	8	Na'uli': "Ane rakio' -ko hilou hi posusaa' poncamokoa, neo' mohura hi pohuraa karabilaa'. Meka' ba ria-di mpai' to rakio' to meliu karabila' -na ngkai iko.
25563	42	14	9	Tumai mpai' pue' tomi mpo'uli' -koko hewa toi: `Wai' -ki hi'a-hana pohuraa tetu!' Me'ea' -ko mpai' hilou mohura hi kadingkia' -na.
25564	42	14	10	Jadi', ane rakio' -ko hilou hi posusaa', agina mohura-ko hi kadingkia' -na, bona pue' tomi mpai' mpo'uli' -koko: `Bale, mai-ta mohura hi pohuraa to lompe' toe mai.' Ane hewa toe, rabila' lau-moko hi mata ntodea.
25565	42	14	11	Hawe'ea to mpomolangko nono-ra, Pue' Ala mpodingkihi-ra, pai' hawe'ea to mpakadingki' nono-ra, Pue' Ala mpomolangko-ra."
25566	42	14	12	Oti toe, mololita wo'o-imi Yesus mpololitai pue' tomi. Na'uli': "Ane takio' tauna ngkaralai posusa' -ta, ba ngkoni' mpo'eo ba ngkabengia, neo' mpokio' bale-ta, ompi' -ta, ba topo'ua' rala ngata. Apa' bate rakio' wo'o-ta mpai', alaa-na tehiwili-mi kehi-ta.
25567	42	14	13	Jadi' ane tababehi posusa', kio' tauna tokabu, tokeru, topungku pai' towero.
25568	42	14	14	Ane wae pobabehi-ta, Pue' Ala mpogane' -ta mpai', apa' tauna to hewa toe uma mpokulei' mpohiwili kehi-ta. Kehi-ta tetu nahiwili moto mpai' Pue' Ala hi Eo Kiama, nto'u kanapotuwu' -ra nculii' tauna to monoa' hi poncilo-na."
25569	42	14	15	 Bula-ra ngkoni' toe, hadua torata mpo'epe lolita-na Yesus, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Marasi' tauna to mpokaralai posusa' hi rala Kamagaua' -na Alata'ala."
25570	42	14	16	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki tauna toei: "Hangkani ria hadua tauna to mpobabehi susa' bohe, pai' mpokio' wori' tauna.
25571	42	14	17	Sadia-mi omea, nahubui pahawaa' -na hilou mpo'uli' -raka to rakio': `Mai-tamo hilou hi posusaa', apa' sadia-mi omea.'
25572	42	14	18	Aga tauna to rakio' toera, motance omea-ra. To lomo' -na mpo'uli': `Lako' me'oli tana' -a, pai' kana hilou ulu kupehiloi. Merapi' ampu-a, uma-a tilou.'
25573	42	14	19	To hadua-na mpo'uli': `Lako' mpo'oli japi-a lima moko, hilou kuperao mpake' -ra mopajeko'. Merapi' ampu-a, uma-a tilou!'
25574	42	14	20	To ntani' -na wo'o mpo'uli': `Aku' lako' oti ncamoko-a. Uma-a bisa tilou.'
25575	42	14	21	"Pahawaa' toei nculii' hilou hi pue' susa' mpowoli' lolita-ra toe. Uma-pi mowo kamoroe-na pue' susa', na'uli' -ki pahawaa' -na: `Pesahui hilou hi karajaa pai' hi porompengaa ohea hi rala ngata. Bawai-ramo tumai tokabu, tokeru, towero, pai' topungku.' Hilou mpu'u-imi-hawo pahawaa' toei mpotuku' hawa' pue' susa'.
25576	42	14	22	"Karata-na nculii', na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki pue' susa': `Tuama, hawa' -nu kupopomako' -mi, aga ko'ia ihia' tomi-nu, ria-pidi pohuraa.'
25577	42	14	23	"Na'uli' pue' susa': `Hilou tena-ko hi ohea bohe pai' ohea to kedi' hi mali ngata, pewuku-ra tauna tumai, bona tomi-ku ihia' hobo'.
25578	42	14	24	Mpu'u ku'uli', ngkai hawe'ea tauna to kukio' toera lou, uma haduaa-ra to mpokoni' ba apa-apa hi posusa' -ku.'"
25579	42	14	25	 Wori' tauna mpotuku' Yesus rala pomakoa' -na. Yesus mewili' hi tauna toera pai' na'uli' -raka:
25580	42	14	26	"Tauna to doko' mpotuku' -a, aga uma meliu pe'ahi' -na hi Aku' ngkai pe'ahi' -na hi tina-na, tuama-na, tobine-na, ana' -na, ompi' -na, ba paiana woto-na moto-mi, uma-i ma'ala jadi' topetuku' -ku.
25581	42	14	27	Tauna to jadi' topetuku' -ku kana mpopaha'a kaju parika' -na-- batua-na kana sadia-i mporata kaparia ba paiana rapatehi sabana petuku' -na hi Aku'. Jadi', tauna to uma dota mpopaha'a kaju parika' -na pai' mpotuku' -a, uma-i ma'ala jadi' topetuku' -ku.
25582	42	14	28	"Ane ria to doko' mpowangu tomi bohe, napohura-ki ulu mporeke ongkoso' pompowangu-na, ba hono' mpai' doi-na ba uma-di.
25583	42	14	29	Apa' ane mpolia' natu'u-mi parawatu-na pai' uma hudu nawangu apa' naka'otii doi-na, hawe'ea tauna to mpohilo mpotawai-i,
25584	42	14	30	ra'uli': `Ii, ni'anu-di doko' mpowangu tomi bohe, ntaa' uma-di hono' doi-nae!'
25585	42	14	31	"Wae wo'o, ane hadua magau' to ria tantara-na hampulu' ncobu manga'e hante hadua magau' to ria tantara-na rompulu' ncobu, kana napekiri ncala', ba rakule' mpo'ewa-ra ba uma-di.
25586	42	14	32	Ane na'inca ka'uma-na mpai' hompe tantara-na, molaa-pidi bali' -na, nahubui-mi suro hilou mpali' kahintuwuaa'."
25587	42	14	33	Yesus mpokaliliu lolita-na, na'uli': "Wae wo'o koi', ane uma-koi mpobahaka hawe'ea to ria hi koi', uma-koi ma'ala jadi' topetuku' -ku.
25588	42	14	34	"Poi', wori' kalaua-na. Aga ane mobali' -mi kapoi' -na alaa-na uma-pi mopoi', napa tena to ma'ala mpakapoi' -i?
25589	42	14	35	Uma ntoto-pi ria tuju-na, ba raruduhi-ki hinu'a ba rapopai-pai. Agina ratadi lau-imi. Hema-koi to tilingaa, pe'epei lompe'!"
25590	42	15	1	 Rala-na ha'eo, wori' topesingara' paja' pai' tau ntani' -na to ra'uli' ntodea dada'a kehi-ra rata mpo'epe lolita Yesus.
25591	42	15	2	To Parisi pai' guru agama mporuge' -i, ra'uli': "Ii, tau toe-idi mai mpobale-raka topojeko', pai' ngkoni' dohe-rae."
25592	42	15	3	Toe pai' Yesus mpololitai-ra hante lolita rapa' toi.
25593	42	15	4	Na'uli': "Rapa' -na ria doo-ta to ria-ki bima-na ha'atu ma'a. Ane moronto hama'a, napa to nababehi? Bate napalahii bima-na to sio mpulu' sio hi papada, pai' -i hilou mpali' bima-na to moronto duu' -na narua'.
25594	42	15	5	Ane narua' -pi, uma mowo kagoe' -na. Ngkai kagoe' -na napololopongko' bima-na toei, pai' nakeni nculii' hilou hi tomi-na.
25595	42	15	6	Oti toe, pai' -i mpokio' bale-na pai' tongki-na, na'uli' -raka: `Mai-mokoi goe' dohe-ku. Apa' bima-ku to moronto kurua' nculii' -imi.'
25596	42	15	7	Wae wo'o, ane hadua topojeko' medea ngkai jeko' -na, meliu kagoe' -ra ihi' suruga mpokagoe' -i ngkai kagoe' -ra mpokagoe' sio mpulu' sio tauna to monoa' po'ingku-ra, to uma-ra-rana mingki' medea.
25597	42	15	8	"Rapa' -na ria hadua tobine to ria-ki hampulu' mpepa' doi pera' -na. Ane moronto hampepa', napa to nababehi? Mposuwe palita-i pai' -i mpehaii tomi-na, pai' napali' hiapa-apa karontoa-na, duu' -na narua'.
25598	42	15	9	Wae kanarua' -na, nakio' -ramo bale-na pai' tongki-na, na'uli' -raka: `Mai-mokoi goe' dohe-ku. Apa' kurua' nculii' -mi doi-ku to moronto.'
25599	42	15	10	Wae wo'o-ra mala'eka Alata'ala mpokagoe' hadua tauna topojeko' to medea ngkai jeko' -na."
25600	42	15	11	 Na'uli' tena Yesus: "Ria hadua tuama to ria-ki rodua ana' -na tomane.
25601	42	15	12	Tokahudu mpo'uli' -ki tuama-ra: `Mama, wai' ami' -ama-kuna bagia-ku ngkai rewa-nu.' Jadi', nabagi mpu'u-mi rewa-na hi ana' -na to rodua toera.
25602	42	15	13	"Ba hangkuja eo olo' -na ngkai ree, ana' -na tokahudu mpobalu' bagia-na, pai' -i hilou hi ngata to molaa. Hi ria-i mpo'oti mara doi-na hante kehi to uma tumotoa.
25603	42	15	14	Ka'oti doi-na omea, ria-mi oro' hi ngata toe, duu' -na mpe'ahii' -mi tuwu' -na.
25604	42	15	15	Hilou-imi hi pue' ngata doko' ngkoni' gaji'. Pue' ngata toei mpohubui-i mpodoo wawu-na.
25605	42	15	16	Ngkai kamo'oro' -na, mehina-imi-hawo doko' mpokoni' kano wawu. Hiaa' uma hema to mpowai' -i pongkoni'.
25606	42	15	17	"Ka'omea-na, mokanono-imi, na'uli': `Topobago hi tomi tuama-kule, melabi lia pongkoni' -ra. Hiaa' aku' -mi-kuna hi rehe'i, neo' mate modupu' -ama.
25607	42	15	18	Wae-pi, nculii' -ama hilou hi tuama-ku, ku'uli' -damo-ki: Mama, masala' -ama hi Pue' Ala pai' hi Mama wo'o.
25608	42	15	19	Uma-apa natao nukio' ana' -nu Mama. Agina nuponcawa batua-nua-damo.'
25609	42	15	20	Kame'ongko' -nami hilou hi tuama-na. "Molaa-i-pidi ngkai tomi-na, pehilo-mi tuama-na. Ngkai kama'ahi' -na, pokeno-nami hilou mpohirua' -ki ana' -na, nakupui pai' na'eki.
25610	42	15	21	Na'uli' -mi to ana': `Mama, masala' -ama hi Pue' Ala pai' hi Mama wo'o. Uma-apa natao nukio' ana' -nu....'
25611	42	15	22	"Aga tuama-na mpokio' topobago-na, pai' na'uli' -raka: `Pesahui, ala' pohea to lompe' lia, pai' heai-i. Uncoi' karawe-na hante hinci, pai' sapatui' wo'o-i.
25612	42	15	23	Oti toe, hilou-koi mpohoko' ana' japi to morudu' pai' nisumale'. Ngkoni' -ta goe' -goe'!
25613	42	15	24	Apa' ana' -ku tohe'ii, ma'ala-mi ta'uli' mate-imi, aga tuwu' nculii' -imi. Moronto-i, aga kurua' nculii' -imi.' Kamosusa' -rami.
25614	42	15	25	"Nto'u toe, lingku' ana' -na to ulumua' hi bonea. Ponculi' -na ngkai bonea, mohu' -mi hi tomi, na'epe-hawo to molalowe pai' moni karamea.
25615	42	15	26	Nakio' hadua topobago-ra, napompekunei' ba moapa-ra hi tomi.
25616	42	15	27	Na'uli' topobago toei: `Tu'ai-nule, rata nculii' -imi-hawo! Tuama-nu mpehubui mposumale' ana' japi to morudu', apa' ana' -na to moronto narua' nculii' -mi hante kalompea' -na.'
25617	42	15	28	"Kamoroe-nami ana' to ulumua' toei, oja' -i mesua' hi rala tomi. Tuama-na hilou mpobawai-i mesua'.
25618	42	15	29	Tapi' na'uli' to ana': `Mompae-mpae-ama mobago huduwuku-ku mpobago-koko Mama. Uma-kuna hangkania-a mposapuaka hawa' -nu. Hiaa' ntahawe' hama'a kebe' -kuwo, ko'ia-kuna ria nuwai' -a bona kubabehi-kuwo kagoea' hante bale-ku.
25619	42	15	30	Hiaa' ana' -nu tetui to mpe'oti hinyai' rewa-nu hante tobine to ele', wae kanculii' -na nusumale' lau-ki japi to morudu'!'
25620	42	15	31	"Na'uli' tuama-na: `Ana', iko-le tida dohe-ku oa' -ko-kona. Ihi' tomi-kule, iko wo'o pue' -na.
25621	42	15	32	Hiaa' toto-na lia-ta mosusa' goe' -goe', apa' tu'ai-nu to mate-imi-hana, tuwu' nculii' -imi. Moronto-imi, tapi' tarua' nculii' -imi-hawo.'"
25622	42	16	1	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Ria hadua topo'ua', pai' ria-ki hadua topobago-na to ngkakamu doi-na. Ria to mpakilu topobago toei hi topo'ua', ra'uli': `Ntora napewai' mara-hana doi-nu!'
25623	42	16	2	Toe pai' topo'ua' toei mpokio' topobago-na, na'uli' -ki: `Napa-di to ku'epe to rapakilu-koko toi-e? Wae lau, popehuwu-ka hawe'ea buku popa'intaa. Ngkai eo toe lau, uma-pi iko to ngkakamu ka'uaa' -ku!'
25624	42	16	3	"Mokanono-imi topobago toei, na'uli': `Napa-le' to kubabehi-e? Naleso' -ama mpai' sepu' -ku ngkai bago-ku. Momangki uma kukulei'. Kakarapi' -rapi', me'ea' -a.'
25625	42	16	4	Ngkai ree na'uli': `Aa, ria akala-ku! Apa' neo' raleso' -ama ngkai bago-kue, agina mpali' ncala' -a bale-ku wori' -wori', bona hira' mpai' mpotarima-a hi tomi-ra.'
25626	42	16	5	"Jadi' ngkai ree, nakio' -mi butu dua tauna to mo'inta hi sepu' -na. Hi to lomo' -na na'uli': `Hangkuja inta-nu hi sepu' -ku?'
25627	42	16	6	"Metompoi' tauna toei: `Tolu ncobu lite lana.' "Na'uli' topobago toei: `Oi sura popa'intaa-nu. Mohura-moko, uki' pesahui, hancobu lima atu lite-wadi!'
25628	42	16	7	"Oti toe, pai' na'uli' -ki karodua-na: `Hiaa' iko, hangkuja-kowo inta-nu?' "Natompoi' -hawo: `Hancobu karu' pae.' "Na'uli' topobago toei: `Ohe'i sura inta-nu, uki' -mi walu atu karu' -wadi.'
25629	42	16	8	"Kana'epe-na topo'ua' napa to nababehi topobago-na to bengku' gau' -na tetui, na'une' lau-imi, apa' pante-i-hana mpali' akala-na bona lompe' katuwu' -na. Apa' tauna to uma mpo'incai Pue' Ala, meliu kapante-ra mpo'urusi katuwu' -ra hante hingka doo-ra, ngkai kapante-ra tauna to hi rala kabajaa-na Pue' Ala mpo'urusi katuwu' -ra hi eo mpeno.
25630	42	16	9	"Toe pai' ku'uli' -kokoi: Kana tapake' ka'uaa' hi dunia' tohe'i mpotulungi doo, bona ane uma-pi mpai' mokalaua ka'uaa' dunia' toi, ratarima lompe' -ta hi po'ohaa' to tida duu' kahae-hae-na.
25631	42	16	10	Tauna to ma'ala rasarumaka hante rewa to hangkedi', ma'ala wo'o-i rasarumaka hante rewa to wori'. Tauna to uma monoa' kehi-na hante rewa to hangkedi', uma wo'o mpai' monoa' kehi-na hante rewa to wori'.
25632	42	16	11	Jadi', ane uma lompe' pompewili' -ta hi ka'uaa' dunia' tohe'i, hema to mposarumaka-ta hi poko ka'uaa' to hi suruga?
25633	42	16	12	Ane uma lompe' pompewili' -ta hi rewa to rasarumaka-taka hi dunia' toi, hema mpai' to mpowai' -ta rewa to jadi' anu-ta moto hi suruga?
25634	42	16	13	"Uma-hawo ria hadua topobago mobago hi rodua tua. Apa' hadua mpai' nape'ahi', hadua napokahuku'. Hadua natuku' -ki hawa' -na, hadua nasapuaka. Wae wo'o koi', uma-koi bisa mpotuku' konoa Alata'ala, pai' hamali-koi ntora mporumpu rewa dunia'."
25635	42	16	14	To Parisi mpo'epe hawe'ea lolita Yesus toe. Rapotawai lau-i-wadi, apa' hira' toe-mi to mpokahina doi.
25636	42	16	15	Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Koi' tetu-mi mpemanoa' po'ingku-ni hi poncilo manusia'. Aga Alata'ala mpo'inca ihi' nono-ni. Apa' napa to rabila' manusia', napokahuku' Alata'ala.
25637	42	16	16	"Napa to te'uki' hi rala Atura Musa pai' sura nabi bate-na rapake' -pidi duu' rata hi tempo Yohanes Topeniu'. Ngkai tempo toe, rapalele-mi Kareba Lompe' to mpo'uli' Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Pai' wori' tauna mpohuduwukui doko' jadi' ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na toe.
25638	42	16	17	Tapi' butu mela to te'uki' hi rala Atura Pue' bate kana madupa'. Mojoli-pi langi' pai' dunia' mokero, ngkai hamela lolita hi rala Atura Pue' uma madupa'.
25639	42	16	18	"Hema to mpogaa' -ki tobine-na pai' ncamoko hante tobine ntani' -na, mobualo' -i-hana. Pai' tauna to mpotobine kabulisa doo, mobualo' wo'o-i-hawo.
25640	42	16	19	 "Ria hadua topo'ua'. Pohea-na hewa pohea magau', paka' to masuli' oli-na. Tuwu' -na butu eo-na hewa toposusa' -damo.
25641	42	16	20	Hi wobo' -na ratu'u hadua tauna to kabu, hanga' -na Lazarus. Woto-na hobo' paka' waka'.
25642	42	16	21	Doko' -i-hawo ngkoni' rupu' to mohewu' ngkai meja' topo'ua' toei. Wae-mi-hawo kampe'ahii' -na, rata wo'o-pi dike' mpojilai' waka' -na.
25643	42	16	22	"Rala-na ha'eo, mate-imi tokabu toei, pai' mala'eka mpokeni-i hilou hi pohuraa to lompe' hi ncori Abraham. Topo'ua' toei, mate wo'o-imi-hawo, pai' -i ratana.
25644	42	16	23	Hi po'ohaa' tomate, ntora ntodohaka-i. Hampengoa' -na ngkai ree, nahilo-hawo molaa lia, oe-imi mai Abraham, hante Lazarus mohura hi ncori-na.
25645	42	16	24	Pekio' -nami topo'ua' toei, na'uli': `Mama Abraham! Poka'ahi' -a-kuwo! Hubui-i Lazarus mpotubu' karawe-na hi rala ue pai' tumai natudohi-ka-kuwo jila' -ku. Pepa rahi-mi ku'epe rala apu tohe'i!'
25646	42	16	25	"Na'uli' Abraham: `Kiwoi-dile ana': Bula-nu tuwu' -pidi hi rala dunia', iko mporata hawe'ea to lompe', hiaa' Lazarus-hana mporata-i paka' to dada'a. Tempo toi, tetanta'u-imi hi rehe'i, pai' iko-kowo, mporata pepa-moko.
25647	42	16	26	Hiaa' etu, hi olo' -ta ria tumata to bohe lia. Tauna ngkai rehe'i uma bisa tilou hi retu, pai' tauna ngkai retu uma bisa tumai hi rehe'i.'
25648	42	16	27	"Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o topo'ua' toei: `Ane wae-di Mama, kuperapi' bona nuhubui-i Lazarus hilou hi tomi tuama-ku.
25649	42	16	28	Apa' ria-ra-pidi lima ompi' -ku. Hubui-i Lazarus mpopo'ingai' -ra bona neo' -ra mpai' tumai hi po'ohaa' pontodohakaa toi.'
25650	42	16	29	"Na'uli' Abraham: `Ria-miraka sura to na'uki' Musa pai' nabi-nabi ntani' -na. Mpotuku' napa to te'uki' hi rala sura toe-ra-damo-rawo.'
25651	42	16	30	"Na'uli' topo'ua' toei: `Ane muntu' toe-wadi, uma hono'! Kana ria tomate tuwu' nculii' hilou mpololitai-ra, pai' lako' medea-rada ngkai jeko' -ra!'
25652	42	16	31	"Na'uli' Abraham: `Ane lolita nabi Musa pai' nabi ntani' -na uma rapangalai', uma oa' -ra mpai' mepangala', nau' gati ria mpu'u tomate tuwu' nculii'.'"
25653	42	17	1	 Yesus mpololitai ana'guru-na, na'uli': "Bate ria to mpopanawu' tauna alaa-ra mojeko'. Aga silaka-ra tauna to mepanawu' toera!
25654	42	17	2	Agina lau-pi hameha' watu po'ahaa' ratoe hi wuroko' -ra, pai' -ra ratene' hi rala tahi', ngkai mpopanawu' -ra nau' hadua tauna to hangkedi' pepangala' -na duu' -na mpobabehi jeko'.
25655	42	17	3	Toe pai' kana mo'inga' -inga' -ta! "Ane ompi' -ta mpobabehi to sala' hi kita', tudui' -i. Ane soho' -pi nono-na, ampungi-i.
25656	42	17	4	Nau' pitu ngkani rala-na ha'eo-i masala' hi kita', pai' butu ngkani-na tumai-i merapi' ampu, ampungi-i-hawo."
25657	42	17	5	Ra'uli' suro Pue' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Pue', pakaroho-kaka-kaiwo pepangala' -kai!"
25658	42	17	6	Na'uli' Pue' Yesus: "Ane rii-ria-mi pepangala' -ni nau' hangkutuno' -wadi, ma'ala ni'uli' -ki kaju to bohe tohe'i: `Mowuka-moko ngkai rei, mentoli-ko ree mai hi rala tahi'!' bate mentoli mpu'u-i ntuku' hawa' -ni.
25659	42	17	7	"Rapa' -na ria batua-ta to molia' ba to mpodoo porewua. Ane nculii' -i ngkai pehompoa-na, napa to ta'uli' -ki? Ba ta'uli' wae: `Sahu tumai ngkoni''?
25660	42	17	8	Uma-hawo. Tantu ta'uli' -ki hewa tohe'i: `Porodo-mi pongkoni' -ku! Moheai-ko to uma babo'. Peka'au-a bula-ku nginu pai' ngkoni'. Oti-a-damo ngkoni', pai' lako' ngkoni' -dako-kowo.'
25661	42	17	9	Uma-hawo mingki' ta'uli' tarima kasi hi batua-ta, apa' muntu' mpotuku' hawa' -i-wadi.
25662	42	17	10	Wae wo'o koi'. Ane oti-mi nituku' hawe'ea to napahawa' -kokoi Alata'ala, uli' -mi-hana: `Kai' -kaiwo-le, batua biasa-wadi-ka-kaiwo. To kibabehi-le, muntu' to rapahawa' -kakai.'"
25663	42	17	11	 Rala pomakoa' -na hilou hi Yerusalem, Yesus ntara hi sipa' tana' to Samaria pai' to Galilea.
25664	42	17	12	Kamesua' -na hi rala ngata, rata-mi hampulu' topohaki' poko' mpohirua' -ki. Ngkai molaa-ra-wadi mekio',
25665	42	17	13	ra'uli': "Yesus! Guru! Poka'ahi' -ka-kaiwo!"
25666	42	17	14	Kanahilo-ra Yesus, na'uli' -miraka: "Hilou-mokoi mpopehuwu woto-ni hi imam." Hilou mpu'u-ramo. Bula-ra momako', mo'uri' -ramo.
25667	42	17	15	Kanahilo-na to hadua mo'uri' -imi, kanculii' -nami hilou hi Yesus, mpo'une' -une' Alata'ala napesukui.
25668	42	17	16	Karata-na hi Yesus, motingkua' -imi mpo'uli' tarima kasi. Hi'a toei to Samaria.
25669	42	17	17	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ha uma hampulu' to kupaka'uri' -e? Hiapa-ramo to sio?
25670	42	17	18	Beiwa pai' muntu' hadua toei-wadi to nculii' mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala-e? Hiaa' bela-i he'e to Yahudi!"
25671	42	17	19	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi mpo'uli' -ki tauna toei: "Mokore-moko, pai' -ko hilou-mi. Mo'uri' -moko sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'."
25672	42	17	20	 Ba hangkuja dua to Parisi mpekune' Yesus, nto'uma Alata'ala tumai jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Na'uli' Yesus: "Kamagaua' Alata'ala-le uma ntepu'u hante tanda-tanda to kahiloa.
25673	42	17	21	Uma mpai' ria to mpo'uli': `Hilo, ohe'i-mi Kamagaua' -na Alata'ala,' ba `Etu-mi mai Kamagaua' Alata'ala,' apa' Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi laintongo' -ni."
25674	42	17	22	Oti toe, Yesus mpololitai ana'guru-na. Na'uli': "Rata mpai' tempo-na, doko' lia-koi mpohilo-a nau' kampa' ha'eo, aga uma-apa nihiloi.
25675	42	17	23	Nto'u toe mpai', ria to mpo'uli' -kokoi: `Magau' Topetolo' oe-imi ria!' Ba ria to mpo'uli': `Ohe'i-imi!' Aga neo' -koi hilou mpotuku' -ra!
25676	42	17	24	Apa' ane rata nculii' mpu'u-apa mpai', karata-ku incana hobo' hi dunia'. Hewa kila' mpohinii raoa ngkai wuntu-na hamali rata hi wuntu-na hamali, hewa toe wo'o mpai' hi eo karataa-ku, Aku' Ana' Manusia'.
25677	42	17	25	Aga lomo' -lomo' -na, kana rasesa' -a pai' rasapuaka tauna to tuwu' tempo toi.
25678	42	17	26	"Hewa to majadi' hi tempo nabi Nuh owi, hewa toe wo'o mpai' to jadi' hi eo karata-ku Aku' Ana' Manusia'.
25679	42	17	27	Hi tempo nabi Nuh, tauna ntora ngkoni', nginu, rapoponcamoko pai' mepoponcamoko, kawae-kawae-na duu' -na nabi Nuh mesua' hi rala sakaya bohe pai' ue mowo' mpopatehi-ra omea.
25680	42	17	28	Wae wo'o kalempe' tauna owi hi ngata Sodom nto'u Lot mo'oha' hi ria. Tauna ntora ngkoni', nginu, mobabalu', molia' pai' mpowangu tomi.
25681	42	17	29	Ntaa' palai-na Lot ngkai Sodom, hompo-mi apu pai' watu to morea' ngkai langi' mpopatehi-ra omea.
25682	42	17	30	Wae wo'o mpai' kalempe' -ra manusia' hi eo karata-ku nculii' hi dunia' mpopehuwu kabaraka' -ku.
25683	42	17	31	"Hi eo toe mpai', sohi' metibo' -koi! Tauna to mohura hi parawa, neo' -pi leba' mesua' hi rala tomi mpo'ala' rewa-na. Wae wo'o tauna to hi bonea, neo' -pi leba' nculii' mpo'ala' napa-napa hi rala ngata.
25684	42	17	32	Kiwoi-dile napa to jadi' hi tobine-na Lot-e!
25685	42	17	33	Hema to mpentaei konoa-na moto, uma-i mpai' mporatai katuwua' to lompe'. Aga hema to mpobahaka konoa-na sabana petuku' -na hi Aku', nau' napopate-ki, hi'a lau-mi mpai' to mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
25686	42	17	34	"Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Hi eo ponculia' -ku mpai', tauna rodua to more'eli turu ngkabengia, hadua ra'ala', to hadua rapalahii.
25687	42	17	35	Rodua tobine to motongke' momanyu, hadua ra'ala', to hadua rapalahii. ((
25688	42	17	36	Rodua tauna mo'ema' mobago hi bonea, hadua ra'ala', to hadua rapalahii.))"
25689	42	17	37	Hudu lolita Yesus toe, ana'guru-na mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Hiapa mpai' kajadia' tetu-e, Pue'?" Yesus mpotompoi' -ra hante walatu toi: "Ane ria anu mate, incana moto apa' wori' danci morumpu mpokoni'. Wae wo'o mpai' karata-ku nculii': uma-a tumai ngkawuni, incana moto mpai'."
25690	42	18	1	 Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' hanyala lolita rapa', mpotudui' ana'guru-na bona tida-ra mosampaya pai' neo' mere' nono-ra.
25691	42	18	2	Na'uli': "Rala ngata hamola', ria hadua topobotuhi to uma mengkoru hi Alata'ala pai' uma wo'o-i mposaile' ba hema-hema.
25692	42	18	3	Hi ngata toe wo'o, ria hadua tobine tobalu. Wori' ngkani-imi hilou mponyanyo topobotuhi toei ngkeni kara-kara-na, na'uli': `Tulungi-a-kuwo mposinyanyo-ki bali' -ku.'
25693	42	18	4	"Lomo' -lomo' -na, topobotuhi toei uma dota mpotulungi-i. Aga ka'oo-omea-na na'uli' hi rala nono-na: `Nau' uma-a mengkoru hi Alata'ala pai' uma wo'o-a mposaile' ba hema-hema,
25694	42	18	5	agina kutulungi lau-imi tobalu toei, apa' najojo rahi tumai mposaleroi-a. Apa' ane uma kutulungi-i, uma oa' mpai' nabahakai tumai, alaa-na kupo'oha lau wo'o-kuwo mpai'.'"
25695	42	18	6	Oti toe, na'uli' Pue' Yesus: "Pe'epei-koi napa to na'uli' topobotuhi toei. Nau' uma monoa' nono-na, dota moto-i mpotulungi tobalu to ntora mperapii' -i.
25696	42	18	7	Peliu-liu-nami Alata'ala doko' mpotulungi topetuku' -na to mekakae ncuu hi eo-na pai' hi bengi-na. Ba ni'uli' -koina, napeka'au ncala' pai' lako' natulungi-rae?
25697	42	18	8	Uma-hawoe'! Bate napesahui moto-hawo mpotulungi-ra. Aga ane rata nculii' -apa mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia', ha ria-ra-pidi kurua' tauna to mepangala' hi rala dunia' toi?"
25698	42	18	9	 Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' hanyala-pi lolita rapa'. Lolita rapa' toi mpotoa' tauna to mpo'uli' hira' -wadi to monoa', pai' -ra mporuge' doo.
25699	42	18	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Rodua tauna hilou hi Tomi Alata'ala, lou mosampaya. To hadua to Parisi, to hadua topesingara' paja'.
25700	42	18	11	To Parisi toei mokore pai' mosampaya hi rala nono-na, na'uli': `Oo Alata'ala, mpo'uli' -a tarima kasi, apa' uma-a hewa tau ntani' -na-- toperampaki, to bengku' nono-ra, topobualo', ba hewa topesingara' paja' toei mai.
25701	42	18	12	Aku', mopuasa' -a rongkani rala-na hamingku. Pai' hampobagiahampulu' ngkai hawe'ea pomporataa-ku kuwai' -koko Pue'.'
25702	42	18	13	"Hiaa' topesingara' paja' toei-hawo, mokore ngkawao-i-wadi, pai' uma-i daho' ngkongoa' hi langi'. Ntora mporera' hunamu-nai, pai' na'uli': `Oo Alata'ala! Poka'ahi' -a-kuwo, tauna topojeko' toi-a!'"
25703	42	18	14	Ngkai ree, napohudui Yesus lolita-na, na'uli': "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: kanculii' -ra hi tomi, topesingara' paja' toe-imi to jadi' monoa' hi poncilo-na Alata'ala, bela to Parisi toei. Apa' hawe'ea to mpomolangko nono-ra, Pue' Ala mpodingkihi-ra. Pai' hawe'ea to mpakadingki' nono-ra, Pue' Ala mpomolangko-ra."
25704	42	18	15	 Hangkani, ria tauna to mpokeni ana'lei-ra hi Yesus bona najama pai' nagane' -ra. Mpohilo toe we'i, moroe-ramo ana'guru-na, mpokaroe-ra to mpokeni ana' -ra toe.
25705	42	18	16	Aga Yesus mpokio' ana' toera pai' na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Pelele' moto-ra ana' tetura tumai hi Aku', neo' -ra nitagi. Apa' tauna to hewa toe-ramo to jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na.
25706	42	18	17	Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Ane uma-koi mengkoru hi Alata'ala hewa ana', uma-koi mpai' jadi' ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
25707	42	18	18	 Hangkani, hadua pangkeni to Yahudi mpekune' Yesus, na'uli': "Guru to lompe', napa to kana kubabehi bona mporata-a-kuwo katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae?"
25708	42	18	19	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa pai' nu'uli' tauna to lompe' -a? Uma ria ntani' -na to lompe', hadua Alata'ala-wadi.
25709	42	18	20	Nu'inca moto parenta to te'uki' hi rala Atura Pue': `Neo' mobualo', neo' mepatehi, neo' manako, neo' mosabi' boa', pai' kana tabila' tina pai' tuama-ta.'"
25710	42	18	21	Na'uli' tau toei: "Hawe'ea parenta tetu lau, kutuku' omea-mi ngkai kakedia' -ku."
25711	42	18	22	Mpo'epe toe, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Hanyala-pi to kana nubabehi. Pobalu' -mi hawe'ea rewa-nu pai' doi oli-na bagi-raka tokabu. Ane nubabehi hewa toe, bohe mpai' rasi' to nurata hi rala suruga. Oti toe, pai' tumai-moko mpotuku' -a."
25712	42	18	23	Kana'epe-na lolita tohe'e, peda' -mi nono-na, apa' mo'ua' lia-i.
25713	42	18	24	Nahilo-mi Yesus kapeda' nono-na. Toe pai' na'uli': "Mokoro rahi tauna to wori' rewa-ra mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra.
25714	42	18	25	Mojoli-pi hama'a unta ntara hi wulou' jaru ngkai tauna to mo'ua' mengkoru hi Alata'ala bona Hi'a jadi' Magau' -ra."
25715	42	18	26	Konce-ramo tauna to mpo'epe lolita Yesus tohe'e, ra'uli': "Ane wae-di, hema lau-damo to ma'ala mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-nae?"
25716	42	18	27	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane hante pakulea' manusia' -le, uma ami' hema. Aga nakule' moto Alata'ala mpobabehi to meliu ngkai pakulea' manusia'."
25717	42	18	28	Ngkai ree, na'uli' Petrus: "Hiaa' kai', kipalahii-mi-kaina rewa-kai, pai' kituku' -ko."
25718	42	18	29	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hema-hema to mpalahii tomi-na, tobine-na, ompi' -na, totu'a-na ba ana' -na apa' mpotuku' hawa' Alata'ala Magau' -na,
25719	42	18	30	tauna toe-mi to mporata wori' ngkani hiwili-na hi dunia' toi. Pai' hi eo mpeno mporata wo'o-i katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na."
25720	42	18	31	 Yesus mpokio' ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua mopahantani' pai' na'uli' -raka: "Epe-koi! Hilou-tamo tohe'i-e mpotoa' Yerusalem. Hi ria mpai' hawe'ea to ra'uki' nabi-nabi owi to mpolowa Ana' Manusia' kana madupa' hi Aku'.
25721	42	18	32	Ratonu-a mpai' hi tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi. Rapopo'ore' -a, raruge', ra'uelikui,
25722	42	18	33	raweba', pai' -a rapatehi. Aga hi eo katolu-na, tuwu' nculii' moto-a."
25723	42	18	34	Aga hawe'ea to na'uli' toe, bate uma rapaha ana'guru-na. Apa' batua-na tewunii' -raka, uma ra'incai kahompoa lolita-na.
25724	42	18	35	 Mohu' -mi Yesus hi ngata Yerikho, ria hadua tauna to wero mohura hi wiwi' ohea karapi' -rapi'.
25725	42	18	36	Kampo'epe-na wori' tauna liu, napekune': "Napa-die?"
25726	42	18	37	Ra'uli' -ki: "Yesus to Nazaret-le liu oe-e lou!"
25727	42	18	38	Mpo'epe toe we'i, pekio' -nami towero toei, na'uli': "Yesus, muli Magau' Daud! Poka'ahi' -a-kuwo!"
25728	42	18	39	Tauna to momako' ri'ulu ngkai Yesus mpokaroe-i, ra'uli': "Ngkalino-ko!" Aga hangkedi' kanapesukui-na mekio', na'uli': "Muli Magau' Daud, poka'ahi' -a-kuwo!"
25729	42	18	40	Ngkai ree, mentoda' -imi Yesus pai' na'uli': "Keni tumai towero toei mai!" Rakeni mpu'u-miki. Karata-na hi ree, Yesus mpekune' -i, na'uli': "Napa to nupokono kubabehi-koko?"
25730	42	18	41	Natompoi' towero toei: "Pue', bona pehilo-a-kuwo!"
25731	42	18	42	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae, pehilo-moko! Kupaka'uri' -ko sabana pepangala' -nu hi Aku'."
25732	42	18	43	Ncaliu pehilo mpu'u-imi. Ngkai ree, ntora mpotuku' Yesus-imi, pai' mpo'uli' wori' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala. Hawe'ea tauna to mpohilo kajadia' toe, mpo'une' Alata'ala-ramo.
25733	42	19	1	 Nto'u karata-na Yesus hi ngata Yerikho, momako' ncuu-i ntara rala ngata toe.
25734	42	19	2	Hi ngata toe, ria hadua topo'ua' to mpokapalai' topesingara' paja', hanga' -na Zakheus.
25735	42	19	3	Doko' -i-hawo mpohilo beiwa lence-na Yesus. Aga uma-i bisa mpohilo apa' wori' rahi tauna, bo hi'a he'e tauna to dingki'.
25736	42	19	4	Jadi', pokeno-nami mpori'uluhi ntodea, pai' -i ngkahe' kaju ara bona ma'ala-i-hawo mpopanto' Yesus ane liu-ipi hi ree.
25737	42	19	5	Kaliu-na Yesus hi ree, pengoa' -nami pai' na'uli': "Zakheus, pesahui mana'u! Apa' eo toe lau, kana mehani-a hi tomi-nu."
25738	42	19	6	Napesahui mpu'u-mi-hawo Zakheus mana'u, pai' goe' -i mpotarima Yesus hi tomi-na.
25739	42	19	7	Kapehilo-ra ntodea hilou-i Yesus hi tomi Zakheus, ngkunuti-ramo, ra'uli': "Ii, napa-di pai' mencua' hi tomi topojeko' -i-hanae!"
25740	42	19	8	Bula-na Pue' Yesus hi tomi Zakheus, mokore-imi Zakheus mpo'uli' -ki: "Pue', bagi ntongo' ngkai rewa-ku kuwai' -raka tokabu, pai' hema-hema to kubagiu, kupoponculi' opo' ngkani ngkai to kubagiu-raka."
25741	42	19	9	Na'uli' Yesus: "Hi eo toe lau, tauna hi tomi toi tebahaka ngkai huku' jeko' -ra, apa' Zakheus toii, muli Abraham wo'o-i-hawo.
25742	42	19	10	Apa' toe-mile pai' tumai-ae, Aku' Ana' Manusia'. Tumai-a mpopali' tauna to molaa ngkai Alata'ala, pai' mpohore-ra ngkai huku' jeko' -ra."
25743	42	19	11	 Neo' rata-imi Yesus hi Yerusalem, toe pai' wori' tauna mpo'uli' neo' rata mpu'u-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Jadi', bula ntodea mpe'epei lolita-na, na'umpui' wo'o-mi lolita-na hante hanyala lolita rapa'.
25744	42	19	12	Na'uli': "Ria hadua maradika mopatuju hilou hi ngata to molaa, lou ralanti' jadi' magau' pai' nculii'.
25745	42	19	13	Jadi', kako'ia-na me'ongko', mpokio' -i hampulu' pahawaa' -na pai' nawai' -ra hore-hore hampepa' doi bulawa. Na'uli' maradika toei: `Mobabalu' -koi hante doi to kuwai' -kokoi tetu lingku' -ku hilou.'
25746	42	19	14	Aga hi ngata maradika toe, ria wo'o-rawo tauna to mpokahuku' -i. Pe'ongko' -na maradika tohe'e, rapahawa' suro hilou mpotuku' -i pai' mpo'uli': `Oja' -ka-kaina maradika tetu jadi' magau' -kai!'
25747	42	19	15	"Aga ra'ongko' moto-i jadi' magau', pai' nculii' -imi hilou hi ngata-na. Karata-na hi ngata, nakio' -ramo pahawaa' -na mpohirua' -ki, napongincai kahangkuja-nami rasi' to rarata.
25748	42	19	16	To lomo' -na rata pai' na'uli': `Magau', doi bulawa to hampepa' to nuwai' -ka, ria-mi ana' -na hampulu'.'
25749	42	19	17	"Na'uli' magau' toei: `Lompe' -mi, iko pahawaa' to lompe'. Wae-pi, apa' monoa' -ko hi to hangkedi', ku'ongko' -moko jadi' topohawa' to mpohawai' hampulu' ngata.'
25750	42	19	18	"Pahawaa' karodua-na rata wo'o pai' mpo'uli': `Magau', doi bulawa to hampepa' to nuwai' -ka, jadi' lima mpepa' -mi.'
25751	42	19	19	"Na'uli' wo'o-mi magau' hi karodua-na tohe'ei: `Iko wo'o ku'ongko' jadi' topohawa' hi lima ngata.'
25752	42	19	20	"Ngkai ree, rata wo'o-imi-hawo pahawaa' kahadua-na. Na'uli': `Oi-mi doi-nu Magau'. Kutimamahi lompe', kuputu' hante lenco.
25753	42	19	21	Me'eka' -a hi Magau', apa' ku'inca kasoa-nu. Nupepae to bela-kowo hinu'a-nu, nu'ala' to uma nukarokoi.'
25754	42	19	22	"Na'uli' magau' mpo'uli' -ki: `Iko pahawaa' to dada'a! Ane nu'inca kasoa-ku, ane nu'inca kampepae-ku to bela hinu'a-ku, pai' kampo'ala' -ku to uma kukarokoi,
25755	42	19	23	napa pai' doi-ku uma nupopesua' hi bank, bona ane rata-apa, ku'ala' hante ana' -na!'
25756	42	19	24	Oti toe, na'uli' wo'o-mi hi tauna to mokore hi ncori-na: `Ala' doi to hi tauna tetui, pai' wai' -ki to ria-ki hampulu'.'
25757	42	19	25	"Ingu' -ramo to napahawa' toera, ra'uli': `Napa pai' hewa tetu, Magau'? Apa' ria-miki-hana hampulu' mpepa'!'
25758	42	19	26	"Na'uli' magau': `Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: Tauna to ma'ala rasarumaka hante anu to rawai' -ki, rawai' tena-i-pidi. Tapi' tauna to uma rasarumaka, anu hangkedi' to ria hi hi'a, ra'alai' lau-i.
25759	42	19	27	Pai' wae lau, keni-ramo tumai bali' -ku to mpoka'oja' -a jadi' magau' -ra. Patehi-ramo hi rehe'i bona kuhilo!'"
25760	42	19	28	 Ka'oti-na Yesus mpo'uli' hawe'ea toe, pomako' -nami meri'ulu ngkai doo-na hilou hi Yerusalem.
25761	42	19	29	Mohu' -ramo hi ngata Betfage pai' Betania hi bulu' Zaitun, nahubui rodua ana'guru-na mako' meri'ulu.
25762	42	19	30	Na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi hi ngata to tanyanyohi toe mai. Ane mesua' -pokoi hi rala ngata, nihilo mpai' hama'a ana' keledai to tehoo'. Keledai toe ko'ia hangkania rahawi'. Bongka koloro-na pai' keni-i tumai.
25763	42	19	31	Ane ria tauna mpekune' -koi napa pai' nibongka-i, uli': `Apa' Pue' mparaluu-i.'"
