25764	42	19	32	Hilou mpu'u-ramo ana'guru-na to rodua tohe'era, pai' rarata bate hewa to na'uli' -raka Yesus.
25765	42	19	33	Bula-ra mpobongka keledai toe, mepekune' -mi pue' -na: "Napa pai' nibongka keledai tetu-e?"
25766	42	19	34	Ratompoi': "Apa' Pue' mparaluu-i."
25767	42	19	35	Karakeni-nami hilou hi Yesus, ralampii hante baju-ra, pai' rapopehawi' -i Yesus.
25768	42	19	36	Kaliu-na Yesus mpohawi' keledai tohe'e, tauna mpokodo baju-ra hi mata ohea, tanda pebila' -ra.
25769	42	19	37	Mohu' -mi hi ngata Yerusalem, hi pana'ua-na hi bulu' Zaitun, hawe'ea topetuku' -na to wori' toe ntepu'u mpo'une' Alata'ala. Mogora-ra-damo nakeni kagoe' nono-ra sabana hawe'ea anu mekoncehi to rahilo.
25770	42	19	38	Ra'uli' hi rala pe'une' -ra: Pue' Ala mpogane' Magau' to tumai mpokeni hanga' -na!" Une' -imi Pue' Ala to hi suruga, apa' nawai' -tamo kalompea'."
25771	42	19	39	Ngkai ree, ba hangkuja dua to Parisi to hi olo' tauna to wori' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, tagi-ramo ana'guru-nu bona neo' -ra mpo'uli' hewa tetu!"
25772	42	19	40	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma-e'! Apa' ane mengkalino-ra ana'guru-ku, watu toe lau-ramo mpai' to mogora mpo'une' -a."
25773	42	19	41	 Kamoo-mohua' -imi Yesus hi Yerusalem, duu' -na mpohilo-i ngata toe. Kageo' -nami mpokageoi' ngata toe.
25774	42	19	42	Na'uli': "Mpe'ahii' -koi to Yerusalem! Uma mowo kalompe' -na ane ke ni'inca napa to ngkeni-kokoi kalompea' tuwu' hi eo toe lau. Aga hawe'ea toe teleru ngkai mata-ni.
25775	42	19	43	Rata mpai' tempo-na, bali' -ni mpanga'ei ngata-ni, ratipuhi ntololikia hante wala, duu' -na uma-pi ria ohea metibo'.
25776	42	19	44	Raropuhi mpai' ngata-ni hante hawe'ea ihi' -na, duu' -na uma-pi ria watu to bate pomeduncu-na. Apa' uma-koina nisaile' karata-na Pue' Ala doko' mpotulungi-koi."
25777	42	19	45	Oti toe, Yesus mesua' hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala pai' -i mpopalai tauna to mobabalu' hi ree.
25778	42	19	46	Na'uli' -raka: "Hi rala Buku Tomoroli', Alata'ala mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Tomi-ku, tomi posampayaa.' Hiaa' koi' -koina, niponcawa tomi toperampaki-di!"
25779	42	19	47	Butu eo-na Yesus metudui' hi Tomi Alata'ala. Imam pangkeni hante guru agama pai' pangkeni to Yahudi ntani' -na mpali' akala-ra doko' mpatehi-i,
25780	42	19	48	aga uma ria ohea-ra mpobabehi anu hi nono-ra, apa' lutu-ramo ntodea mpe'epei lolita-na.
25781	42	20	1	 Rala-na ha'eo Yesus metudui' pai' mparata Kareba Lompe' hi wori' tauna hi Tomi Alata'ala. Muu-mule' rata-ramo imam pangkeni hante guru agama pai' pangkeni to Yahudi ntani' -na. Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus:
25782	42	20	2	"Uli' -kakai pe' ngkaiapa huraa-nu mpobabehi hawe'ea tetu hi Tomi Alata'ala! Hema to mpowai' -ko kuasa tetu-e?"
25783	42	20	3	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku', ria wo'o-kuwo pompekunea' -ku hi koi'.
25784	42	20	4	Uli' -ka pe', ngkaiapa kuasa-na Yohanes Topeniu' mponiu' tauna? Ngkai Alata'ala-di, ba ngkai manusia' -di?"
25785	42	20	5	Momepololitai-ramo pangkeni to Yahudi toera, ra'uli': "Beiwa-tale' mpotompoi' -ie? Ane ta'uli' ngkai Alata'ala kuasa-na, na'uli' mpai': `Ane wae, napa pai' uma-i nipangala'?'
25786	42	20	6	Hiaa' ane ta'uli' ngkai manusia' -wadi kuasa-na, rawatuhi-ta mpai' ntodea toera lau, apa' hawe'ea-ra mpo'uli' Yohanes hadua nabi."
25787	42	20	7	Toe pai' ratompoi': "Uma ki'incai kangkaiapa kuasa-na."
25788	42	20	8	Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane wae, uma wo'o-kuwo ku'uli' -kokoi kangkaiapa kuasa-ku mpobabehi toe lau!"
25789	42	20	9	 Oti toe, Yesus mpololitai ntodea, mpo'uli' -raka lolita rapa' tohe'i: "Ria tau hadua mpohu'ai bonea-na hante anggur, oti toe napewai' bonea-na rapobago hi ba hangkuja dua tauna, pai' hilou-imi hi ngata to molaa, pai' mahae-i tida hi ria.
25790	42	20	10	Rata-mi tempo mpohopu' wua' anggur, napahawa' hadua batua-na hilou mperapi' bagia-na hi tompodoo bonea-na toera. Tapi' tompodoo bonea-na toera mpopao' suro tetu pai' -i rapopalai mara.
25791	42	20	11	Oti toe, pue' bonea toei mpopahawa' tena wo'o-pi hadua batua. Aga rapao' wo'o-i-wadi-hawo, ralibui' pai' rapopalai mara.
25792	42	20	12	Oti toe wo'o, nahubui tena batua katolu-na. Aga raserohi wo'o-i-wadi pai' rapetadi hi mali bonea.
25793	42	20	13	"Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi pue' bonea toei: `Napa-le' to kubabehi-e? Agina ana' -ku to kupe'ahi' moto lau-mi kupahawa' hilou, apa' bate rapengkorui-ile mpai'.'
25794	42	20	14	"Ntaa' we'i, karahilo-na tompodoo bonea toera ana' pue' bonea tohe'ei, mohawa' -ramo, ra'uli': `Etu-mi tumai ana' -na! Hi'a mpai' to jadi' pue' bonea tohe'i-e. Kita tapatehi-i bona bonea-na toi kita' -mi pue' -na.'
25795	42	20	15	Ngkai ree, radii' -imi hilou hi mali bonea pai' -i rapatehi. "Jadi', napa mpai' to nababehi pue' bonea toei hi tauna to mpodoo bonea-na?
25796	42	20	16	Bate tumai-ile mpopatehi-ra, pai' nawai' bonea-na hi tau ntani' -na." Kara'epe-na ntodea lolita rapa' tohe'e, ra'uli' -mi: "Neo' mpu'u-kona jadi' hewa tetu-e'!"
25797	42	20	17	Yesus mponaa-ra pai' na'uli' -raka: "Hiaa' toe-mile batua-na walatu to hi rala Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': `Watu to ratadi topowangu tomi, watu toe lau-mi to jadi' poko parawatu.'
25798	42	20	18	Hewa kura to monawu' hi watu mopengka, hewa kura to napitihi watu moreja', hewa toe wo'o mpai' tauna to mposapuaka-a."
25799	42	20	19	Guru agama pai' imam pangkeni mpo'inca kahira' -na to natoa' Yesus hante lolita rapa' -na toe we'i. Toe pai' ria-mi nono-ra doko' mpohoko' -i hi jaa toe wo'o. Aga uma-ra daho', apa' mpoka'eka' -ra ntodea.
25800	42	20	20	 Jadi' rapali' loga to lompe'. Mpopahawa' -ra tauna hilou mpolelemata-i. Tauna toera, ntani' hewa tauna to monoa' nono-ra, tapi' patuju-ra mpo'opa kasala' lolita-na, bona rapakilu-i hi gubernur.
25801	42	20	21	Karata-ra hi Yesus, ra'uli' -mi to rapahawa' toera: "Guru, ki'inca hawe'ea lolita-nu pai' tudui' -nu makono omea. Metudui' -ko hante kalonto' -lonto' -na mpo'uli' napa konoa Pue' Ala hi manusia', pai' uma-ko mpelence tauna.
25802	42	20	22	Jadi', toe pai' kiperapi' bona nu'uli' -kakai Guru: ntuku' atura agama-ta, ba ma'ala moto-ta mpobayari paja' hi Kaisar, ba uma-di?"
25803	42	20	23	Yesus mpo'inca pepanawu' -ra. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka:
25804	42	20	24	"Popohiloi-a ulu doi hampepa'! Lence hema pai' hanga' hema to hi doi tetu-e?" Ratompoi': "Lence pai' hanga' Kaisar."
25805	42	20	25	Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane wae-di, wai' -ki Kaisar napa to kasipato' -na rawai' -ki Kaisar, pai' wai' -ki Alata'ala napa to kasipato' -na rawai' -ki Alata'ala."
25806	42	20	26	Ka'omea-na madagi-ramo bali' Yesus toera. Uma raruai' nau' hanyalaa sala' lolita-na hi nyanyoa ntodea. Konce-ra mpo'epe tompoi' -na, toe pai' ngkalino-ramo.
25807	42	20	27	 Ba hangkuja dua tauna to mpotuku' tudui' to Saduki rata hi Yesus. To Saduki toera, pangkeni agama Yahudi to ncapuaka tauna to mate tuwu' nculii' hi eo mpeno. Karata to Saduki toera, ra'uli' -ki Yesus:
25808	42	20	28	"Guru, nabi Musa mpo'uki' hi rala buku atura hewa toi: ane hadua tomane mate hiaa' uma-ki ria ana' -na, pudupuhe-na kana mpotobine balu-na, bona ria-ki-hawo muli tomate toei.
25809	42	20	29	Jadi', ria pitu ntali ompi', paka' tomane. To ulumua' motobinei, mate-i hante uma ria ana' -na.
25810	42	20	30	Tu'ai-na mpotobine balu-na, aga mate wo'o-i-wadi, ko'ia napoka'alai mo'anai'.
25811	42	20	31	Wae oa' -mi to jadi' hi katolu-na duu' -na hi kapitu-na. Mate omea-ra hante uma ria ana' -ra.
25812	42	20	32	Ka'omea-na mate wo'o-imi-hawo tobine toei.
25813	42	20	33	Jadi', hi eo mpeno, ane tuwu' nculii' mpu'u-di hawe'ea tomate-e, hema-ramo mpai' pue' tobine toei, apa' pitu-ramo mpotobine-i."
25814	42	20	34	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Tauna hi dunia' toi motobinei pai' motomanei.
25815	42	20	35	Aga tauna to napotuwu' nculii' Pue' Ala pai' to masipato' mporata bagia hi dunia' to bo'u mpai', uma-rapa-hana motobinei ba motomanei.
25816	42	20	36	Apa' tuwu' -ra hewa tuwu' mala'eka, uma-rapa mate. Ana' Alata'ala-ramo, apa' napotuwu' nculii' -ramo Alata'ala.
25817	42	20	37	"Ane katuwu' -ra nculii' tomate-e, nabi Musa moto to mpakanoto katuwu' -ra nculii'. Hi rala jarita julumpu to jela', Musa mpokahangai' Pue' Ala hewa toi: `Alata'ala to napue' Abraham, to napue' Ishak, pai' to napue' Yakub.'
25818	42	20	38	Jadi', ngkai lolita-na nabi Musa toe, monoto-mi ta'inca katuwu' -ra moto Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub. Apa' bela tauna to mate to mepue' hi Alata'ala, tauna to tuwu' -hana to mpopue' -i. Apa' hi Alata'ala hawe'ea tauna tuwu'."
25819	42	20	39	 Oti toe, ba hangkuja dua guru agama mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Lompe' lia petompoi' -nu Guru."
25820	42	20	40	Ngkai ree, uma-rapa daho' mepekune' ba napa-napa hi Yesus.
25821	42	20	41	Ngkai ree, mepekune' wo'o-imi-hawo Yesus mpo'uli' -raka guru agama toera: "Beiwa pai' ra'uli' Magau' Topetolo' muli-na Magau' Daud?
25822	42	20	42	
25823	42	20	43	
25824	42	20	44	Hiaa' bo Daud moto-hawo mpokahangai' -i Pue' -na. Hi rala Buku Rona' na'uli': Pue' Ala mpo'uli' -ki Pue' -ku: `Mohura-moko hi mali ngka'ana-ku duu' -na kupopengkoru hawe'ea bali' -nu hi Iko.'
25825	42	20	45	Bula tauna mpe'epei lolita-na Yesus toe we'i, napololitai ana'guru-na, na'uli':
25826	42	20	46	"Pelompehi-koi, neo' -koi mpenau' kehi-ra guru agama. Apa' goe' -ra modao' mpopake' baju to moloe, goe' -ra ane tauna hi wiwi' karajaa motingkua' mpotabe-ra. Goe' -ra rapopohura hi pohuraa karabilaa' hi tomi posampayaa, goe' -ra ane rapopohura-ra hi pohuraa to lompe' hi posusaa'.
25827	42	20	47	Mpobagiu-ra tobine tobalu pai' rahagoi tomi-ra. Pai' -ra mpowunii' kadada'a gau' -ra tohe'e hante mosampaya rapomoloe-loe. Huku' -ra motomo lia mpai'."
25828	42	21	1	 Hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, Yesus mpohilo topo'ua' mpopuna' doi hi rala peti' pompunaa' doi pepue'.
25829	42	21	2	Mpohilo wo'o-i hadua tobalu to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -na mpopuna' rompepa' doi ngkala.
25830	42	21	3	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: tobalu to mpe'ahii' tuwu' -na tohe'e mai, meliu pewai' -na ngkai pewai' hawe'ea tauna toera lau.
25831	42	21	4	Apa' hira' mewai' ngkai labi ka'uaa' -ra. Tapi' tobine toei, nau' hewa apa-mi kampe'ahii' -na, napewai' omea-mi-hana to ria hi hi'a, to naparaluu-hawo hi katuwu' -na."
25832	42	21	5	 Nto'u toe, ria tauna mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Lompe' lia Tomi Alata'ala toi, apa' rawangu hante watu to ncola pai' rarampai hante rewa to rapopepue' hi Pue' Ala." Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus:
25833	42	21	6	"Rata mpai' tempo-na hawe'ea to nihilo toe lau ragero, uma-pi mpai' ria hamehaa' watu to bate pomeduncu-na."
25834	42	21	7	Ngkai ree, mepekune' -ra ana'guru-na mpekune' -i: "Guru, nto'uma mpai' kadupa' -na to nu'uli' toe-e we'i? Pai' napa mpai' to jadi' tanda ane neo' madupa' -pi?"
25835	42	21	8	Na'uli' Yesus: "Pelompehi, neo' -koi ma'ala rabagiu. Apa' wori' mpai' tauna to mehupa' to mpo'uli' kahira' -na Magau' Topetolo'. Ria wo'o to mpo'uli' karata-na mpu'u Eo Kiama. Aga neo' nituku' -ra.
25836	42	21	9	Neo' wo'o-koi me'eka' mpo'epe kareba to mpo'uli' wori' tauna manga'e pai' mpo'ewa topoparenta. Apa' hawe'ea tohe'e kana jadi' mperi'ulu. Tapi' ko'ia-hawo rata mpu'u-mi kahudua dunia'."
25837	42	21	10	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpokaliliu lolita-na, na'uli': "Hi eo toe mpai', wori' ngata mosipanga'ei, magau' hadua mpo'ewa magau' kahadua-na.
25838	42	21	11	Ria mpai' linu bohe, pai' hiapa-apa ria haki' ropu' pai' oro'. Pai' hi langi' ria tanda bohe to mewulungahi.
25839	42	21	12	Aga kako'ia-na hawe'ea toe jadi', koi' mpai' rahoko' pai' rabalinai'. Rapakilu-koi hi rala tomi posampayaa, pai' -koi ratarungku'. Rabua' -koi hi magau' pai' hi topoparenta sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku'.
25840	42	21	13	Nto'u toe mpai', ria loga-ni mpo'uli' -raka pepangala' -ni hi Aku'.
25841	42	21	14	Pakaroho ami' -mi nono-ni, neo' -koi mingki' mpekiri ncala' ba beiwa mpai' tompoi' -ni.
25842	42	21	15	Aku' moto-damo mpai' to mpowai' -koi petompoi' to monoto, alaa-na uma ria haduaa ngkai bali' -ni to mpokule' mpobaro ba mposapuaka napa to ni'uli'.
25843	42	21	16	
25844	42	21	17	Nto'u toe mpai', hawe'ea tauna mpokahuku' -koi sabana petuku' -ni hi Aku'. Ntahawe' totu'a-ni, ompi' -ni, posantina-ni, pai' ema' -ni mpewai' -koi hi bali' -ni. Hantongo' -koi mpai' rapatehi.
25845	42	21	18	Aga kakoo-kono-na uma moto-koi moapa. Nau' hangkaho wuluwoo' -ni uma mpai' ria to moronto.
25846	42	21	19	Ane uma mogego' pepangala' -ni hi Aku', bate mporata-koi katuwua' to lompe'.
25847	42	21	20	 "Ane nihilo-damo ngata Yerusalem toi ratipuhi tantara bali', ni'inca-mi ka'uma-napi mahae Yerusalem ragero.
25848	42	21	21	Nto'u toe mpai', tauna to mo'oha' hi Yudea, agina metibo' -ra hilou hi bulu' -na. Tauna to hi rala ngata agina metibo' ngkai rala ngata. Pai' tauna to hi mali ngata neo' -pi leba' mesua' hi rala ngata.
25849	42	21	22	Apa' tempo toe mpai', tempo pehukua' Alata'ala, bona madupa' -mi hawe'ea to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'.
25850	42	21	23	Mpe'ahii' -ra mpai' tobine to nto'u-ra motina'i pai' to mpentii' ana' -ra hi tempo toe, apa' mokoro petibo' -ra. Apa' ngata toi narumpa' silaka bohe, pai' Pue' Ala mpohuku' pue' ngata.
25851	42	21	24	Ria-ra mpai' to jadi' konia' piho'. Ria-ra to ratawani pai' rapatau' hi humalili' dunia'. Pai' ngata Yerusalem toi ralisa tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi, duu' -na hudu tempo to napakatantu-raka Pue' Ala.
25852	42	21	25	"Nto'u toe mpai', ria tanda hi eo, hi wula pai' hi betue'. Hawe'ea manusia' mokaratu nono-ra pai' ingu' mpo'epe pomoni pai' pojago tahi'.
25853	42	21	26	Ria mpai' tauna to mate ngkokore nakeni kawulunga-ra, mpohilo to jadi' hi humalili' dunia'. Apa' hawe'ea anu to mobaraka' hi langi' ralengo.
25854	42	21	27	Nto'u toe-damo mpai', hawe'ea tauna mpohilo-a, Aku' Ana' Manusia', mana'u tumai hi rala limu'. Uma mowo pehini-ku pai' kabaraka' -ku nto'u toe.
25855	42	21	28	Ane hawe'ea toe ntepu'u majadi', pakaroho-mi nono-ni pai' mengoa' -mokoi, apa' neo' rata-mi tempo-na rabahaka-koi ngkai kaparia-ni."
25856	42	21	29	 Yesus mpololitai ana'guru-na hante lolita rapa' tohe'i, na'uli': "Petonoi-koi kaju ara pai' kaju-kaju ntani' -na wo'o.
25857	42	21	30	Ane nihilo-damo mela' -mi rau-na, ni'inca-mi ka'uma-napi mahae mara eo.
25858	42	21	31	Wae wo'o ane nihilo-damo kajadia' toe we'i lou, ni'inca-mi ka'uma-napi mahae Alata'ala jadi' Magau' mpu'u-mi hi dunia'.
25859	42	21	32	"Mpu'u ku'uli' -kokoi: hawe'ea toe we'i bate madupa' kako'ia-na mate omea tauna to tuwu' tempo toi.
25860	42	21	33	Langi' pai' dunia' mogero moto mpai'. Tapi' lolita-ku bate-bate-na duu' kahae-hae-na.
25861	42	21	34	"Mo'inga' -inga' -koi, neo' -koi sese' ntora mosusa' pai' nginu palangu-langu, ba ntora mpenonoi katuwu' -ni hi dunia', alaa-na lempe' moto-koi hi eo karata-ku. Apa' rata ncorobaa-a mpai'.
25862	42	21	35	Karata-ku mpai' mporumpa' hawe'ea tauna hi dunia' hewa tewo' mpowoko' wulehu'.
25863	42	21	36	Mo'inga' -inga' -koi pai' tida mekakae hi Pue' Ala, bona moroho-koi ntaha hawe'ea kaparia to neo' jadi' toe, duu' -na mpohirua' -ka Aku' Ana' Manusia'."
25864	42	21	37	Hi eo-na, Yesus metudui' hi Tomi Alata'ala. Hi bengi-na, hilou-i hi mali ngata Yerusalem, pai' -i turu hi Bulu' Zaitun.
25865	42	21	38	Butu mepulo-na ntodea morumpu hi Tomi Alata'ala doko' mpo'epe tudui' -na.
25866	42	22	1	 Mohu' -mi eo bohe to Yahudi to rahanga' Posusa' Roti to Uma Raragii, to rahanga' wo'o Eo Paskah.
25867	42	22	2	Nto'u toe, imam pangkeni pai' guru agama mpali' ohea-ra ke mpatehi bongo Yesus, apa' me'eka' -ra mpoka'eka' ntodea.
25868	42	22	3	Ngkai ree, Magau' Anudaa' mesua' hi rala nono Yudas, to rahanga' wo'o Iskariot, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na Yesus to hampulu' rodua.
25869	42	22	4	Toe pai' hilou-imi mpololitai imam pangkeni hante kapala' polisi Tomi Alata'ala, ba beiwa akala-na mpobalu' Yesus hi hira'.
25870	42	22	5	Goe' -ramo mpo'epe lolita Yudas toe, ra'uli' -ki: "Ane nutonu Yesus hi kai', kiwai' -ko doi."
25871	42	22	6	Na'io' -mi Yudas, pai' ngkai ree napali' loga to lompe' mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na hante uma ra'incai ntodea.
25872	42	22	7	 Rata-mi tempo-na Posusa' Roti to Uma Raragii. Pai' eo to lomo' -na hi rala posusa' tohe'e, eo posumalea' bima to rakoni' hi Eo Paskah.
25873	42	22	8	Yesus mpohubui Petrus pai' Yohanes, na'uli' -raka: "Hilou-mokoi mporodo-taka pongkoni' Paskah-ta."
25874	42	22	9	Rapekune' -i: "Hiapa Pue' nupokono kipomporodoi-e?"
25875	42	22	10	Na'uli' -raka: "Ane mesua' -koi mpai' hi rala ngata, hirua' -koi hante hadua tomane to ngkeni pontomua' oti ntomu'. Tuku' -i rata hi tomi pesuaa' -na.
25876	42	22	11	Rata hi tomi pesuaa' -na, uli' -ki pue' tomi hewa toi: `Na'uli' Guru: Hiapa-kuwo pobabehia-ku Posusa' Paskah hante ana'guru-ku?'
25877	42	22	12	Pue' tomi toei mpai' mpotudo' -kokoi hameha' kamar to bohe hi lolo-na. Kamar toe teporodo ami' -mi, hono' -mi rewa-na. Hi retu-mi mpai' niporodo pongkoni' Paskah-ta."
25878	42	22	13	Hilou mpu'u-ramo Petrus pai' Yohanes, pai' rarata mpu'u-mi hewa to na'uli' -raka Yesus, pai' -ra mporodo-mi pongkoni' Paskah.
25879	42	22	14	Karata-na mpu'u-mi tempo ngkoni' pongkoni' Paskah tohe'e, mohura-imi Yesus hante suro-na hi tomi toe.
25880	42	22	15	Na'uli' -raka: "Doko' lia-a ngkoni' dohe-ni hi Eo Paskah toi, kako'ia-ku mporata kaparia.
25881	42	22	16	Apa' bona ni'inca: uma-apa ngkoni' pongkoni' Paskah to hewa toi, duu' -na madupa' mpu'u-mi batua-na posusa' toi nto'u Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'."
25882	42	22	17	Oti toe, Yesus mpo'ala' sangkiri' to ihia' anggur, na'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala, pai' na'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Ala' -mi tohe'i pai' nibagi-bagi.
25883	42	22	18	Apa' bona ni'inca: ntepu'u ngkai wae lau, uma-apa nginu anggur duu' -na rata mpu'u-mi tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'."
25884	42	22	19	Oti toe, na'ala' -mi roti, pai' ka'oti-nai mpo'uli' tarima kasi hi Pue' Ala, napihe-pihe pai' natonu-miraka, na'uli': "Roti to kutonu-kokoi toi, toi-mi woto-ku ((to kutonu mpotolo' -koi. Babehi-mokoi ada toi bona mpokiwoi-a."
25885	42	22	20	Wae wo'o, ka'oti-ra ngkoni', na'ala' sangkiri' to ihia' anggur pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ihi' sangkiri' toi mpobatuai pojanci Alata'ala to bo'u, to mpoposidai' Alata'ala pai' manusia'. Pojanci toe, rapadupa' hante raa' -ku, to rabowo mpai' ane mate-a mpotolo' -koi.))
25886	42	22	21	 "Aga hilo pe', tauna to mpobalu' -a mpai', ria-imi hi rehe'i lau, ngkoni' dohe-ku toi-e!
25887	42	22	22	Aku' Ana' Manusia' bate kana mate hewa to napakatantu Alata'ala. Aga mpe'ahii' tauna to mpobalu' -a tetui!"
25888	42	22	23	Kara'epe-na ana'guru-na toe, momepekune' -ramo ba hema-ra mpai' to mpobabehi hewa toe.
25889	42	22	24	Ngkai ree, momehono' -ramo ana'guru-na Yesus, ba hema-ra to meliu kabohe pangka' -ra.
25890	42	22	25	Toe pai' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ane hi tauna to uma mpo'incai Alata'ala, uma mowo kasoa-na magau' mpohawai' ntodea. Pai' tauna to bohe pangka' -ra doko' rahanga' `to mpotiroi ntodea.'
25891	42	22	26	Aga koi', neo' hewa tetu! Timali-na lau-di. Hema-koi to meliu kabohe pangka' -na kana mo'ingku hewa to kedi' lia tuwu' -na. Pai' tauna to mehawai' kana mo'ingku hewa hadua pahawaa'.
25892	42	22	27	Kupekune' -koi ulu: hema to meliu kabohe pangka' -na? To mohura ngkoni' -di, ba to metonui-di? Tantu tauna to mohura. Hiaa' ohe'i-a hi laintongo' -ni hewa tauna to mpotonui-koi.
25893	42	22	28	"Koi' tohe'i-e lau, ria oa' -koi dohe-ku hi rala hawe'ea kasusaa' -ku.
25894	42	22	29	Jadi', hewa Tuama-ku mpowai' -a kuasa moparenta, wae wo'o Aku' mpowai' -koi kuasa moparenta.
25895	42	22	30	Toe pai' goe' wo'o-ko-koiwo mpai' ngkoni' pai' nginu dohe-ku hi rala Kamagaua' -ku ane jadi' Magau' -apa mpai'. Pai' mohura moto-koi mpai' hi pohuraa to hampulu' romeha', mpoparentai to Israel to hampulu' rontina."
25896	42	22	31	Oti toe, Pue' Yesus mpololitai Simon Petrus, na'uli': "Ee', Simon! Epe: Magau' Anudaa' rawai' loga mposori-koi omea. Hewa pae to ratapi, hewa toe wo'o mpai' kagaga-na pesori to mporumpa' -koi.
25897	42	22	32	Aga kuposampayai ami' -moko Simon, bona neo' lelu' pepangala' -nu. Jadi', ane monoto nculii' mpai' nono-nu, iko kana mporohoi nono doo-nu."
25898	42	22	33	Na'uli' Petrus: "Pue', nau' ratarungku' -a mpai' ba paiana rapatehi-a dohe-nu, sadia moto-a mpotuku' -ko!"
25899	42	22	34	Na'uli' Yesus: "Petrus, bona nu'inca: kako'ia-na turua' manu' bengi toe mpai' lau, mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku."
25900	42	22	35	Oti toe Yesus mpololitai-ra, na'uli': "Nto'u kakuhubui-ni wengi hilou ngkeni Kareba Lompe', uma-koi kupiliu mpokeni karepe' doi ba boku ba sapatu'. Ha ria-mokoi nakakurai' ba napa-napa-e?"
25901	42	22	36	Ratompoi': "Uma-hawo." Na'uli' Yesus: "Aga hewa toe lau, hema-koi to ria doi-ni ba boku-ni kana nikeni. Pai' hema-koi to uma ria piho' -ni, pobalu' baju-ni nipope'oli piho'.
25902	42	22	37	Apa' ria lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': `Magau' Topetolo' mpai' rapohewa tauna to dada'a.' Pai' napa to te'uki' toe kana madupa' hi Aku'. Apa' napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' to mpolowa-a, neo' madupa' mpu'u-mi wae lau."
25903	42	22	38	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Pue', ohe'i moto piho' romata." Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae-mi."
25904	42	22	39	 Oti toe, malai-imi Yesus ngkai rala ngata, pai' hewa kabiasaa-na hilou-imi hi Bulu' Zaitun, pai' ana'guru-na hilou wo'o dohe-na.
25905	42	22	40	Karata-ra hi ria, na'uli' mpo'uli' -raka: "Mosampaya-mokoi bona neo' -koi mporata pesori."
25906	42	22	41	Oti toe, pai' hilou-i molaa hala' ngkai hira', pai' -i mowilingkudu mosampaya.
25907	42	22	42	Na'uli': "Tuama-ku, ane dota-ko, wi'iha-ka-kuwo kaparia to neo' mporumpa' -a tohe'i. Aga bela konoa-ku Aku' to jadi', agina konoa-nu Iko moto." ((
25908	42	22	43	Ngkai ree, mehupa' -mi hadua mala'eka ngkai suruga mporohoi-i.
25909	42	22	44	Hangkedi' kanahuduwukui-na mosampaya, apa' pepa mpu'u na'epe. Ini' -na tudo' hi tana' hewa raa'.))
25910	42	22	45	Oti mosampaya, mokore-imi hilou nculii' hi ana'guru-na. Narata-ra bula-ra leta', nakeni kasusa' nono-ra.
25911	42	22	46	Na'uli' -raka: "Napa-di pai' leta' -koie! Memata-mokoi pai' mosampaya bona neo' -koi mporata pesori."
25912	42	22	47	 Bula-na Yesus mololita-pidi, muu-mule' rata-mi tauna hampodooa. Yudas, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, hi'a-mi to mpakeni-ra. Karata-ra hi ree, hilou-imi Yudas mpomohui' Yesus, doko' natabe-i hante me'eki ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi.
25913	42	22	48	Aga Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Ee' Yudas, ha hante petabe-nu tetu-tanoe nupobalu' -a, Aku' Ana' Manusia' -e!"
25914	42	22	49	Karahilo-na ana'guru-na napa to neo' jadi', ra'uli': "Pue', ki'ewa-ramo hante piho'!"
25915	42	22	50	Ngkai ree, hadua ngkai ana'guru-na mpotime batua Imam Bohe, bela mpoholu tilinga ka'ana-na.
25916	42	22	51	Na'uli' Yesus: "Neo' -pi!" Pai' najama tilinga-na napaka'uri' -ki.
25917	42	22	52	Oti toe, Yesus mpololitai-ra imam pangkeni pai' polisi Tomi Alata'ala hante pangkeni to Yahudi to tumai mpohoko' -i. Na'uli' -raka: "Ha toperampaki-a toi-e, pai' mingki' tumai-koi ntali piho' pai' sumampu-e!
25918	42	22	53	Butu eo-na ria lalau-a dohe-ni hi Tomi Alata'ala, tapi' uma-koi hema to dungku pale-ni hi Aku' nto'u toe. Tempo mobengi-damo pai' lako' daho' -koi mpohoko' -a. Toi-mi tempo-ni koi', pai' tempo-na magau' kabengia!"
25919	42	22	54	 Ngkai ree, rahoko' mpu'u-imi, pai' -i rakeni hilou hi tomi Imam Bohe. Petrus metuku' ngkawao-wadi.
25920	42	22	55	Hi laintongo' berewe, rapobaa apu raponerui, pai' Petrus hilou wo'o-hawo mohura dohe-ra mpotololiki apu.
25921	42	22	56	Hadua tobine topobago hi tomi Imam Bohe mpohilo Petrus bula-na moneru. Napelence pai' na'uli': "Tau tetui, hadua doo-na Yesus!"
25922	42	22	57	Nasapu Petrus, na'uli': "Uma-kuna ku'incai-i!"
25923	42	22	58	Uma mahae ngkai ree, kahadua-na mpohilo Petrus pai' na'uli' -ki: "Iko wo'o-mi hadua doo-ra ngone!" Na'uli' wo'o Petrus: "Uma! Bela aku'."
25924	42	22	59	Ba ria hajaa ngkai ree, hadua wo'o-mi mpo'uli': "Bate hi'a mpu'u-di doo-nae, apa' to Galilea wo'o-i-hawo!"
25925	42	22	60	Na'uli' Petrus: "Napa to nu'uli' tetu, uma-kuna ku'incai!" Bula-na Petrus mololita-pidi, turua' -mi manu',
25926	42	22	61	pai' Pue' me'ili' mponaa-i. Ngkai ree, nakiwoi-mi lolita-na Pue' to mpo'uli' -ki: "Kako'ia-na turua' manu' bengi mpai', mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku."
25927	42	22	62	Palai-nami Petrus hilou hi mali-na, pai' -i geo' ngkai kapeda' nono-na.
25928	42	22	63	 Tauna to mpodongo Yesus mpopo'ore' -i pai' mpohopo' -i.
25929	42	22	64	Raputu' lio-na bona neo' -i pehilo, pai' -i rapekune': "Ee nabi! Pe'uli' pe' ba hema to mpohopo' -koe!"
25930	42	22	65	Wori' wo'o-pidi lolita peruge' -ra mporuge' -i.
25931	42	22	66	Kamobaja-na, hawe'ea imam pangkeni pai' guru agama hante pangkeni to Yahudi ntani' -na moromu, pai' Yesus rakeni hi nyanyoa-ra.
25932	42	22	67	Ra'uli' topohura toera mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Uli' -kakai hi rehe'i, ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' Topetolo' -e?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Nau' ku'uli' -kokoi, bate uma-le nipangalai' -e.
25933	42	22	68	Pai' ane Aku' mepekune' hi koi', bate uma-le nitompoi' -ae.
25934	42	22	69	Aga ngkai wae-e lau, Aku' Ana' Manusia' mohura pai' moparenta hi mali ngka'ana Alata'ala to Mobaraka'."
25935	42	22	70	Ra'uli' wo'o-mi topohura toera: "Ane wae-di, Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-ko?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae mpu'u-di, hewa to ni'uli' tetu-e."
25936	42	22	71	Ngkai ree, ra'uli' -mi: "Uma-pi mingki' ria sabi'! Ta'epe moto-mi ngkai wiwi-na kasalaa' -na!"
25937	42	23	1	 Oti toe, mokore-ramo hawe'ea topohura toera pai' Yesus rakeni hilou hi Gubernur Pilatus.
25938	42	23	2	Karata-ra hi ria, rapakilu-imi, ra'uli': "Tau toii kirata bula-na mpopanawu' ntodea! Na'uli' -raka neo' mpobayari paja' hi Kaisar. Pai' na'uli' wo'o, Hi'a-mi Kristus, hadua magau'."
25939	42	23	3	Jadi', mepekune' Pilatus hi Yesus: "Ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' to Yahudi-e?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Wae mpu'u, hewa to nu'uli' tetu-e."
25940	42	23	4	Ngkai ree, na'uli' Pilatus hi imam pangkeni pai' hi ntodea: "Uma-kuna kuruai' sala' -na tau toii."
25941	42	23	5	Tapi' rajojo lau-mi mpo'uli': "Na'ukei' ntodea hante tudui' -na, hobo' hi tana' to Yahudi. Lomo' -na hi Galilea-i, hiaa' wae lau rata-imi hi rehe'i."
25942	42	23	6	Kana'epe-na Pilatus tohe'e, mepekune' -i: "Ha to Galilea-i?"
25943	42	23	7	Ratompoi': "Io', to Galilea-i-hawo." Mpo'epe toe, Pilatus mpohubui tauna mpokeni Yesus hilou hi Magau' Herodes, apa' Herodes toei topoparenta hi tana' Galilea. Pai' nto'u toe, hi Yerusalem wo'o-i-hawo Herodes.
25944	42	23	8	Goe' lia-imi Herodes mpohilo Yesus, apa' mahae-imi mpo'epe tauna mpotompo'wiwi-i, pai' doko' nahilo-i. Nasarumaka, Yesus mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi bona nahilo.
25945	42	23	9	Toe pai' wori' pompekunea' -na hi Yesus, aga Yesus uma winihi.
25946	42	23	10	Imam pangkeni pai' guru agama ria wo'o-ra hi ree, karapo' -damo lolita-ra mpopakilu Yesus hi Herodes.
25947	42	23	11	Oti toe, Herodes hante tantara-na mpopo'ore' pai' mporuge' Yesus. Raheai-i hante pohea magau', pai' rakeni nculii' -i hilou hi Pilatus.
25948	42	23	12	Hi eo tohe'e momekalompei' -ramo Herodes pai' Pilatus, hiaa' ri'ulu mosisala-ra.
25949	42	23	13	 Ngkai ree, Pilatus mporumpu hawe'ea imam pangkeni pai' totu'a ngata hante ntodea,
25950	42	23	14	pai' na'uli' -raka: "Tau toii nikeni tumai, ni'uli' mpopanawu' -i ntodea. Kuparesa' -imi hi nyanyoa-ni omea, aga uma ria kuruai' hanyalaa gau' -na to dada'a hewa to nipakilu-ki.
25951	42	23	15	Wae wo'o-hawo pomporata-na Herodes, apa' napoponculi' -imi hi aku'. Tau toii, uma-i mpobabehi ba napa-napa to masipato' rahuku' mate-ki.
25952	42	23	16	Jadi', kuweba' -i-wadi pai' kubahaka-i." ((
25953	42	23	17	Pilatus mpo'uli' hewa toe, apa' biasa-na butu Eo Paskah kana nabahaka hadua tauna to ratarungku', bona mpo'ala' nono ntodea. Toe pai' na'uli': "Kuweba' -i-wadi pai' kubahaka-i."))
25954	42	23	18	Mpo'epe toe, mogora-ramo ntodea mpo'uli': "Patehi-imi! Bahaka-kakai Barabas!"
25955	42	23	19	Barabas toe ratarungku' sabana pe'ewa-na hi topoparenta hi rala ngata pai' topepatehi wo'o-i.
25956	42	23	20	Jadi', apa' Pilatus doko' mpobahaka Yesus, toe pai' mololita tena-i hi ntodea.
25957	42	23	21	Aga rajojo lau-mi mogora, ra'uli': "Parika' -i! Parika' -i!"
25958	42	23	22	Nakatolu-ngkanii Pilatus mpo'uli' -raka: "Hiaa' napa-mile sala' -nae? Uma ria kuruai' nau' hanyalaa sala' -na to masipato' rahuku' mate-ki. Kuweba' -i-wadi pai' kubahaka."
25959	42	23	23	Aga rahudukulei' lau-mi merapi' bona Yesus raparika'. Ka'omea-na medagi mpu'u-ramo.
25960	42	23	24	Napomonoa' -mi Pilatus bona Yesus rahuku' mate, ntuku' pomperapia' -ra.
25961	42	23	25	Pai' napomonoa' wo'o mpobahaka-raka tauna to raperapi', to ratarungku' sabana pe'ewa-na pai' pepatehi-na. Yesus ratonu hi tantara to Roma bona rapatehi ntuku' konoa-ra to Yahudi.
25962	42	23	26	 Ngkai ree, rakeni-imi Yesus hilou hi mali ngata, pai' hi lengko ohea hirua' -ra hante hadua tauna to rahanga' Simon to Kirene. Hi'a tohe'ei, lako' rata hi ngata. Tantara to Roma mpentoe Simon, rapewuku-i mpaha'a kaju parika' hilou dohe-ra mpotuku' Yesus.
25963	42	23	27	Bula-na Yesus rakeni hilou hi mali ngata, wori' tauna to metuku'. Ria wo'o-ra ba hangkuja dua tobine to metuku'. Tobine toera mpokageoi' pai' mpotantangii' -i.
25964	42	23	28	Yesus mpewili' -ra pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ee tobine to Yerusalem, neo' -a nikageoi'. Agina woto-ni moto pai' ana' -ni nikageoi'.
25965	42	23	29	Apa' rata mpai' tempo-na tauna mpo'uli': `Marasi' lau-ramo tobine to lalo, to uma hangkania mo'ana', pai' to uma hangkania mpentii' ana'!'
25966	42	23	30	Nto'u toe mpai', tauna mpololitai bulu' hewa toi: `Duruhi-makai bulu'! Lulihi-makai watu!'
25967	42	23	31	Apa' ane Aku', to uma ria sala' -ku, rapohewa toe, peliu-liu-nami mpai' koi'."
25968	42	23	32	 Nto'u Yesus rakeni hilou raparika' toe, ria wo'o rodua tau ntani' -na to rakeni hilou dohe-na bona rapatehi. To rodua toe, paka' to dada'a gau' -ra.
25969	42	23	33	Karata-ra hi po'ohaa' to rahanga' Bulu' Banga'woo', raparika' -imi Yesus. Pai' to rodua to dada'a gau' -ra toera, raparika' wo'o-ramo-rawo, hadua hi mali ka'ana-na hadua mali ki'ii-na.
25970	42	23	34	Yesus mosampaya, na'uli': "Tuama-ku, ampungi-ra-rawo, apa' uma ra'incai napa to rababehi." Tantara to mpoparika' Yesus mpotene' undi hewa pompenoa' -ra, ba hema-ra to mporata pohea-na.
25971	42	23	35	Wori' tauna tumai mokore hilau merono. Wae wo'o pangkeni to Yahudi mpopo'ore' -i, ra'uli': "Tau ntani' -na natulungi-ramo. Agina woto-na moto-pi natulungi, ane makono Kahi'a-na Magau' Topetolo' to napelihi Alata'ala-e!"
25972	42	23	36	Tantara-tantara wo'o mpopo'ore' -i. Ramohui' -i pai' rapopo'inui-i anggur to mo'onco,
25973	42	23	37	pai' ra'uli': "Ane Magau' to Yahudi mpu'u-ko, wae-pi tulungi moto-mi-kowo woto-nu!"
25974	42	23	38	Hi kaju parika' -na Yesus hi ntoto woo' -na ria ukia' hewa toi: TOI-MI MAGAU' TO YAHUDI.
25975	42	23	39	Hadua todada'a to raparika' dohe-na Yesus, mpolibui' Yesus, na'uli': "Nu'uli' -kona Iko Magau' Topetolo' -e! Ane bongko wae, tulungi-mi woto-nu pai' kai' wo'o-kaiwo!"
25976	42	23	40	Aga to hadua-i-hana mpotanee' doo-na, na'uli' -ki: "Ha uma-ko me'eka' -e? Uma-ko mengkoru hi Alata'ala-e? Rahuku' mate omea-ta toi-e.
25977	42	23	41	Aga huku' -ta kita' rodua, toto-na-tana ntuku' kadada'a gau' -ta. Hiaa' Hi'a-hana, uma ria sala' -na."
25978	42	23	42	Oti toe, pai' -i mpololitai Yesus, na'uli': "Yesus, kiwoi-a-kuwo, ane rata-poko mpai' jadi' Magau'!"
25979	42	23	43	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Mpu'u ku'uli' -koko: eo toe mpai' lau, ria-ko dohe-ku hi Firdaus."
25980	42	23	44	 Tebua' -mi eo, muu-mule' uma-pi mehini eo. Hangaa mobengi-mi hobo' hi ngata toe, duu' rata jaa tolu.
25981	42	23	45	Kain porini-olo' to tetoe hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, mobika' ntongo' jadi' rontau.
25982	42	23	46	Oti toe, me'au-imi Yesus napesukui mpo'uli': "Tuama-ku, hi rala pale-nu kutonu-mi kao' -ku!" Ka'oti-na mololita hewa toe, modupe' -mi inoha' -na.
25983	42	23	47	Kanahilo-na tadulako tantara napa to jadi' toe, mpo'une' Alata'ala-imi, na'uli': "Makono mpu'u-tawo! Hi'a he'e tauna to monoa'!"
25984	42	23	48	Hawe'ea tauna to morumpu merono, karahilo-na napa to jadi' toe, nculii' -ramo hilou hi tomi-ra, pai' halengko ohea mporera' -rera' hunamu-ra.
25985	42	23	49	Ane hawe'ea pome'inca-na Yesus hante tobine-tobine to mpotuku' -i ngkai Galilea, mokore molaa-ra mpohilo hawe'ea to jadi' toe.
25986	42	23	50	
25987	42	23	51	Ria hadua tomane to rahanga' Yusuf to ngkai ngata Arimatea hi tana' Yudea. Yusuf toei, tauna to lompe' pai' monoa' ingku-na, pai' to mpopea wo'o tempo-na Alata'ala jadi' Magau' hi dunia'. Nau' -i hadua topohura hi Polibua' Bohe Agama to Yahudi, aga uma napokonoi hawa' pai' kabotu' -ra to mpo'uli' Yesus kana rapatehi.
25988	42	23	52	Yusuf toei hilou hi Gubernur Pilatus mperapi' woto-na Yesus.
25989	42	23	53	Napopana'u-mi woto Yesus ngkai kaju parika' -na, naputu' hante kain to bula, pai' napopoturu hi rala daeo' to ralonga' hi panapa bulu'. Daeo' toe bo'u-pidi, ko'ia hangkania rapotanai.
25990	42	23	54	Eo toe, eo pomporodoa, pai' ntuku' ada to Yahudi ntepu'u ncimonou' toe rapalii' mobago, apa' ntepu'u-mi eo pepuea'.
25991	42	23	55	Toe pai' tobine to mpodohei Yesus ngkai Galilea mpotuku' Yusuf hilou hi daeo' toe. Rahilo beiwa woto Yesus ratu'u hi rala daeo'.
25992	42	23	56	Oti toe, nculii' -ramo hilou hi ngata, mporodo rampa-rampa hante lana honga bona ragelai' -ki woto Yesus. Oti toe, hi eo pepuea' rapento'oi-mi mobago ntuku' Atura Musa.
25993	42	24	1	 Eo Mingku mepupulo ngkii, tobine toera hilou hi daeo' mpokeni anu mohonga to oti-mi raporodo.
25994	42	24	2	Rata hi ria, rahilo-rawo watu po'unca-na tederu' -mi.
25995	42	24	3	Pesua' -rami hi rala daeo', aga uma raruai' woto-na Pue' Yesus.
25996	42	24	4	Bula-ra mokore nakeni ka'ingu' -ra, muu-mule' mehupa' rodua tomane to moheai meringkila' mokore hi ncori-ra.
25997	42	24	5	Wulunga-ramo tobine toera, pai' -ra motumpa hi tana'. Ra'uli' to rodua toera mpo'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' nipali' tauna to tuwu' hi olo' tomate?
25998	42	24	6	Uma-ipi ria hi rehe'i. Tuwu' nculii' -imi! Kiwoi-dile napa to na'uli' -kokoi wengi hi Galilea-e.
25999	42	24	7	Na'uli': Ana' Manusia' kana ratonu hi tauna to dada'a bona raparika', aga hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii' -i."
26000	42	24	8	Ngkai ree, rakiwoi mpu'u-mi lolita Yesus.
26001	42	24	9	Ponculi' -rami ngkai daeo', pai' ratutura hawe'ea to jadi' toe hi ana'guru Yesus to hampulu' hadua pai' hi hawe'ea topetuku' ntani' -na.
26002	42	24	10	Tobine toera, hira' Maria Magdalena, Yohana, pai' Maria tina Yakobus, pai' tobine ntani' -na to dohe-ra. Ratutura hawe'ea to jadi' toe hi suro Yesus.
26003	42	24	11	Aga suro toera uma mpangalai' lolita-ra, ra'uli' lolita to ratamangko-wadi.
26004	42	24	12	Hiaa' Petrus-hana, pokeno-nami hilou hi daeo'. Pengkabungku' -nami mpelongi' hi rala-na, nahilo muntu' hompu' -na-damo to hi ree. Oti toe, nculii' -imi hilou hi tomi-na, pai' ntora mokanono mpenonoi napa to jadi' tohe'e.
26005	42	24	13	 Hi eo toe wo'o, rodua topetuku' Yesus mako' hilou hi ngata Emaus, kalaa-na kira-kira hampulu' hakilo ngkai Yerusalem.
26006	42	24	14	Bula-ra momako' toe, ntora mololita-ra, mpololita hawe'ea to lako' jadi'.
26007	42	24	15	Bula-ra mololita pai' momepekune', muu-mule' rata-imi Yesus mpomohui' -ra pai' mako' dohe-ra.
26008	42	24	16	Pehilo moto-ra, aga ria anu to mpohilingai' -ra, alaa-na uma ra'incai Kayesus-na.
26009	42	24	17	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Napa-die to ntora nilolita ngkalako' -e?" Mentoda' -ra hante lence to monto'.
26010	42	24	18	To hadua, to rahanga' Kleopas, mpekune' Yesus, na'uli': "Ha lako' rata-ko-tanoe hi Yerusalem-e, pai' uma-di nu'incai napa to jadi' ba hangkuja eo to liu toi-e?"
26011	42	24	19	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa-die?" Hampetompoi' -ra: "To jadi' hi Yesus to Nazaret-le! Hi'a nabi to mobaraka' hi pobago-na pai' pololita-na, lompe' hi poncilo Alata'ala pai' hi poncilo ntodea.
26012	42	24	20	Imam pangkeni pai' totu'a ngata-ta mpotonu-i hi topoparenta bona rahuku' mate. Oti toe, raparika' mpu'u-i.
26013	42	24	21	Hiaa' haru' -mi-kaina nono-kai, apa' ki'uli' Hi'a-mi mpai' to mpobahaka-ta to Israel ngkai bali' -ta. Eo toe lau, eo katolu-nami ngkai karapatehia-na.
26014	42	24	22	Hiaa' toe-e, ba hangkuja dua tobine doo-kai mpolahoi ta'i-kai, apa' hilou-ra hi daeo' -na mepupulo ngone,
26015	42	24	23	tapi' woto-na uma-pi raruai'. Nculii' -ramo ra'uli' -kakai kampohilo-ra mala'eka to mpo'uli' tuwu' nculii' -imi.
26016	42	24	24	Ngkai ree, ba hangkuja dua doo-kai hilou hi daeo'. Rata hi ria, rahilo bate hewa to ra'uli' tobine toera. Aga Yesus uma rahiloi."
26017	42	24	25	Oti toe, Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Wojo mpu'u-koi! Uma oa' -tanoe niparasaya hawe'ea to ra'uli' nabi owi-e!
26018	42	24	26	Magau' Topetolo', bate kana mporata kaparia ncala' -i, pai' lako' mporata-i kabohe tuwu' -na."
26019	42	24	27	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpakanoto-raka hawe'ea to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' to mpolowa woto-na, ntepu'u ngkai sura to na'uki' nabi Musa duu' rata hi hawe'ea sura nabi.
26020	42	24	28	Mohu' -mi ngata to ratoa', Yesus ntani' kaliliu-i.
26021	42	24	29	Ntaa' ratagi-idi, ra'uli' -ki: "Mehani-tamo ulu hi rehe'i! Ncimonou' -mi, neo' mobengi-mi." Jadi' mehani mpu'u-imi Yesus dohe-ra.
26022	42	24	30	Mohura-ramo hangkaa-ngkania bona ngkoni'. Yesus mpo'ala' roti, naposampayai, napihe-pihe pai' natonu-miraka.
26023	42	24	31	Nto'u toe, lako' monoto-rada, pai' ra'inca Kayesus-na. Ngkai ree, hangaa mengkaronto-imi, uma-ipi rahiloi.
26024	42	24	32	Momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Toe-tawo' pai' tuna nono-ta hi ohea-e we'i, bula-na mpololitai-ta pai' mpakanoto-taka ihi' Buku Tomoroli' -e!"
26025	42	24	33	Pe'ongko' -ra wo'o-mi nculii' hilou hi Yerusalem, mpohirua' -raka ana'guru Yesus to hampulu' hadua, to bula-ra morumpu hante doo-ra.
26026	42	24	34	Ra'uli' to morumpu toera: "Makono mpu'u-di, katuwu' -na nculii' Pue' -e! Mehupa' -imi hi Simon!"
26027	42	24	35	Jadi', to rodua to lako' rata toera mpotutura wo'o-mi-rawo napa to jadi' hi lengko ohea we'i, pai' kara'inca-na Yesus nto'u kampopihe-pihe-na roti.
26028	42	24	36	 Bula-ra mololita-pidi, muu-mule' mokore wo'o-imi Yesus hi laintongo' -ra, pai' -i mpotabe-ra, na'uli': "Kalompea' rata hi koi'."
26029	42	24	37	Hakene-radile me'eka', apa' ra'uli' -rana mpohilo-ra kiu.
26030	42	24	38	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Napa pai' me'eka' -koi pai' morara' nono-nie?
26031	42	24	39	Hilo-dile rari' to hi pale-ku pai' to hi witi' -kue. Aku' -mile toi-e! Ganga-a pai' petonoi, apa' ane rate-hana, uma-hawo ihia pai' wukua hewa to nihilo hi Aku' toi-e."
26032	42	24	40	Oti toe, pai' napopohiloi-ramo pale pai' witi' -na.
26033	42	24	41	Ncaruku' raparasaya Kahi'a-na mpu'u-mi. Wule' mokanganga-ramo nakeni kagoe' nono-ra mogalo ingu'. Toe pai' Yesus mpekune' -ra, na'uli': "Ha ria koni' -ni?"
26034	42	24	42	Ratonu-miki bau' uru to ratunu.
26035	42	24	43	Nadoa-mi pai' nakoni', bona rahilo kabela-na-hawo kiu.
26036	42	24	44	Oti toe, na'uli' -miraka: "Toe-mile to ku'uli' -kokoie bula-ku dohe-ni-pidi. Butu nyala-na to mpolowa woto-ku to te'uki' hi rala sura to na'uki' nabi Musa pai' sura nabi-nabi pai' Buku Rona' Daud, hawe'ea-na kana madupa'."
26037	42	24	45	Oti toe, nanotohi nono-ra bona rapaha ihi' Buku Tomoroli'.
26038	42	24	46	Na'uli': "Hi rala Buku Tomoroli' te'uki': Aku' Magau' Topetolo' kana mporata kaparia pai' kana rapatehi, pai' hi eo katolu-na tuwu' nculii'.
26039	42	24	47	Pai' hi rala hanga' -ku Kareba Lompe' kana rapalele hi hawe'ea tauna, bona medea-ra ngkai jeko' -ra pai' Alata'ala mpo'ampungi-ra. Kareba toe kana rapalele hi humalili' dunia', ntepu'u ngkai Yerusalem.
26040	42	24	48	Koi' -mile to jadi' sabi' ngkai hawe'ea tohe'e-e lau.
26041	42	24	49	"Pe'epei lompe': kupakatu moto mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli' tumai hi koi', hewa to najanci Tuama-ku. Aga kana nipopea ulu hi rala ngata toi, duu' -na baraka' ngkai Alata'ala mana'u tumai mporohoi-koi."
26042	42	24	50	 Oti toe, Yesus mpo'ema' -ra hilou hi mali ngata Yerusalem, mohu' hi ngata Betania. Na'ongko' pale-na pai' nagane' -ramo.
26043	42	24	51	Bula-na mpogane' -ra toe, kate'oo-ongkoa' -imi mpogaa' -raka pai' hilou-imi hi suruga.
26044	42	24	52	Mowilingkudu-ramo mponyompa-i, pai' goe' lia nono-ra nculii' hilou hi Yerusalem.
26045	42	24	53	Eo-eo-na tida-ra hi rala Tomi Alata'ala mpo'une' -une' Alata'ala.
26046	43	1	1	 Lomo' -na, kako'ia-na dunia' rapajadi', mpolia' ria-imi-hana Lolita. Lolita toei, dohe Alata'ala-i, pai' Lolita toei, Hi'a moto-mi Alata'ala.
26047	43	1	2	Ngkai lomo' -na-imi dohe Alata'ala-e.
26048	43	1	3	Hi'a-mi to napopale Alata'ala mpopajadi' hawe'ea to rapajadi'. Uma ria hanyalaa to jadi' ane uma Hi'a.
26049	43	1	4	Hi'a-mi pehupaa' katuwua', pai' Hi'a-mi baja to mpobajahi nono manusia'.
26050	43	1	5	 Baja toe mehini ncuu hi rala kabengia-na, pai' kabengia uma mpakulei' mpopatehi-i.
26051	43	1	6	Rata hadua tauna to nasuro Alata'ala, hanga' -na Yohanes Topeniu'.
26052	43	1	7	Karata-na Yohanes toe, hi'a-mi jadi' sabi' to mpopalele baja toe hi hawe'ea tauna, bona hawe'ea-ra mpo'epe posabi' -na pai' mepangala' hi baja toei.
26053	43	1	8	Yohanes, bela-hawo hi'a baja toe-e. Pai' -i tumai, mpopalele baja toe hi hawe'ea tauna.
26054	43	1	9	Lolita toei, Hi'a-mi poko baja to mpobajahi nono hawe'ea tauna, rata-i hi rala dunia'.
26055	43	1	10	Hi'a-mi to napopale Alata'ala mpopajadi' dunia' toi. Tapi' karata-na hi dunia', tauna hi dunia' uma mpo'incai-i.
26056	43	1	11	Rata-i hi ngata-na moto, tapi' hingka ngata-na uma dota mpotarima-i.
26057	43	1	12	Tapi' hema-hema to mpotarima-i pai' mepangala' hi Hi'a, nawai' -ra huraa jadi' ana' Alata'ala.
26058	43	1	13	Uma-ra mewali ana' Alata'ala sabana totu'a-ra, bela wo'o ngkai kuasa manusia', ba ngkai poncamoko. Alata'ala moto to mpopajadi' -ra ana' -na.
26059	43	1	14	Lolita toei, mewali manusia' -imi, pai' -i mo'oha' hi laintongo' -ta. Kai', kihilo-mi-kaina kabaraka' -na. Kabaraka' -na toe narata ngkai Tuama-na, apa' Hi'a-mi Ana' -na to Hadudua. Ngkai Hi'a toe-mi pai' alaa-na ta'inca Alata'ala pai' kabula rala-na hi kita'.
26060	43	1	15	 Yohanes Topeniu' mpopo'incai ntodea kahema-na Lolita toei. Mekio' -i napesukui na'uli': "Hi'a toi-mile to ku'uli' -e wengi! Ku'uli': ria mpai' to tumai ngkabokoa' ngkai aku', aga meliu kabaraka' -na ngkai aku'. Apa' kako'ia-ku putu, mpolia' ria-imi-hana."
26061	43	1	16	Uma ria ka'otia ahi' -na, pai' ngkai ahi' -na toe nagane' -tamo omea, uma ria kaputua-na rasi' to tarata ngkai Hi'a.
26062	43	1	17	Ngkai nabi Musa tatarima Atura Pue' Ala. Tapi' ngkai Yesus Kristus toe-mi pai' ta'inca mpu'u-i Alata'ala, pai' kabula rala-na hi kita'.
26063	43	1	18	Uma ria haduaa to mpohilo Alata'ala. Tapi' Ana' -na to Hadudua toei, to tida oa' hi ncori-na, Hi'a-mi to mpakanoto Alata'ala hi kita'.
26064	43	1	19	 Hewa toi posabi' -na Yohanes Topeniu' mpo'uli' kahema-nai Yesus. Topoparenta to Yahudi hi Yerusalem mposuro ba hangkuja dua imam pai' to Lewi hilou hi Yohanes. Karata-ra hi Yohanes, mepekune' -ra: "Pai' -kai tumai toi-e, tumai mpekune' -ko ba hema-ko. Ba iko mpu'u-mi Magau' Topetolo' -e?"
26065	43	1	20	Yohanes mpotompoi' -ra hante kalonto' -lonto' -na, na'uli' -raka: "Bela-kuwo aku' Magau' Topetolo'."
26066	43	1	21	Mepekune' tena-ra: "Ane wae, hema-ko? Ba nabi Elia-dako?" Na'uli' Yohanes: "Bela wo'o." Mepekune' tena-ra: "Ba iko lau-midi nabi bohe to rajanci owi, to ra'uli' tumai mpai' hi rala dunia' -e?" Na'uli' Yohanes: "Bela wo'o."
26067	43	1	22	Ngkai ree, ra'uli' tena: "Ane wae, uli' -kakai ba hema mpu'u-ko, bona ria woli' -na kiparata-raka to mposuro-kai. Beiwa petompoi' -nu kahema-na mpu'u-ko."
26068	43	1	23	Yohanes mpotompoi' -ra hante lolita nabi Yesaya owi, na'uli': "Aku' toi-le, Tauna to mekio' hi papada to wao': 'Neo' rata-imi Pue'. Porodo ami' -miki ohea-na!'"
26069	43	1	24	
26070	43	1	25	Ra'uli' wo'o-mi suro to Parisi toera: "Ane bela-ko Magau' Topetolo', bela-ko nabi Elia, bela wo'o-ko nabi to rajanci, napa-di pai' mponiu' -ko tauna-e?"
26071	43	1	26	
26072	43	1	27	Na'uli' Yohanes: "Aku' -le mponiu' tauna hante ue-wadi. Tapi' rata mpai' hadua tauna ngkabokoa' ngkai aku'. Ria moto-imile hi laintongo' -ni tempo toi-e, tapi' uma-i ni'incai. Bangku' jadi' pahawaa' -na mpobongka koloro sapatu' -na, uma-a-kuwo natao."
26073	43	1	28	Hawe'ea toe jadi' hi ngata Betania, hi peniua' -na Yohanes hi dipo ue Yordan.
26074	43	1	29	 Kampeneo-na, Yohanes mpohilo Yesus rata mpotoa' -i. Na'uli' -mi hi ntodea: "Hilo! Etu-imi tumai Ana' Bima to naporodo Alata'ala. Hi'a-mi to jadi' tolo' woto to mpolali jeko' manusia'.
26075	43	1	30	Hi'a-mi to ku'uli' -e wengi. Ku'uli' rata-i ngkabokoa' ngkai aku', aga meliu kabaraka' -na ngkai aku'. Apa' kako'ia-ku putu, mpolia' ria-imi-hana.
26076	43	1	31	Lomo' -na wengi, ko'ia wo'o-kuwo ku'incai Kahi'a-nami Magau' Topetolo'. Hiaa' katumai-ku toi-e, bona mponiu' -ra to Israel hante ue pai' mpotudo' -raka kahema-na Magau' Topetolo' toe-e."
26077	43	1	32	
26078	43	1	33	
26079	43	1	34	Ria wo'o-mi posabi' -na Yohanes toi. Na'uli': "Lomo' -na uma ku'incai Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo'. Tapi' Alata'ala mpohubui-a mponiu' tauna hante ue, pai' na'uli' -ka hewa toi: 'Ane nampa' nuhilo mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli' mana'u pai' rodo hi hadua tauna, Hi'a-mi mpai' to mponiu' tauna hante Inoha' Tomoroli'.' Jadi', kuhilo mpu'u-mi Inoha' Tomoroli' mana'u ngkai suruga molence danci mangkebodo, mehompo pai' mengkarodo hi Yesus. Toe pai' toi-ka lolita-ku: Yesus, Hi'a-mi Ana' Alata'ala."
26080	43	1	35	Kampeneo-na, ria wo'o-i Yohanes hi ree hante ana'guru-na rodua.
26081	43	1	36	Kanahilo-na Yesus liu, na'uli': "Hilo, etu-imi tumai Ana' Bima Alata'ala!"
26082	43	1	37	 Kara'epe-na ana'guru-na lolita toe, kahilou-rami mpotuku' Yesus.
26083	43	1	38	Yesus mewili', nahilo-ra mpotuku' -i. Napekune' -ra: "Napa to nipali' -e?" Ra'uli' -ki: "Hiapa po'ohaa' -nu Guru?"
26084	43	1	39	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mai-mokoi, nihilo moto mpai'." Hilou mpu'u-ramo mpotuku' -i rata hi po'ohaa' -na. Pai' hi ree-ramo dohe-na ngkai jaa opo' duu' mobengi.
26085	43	1	40	Ana'guru-na Yohanes toera mpotuku' Yesus, apa' mpo'epe-ra lolita-na Yohanes Topeniu' we'i. Hadua ngkai to rodua toera, hanga' -na Andreas, ompi' -na Simon Petrus.
26086	43	1	41	Kaliliu hilou-imi Andreas mpopali' Simon, na'uli' -ki: "Kirua' -imi-kaina Mesias!" (batua-na: Magau' Topetolo').
26087	43	1	42	Pai' napo'ema' -imi hilou hi Yesus. Yesus mponaa Simon, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Iko Simon ana' -na Yohanes. Aga ntepu'u tempo toi, rahanga' Kefas-moko." (Hanga' "Kefas" hi rala basa-ra to Yahudi, hibalia hante hanga' "Petrus" hi rala basa Yunani. Batua-na: watu.)
26088	43	1	43	 Kampeneo-na, Yesus mopatuju hilou hi tana' Galilea. Kako'ia-na me'ongko', hilou-imi mpohirua' -ki Filipus pai' na'uli' -ki: "Tuku' -ama!"
26089	43	1	44	Filipus toei, ngkai ngata Betsaida, ngata-ra hira' Andreas pai' Petrus.
26090	43	1	45	Ngkai ree, hilou wo'o-imi-hawo Filipus mpohirua' -ki doo-na to rahanga' Natanael, na'uli' -ki: "Kirua' -imi-kaina Magau' Topetolo' -e, hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Atura Musa pai' sura nabi owi! Hanga' -na Yesus ngkai Nazaret, ana' -na Yusuf."
26091	43	1	46	Hampetompoi' Natanael: "Ha ria wo'o-hawo to lompe' to mehuwu ngkai Nazaret-e?" Na'uli' Filipus: "Mai-moko, nuhilo moto-i mpai'!" Hilou-ramo hi Yesus.
26092	43	1	47	Yesus mpohilo Natanael tumai mpohirua' -ki, na'uli': "Etu-i tumai hadua to Yahudi to mpo'uhi mpu'u kehi-na Israel ntu'a-na owi, bela-i topebagiu!"
26093	43	1	48	Na'uli' Natanael: "Ngkaiapa kanu'incaa-ku Guru?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Kako'ia-na nakio' -ko Filipus, kuhilo-mokole, hi tawu kaju ara toe-e ria."
26094	43	1	49	Na'uli' Natanael: "Ana' Alata'ala mpu'u-ko-tawo', Guru! Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' to Israel!"
26095	43	1	50	Na'uli' Yesus: "Nupangala' apa' ku'uli' kakuhilo-nu hi tawu kaju ara-e? Nuhilo tena-pi mpai' to meliu kabohe-na ngkai tetu."
26096	43	1	51	Oti toe, na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: nihilo mpai' langi' tebea pai' mala'eka Alata'ala ngkahe' pai' mana'u tumai hi Aku', Ana' Manusia'."
26097	43	2	1	 Timpaliu ro'eo ngkai toe, ria susa' poncamokoa hi ngata Kana hi tana' Galilea. Tina-na Yesus mpokaralai susa' toe.
26098	43	2	2	Pai' Yesus hante ana'guru-na, rakio' wo'o-ra-rawo ngkaralai susa' toe.
26099	43	2	3	Bula-ra mosusa' toe, naka'otii-ramo ue anggur. Tina-na Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Naka'otii-ra ue anggur."
26100	43	2	4	Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa pai' nu'uli' -ka hewa tetu-e, Ina'? Ko'ia rata tempo-na kupopo'incai-ra kahema-ku."
26101	43	2	5	Ngkai ree, na'uli' tina-na Yesus mpo'uli' -raka topobago: "Napa-napa mpai' to nahubui-kokoi Yesus, nibabehi-e'!"
26102	43	2	6	Hi tomi toe, ria ono meha' pontu'ua ue to rababehi ngkai watu. Pontu'ua ue toe rapake' rapontu'ui ue pobohoi' witi' pai' pale, ntuku' ada-ra to Yahudi. Kawori' ihi' -na, nte ha'atu lite butu meha' -na.
26103	43	2	7	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka topobago toera: "Ihii' pontu'ua ue tetu lau hante ue." Ra'ihii' mpu'u-mi rapoponu'.
26104	43	2	8	Oti toe, na'uli' wo'o-miraka: "Tolou' hangkedi', keni hilou hi tompohawai' susa'." Ratolou' mpu'u-mi pai' rakeni hilou hi topohawa'.
26105	43	2	9	Topohawa' toei mpemita ue to rakeni-ki. Bela-pi ue nonto, mobali' -mi mewali ue anggur. Aga uma-hawo na'incai kangkaiapa-na, muntu' topobago-wadi to mpo'inca. Ka'oti-na mpemita ue anggur toe, mekio' -i mpokio' topemua',
26106	43	2	10	pai' na'uli' -ki: "Kabiasaa-ta-hawo, anggur to motomo' -di-hawo to ri'ulu ratua-raka torata. Ane oha-ra-damo nginu, pai' lako' ratua to uma ncako motomo'. Hiaa' iko-kona mpotalaa anggur to motomo', pai' lako' tempo toi-di nupewai' ratua!"
26107	43	2	11	Yesus mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi toe hi ngata Kana hi tana' Galilea. Toe-mi tanda mekoncehi to lomo' -na to nababehi. Hante tanda toe napopohiloi kabaraka' -na, pai' ana'guru-na mepangala' hi Hi'a.
26108	43	2	12	 Hudu susa' toe, hilou-imi hi ngata Kapernaum hante tina-na, ompi' -na pai' ana'guru-na. Mo'oha' hi ree-ramo ba hangkuja mengi.
26109	43	2	13	Neo' rata-mi tempo-na eo bohe agama Yahudi to rahanga' Eo Paskah. Jadi', hilou-imi Yesus hi Yerusalem mpokaralai eo bohe toe.
26110	43	2	14	Hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala, mpohilo-i tauna to mpobalu' japi, bima pai' danci mangkebodo. Ria wo'o tauna to mposula' doi mohura hi ree.
26111	43	2	15	Yesus mpobabehi poweba' ngkai koloro, pai' nawuso omea-ra ngkai berewe Tomi Alata'ala, hante bima pai' japi-ra. Meja' -ra toposula' doi nabilingko, alaa-na pahawu' -hawu' -mi doi-ra.
26112	43	2	16	Na'uli' -raka topobabalu' danci mangkebodo: "Koi', keni omea tetu lau hilou hi mali-na! Tomi Tuama-ku neo' niponcawa tomi pobabalua'!"
26113	43	2	17	Ana'guru-na mpokiwoi lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli' hewa tohe'i: "Dede' nono-ku, apa' kupe'ahi' Tomi-nu Pue'."
26114	43	2	18	Ngkai ree, topoparenta to Yahudi mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Napa ntoto-kowo huraa-nu mpobabehi tetu-e? Ane ria mpu'u huraa-nu, popohiloi-kai tanda mekoncehi!"
26115	43	2	19	Na'uli' Yesus: "Gero-mi-hana Tomi Alata'ala toi, nihilo moto mpai' kadupa' -na rala-na tolu eo kuwangu nculii'."
26116	43	2	20	Konce-ra topoparenta to Yahudi, ra'uli': "Beiwa!? Tomi Alata'ala toi rawangu rala-na opo' mpulu' ono mpae, hiaa' nu'uli' -kona nuwangu nculii' rala-na tolu eo-wadi?"
26117	43	2	21	Api' woto-nadi to nawalatu Yesus, mpokahangai' Tomi Alata'ala-e.
26118	43	2	22	Ngkabokoa' -na ngkai toe, katuwu' -na nculii' mpu'u-mi Yesus, ana'guru-na mpokiwoi lolita-na toe-e. Ngkai ree rapangala' -mi napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' pai' napa to na'uli' Yesus.
26119	43	2	23	 Bula-na Yesus hi Yerusalem mpokaralai Eo Paskah toe, wori' tauna to mepangala' hi Hi'a, apa' rahilo tanda-tanda mekoncehi to nababehi.
26120	43	2	24	Aga Yesus uma mpangala' -ra, apa' na'inca nono hawe'ea tauna.
26121	43	2	25	Uma mingki' kahadua-na to mpo'uli' -ki kabeiwa-na manusia', apa' na'inca ami' napa to hi rala nono manusia'.
26122	43	3	1	 Ria hadua tauna to rahanga' Nikodemus. Nikodemus toei, to Parisi pai' pangkeni agama Yahudi.
26123	43	3	2	Rala-na hamengi, rata-i mpohirua' -ki Yesus, na'uli' -ki: "Guru, to ki'inca, Iko hadua guru to nasuro Alata'ala, apa' uma ria tauna to bisa mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi hewa to nubabehi, ane uma-i nadohei Alata'ala."
26124	43	3	3	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Ane tauna uma putu nculii', uma-i mpai' jadi' ntodea Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na."
26125	43	3	4	Na'uli' Nikodemus: "Ha beiwa-hawo tauna to motu'a-mi putu nculii' -e? Ha bisa-i mempuna' hi rala puanaka tina-na, pai' -i putu karongkani-nae?"
26126	43	3	5	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Ane tauna uma putu hante ue pai' hante baraka' Inoha' Alata'ala, uma-i jadi' ntodea Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na.
26127	43	3	6	Manusia' tuwu' hi rala dunia' toi, apa' putu ngkai totu'a-na. Tapi' katuwua' kao' -na to bo'u narata ngkai Inoha' Tomoroli'.
26128	43	3	7	Jadi', neo' nupokakonce lolita-ku tohe'i to mpo'uli': koi' omea kana putu nculii'.
26129	43	3	8	Rapa' -na ngolu', mewui hiapa kalaua-na. Wule' sere-na ta'epe, uma ta'incai kangkaiapa-na ba hilou hiapa-i. Wae wo'o hante tauna to putu ngkai baraka' Inoha' Alata'ala."
26130	43	3	9	Na'uli' Nikodemus: "Beiwa wo'o-hawo kawali-na tetu-e?"
26131	43	3	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Iko-le hadua guru to Israel to rabila', hiaa' uma-di-kona nu'incai batua-na lolita-ku toi-e!
26132	43	3	11	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Kai' mpo'uli' napa to ki'inca, kilolita napa to kihilo. Hiaa' uma-di nipangalai' lolita-kai.
26133	43	3	12	Ane kututura-kokoi napa to jadi' hi dunia', uma nipangala'. Peliu-liu-nami mpai' ane kututura-kokoi napa to jadi' hi suruga.
26134	43	3	13	Uma ria haduaa tauna hi dunia' to manake' hilou hi suruga. Muntu' Aku' -wadi to mpo'inca napa to jadi' hi suruga, apa' Aku' Ana' Manusia' to mo'oha' hi suruga ngkai owi pai' to mana'u tumai ngkai suruga.
26135	43	3	14	"Owi hi papada to wao', nabi Musa mpobabehi lence ule ngkai ngkala, pai' natu'u hi doe hampole kaju pai' natunya' napopokore. Hema-hema to natilo' ule, ane rangoa' lence ule ngkala toe, tuwu' moto-ra. Jadi', hewa ule ngkala toe rapokalangko owi, wae wo'o mpai' Aku' Ana' Manusia' kana rapokalangko,
26136	43	3	15	bona hema-hema to mepangala' hi Aku' mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na."
26137	43	3	16	Hewa toi-mi Alata'ala mpoka'ahi' hawe'ea tauna hi dunia', alaa-na napewai' Ana' -na to Hadudua, bona hema-hema to mepangala' hi Ana' -na toe, uma-ra mporata huku', tapi' mporata-ra katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26138	43	3	17	Bela patuju-na Alata'ala mposuro Ana' -na tumai hi dunia' bona mpohuku' manusia'. Patuju-na mposuro Ana' -na tumai-le, bona mpohore manusia' ngkai huku' jeko' -ra.
26139	43	3	18	Tauna to mepangala' hi Ana' Alata'ala, uma-ra rahuku'. Aga tauna to uma mepangala', monoa' -mi kanahuku' -ra Alata'ala, apa' uma-ra dota mepangala' hi Ana' Alata'ala to Hadudua toei.
26140	43	3	19	Rata-imi hi dunia' mpokeni baja hi hawe'ea tauna. Tapi' manusia' mpokono-pi bengi ngkai baja, apa' dada'a kehi-ra. Toe pai' Alata'ala mpohuku' -ra.
26141	43	3	20	Hawe'ea tauna to mpobabehi kehi to dada'a, mpokahuku' baja. Uma-ra dota rata hi kabajaa-na, bona neo' mpai' kahiloa kehi-ra to dada'a.
26142	43	3	21	Tauna to monoa' kehi-ra rata hi kabajaa-na, bona kahiloa po'ingku-ra pai' bona monoto-mi kampotuku' -ra konoa Alata'ala.
26143	43	3	22	 Oti toe, Yesus pai' ana'guru-na hilou hi tana' Yudea. Bula-ra hi ree, meniu' -ra mponiu' tauna to doko' jadi' topetuku' -na.
26144	43	3	23	
26145	43	3	24	Nto'u toe, Yohanes Topeniu' ko'ia-i ratarungku'. Meniu' -i hi ngata Ainon, uma molaa ngkai ngata Salim, apa' hi ree wori' ue. Butu eo-na tauna hilou mpopeniu' hi Yohanes.
26146	43	3	25	Rala-na ha'eo, ba hangkuja dua ana'guru Yohanes momehono' hante to Yahudi mpomehonoi' ada peniu' rala agama.
26147	43	3	26	Hilou-ramo hi Yohanes ra'uli' -ki: "Guru, nukiwoi-pidi wengi tauna to dohe-ta hi dipo ue Yordan, to nutudo' -kakaie? Oe-imi ria, meniu' wo'o-i-hawo, pai' kawoo-woria' tauna lou hi Hi'a!"
26148	43	3	27	Na'uli' Yohanes: "Kita' manusia' uma mporata napa-napa ane uma pewai' -na Alata'ala.
26149	43	3	28	Ni'epe moto-mi wengi lolita-ku. Ku'uli': aku' bela Magau' Topetolo'. Pai' -a tumai-kuwo-le, tumai meri'ulu ngkai Hi'a mporodo-ki ohea-na.
26150	43	3	29	"Ane rapa' -na hi susa' poncamokoa, topemua' -di-hana to jadi' poko-na, apa' hi'a-mi pue' tobine to rapemuai'. Ane bale-na topemua' -hawo-le, mokore-i mpopanene' -wadi-ki-hawo pai' mpe'epei hawa' -na. Pai' goe' -i mpo'epe libu' topemua'. Wae-mi-kuwo aku' -e, aku' hewa bale-na topemua'. Goe' -a, pai' gana kagoea' -ku, apa' kawoo-woria' tauna mpotuku' -i Yesus.
26151	43	3	30	Hi'a-mi to kana tepaiwongko tuwu' -na, pai' aku' kana tepai'ara' tuwu' -ku."
26152	43	3	31	Yesus, Hi'a-mi to tumai ngkai suruga, pai' meliu tuwu' -na ngkai hawe'ea. Tauna to ngkai dunia', bate manusia' biasa, pai' lolita-na mpololita napa-napa to jadi' hi dunia'. Aga Yesus, ngkai suruga-i-hana, pai' meliu tuwu' -na ngkai hawe'ea.
26153	43	3	32	Lolita-na mpololita napa to nahilo pai' to na'epe, tapi' uma ria to mpangala' lolita-na.
26154	43	3	33	Aga hema to mpangala' lolita-na mpo'uli': "Bate makono-hanale lolita Alata'ala-e."
26155	43	3	34	Apa' Hi'a-mi to nasuro Alata'ala mpohowa' lolita-na, pai' Alata'ala mpowai' -i Inoha' Tomoroli' hante uma ria huka' -na.
26156	43	3	35	Alata'ala to Tuama mpoka'ahi' Ana' -na, pai' nawai' -imi hawe'ea kuasa-na.
26157	43	3	36	Tauna to mepangala' hi Ana' -na toei, mporata-ramo katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na. Tauna to uma mengkoru hi Ana' -na toei, uma-ra mporata katuwua'. Mporata roe Alata'ala lau-rada duu' kahae-hae-na.
26158	43	4	1	 To Parisi mpo'epe kawoo-woria' tauna to hilou mpopeniu' hi Yesus jadi' topetuku' -na, alaa-na meliu-pi kawori' -na topetuku' -na Yesus ngkai topetuku' -na Yohanes Topeniu'.
26159	43	4	2	(Kakoo-kono-na, bela-hawo Yesus to meniu', ana'guru-na to meniu'.)
26160	43	4	3	Jadi', kana'inca-na Yesus kara'epe-nami to Parisi kareba toe, malai-imi ngkai tana' Yudea hilou nculii' hi tana' Galilea.
26161	43	4	4	 Rala pomako' -na tohe'e, kana mpotara tana' Samaria-i.
26162	43	4	5	
26163	43	4	6	Neo' tebua' -mi eo-na, rata-imi hi ngata to Samaria to rahanga' Sikar, uma molaa ngkai tana' to napewai' Yakub owi hi Yusuf ana' -na. Hi mali ngata toe, ria hameha' buwu to rahanga' buwu Yakub. Mohura-imi Yesus hi wiwi' buwu toe, apa' lenge' -imi momako'.
26164	43	4	7	
26165	43	4	8	Ana'guru-na kaliliu hilou hi ngata me'oli pongkoni'. Ko'ia mahae, rata hadua tobine to Samaria tumai ntomu'. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Totina, wai' -a-kuwo ue ku'inu."
26166	43	4	9	Konce tobine toei, apa' biasa-na to Yahudi morungku mposigalo-raka to Samaria. Toe pai' na'uli': "Iko to Yahudi, aku' to Samaria-a. Napa pai' daho' -ko mperapii' -a ue?"
26167	43	4	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane ke nu'inca kabohe rasi' to nawai' Alata'ala, pai' ane nu'inca-a kahema-ku Aku' to mperapii' -ko ue, tantu merapi' wo'o-ko-kowo hi Aku', pai' kuwai' -ko ue to tuwu'."
26168	43	4	11	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Ngkaiapa-kona ue to tuwu' to nu'uli' tetu-e, bo uma-di ria potolou' -nue, hiaa' buwu toi monala-hana.
26169	43	4	12	Buwu toi sosora ngkai Yakub, ntu'a-kai owi. Hi'a nginu ue ngkai rei moto-i-hawo, wae wo'o ana' -na pai' porewua-na. Ha nu'uli' -kona meliu kabohe tuwu' -nu ngkai Yakub, pai' ma'ala-ko mpewai' ue to meliu kalompe' -na ngkai ue buwu toi-e?"
26170	43	4	13	Na'uli' Yesus: "Hawe'ea tauna to nginu ue ngkai buwu toi, ngkamara nculii' -ra-pidi mpai'.
26171	43	4	14	Tapi' hema to mpo'inu ue to kuwai' -raka, uma-rapa ngkamara duu' kahae-hae-na. Apa' ue to kuwai' -raka toe, jadi' ue tuwu' to mo'ili ncuu hi rala nono-ra-- batua-na, mporata-ra katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na."
26172	43	4	15	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Ane wae, wai' -ama-kuna ue tetu, bona uma-apa ngkamara oa', pai' uma-apa mingki' tumai ntomu' butu eo-na hi rehe'i."
26173	43	4	16	Na'uli' Yesus: "Koi' ulu, kio' tomane-nu, pai' -ko nculii' tumai."
26174	43	4	17	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Uma-kuna motomanei-a." Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono-di,
26175	43	4	18	apa' lima ngkani-mokole motomanei-e, pai' tomane-nu tetu-e lou, bela tomane-nu moto. Jadi', makono lia lolita-nu we'i-e."
26176	43	4	19	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Ei', nabi-ko-tawo'!
26177	43	4	20	Kai' to Samaria, mepue' hi bulu' tohe'i moto-ka-kaiwo, hi bulu' pepuea' ntu'a-kai. Hiaa' koi' to Yahudi mpo'uli', kana hi Yerusalem-wadi pepuea' to makono."
26178	43	4	21	Na'uli' Yesus: "Pangala' -mi lolita-ku toi: Rata mpai' tempo-na, uma-pi wule' hi Yerusalem-wadi tauna mpopue' Alata'ala, uma wo'o hi bulu' toi-wadi.
26179	43	4	22	Koi' to Samaria, uma ni'incai kahema-na to nipue'. Kai' to Yahudi, ki'inca kahema-na to kipue', apa' ria pojanci Alata'ala to mpo'uli' kalompea' manusia' mehuwu ngkai laintongo' to Yahudi.
26180	43	4	23	Tapi' rata mpai' tempo-na-- pai' toi-mi tempo-na-- tauna to mepue' mpu'u-mpu'u hi Alata'ala to Tuama, kana mpopue' -i hante kuasa Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' ntuku' ohea to makono. Pepue' to hewa toe-mi to napokono Alata'ala to Tuama.
26181	43	4	24	Alata'ala, Hi'a-mi Inoha'. Jadi', tauna to mpopue' -i, kana mepue' hante kuasa Inoha' Tomoroli' pai' ntuku' ohea to makono."
26182	43	4	25	Na'uli' tobine toei: "Io', to ku'inca-na, rata mpai' Magau' Topetolo', to rahanga' Kristus. Ane rata-ipi mpai', Hi'a to mpakanoto omea hi kita'."
26183	43	4	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' -mile toi-e, to mpololitai-ko wae-e lau."
26184	43	4	27	 Bula-ra mololita, rata-ramo ana'guru-na ngkai ngata. Konce-ra mpohilo Yesus mpololitai hadua tobine. Aga uma haduaa to daho' mpopekune' tobine toei ba napa paraluu-na. Uma wo'o-ra daho' mpekune' Yesus ba napa pai' napololitai-i.
26185	43	4	28	Ngkai ree, tobine toei mpalahii-mi pontomua' -na hi ree, ncaliu hilou hi ngata mpo'uli' -raka hingka ngata-na:
26186	43	4	29	"Kita hilou mpohilo tauna to mpolohu-ka hawe'ea gau' -ku. Meka' ba lue' Hi'a mpu'u-mi Magau' Topetolo' -e!"
26187	43	4	30	Toe pai' hilou-ramo hi mali ngata doko' mpohirua' -ki Yesus.
26188	43	4	31	Lingku' -na tobine toe hilou hi rala ngata, ana'guru-na Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Guru, mai-tamo ngkoni'."
26189	43	4	32	Aga na'uli' Yesus: "Ria-ka-kuna koni' -ku to uma ni'incai."
26190	43	4	33	Momepekune' -ramo ana'guru-na ra'uli': "Hema-die to mpowai' -i pongkoni' -e?"
26191	43	4	34	Toe pai' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Pongkoni' -kule, mpotuku' konoa Pue' Ala to mposuro-a, pai' mposipolea pobago to nawai' -ka.
26192	43	4	35	Koi' biasa mpo'uli' lolita bulawa toi: Opo' mula-damo pai' lako' mepae-ta. Aga Aku' mpo'uli' -kokoi: Naa-dile, oe lau bonea to mperenene-damo pae-na pai' to hangaa rapepae-damo.
26193	43	4	36	Tauna to mepae bate mporata gaji' -ra, alaa-na topepae pai' to ntuja' goe' hangkaa-ngkania. Wua' to rapepae, batua-na, tauna to mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26194	43	4	37	Jadi', makono lolita bulawa to mpo'uli': 'Kahadua-na to ntuja', kahadua-na to mpepae.'
26195	43	4	38	Kuhubui-koi mpepae to bela tinuja' -ni. Tau ntani' -na to mpotuja', koi' to mpepae wua' pobago-ra."
26196	43	4	39	Hi ngata to Samaria toe, wori' tauna to mepangala' hi Yesus, apa' ra'epe lolita tobine toe we'i to mpo'uli': "Nalohu-maka hawe'ea gau' -ku."
26197	43	4	40	Jadi', kahilou-rami mpohirua' -ki Yesus, pai' raperapi' bona mehani-i hi ngata-ra. Mehani mpu'u-imi hi ree romengia.
26198	43	4	41	Ngkai ree, kawoo-woria' tena pue' ngata to mepangala' hi Yesus, apa' ra'epe moto-mi lolita-na.
26199	43	4	42	Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki tobine toei: "Wae lau kipangala' mpu'u-mi, uma muntu' ngkai lolita-nu iko-wadi. Apa' ki'epe ntilinga moto-mi lolita-na, pai' ki'inca Kahi'a-na mpu'u-mi Magau' Tompohore manusia' ngkai huku' jeko' -ra."
26200	43	4	43	 Timpaliu romengia hi Samaria, Yesus mpokaliliu pomako' -na hilou hi tana' Galilea.
26201	43	4	44	Ria hangkani Yesus mpo'uli': "Hadua nabi uma biasa rabila' hi ngata-na moto."
26202	43	4	45	Jadi', karata-na hi Galilea, tauna mpotarima-i hante kagoe' nono-ra, apa' ria-ra wengi hi Yerusalem mpokaralai eo bohe Paskah, pai' mpohilo hante mata-ra moto-mi hawe'ea anu mekoncehi to nababehi hi ria nto'u toe.
26203	43	4	46	Rata wo'o-imi Yesus hi ngata Kana hi Galilea, hi ngata pompobalia' -na ue jadi' anggur. Uma molaa ngkai Kana toe, ria hadua topohawa' hi ngata Kapernaum, to mobago hi tomi raja, peda' gaga ana' -na.
26204	43	4	47	Kana'epe-na topohawa' toei karata-na Yesus hi Galilea ngkai Yudea, hilou-imi hi ngata Kana mpohirua' -ki, na'uli' -ki: "Pue', hilou-ta hi Kapernaum, nupaka'uri' -ka-kuwo ana' -ku, apa' neo' mate-imi."
26205	43	4	48	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Ane uma-koi mpohilo tanda mekoncehi pai' anu mobaraka', uma oa' -koi mepangala'!"
26206	43	4	49	Na'uli' topohawa' toei: "Pue', hilou-tamo sohi', mate mpai' ana' -ku!"
26207	43	4	50	Na'uli' Yesus: "Nculii' -moko, mo'uri' -imi ana' -nu." Napangala' mpu'u-mi topohawa' toei lolita Yesus, pai' nculii' mpu'u-imi-hawo.
26208	43	4	51	Hi lengko ohea-i-pidi, ba hangkuja dua batua-na mpotomu-i, ra'uli' -ki: "Mo'uri' -imile ana' -nue!"
26209	43	4	52	Napekune' -ramo: "Jaa hangkuja-i mo'uri' -e?" Ra'uli': "Wengi, ba jaa satu mpo'eo tu, uma-ipi ngkelengi'."
26210	43	4	53	Nakiwoi-mi topohawa', nto'u-na toe mpu'u-mi wengi Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Mo'uri' -imi ana' -nu." Ngkai ree, topohawa' toei pai' hira' hantomia, mepangala' -ramo hi Yesus.
26211	43	4	54	Toe-mi tanda mekoncehi karongkani-na to nababehi Yesus hi Galilea karata-na ngkai Yudea.
26212	43	5	1	 Oti toe, nculii' -imi Yesus hilou hi Yerusalem bona mpokaralai-i eo bohe to Yahudi hi ria.
26213	43	5	2	Hi Yerusalem, mohu' hi wobo' wala to rahanga' Wobo' Bima, ria wuhu', hi rala basa Yahudi hanga' -na Betesda. Ntololikia wuhu' toe, ria lima meha' pengkawinaraa.
26214	43	5	3	Hi retu, wori' tauna to peda'. Ria towero, ria tokejo, ria topungku, ntora turu hi pengkawinaraa, ((mpopea kamojago-na ue wuhu'.
26215	43	5	4	Apa' pontu-na ria mala'eka Pue' mana'u tumai hi wuhu' toe mpojago ue-na. Pai' hema to ri'ulu mehompo hi rala wuhu' nto'u ue-na mojago, mo'uri' -i ngkai haki' to natodohaka.))
26216	43	5	5	Ria hi ree hadua tomane, tolu mpulu' walu mpae-imi peda'.
26217	43	5	6	Yesus mpohilo-i turu hi ree, pai' na'inca kamahae-nami peda'. Napekune' -i: "Dota-ko mo'uri'?"
26218	43	5	7	Na'uli' topeda' toei: "Pue', apa' uma-kuwo hema to mpokeni-a hilou rala wuhu' nto'u mojago ue-na. Ke lako' hilou-a-kuwo, to ntani' -na wo'o-mi to mpori'uluhi-a."
26219	43	5	8	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Memata-moko, lulu-mi ali' -nu, pai' mako' -moko."
26220	43	5	9	Kamo'uri' -nami tau toei, nalulu-mi ali' -na, pai' -i momako' -mi. Tohe'e jadi' hi Eo Sabat, eo pepuea' -ra to Yahudi.
26221	43	5	10	Toe pai' topoparenta to Yahudi mpokamaro tauna to lako' mo'uri' toei, ra'uli' -ki: "Eo Sabat-hanale toe-e lau! Uma-ko ma'ala ngkeni ali' -nu."
26222	43	5	11	Na'uli' tauna toei: "Apa' nahubui-a-kuwo tauna to mpaka'uri' -a we'i, na'uli' -ka: 'Lulu-mi ali' -nu pai' mako' -moko.'"
26223	43	5	12	Rapekune' -i: "Hema-i to mpohubui-ko ngkeni ali' -nue?"
26224	43	5	13	Tapi' uma na'incai kahema-na to mpaka'uri' -i, apa' Yesus uma-pi ria hi ree, mpolia' hilou-imi hi olo' tauna to wori'.
26225	43	5	14	Uma mahae ngkai ree, Yesus mpohirua' -ki tauna toei hi Tomi Alata'ala, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Mo'uri' -moko, neo' -pi-hawo mpobabehi jeko', bona neo' mpai' narumpa' -ko ba napa-napa to meliu kada'a-na."
26226	43	5	15	Ngkai ree, hilou-imi tauna toei mpohirua' -raka topoparenta to Yahudi, na'uli' -raka Kayesus-na to mpaka'uri' -i.
26227	43	5	16	Toe pai' topoparenta to Yahudi ntepu'u mpobalinai' Yesus, apa' mepaka'uri' -i-hana hi Eo Sabat.
26228	43	5	17	 Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Tuama-ku mobago duu' eo toi, pai' Aku' wo'o kana mobago."
26229	43	5	18	Ngkai ree, rahuduwukui-mi topoparenta to Yahudi mpali' ohea-ra mpopatehi-i. Apa' uma wule' kampotiboki-na ada hi Eo Sabat, tapi' na'uli' wo'o-hana ka'Alata'ala-na Tuama-na; jadi', napopohibalia-hana woto-na hante Alata'ala.
26230	43	5	19	Toe pai' na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Aku' Ana' Alata'ala, uma-a bisa mobago ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Muntu' to kuhilo ngkai Tuama-ku, toe-mi to kupobago. Napa-napa bago Tuama-ku, tetu wo'o-kuwo bago-ku.
26231	43	5	20	Apa' Tuama-ku mpoka'ahi' -a, pai' napopohiloi-a hawe'ea to napobago. Kakupaka'uri' -na topeda' toe ngone ria, pai' kubabehi wo'o mpai' pobago to meliu kabohe-na ngkai toe, alaa-na konce mpu'u-mokoi mpai'.
26232	43	5	21	Hewa Tuama-ku mpopemata tomate pai' mpowai' -ra katuwua', wae wo'o Aku' mpowai' katuwua' hi hema-hema to kupelihi.
26233	43	5	22	Tuama-ku moto uma mpobotuhi kara-kara manusia'. Hawe'ea kuasa pompobotuhi natonu-mi hi Aku' Ana' -na.
26234	43	5	23	Nababehi toe, bona hawe'ea tauna mpobila' -a hewa pompobila' -ra Tuama-ku. Hema to uma mpobila' -a, uma wo'o-ra mpobila' Tuama-ku to mposuro-a.
26235	43	5	24	"Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Hema to mpo'epe lolita-ku pai' -ra mepangala' hi Pue' Ala to mposuro-a, bate mporata-ra katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na. Uma-ra mpai' rahuku' sabana jeko' -ra. Tebahaka-ramo ngkai kamatea, mporata-ramo katuwua'.
26236	43	5	25	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Rata mpai' tempo-na-- pai' toi-mi tempo-na-- tauna tomate mpo'epe libu' Ana' Alata'ala, pai' hira' to mpo'epe mporata katuwua' to bo'u.
26237	43	5	26	Apa' hewa Tuama-ku mobaraka' mpowai' katuwua', wae wo'o nawai' -a baraka' mpowai' katuwua'.
26238	43	5	27	Nawai' wo'o-a kuasa mpobotuhi kara-kara manusia', apa' Aku' Ana' Manusia'.
26239	43	5	28	"Neo' nipokakonce lolita-ku toi, apa' rata mpai' tempo-na hawe'ea tauna to hi rala daeo' mpo'epe libu' -ku,
26240	43	5	29	pai' -ra memata ngkai daeo' -ra. To mpobabehi gau' to lompe' rapopemata bona mporata katuwua' to lompe'. To mpobabehi gau' to dada'a rapopemata bona rahuku'.
26241	43	5	30	"Aku', uma-a bisa mpobabehi napa-napa ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Kubotuhi ntuku' to nahawai' -ka Alata'ala. Pobotuhi-ku monoa', apa' uma-a mpotuku' dota-ku moto, mpotuku' -a kadota-na Pue' Ala to mposuro-a.
26242	43	5	31	 "Ane ke Aku' moto-wadi to mpo'uli' ka'Aku' -na suro Alata'ala, pai' uma ria tau ntani' -na to mposabii' -a, uma ni'incai ba makono lolita-ku ba uma-di.
26243	43	5	32	Tapi' ria moto kahadua-na to mposabii' -a, pai' ku'inca kamakono-na posabi' -na toe.
26244	43	5	33	Koi' mpohubui doo-ni hilou hi Yohanes Topeniu' wengi, pai' na'uli' -miraka posabi' -na. Napa to na'uli' toe, bate makono omea.
26245	43	5	34	Aga kakoo-kono-na uma kuparaluu posabi' ngkai manusia'. Kupopokiwoii-koi lolita-na Yohanes toe-e, bona mporata-koi kalompea'.
26246	43	5	35	Yohanes toei hewa lampu to mehini pai' ngkeni kabajaa-na hi koi'. Pai' koi', goe' lia moto-koi mpo'epe lolita-na. Aga kagoe' -ni tetu hampai' -wadi.
26247	43	5	36	"Aga Aku', ria-ka-kuna sabi' to mpakanoto kahema-ku, pai' sabi' toei meliu ngkai posabi' -na Yohanes. Ane ninaa lompe' pobago-ku, toe-mile to mposabii' kahema-kue. Napa to kupobago hewa toe lau, pobago to nahawai' -ka Tuama-ku bona kuposipolea. Pobago-ku toi-mi to mpakanoto ka'Aku' -na suro Tuama-ku.
26248	43	5	37	Pai' meliu ngkai toe, Tuama-ku to mposuro-a, Hi'a moto-mi jadi' sabi' -ku mpo'uli' kahema-ku. Tapi' koi', ko'ia hangkania ni'epei libu' -na, ko'ia nihiloi lence-na.
26249	43	5	38	Lolita-na uma nitimamahi hi rala nono-ni, apa' uma-koi mepangala' hi Aku' to nasuro.
26250	43	5	39	Koi' mpewulihi' ihi' Buku Tomoroli', apa' ni'uli' mporata-koi katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na ngkai Buku Tomoroli' toe. Hiaa' Buku Tomoroli' moto wo'o-mi to mpotompo'wiwi-a.
26251	43	5	40	Aga nau' wae, uma oa' -koi dota tumai hi Aku', bona mporata katuwua' to lompe' toe.
26252	43	5	41	"Uma-a mpopebila' hi manusia'.
26253	43	5	42	Apa' ku'inca moto-koi, ka'uma-na ria ahi' -ni hi Alata'ala.
26254	43	5	43	Katumai-ku toi, mpokeni-a hanga' -na Tuama-ku, aga uma-koi dota mpotarima-a. Ane ria to tumai mpokeni hanga' -ra moto-wadi, nitarima lau-ra.
26255	43	5	44	Beiwa kamepangala' -ni hi Aku' -e, apa' doko' rabila' doo-wadi-koi, uma-koi mpali' pebila' to ngkai Alata'ala to Hadudua.
26256	43	5	45	Aga neo' ni'uli' wae, Aku' mpai' to mpakilu-koi hi Tuama-ku. Nabi Musa moto-mi to mpakilu-koi. Ni'uli' -koina ngkai petuku' -ni hi hawa' Musa pai' -koi mporata kalompea'.
26257	43	5	46	Tapi' ane bongko nipangala' mpu'u-i Musa, tantu nipangala' wo'o-a Aku' -e, apa' napa to na'uki' Musa, Aku' -mi kadungkua-na.
26258	43	5	47	Bangku' to na'uki' Musa uma nipangala', peliu-liu-nami ka'uma-na nipangala' lolita-ku."
26259	43	6	1	 Oti toe, hilou-imi Yesus hi dipo Rano Galilea, to rahanga' wo'o Rano Tiberias.
26260	43	6	2	Wori' lia tauna mpotuku' -i, apa' rahilo hawe'ea tanda mekoncehi to nababehi, mpaka'uri' topeda'.
26261	43	6	3	Manake' -i lou hi panapa bulu' hante ana'guru-na, pai' mohura-imi hi ree.
26262	43	6	4	Nto'u toe, neo' rata-mi eo bohe agama Yahudi to rahanga' Eo Paskah.
26263	43	6	5	Yesus mponaa ntololikia-na, nahilo-hawo, mo'iko-ra-damo tauna tumai mpomohui' -i. Na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Filipus: "Hiapa-ta me'oli pongkoni', tapokoni' -raka tauna to wori' toera lau?"
26264	43	6	6	(Kakoo-kono-na, na'inca ami' moto-mi napa mpai' to nababehi. Napekune' hewa toe hi Filipus, apa' doko' naponciloi pepangala' -na.)
26265	43	6	7	Na'uli' Filipus: "Nau' ro'atu doi pera' tapope'oli-ki pongkoni' pai' butu dua-ra tawai' hore hangkedi' -wadi, uma oa' hono'."
26266	43	6	8	Ngkai ree, hadua ana'guru-na to rahanga' Andreas, ompi' -na Simon Petrus, mpo'uli':
26267	43	6	9	"Ohe'i hadua ana' to mobokui lima meha' roti pai' tinapa uru roma'a, aga napa-mile kalaua-na hi tauna to wori' hewa toe-e lau?"
26268	43	6	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Hubui-ramo mohura!" Jadi' mohura-ramo hi kowo' raponcawa ali', apa' wori' kowo' hi ree. Hi olo' ntodea toe, ria ba lima ncobu paka' tomane.
26269	43	6	11	Ngkai ree, na'ala' -mi roti, na'uli' tarima kasi hi Alata'ala, pai' nabagi-bagi hi tauna to wori' to mohura. Hewa toe wo'o pompobabehi-na hante bau' uru. Ngkoni' -ramo omea duu' -ra bohu.
26270	43	6	12	Bohu-ramo omea, na'uli' Yesus hi ana'guru-na: "Rumpu-koi toro-na, bona neo' ria to rakerei."
26271	43	6	13	Rarumpu mpu'u-mi, hampulu' roluncu-pi toro-na ngkai lima meha' roti to rakoni' tauna to wori' we'i.
26272	43	6	14	Karahilo-na ntodea tanda mekoncehi tohe'e, momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Hi'a mpu'u-mi-tawo' nabi to rajanci owi-e, to ra'uli' rata mpai' hi dunia' toi-e!"
26273	43	6	15	 Jadi', ria patuju-ra doko' mpewuku-i jadi' magau' -ra. Kana'inca-na Yesus patuju-ra toe, malai-imi ngkai ree hilou hi bulu' -na.
26274	43	6	16	Ncimonou' tohe'e, mana'u-ramo ana'guru-na hilou hi rano mpopea-i.
26275	43	6	17	Rapopea duu' mobengi, ko'ia oa' -i rata. Jadi', mosakaya moto-ramo hilou mpotoa' ngata Kapernaum.
26276	43	6	18	Bula-ra mosakaya toe, rata ngolu' bohe mporumpa' -ra, alaa-na bohe balumpa hi rano.
26277	43	6	19	Lima ba ono kilo-ramo ngkai talinti, rahilo-rawo, etu-imi tumai Yesus momako' hi lolo ue mpototopa-ra. Aga uma ra'incai Kayesus-na. Me'eka' lia-ramo.
26278	43	6	20	Na'uli' Yesus: "Neo' me'eka'! Aku' -mile toi-e."
26279	43	6	21	Mpo'epe toe-di, goe' -ramo mpodoa Yesus hi rala sakaya. Pesua' -na Yesus hi rala sakaya, rata-ramo hi wiwi' talinti to ratoa'.
26280	43	6	22	 Kampeneo-na, wori' tauna hi dipo rano mpopali' Yesus, ra'uli': "Hiapa-imidie? Uma-idi mohawi' sakaya dohe ana'guru-nae ngone. Hiaa' uma ria sakaya ntani' -na hi rei ngone, muntu' sakaya to rahawi' ana'guru-na-wadi."
26281	43	6	23	Ngkai ree, rata wo'o tauna ngkai ngata Tiberias hi rala sakaya-ra, pai' -ra mencore mohu' hi pongkonia' -ra ntodea wengi, to mpokoni' roti to nagane' Pue' Yesus.
26282	43	6	24	Kara'inca-na ntodea ka'uma-napi ria Yesus hi ree, ntahawe' ana'guru-na uma wo'o-pi ria, mosakaya wo'o-ramo-rawo hilou hi Kapernaum mpopali' -i.
26283	43	6	25	Karata-ra ntodea hi dipo rano mpohirua' -ki Yesus, rapekune' -i: "Nto'uma-ko rata hi rehe'i-e, Guru?"
26284	43	6	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Ku'inca moto-le patuju-ni mpali' -ae. Uma ba kani'inca-na batua-na tanda mekoncehi to kubabehi. Nipali' -ale apa' bohu-mokoi kupokoni'.
26285	43	6	27	Neo' -koi mobago mpali' pongkoni' to sohi' oti pai' waha'. Mobago-koi mpali' pongkoni' to uma ria kawahaa' -na pai' to mpowai' katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na. Aku' Ana' Manusia' to mpowai' -koi pongkoni' tohe'e, apa' Alata'ala to Tuama mpotudo' ka'Aku' -nami to napelihi pai' to napokono."
26286	43	6	28	 Mepekune' -ra ntodea: "Napa to kana kipobago bona pobago-kai ntuku' konoa Alata'ala?"
26287	43	6	29	Na'uli' Yesus: "Toi-mile pobago to napokono Alata'ala-e: mepangala' hi Aku' to nasuro."
26288	43	6	30	Ra'uli' wo'o-mi ntodea: "Ane wae, tanda napa to nupopohiloi-kakai, bona kipangala' -ko kangkai Alata'ala-na mpu'u-ko? Napa to nubabehi?
26289	43	6	31	Wai' -ka-kaiwo pongkoni', hewa to rakoni' ntu'a-ta owi. Bula-ra hi papada to wao', ngkoni' -ra pongkoni' to rahanga' manna, hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli': 'Nawai' -ra pongkoni' ngkai suruga.'"
26290	43	6	32	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Bela nabi Musa owi to mpowai' pongkoni' ngkai suruga. Tempo toi-e, Tuama-ku-hana to mpowai' -koi pongkoni' to mpu'u-mpu'u ngkai suruga.
26291	43	6	33	Pongkoni' to nawai' Alata'ala, batua-na, to mana'u tumai ngkai suruga pai' to mpowai' katuwua' hi manusia'."
26292	43	6	34	Ra'uli' -ki ntodea: "Ane wae, wai' -ka-kaiwo pongkoni' tetu butu-butu eo-na!"
26293	43	6	35	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' toi-mi pongkoni' to mpowai' katuwua'. Hema to tumai hi Aku' uma-rapa mo'oro', pai' hema to mepangala' hi Aku' uma-rapa ngkamara, duu' kahae-hae-na.
26294	43	6	36	Aga hewa to ku'uli' we'i, nau' nihilo-ama, uma oa' -a nipangala'.
26295	43	6	37	Hawe'ea tauna to nawai' -maka Tuama-ku, bate tumai hi Aku'. Pai' hema-hema to tumai hi Aku', bate kutarima-i pai' uma-i kupopalai.
26296	43	6	38	Apa' tumai-a ngkai suruga, uma mpobabehi konoa-ku moto. Tumai-a mpobabehi konoa-na Alata'ala to mposuro-a.
26297	43	6	39	Toi-mi konoa-na: bona ngkai hawe'ea tauna to nawai' -ka, neo' mpai' ria haduaa to moronto, bate kupopemata-ra omea hi Eo Kiama.
26298	43	6	40	Toi-mi konoa Tuama-ku: bona hawe'ea to mpohilo pai' to mepangala' hi Aku' Ana' -na mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na, pai' kupopemata-ra hi Eo Kiama."
26299	43	6	41	Ngkai ree, mparangkunutia-ramo to Yahudi, apa' na'uli' -hana Yesus, Hi'a-mi pongkoni' to mana'u tumai ngkai suruga.
26300	43	6	42	Momepololitai-ramo ra'uli': "Ah, Hi'a toe-le Yesus, ana' Yusuf. Ta'inca moto tina-na pai' tuama-na. Napa-di-hana pai' na'uli' ngkai suruga-ie?"
26301	43	6	43	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Neo' -koi ngkunuti.
26302	43	6	44	Uma ria haduaa to ma'ala tumai hi Aku', ane uma-ra nakeni Tuama-ku to mposuro-a. Pai' kupopemata-ra omea hi Eo Kiama.
26303	43	6	45	Hi rala sura nabi-nabi owi te'uki' hewa toi: 'Alata'ala mpotudui' hawe'ea topetuku' -na.' Jadi', hawe'ea tauna to mpo'epe pai' mpotarima tudui' -na Tuama-ku, bate tumai-ra hi Aku'.
26304	43	6	46	Aga neo' ni'uli' wae, ria mpu'u-ramo to mpohilo Tuama-ku. Muntu' Aku' -wadi to mpohilo-i, apa' Aku' ngkai Alata'ala-a-kuna.
26305	43	6	47	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: hema to mepangala' hi Aku', mporata-ramo katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26306	43	6	48	Aku' -mi pongkoni' to mpowai' katuwua'.
26307	43	6	49	"Pongkoni' to rahanga' manna to rakoni' ntu'a-ni owi hi papada to wao' uma mpowai' katuwua', apa' mate omea moto-ra.
26308	43	6	50	Aga uma hewa toe ane pongkoni' to mana'u tumai ngkai suruga. Hema-hema to ngkoni' pongkoni' toi, uma-ra mate.
26309	43	6	51	Aku' toi-mi pongkoni' to mana'u tumai ngkai suruga, pongkoni' to tuwu'. Tauna to ngkoni' pongkoni' toi tuwu' duu' kahae-hae-na. Pongkoni' to tuwu' tohe'i, batua-na woto-ku to kupewai' bona manusia' mporata katuwua'."
26310	43	6	52	Kara'epe-na to Yahudi lolita-na Yesus toe, momehono' -ramo himpau hira', ra'uli': "Beiwa-i ma'ala mpewai' woto-na hi kita' bona takoni' -e?"
26311	43	6	53	Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Ane uma nikoni' woto-ku, Aku' Ana' Manusia', pai' uma ni'inu raa' -ku, uma-koi mporata katuwua' kao' -ni.
26312	43	6	54	Tauna to ngkoni' woto-ku pai' nginu raa' -ku, mporata-ramo katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na, pai' kupopemata-ra hi Eo Kiama.
26313	43	6	55	Apa' woto-ku pongkoni' mpu'u, pai' raa' -ku ininu mpu'u.
26314	43	6	56	Tauna to ngkoni' woto-ku pai' nginu raa' -ku, tida-ra hintuwu' hante Aku', pai' Aku' hante hira'.
26315	43	6	57	"Tuama-ku to mposuro-a, Hi'a-mi pehupaa' katuwua', pai' Aku' tuwu' ngkai Hi'a. Wae wo'o tauna to ngkoni' woto-ku, mporata-ra katuwua' ngkai Aku'.
26316	43	6	58	Toi mpu'u-mile pongkoni' to mana'u ngkai suruga-e, uma hewa manna to rakoni' ntu'a-ni owi. Nau' -ra ngkoni' manna toe, bate mate oa' -ra. Tapi' tauna to ngkoni' pongkoni' toi-e, tuwu' -ra duu' kahae-hae-na."
26317	43	6	59	Yesus mpololita hawe'ea toe nto'u petudui' -na hi tomi posampayaa hi Kapernaum.
26318	43	6	60	 Kampo'epe-ra lolita Yesus toe we'i, wori' topetuku' -na mpo'uli': "Ah! Mokoro rahi tudui' toe-e. Hema mpai' to mpokule' mpotuku'!"
26319	43	6	61	Ntaa' na'inca moto-di Yesus kangkunuti-ra topetuku' -nae. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ha nipokedi' nono mpo'epe tudui' -ku we'i?
26320	43	6	62	Ane wae-di, beiwa mpai' ane nihilo-apa, Aku' Ana' Manusia', ngkahe' nculii' hilou hi po'ohaa' -ku ami'?
26321	43	6	63	Inoha' Alata'ala-hana to mpowai' katuwua'. Kuasa manusia' uma ria kalaua-na. Lolita to kupohowa' -kokoi mehuwu ngkai Inoha' Alata'ala pai' mpowai' katuwua'.
