26322	43	6	64	Aga nau' wae, ria moto-koi hantongo' to uma mepangala'." Yesus mpo'uli' hewa toe apa' na'inca ami' -mi ngkai lomo' -na kahema-ra to uma mepangala' hi Hi'a, pai' na'inca wo'o kahema-na mpai' to mpobalu' -i hi bali' -na.
26323	43	6	65	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Toe pai' ku'uli' -mi we'i, uma haduaa to ma'ala tumai hi Aku' ane uma-ra napiliu Tuama-ku."
26324	43	6	66	Ntepu'u ngkai tempo toe, wori' topetuku' -na Yesus mpalahii-i. Uma-rapa dota mpotuku' -i.
26325	43	6	67	Jadi', mepekune' wo'o-imi hi ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, na'uli': "Ha malai wo'o-koi mpai' koi' -e?"
26326	43	6	68	Na'uli' Simon Petrus: "Ha hilou hi hema-makai mpai' Pue'? Iko-wadi to mpohowa' lolita to mpowai' katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26327	43	6	69	Kipangala' -mi pai' ki'inca ka'Iko-na Suro to moroli' ngkai Alata'ala."
26328	43	6	70	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' moto-mile to mpelihi-koi to hampulu' rodua toi-e. Nau' wae, hadua ngkai koi' mewali seta mpai'."
26329	43	6	71	To natoa' Yesus, Yudas ana' Simon Iskariot. Apa' nau' Yudas hadua ngkai ana'guru-na to hampulu' rodua, hi'a mpai' to mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na.
26330	43	7	1	 Oti toe, Yesus modao' hi tana' Galilea. Uma-ipi dota hilou hi tana' Yudea, apa' topoparenta to Yahudi hi ria doko' mpopatehi-i.
26331	43	7	2	Nto'u toe, neo' rata-mi eo bohe to Yahudi to rahanga' Posusa' Pobamaru'.
26332	43	7	3	Jadi', ompi' -na Yesus mpobawai-i hilou hi Yudea mpokaralai eo bohe toe, ra'uli' -ki: "Neo' -hawo ntora hi rehe'i! Hilou-tamo hi Yudea, bona topetuku' -nu mpohilo anu mekoncehi to nubabehi.
26333	43	7	4	Uma-ko mpai' jadi' tau bohe ane ntora hi rehe'i-wadi-ko. Ane mpobabehi anu mekoncehi mpu'u-ko, popohiloi hawe'ea tauna hi dunia'!"
26334	43	7	5	Hewa toe-mi lolita-ra ompi' -na Yesus, apa' uma wo'o-ra-rawo mepangala' hi Hi'a.
26335	43	7	6	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ko'ia rata tempo-na kupopehuwu woto-ku. Ane koi' -koina, uma beiwa ba nto'uma-koi hilou hi Yerusalem,
26336	43	7	7	apa' uma ria tauna to mpokahuku' -koi. Aku' -e, rapokahuku' -a-kuna tauna to dada'a hi dunia' toi, apa' ntora ku'uli' -raka kadada'a kehi-ra.
26337	43	7	8	Meri'ulu-mokoi hilou hi posusaa' toe ria. Aku', ko'ia-a-kuna hilou, apa' ko'ia rata tempo-ku."
26338	43	7	9	Wae-mi lolita Yesus hi ompi' -na, pai' tida moto-imi hi Galilea.
26339	43	7	10	Hilou mpu'u-ramo ompi' -na Yesus hi Yerusalem bona mpokaralai Posusa' Pobamaru' hi ria. Ntaa' metuku' bongo moto-idi-hawo Yesus-e, aga hadudua-na bona neo' ra'incai ntodea.
26340	43	7	11	Hi posusaa' toe, topoparenta to Yahudi ntora mpopali' -i, ra'uli': "Hiapa-imidi Yesus-e?"
26341	43	7	12	Pai' ntodea wo'o, mparanusi-ramo mpotompo'wiwi-i. Ria-ra to mpo'uli': "Tauna to lompe' moto-i-hawo." Hantongo' wo'o mpo'uli': "Uma-di! Topebagiu-i-hana!"
26342	43	7	13	Tapi' uma haduaa to daho' mpolonto', apa' me'eka' wo'o-ra wa hi topoparenta to Yahudi.
26343	43	7	14	 Pentongoa' posusa' tohe'e, Yesus mesua' hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, pai' natepu'u-mi metudui'.
26344	43	7	15	Konce-ra topoparenta to Yahudi mpo'epe tudui' -na, ra'uli': "Beiwa pai' na'inca ihi' Buku Tomoroli', bo uma-i-hawo mosikola-e?"
26345	43	7	16	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "To kutudui' -kokoile, tudui' ngkai Alata'ala to mposuro-a, bela tudui' -ku moto.
26346	43	7	17	Hema to doko' mpobabehi konoa Alata'ala, ra'inca mpai' kangkaiapa-na tudui' -ku toi, ba ngkai Alata'ala mpu'u-di ba lolita-ku moto-wadi.
26347	43	7	18	Tauna to mpokeni lolita-na moto, mpope'une' -i-wadi. Tapi' tauna to mpali' karabilaa' -na Alata'ala to mposuro-i, tauna to monoa' -i, uma ria pebagiua-na.
26348	43	7	19	Nabi Musa owi mpowai' -koi Atura Pue'. Tapi' uma-koi ria haduaa to mpotuku' Atura toe. Napa pai' doko' nipatehi-a?"
26349	43	7	20	Ra'uli' ntodea: "Wuli-ko! Hema to doko' mpopatehi-ko?"
26350	43	7	21	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mekehele-koi, apa' mpaka'uri' -a tauna hi Eo Sabat.
26351	43	7	22	Hiaa' koi' wo'o mobago moto hi Eo Sabat ane mpobabehi-koi ada petini'. Nabi Musa owi mpohubui-koi mpotini' ana' -ni. (Tapi' kakoo-kono-na ada petini' toe ngkai ntu'a-ta owi to meri'ulu ngkai Musa, bela ngkai Musa moto.) Ane ria ana' -ni to kana ratini' hi Eo Sabat, bate nitini' moto-i.
26352	43	7	23	Jadi', ane metini' -koi hi Eo Sabat bona neo' ntiboki Atura Musa, napa pai' nikaroe-a apa' mpaka'uri' -a tauna hi Eo Sabat bona hobo' woto-na lompe'?
26353	43	7	24	Neo' ranaa to kahiloa hi mali-na-wadi. Pakanoa' powile-ni bona nihilo napa to makono."
26354	43	7	25	Kara'epe-na pue' ngata Yerusalem lolita-na Yesus toe, ingu' -ramo. Ria-ra to mpo'uli': "Ha bela tauna toe-imi mai to rapali' pangkeni-ta, doko' rapatehi-e?
26355	43	7	26	Hiaa' he'e-imi mai metudui' hante uma ria kakoo-koroa' -na, pai' uma hema to mpokamaro-i. Ba lue' ra'inca lau-mi pangkeni-ta Kahi'a-na Magau' Topetolo' -e?
26356	43	7	27	Aga uma-hawo masipato' Kahi'a-na Magau' Topetolo', apa' ta'inca kangkaiapa-na. Ane rata mpu'u mpai' Magau' Topetolo' to rajanci owi-e, uma mpai' hema to mpo'incai kangkaiapa-na."
26357	43	7	28	Jadi', bula-na Yesus metudui' hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, mekio' -i napesukui, na'uli': "Ni'uli' ni'inca moto kahema-ku pai' kangkaiapa-ku. Tumai-a, uma ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Tumai-a mpotuku' konoa-na Alata'ala to mposuro-a. Hi'a-mi to masipato' rapangala'. Tapi' koi' uma mpo'incai-i.
26358	43	7	29	Aku', ku'inca-i apa' ngkai Hi'a pehupaa' -ku, pai' Hi'a to mposuro-a."
26359	43	7	30	Nto'u toe, ria-ra to doko' mpohoko' -i, aga uma hema to dungku pale-ra hi Hi'a, apa' ko'ia rata tempo-na.
26360	43	7	31	Wori' hi olo' tau ntodea to mepangala' hi Hi'a, ra'uli': "Magau' Topetolo' mpu'u-i-tawo', baa' wori' -di tanda mekoncehi to nababehi-e."
26361	43	7	32	Ria-ra to Parisi to mpo'epe kamparanusi-ra ntodea mpotompo'wiwi Yesus. Toe pai' to Parisi hante imam pangkeni mpohubui ba hangkuja dua topojaga Tomi Alata'ala hilou mpohoko' -i.
26362	43	7	33	Nto'u toe, Yesus mpololitai ntodea, na'uli' -raka: "Hampai' -a-damo dohe-ni. Nculii' -a mpai' hilou hi Hi'a to mposuro-a.
26363	43	7	34	Nipali' -a mpai', aga uma-apa niruai'. Pai' hi kahilouaa-ku uma-koi bisa hilou."
26364	43	7	35	Ingu' -ramo topoparenta to Yahudi mpo'epe lolita-na, pai' momepekune' -ramo, ra'uli': "Hilou hiapa-ile', pai' na'uli' uma-i mpai' taruai' -e? Meka' ba hilou-i mo'oha' dohe to Yahudi to mposowo' -ra to Yunani, pai' -i mpotudui' -ra to Yunani.
26365	43	7	36	Pai' napa batua lolita-na to mpo'uli', tapali' -i aga uma-i taruai', pai' uma-ta bisa hilou hi kahilouaa-na?"
26366	43	7	37	 Eo ka'omea-na susa' tohe'e, eo to meliu karapomobohe-na. Hi eo toe, mokore-imi Yesus hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, pai' -i mekio': "Hema-koi to ngkamara, tumai-mokoi hi Aku' pai' nginu!
26367	43	7	38	Hewa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli': hema to mepangala' hi Aku', ngkai nono-ra mo'ili wori' ue to tuwu'."
26368	43	7	39	Lolita-na Yesus toe mpowalatu Inoha' Tomoroli', to mehompo mpai' hi tauna to mepangala' hi Hi'a. Nto'u pololita-na Yesus toe, Inoha' Tomoroli' ko'ia mehompo hi topetuku' -na, apa' Yesus ko'ia rapomobohe.
26369	43	7	40	Wori' tauna mpo'epe lolita Yesus toe, pai' ria-ra hantongo' to mpo'uli': "Bate Hi'a-mile nabi to najanci Alata'ala owi-e."
26370	43	7	41	Hantongo' wo'o-ra mpo'uli': "Magau' Topetolo' mpu'u-idi!" Aga ria wo'o-ra to mpo'uli': "Ah, to Galilea-i-hanale! Uma masipato' Magau' Topetolo' mehupa' ngkai Galilea.
26371	43	7	42	Rala Buku Tomoroli' te'uki': Magau' Topetolo' muli Magau' Daud, pai' mehupa' ngkai ngata Betlehem, ngata kaputua Daud."
26372	43	7	43	Alaa-na momehono' lau-ramo ntodea: hantongo' -ra mepangala' hi Yesus, hantongo' uma.
26373	43	7	44	Ria-ra to doko' mpohoko' -i, aga uma hema to dungku pale-ra.
26374	43	7	45	 Topojaga Tomi Alata'ala to rahubui mpohoko' Yesus, nculii' -ramo hilou hi to Parisi pai' imam pangkeni. Uma-ra oko mpohoko' -i. Ra'uli' pangkeni toera: "Napa-di pai' uma-i nihoko' pai' nikeni tumai-e?"
26375	43	7	46	Ratompoi': "Apa' ko'ia ria ki'epei tauna to mololita hewa Hi'a!"
26376	43	7	47	Mehono' to Parisi toera: "Ei' -e! Ha nabagiu wo'o-moko-koiwo koi' -e?
26377	43	7	48	Hilo, uma ria hadua pangkeni ba to Parisi to mepangala' hi Yesus.
26378	43	7	49	Muntu' ntodea to mpangala' -i, apa' uma ra'incai Atura Musa. Harala-rada!"
26379	43	7	50	Ngkai ree, mololita wo'o-mi-hawo hadua to Parisi to rahanga' Nikodemus. Nikodemus toei, ria-imi hangkani mpencuai' Yesus. Na'uli' Nikodemus mpo'uli' -raka doo-na:
26380	43	7	51	"Ntuku' atura-ta-hawo, uma-ta ma'ala mpohuku' tauna ane ko'ia-hawo ra'epe noa' -na pai' raparesa' gau' -na."
26381	43	7	52	Hampetompoi' doo-na: "Ha ngkai Galilea wo'o-ko-kowo iko-e! Wile-dile pai' kamata rala Buku Tomoroli' -e. Uma ria nabi to mehupa' ngkai Galilea."
26382	43	7	53	Oti toe, nculii' -ramo, hore-hore hilou hi tomi-ra.
26383	43	8	1	 Tapi' Yesus hilou hi Bulu' Zaitun.
26384	43	8	2	Kampeneo-na mepupulo ngkii, hilou wo'o-imi hi Tomi Alata'ala. Tumai-ramo ntodea mpomohui' -i, pai' mohura-imi mpotudui' -ra.
26385	43	8	3	Bula-na metudui' toe, rata-ramo guru agama hante to Parisi, mpokeni hadua tobine to rarata bula-na mobualo', rapopokore-i hi laintongo' ntodea.
26386	43	8	4	Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Guru, tobine tetui rarata kongko bula-na mobualo'!
26387	43	8	5	Hi rala Atura Musa, ria parenta to mpo'uli': tobine to mogau' hewa toe kana rapana' watu duu' -na mate. Jadi' Iko, beiwa-kowo pobotuhi-nu?"
26388	43	8	6	Patuju pompekunea' -ra toe, mpali' kedo', bona ma'ala-ra mposalai' Yesus. Tapi' Yesus, uma-i winihi. Motungka' -i-wadi mo'uki' hi tana' hante karawe-na.
26389	43	8	7	Ka'omea-na, apa' rajojo mpekune' -i, mebago' -imi pai' na'uli' -raka: "Hema-koi to uma ria jeko' -ni, hi'a-mi to lomo' -na mpopana' tobine toei!"
26390	43	8	8	Oti toe, motungka' wo'o-imi, pai' -i mo'uki' tena hi tana' hante karawe-na.
26391	43	8	9	Kara'epe-na pangkeni to Yahudi lolita Yesus tohe'e, pengkawusili-rami hadua hadua, ntepu'u ngkai totu'a duu' rata hi to mongura. Ka'omea-na, malai omea-ramo, muntu' Yesus-damo to hi ree hante tobine toei hi laintongo' ntodea.
26392	43	8	10	Ngkai ree, mebago' -imi Yesus pai' mpo'uli' -ki tobine toei: "Hiapa-ramo we'i to mpakilu-koe? Ha uma-rapa ria to doko' mpohuku' -koe?"
26393	43	8	11	Natompoi' tobine toei: "Uma-pi hema, Pue'." Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' wo'o uma mpohuku' -ko. Wae-pi, hilou-moko, pai' nubahakai-mi mpobabehi jeko'."))
26394	43	8	12	 Oti toe, mololita wo'o-imi Yesus hi to Yahudi, na'uli': "Aku' toi-mi baja to mpobajahi nono manusia'. Tauna to mpotuku' -a, uma-ra momako' hi rala kabengia-na. Mporata-ra baja to mpowai' katuwua'."
26395	43	8	13	Ra'uli' to Parisi: "Uma-le makono lolita-nue, apa' mpo'une' woto-nu moto-moko-kona."
26396	43	8	14	Na'uli' Yesus: "Nau' mpotompo'wiwi woto-ku moto-ale, makono oa' lolita-ku, apa' ku'inca kangkaiapa-ku, pai' ku'inca hiapa kahilouaa-ku. Aga koi', uma ni'incai.
26397	43	8	15	Koi' mpohurai kara-kara ntuku' pekiri manusia'. Aku', uma-a mpohurai kara-kara hema-hema.
26398	43	8	16	Ane rapa' -na mpohurai-a kara-kara tauna, pobotuhi-ku bate monoa', apa' uma hadudua-ku. Tuama-ku to mposuro-a, Hi'a-mi doo-ku.
26399	43	8	17	"Hi rala Buku Atura-ni moto te'uki' hewa tohe'i: 'Ane ria nte rodua sabi' to hibalia lolita-ra, posabi' -ra toe ma'ala rapangala'.'
26400	43	8	18	Ria-mi rodua sabi' -ku: Aku' moto-mi hadua, pai' karodua-na Tuama-ku to mposuro-a."
26401	43	8	19	Ra'uli' to Parisi: "Ha hiapa-i tuama-nue?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Apa' uma ni'incai-a, toe pai' uma wo'o ni'incai Tuama-ku. Ane ke ni'inca mpu'u-a, tantu ni'inca wo'o-i Tuama-ku."
26402	43	8	20	Hawe'ea toe na'uli' Yesus bula-na metudui' hi rala Tomi Alata'ala, mohu' peti' pompunaa' doi pepue'. Ko'ia oa' -i rahoko', apa' ko'ia rata tempo-na.
26403	43	8	21	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus hi topoparenta to Yahudi: "Hilou-a mpai', pai' nipali' -a, aga mate-koi mpai' ntali jeko' -ni-pidi. Hi kahilouaa-ku uma-koi bisa hilou."
26404	43	8	22	Mpo'epe toe, momepololitai-ramo topoparenta to Yahudi, ra'uli': "Napa batua-na lolita-na toe-e we'i? Ba doko' mengkahunca' -idi, pai' na'uli' uma-ta bisa hilou hi kahilouaa-nae."
26405	43	8	23	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Koi' -le ngkai kadingkia' -na, Aku' ngkai kalangkoa-na. Koi' ngkai dunia' toi, Aku' uma-a ngkai dunia' toi.
26406	43	8	24	Toe pai' ku'uli' -kokoi, mate-koi mpai' ntali jeko' -ni. Apa' ane uma nipangala' lolita-ku to mpo'uli' kahema-ku, bate mate mpu'u-koi ntali jeko' -ni."
26407	43	8	25	Rapekune' -i: "Ha hema mpu'u-ko-kowo Iko-e?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Napa-pi kalaua-na mpololitai-koi!
26408	43	8	26	Wori' -pidile ke to ku'uli' mposalai' -koie. Tapi' Hi'a to mposuro-a, masipato' lia-i rapangala', pai' napa to ku'epe ngkai Hi'a, toe-mi to kuparata hi koi' to hi dunia'."
26409	43	8	27	To na'uli' Yesus tohe'e, mpotompo'wiwi Tuama-na, tapi' uma ra'incai batua-na.
26410	43	8	28	Toe pai' na'uli' tena-raka: "Ane nipokalangko-apa mpai', Aku' Ana' Manusia', lako' ni'inca-di ka'Aku' -nami. Uma ria hanyalaa to kubabehi ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Muntu' mpo'uli' -a napa to natudui' -ka Tuama-ku.
26411	43	8	29	Hi'a-mi to mposuro-a, pai' nadohei oa' -a. Uma-a napelele' hadudua-ku, apa' kubabehi oa' napa to mpakagoe' nono-na."
26412	43	8	30	Ka'oti-na Yesus mpo'uli' hawe'ea toe, wori' tauna mepangala' hi Hi'a.
26413	43	8	31	 Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka to Yahudi to mepangala' hi Hi'a: "Ane tida-koi mpotuku' tudui' -ku, koi' jadi' topetuku' -ku mpu'u.
26414	43	8	32	Pai' ane topetuku' -ku mpu'u-mokoi, ni'inca mpu'u mpai' tudui' to makono, alaa-na tebahaka-mokoi."
26415	43	8	33	Hampetompoi' -ra: "Kai' toi-le, muli Abraham! Uma-ka-kaina ria rapobatua. Napa-di pai' nu'uli' tebahaka-kai mpai'?"
26416	43	8	34	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: hawe'ea tauna to mpobabehi jeko', napobatua jeko' -ramo.
26417	43	8	35	Ane batua, uma monoa' katida-na hi tomi maradika-na. Aga ane ana' maradika moto-hana, monoa' katida-na hi tomi tuama-na.
26418	43	8	36	Jadi', ane Aku' mpobahaka-koi ngkai jeko' -ni, tebahaka mpu'u-mokoi, apa' Aku' Ana' Alata'ala-a.
26419	43	8	37	Ku'inca moto-le kamuli-na Abraham-koie. Aga ria-koi to doko' mpatehi-a, apa' uma nipoinono lolita-ku.
26420	43	8	38	 Napa to kuhilo hi Tuama-ku, tetu-mi to ku'uli' -kokoi. Hiaa' koi' -koina mpobabehi napa to natudui' -kokoi tuama-ni."
26421	43	8	39	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Tuama-kaile, Abraham!" Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane muli Abraham mpu'u-koi, tantu nituku' po'ingku-na.
26422	43	8	40	Kuparata-kokoi tudui' to makono to kutarima ngkai Alata'ala, hiaa' doko' nipatehi lau-ada! Uma hewa po'ingku-ni tetu po'ingku-na Abraham.
26423	43	8	41	Po'ingku-ni tetu bate mpotuku' po'ingku tuama-ni!" Hampetompoi' to Yahudi: "Aga kai' -le, bela-kai ana' una! Tuama-kai hadua lau-wadi, Hi'a-mi Alata'ala."
26424	43	8	42	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane bongko Alata'ala mpu'u Tuama-ni, ke nipoka'ahi' -a, apa' Aku' ngkai Alata'ala-a, pai' ohe'i-ama naposuro. Uma-a tumai ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Tumai-a ntuku' konoa-na Alata'ala, apa' Hi'a to mposuro-a.
26425	43	8	43	Uma ami' ni'incai batua-na lolita-ku, apa' uma-koi ntaha mpo'epe tudui' -ku.
26426	43	8	44	Magau' Anudaa' -hanale tuama-nie! Pai' doko' oa' -koi mpotuku' konoa tuama-ni tetu. Ngkai lomo' -na, topepatehi ami' -imi. Uma-i ria mpo'uli' napa to makono, apa' uma ria napa-napa to makono hi hi'a. Ane moboa' -i, gati-nami-hana, apa' topoboa' ami' -i, pai' hawe'ea tauna to moboa' mpo'uhi kehi-na.
26427	43	8	45	Jadi', toe pai' uma-a nipangala', apa' mpo'uli' to makono-a-kuna.
26428	43	8	46	 Hema-koi to ma'ala mpotudo' karia jeko' -ku? Ane mpo'uli' -a anu makono, napa-di pai' uma-a nipangala' -e?
26429	43	8	47	Tauna to napo'ana' Alata'ala doko' mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala. Tapi' koi', uma-koi dota mpo'epe lolita-ku, apa' bela-koi ana' Alata'ala."
26430	43	8	48	To Yahudi mporuge' -i Yesus, ra'uli': "To Samaria-ko! Wuli-ko, hewa to ki'uli' ami' -mi!"
26431	43	8	49	Na'uli' Yesus: "Uma-a wuli. Aku' mpobila' Tuama-ku. Hiaa' koi', uma nibila' -a.
26432	43	8	50	Uma-a mpope'une'. Alata'ala-damo to mpobila' -a, pai' Hi'a to mpobotuhi kamakono-ku ba ka'uma-na.
26433	43	8	51	 Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Hema to mpotuku' lolita-ku, uma-ra mate, tuwu' -ra duu' kahae-hae-na."
26434	43	8	52	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Wae lau ki'inca mpu'u-mi kawuli-nu! Bangku' Abraham-hawoe', mate moto-i. Wae wo'o hawe'ea nabi owi, mate moto-ra. Hiaa' nu'uli' -kona, hema to mpotuku' lolita-nu uma-ra mate.
26435	43	8	53	Ha nu'uli' -kona meliu tuwu' -nu ngkai ntu'a-ta Abraham, to mahae-imi mate? Ha meliu tuwu' -nu ngkai hawe'ea nabi to mate-ramo? Nu'uli' hema rahi-dakoe?"
26436	43	8	54	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane rapa' -na mpakalangko woto-ku moto-a, uma ntoto ria kalaua-na. Tapi' Tuama-kumi to mpakalangko-a. Ni'uli' -koina Kahi'a-na Alata'ala to nipue'.
26437	43	8	55	Tapi' kakoo-kono-na uma-i ni'incai. Ane Aku', ku'inca-i. Ane rapa' -na ku'uli' uma-i ku'incai, boa' -ama hewa koi'. Apa' ku'inca mpu'u-i, pai' kutuku' lolita-na.
26438	43	8	56	Ane ntu'a-ni Abraham, goe' -i apa' na'inca kanahilo-na mpai' eo karataa-ku. Jadi' hewa toe lau, nahilo-mi karataa-ku pai' goe' lia-imi."
26439	43	8	57	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Umuru-nule, ko'ia hono' lima mpulu' mpae. Ha pasi' nuhilo-imi-kona Abraham-e?"
26440	43	8	58	Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Kako'ia-na putu Abraham, Aku' toi, mpolia' ria-ama!"
26441	43	8	59	Kara'epe-na to Yahudi toe we'i, ntima' watu-ramo doko' rawatuhi-ki bona mate-imi. Ntaa' we'i, mengkawusili-imi Yesus ngkai Tomi Alata'ala.
26442	43	9	1	 Bula-na Yesus momako', mpohilo-i hadua tauna to wero ngkai lomo' kaputu-na.
26443	43	9	2	Ana'guru-na mpekune' -i: "Guru, napa pai' wero ami' -i ngkai kaputu-nae? Ba jeko' -na moto-di, ba jeko' totu'a-nadi?"
26444	43	9	3	Na'uli' Yesus: "Bela jeko' -na moto, pai' bela wo'o jeko' totu'a-na. Toi jadi' bona tauna mpohilo baraka' Alata'ala to madupa' hi woto-na.
26445	43	9	4	Bula-na mobaja-pidi, kana tapobago bago-na Alata'ala to mposuro-a. Apa' neo' rata-mi bengi-na, pai' uma-pi hema to mobago.
26446	43	9	5	Bula-ku hi dunia' -pidi, Aku' toi-mi baja to mpobajahi nono manusia'."
26447	43	9	6	Ka'oti-na mololita hewa toe, na'uelikui-mi tana', nagalo hante tana' hangkedi' bona morege', nagelai' -ki mata-na towero toei,
26448	43	9	7	pai' na'uli' -ki: "Hilou-ko monoku hi wuhu' Siloam." (Hanga' "Siloam" toe, batua-na "Rasuro.") Kahilou-nami monoku. Ponculii' -na, pehilo-imi-hawo.
26449	43	9	8	 Ngkai ree, tongki-na pai' tauna to biasa mpohilo-i kakarapi' -rapi', momepekune' -ramo ra'uli': "Hema-idi toe-e mai? Ha bela hi'a-mi towero to biasa mohura kakarapi' -rapi' -e?"
26450	43	9	9	Ria to mpo'uli': "Hi'a-midi!" Aga ria wo'o mpo'uli': "Bela-e'. Kahibalia lence-ra-wadi-hawo." Hiaa' hi'a moto-mi-hawo mpo'uli': "Aku' -midi!"
26451	43	9	10	Jadi', rapekune' -i: "Ha beiwa pai' alaa-na pehilo-ko?"
26452	43	9	11	Na'uli' -raka: "Tauna to rahanga' Yesus mpobabehi rege', nagelai' -ki mata-ku, na'uli' -ka: 'Hilou-ko monoku hi wuhu' Siloam.' Hilou mpu'u-ama monoku, ngkai ree pehilo-ama-kuwo!"
26453	43	9	12	Rapekune' -i: "Hiaa' hiapa-imi we'i?" Na'uli' -raka: "Uma-kuwo ku'incai."
26454	43	9	13	
26455	43	9	14	Yesus mpogalo ueliku-na hante tana' pai' mpaka'uri' towero toe we'i nto'u Eo Sabat, eo pepuea' -ra to Yahudi. Jadi', towero to pehilo-mi toei rakeni hilou hi to Parisi.
26456	43	9	15	To Parisi wo'o-mi-rawo mpekune' -i, ra'uli': "Beiwa pai' alaa-na pehilo-koe?" Na'uli' -raka: "Nagelai' mata-ku hante rege', pai' kamonoku-ku, pehilo-ama."
26457	43	9	16	Ba hangkuja dua ngkai to Parisi toera mpo'uli': "Tauna to mpobabehi tetu, uma-i ngkai Alata'ala, bo uma-i mpotuku' palia-ta hi Eo Sabat." Tapi' to hantongo' mpo'uli': "Hiaa' ane topojeko' -i, ngkaiapa-di baraka' -na mpobabehi wori' tanda mekoncehi hewa tohe'i-e?" Alaa-na, ria lau-mi pomehonoa' hi himpau hira'.
26458	43	9	17	Ngkai ree, mepekune' tena-ra to Parisi hi towero toei, ra'uli': "Beiwa-kowo iko, napa to nu'uli', apa' napaka'uri' -koko mata-nue." Na'uli' towero toei: "Tantu Hi'a hadua nabi."
26459	43	9	18	Tapi' topoparenta to Yahudi, uma-ra mparasaya kahi'a-na mpu'u-mi towero-e ngone, pai' muu-mule' pehilo-imi. Toe pai' rakio' tina pai' tuama-na bona mpohirua' -raka,
26460	43	9	19	pai' rapompekunei': "Ha makono mpu'u tauna toii ana' -ni, to ni'uli' wero ngkai lomo' kaputu-nae? Hiaa' beiwa pai' alaa-na pehilo-i?"
26461	43	9	20	Ra'uli' -rawo tina pai' tuama-na: "To ki'inca-le, bate ana' -kai mpu'u-i-hawo, pai' wero mpu'u-i ngkai lomo' kaputu-na.
26462	43	9	21	Aga beiwa pai' alaa-na pehilo-i, uma-kaiwo ki'incai. Pai' hema to mpaka'uri' -i, uma wo'o-kaiwo ki'incai. Kama-imi-hawo, pekune' -ki hi'a moto-mi-koiwo. Ma'ala-imi metompoi' moto."
26463	43	9	22	Tina pai' tuama-na mpo'uli' hewa toe, apa' me'eka' -ra hi topoparenta to Yahudi. Apa' hibalia-mi pohawa' -ra: hema-hema to mpo'uli' Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo' rapopalai ngkai tomi posampayaa.
26464	43	9	23	Toe pai' totu'a-na mpo'uli': "Kama-imi-hawo, pekune' -ki hi'a moto-mi-koiwo."
26465	43	9	24	Oti toe, rakio' tena-i tauna to wero toei we'i, pai' ra'uli' -ki: "Alata'ala mpotiroi-ta! Jadi', uli' mpu'u-e' napa to makono! Ki'inca moto-i Yesus tetui tauna topojeko'."
26466	43	9	25	Na'uli' -raka: "Aku' -le, uma ku'incai ba topojeko' -i ba uma. Sampale to ku'inca, wero-a wengi, tempo toi pehilo-ama."
26467	43	9	26	Ngkai ree, rapekune' tena-i: "Napa to nababehi-koko? Beiwa-i mpaka'uri' -ko?"
26468	43	9	27	Natompoi' -ra: "Oti-mi kututura-kokoi we'i, ha uma ni'epei? Napa pai' nipengeei oa' -e? Ba doko' jadi' ana'guru-na lau-dakoie?"
26469	43	9	28	Ngkai ree, ralibui' -imi pai' ra'uli' -ki: "Iko-le ana'guru-na tau tetu-e! Kai' ana'guru-na nabi Musa-ka-kaina!
26470	43	9	29	Monoa' ki'inca Alata'ala mpoparata lolita-na hi Musa owi. Tapi' Yesus tetui, uma ki'incai kangkaiapa-na."
26471	43	9	30	Mehono' -i towero toei: "Me'ingui' lia-koi! Ni'uli' uma ni'incai kangkaiapa-na, hiaa' napaka'uri' mata-ku!
26472	43	9	31	Ta'inca moto Alata'ala uma mpotompoi' pomperapia' tauna topojeko'. Sampale-di mpobini' -i tilinga-na hi hema-hema to mengkoru hi Hi'a pai' to mpotuku' hawa' -na.
26473	43	9	32	Ngkai lomo' kajadi' dunia', ko'ia ria ta'epei tutura-na tauna towero ngkai lomo' kaputu-na ma'ala rapaka'uri'.
26474	43	9	33	Ane Yesus uma-i ngkai Alata'ala, tantu uma-i bisa mpobabehi napa-napa."
26475	43	9	34	Hampetompoi' -ra: "Iko tetu to ponu' jeko' ngkai kaputu-nu, nta'ena' metudui'!" Ngkai ree, rapopalai-imi ngkai tomi posampayaa.
26476	43	9	35	 Yesus mpo'epe karapopalai-na ngkai tomi posampayaa. Jadi' hilou-imi mpohirua' -ki, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ha mepangala' -ko hi Ana' Manusia' -e?"
26477	43	9	36	Na'uli' tauna toei: "Uli' -ka-kuwo kahema-nai, bona kupangala' -i."
26478	43	9	37	Na'uli' Yesus: "Nuhilo-imile! Hi'a-mile to mpololitai-koe."
26479	43	9	38	Na'uli' tauna toei: "Kupangala', Pue'!" pai' mowilingkudu-imi mponyompa-i.
26480	43	9	39	 Na'uli' Yesus: "Katumai-ku hi dunia' toi, tumai mpobotuhi kara-kara manusia', bona tauna to wero ma'ala pehilo, pai' tauna to mpo'uli' pehilo moto-ra, wero lau-ra."
26481	43	9	40	Ba hangkuja dua to Parisi to hi ree mpo'epe lolita-na Yesus. Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Ha nu'uli' -kona wero wo'o-kai kai' -e?"
26482	43	9	41	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane rapa' -na hewa towero mpu'u-koi apa' uma ni'incai napa to makono, ke uma-koi masala'. Tapi', apa' ni'uli' -koina pehilo moto-koie, bate masala' -koi-hawo."
26483	43	10	1	 Na'uli' Yesus: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: ane ria tauna to mesua' hi rala gimpu ngkahe' wala, pai' uma-i ntara hi wobo', topanako pai' toperampaki-i-hana.
26484	43	10	2	Ane topo'ewu, mesua' ntara hi wobo' moto-i.
26485	43	10	3	Topodongo wobo' mpobea-ki wobo', pai' bima-na mpetonoi libu' -na ane nakio' hanga' -ra butu-butu ma'a-na, pai' nakeni-ra hilou hi mali-na.
26486	43	10	4	Kanakeni-ra hilou hi mali-na omea, mako' meri'ulu-i ngkai bima-na, pai' bima-na mpotuku' -i, apa' ra'inca mpetonoi libu' -na.
26487	43	10	5	Uma-ra mpotuku' tau ntani' -na. Ane ria tauna to bela topo'ewu-ra to mpokio' -ra, rapetiboi' -i, apa' uma ra'incai mpetonoi libu' -na."
26488	43	10	6	Yesus mpo'uli' walatu toe hi to Parisi, aga uma ra'incai patuju-na.
26489	43	10	7	Toe pai' na'uli' wo'o-mi: "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Aku' toi-mi wobo' to natara bima mesua' hi rala gimpu.
26490	43	10	8	Hawe'ea tauna to rata meri'ulu ngkai Aku', topanako pai' toperampaki-ra-hana. Aga bima-ku uma mposaile' pekio' -ra.
26491	43	10	9	Aku' toi-mi wobo'. Hema to mesua' ntara hi Aku', mporata-ra kalompea'. Hira' hewa bima to mesua' hi rala gimpu pai' mehupa' hilou hi mali-na mporata kowo' to morudu'.
26492	43	10	10	Patuju-na topanako-le, tumai doko' manako, mepatehi pai' megerohi. Tapi' Aku' tumai bona manusia' mporata katuwua' to uma mowo kalompe' -na.
26493	43	10	11	"Aku' toi-mi topo'ewu to lompe'. Kupewai' tuwu' -ku bona bima-ku tuwu'.
26494	43	10	12	Ane tauna to baha ragaji', uma lompe' pompo'ewu-na, apa' bela hi'a pue' bima. Ane mpohilo-i serigala tumai, metibo' -i mpalahii bima ewua-na. Jadi' bima toe nadapa' pai' nahungongo' serigala, alaa-na pagaa' -gaa' -ramo.
26495	43	10	13	Tauna to ragaji' toei metibo', apa' mobago baha ragaji' -wadi. Uma-i mposaile' ewua-na.
26496	43	10	14	
26497	43	10	15	"Aku' toi-mi topo'ewu to lompe'. Hewa Tuama-ku mpo'inca-a, pai' Aku' mpo'inca Tuama-ku, wae wo'o Aku' mpo'inca bima-ku, pai' bima-ku mpo'inca-a. Kupewai' tuwu' -ku bona bima-ku tuwu'.
26498	43	10	16	"Ria wo'o-pidi bima-ku to ntani' -na, to uma hi rala gimpu toi. Hira' wo'o mpai' kana kukeni tumai. Rapetonoi mpai' libu' -ku, bona hawe'ea bima-ku jadi' mopahantuda lau, pai' hadua-ku-wadi to mpo'ewu-ra omea.
26499	43	10	17	"Tuama-ku mpoka'ahi' -a, apa' kupewai' tuwu' -ku bona kurua' nculii' tuwu' -ku.
26500	43	10	18	Uma ria haduaa to mpatehi-a ane uma konoa-ku. Ku'agi mate hante karoli' -roli' nono-ku. Ria kuasa-ku mpewai' tuwu' -ku bona rapatehi, pai' ria wo'o kuasa-ku tuwu' nculii'. Toe-mi hawa' to kutarima ngkai Tuama-ku."
26501	43	10	19	 Kara'epe-na to Yahudi pololita-na Yesus toe, momehono' wo'o-ramo.
26502	43	10	20	Wori' -ra to mpo'uli': "Kahawia' -ile! Wuli-i! Napa-pi kalaua-na tape'epei lolita-na."
26503	43	10	21	Aga ria wo'o to mpo'uli': "Uma-di! Tauna to napesuai' seta-le uma-hawo mololita hewa toei. Ha bisa wo'o-hawo seta mpaka'uri' tauna to wero-e?"
26504	43	10	22	 Hi Yerusalem nto'u toe, tauna mpobabehi karamea mpokiwoi eo bohe pompowatia' Tomi Alata'ala owi. Nto'u toe, tempo lengi'.
26505	43	10	23	Yesus momako' hi berewe Tomi Alata'ala, hi pengkawinaraa to rahanga' Pengkawinaraa Salomo.
26506	43	10	24	Topoparenta to Yahudi mpotipuhi Yesus pai' ra'uli' -ki: "Napa pai' nupelele' oa' -kai ingu', uma oa' nupakalonto' kahema-nue? Ane bongko Magau' Topetolo' mpu'u-kole, uli' pakalonto' lau-mi."
26507	43	10	25	Na'uli' Yesus: "Oti-mi ku'uli' -kokoie, aga uma-koi dota mpangala'. Anu mekoncehi to kubabehi hante kuasa Tuama-ku, toe-mi to mpakanoto kahema-ku.
26508	43	10	26	Tapi' uma oa' nipangala', apa' bela-koi bima-ku.
26509	43	10	27	Bima-ku mpetonoi libu' -ku. Ku'inca moto-ra, pai' -ra mpotuku' -a.
26510	43	10	28	Kuwai' -ra katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na, pai' monoa' -mi ka'uma-ra mpai' rahuku' hi naraka. Uma ria haduaa to ma'ala mpo'agoi-a bima-ku.
26511	43	10	29	Tuama-ku meliu kabaraka' -na ngkai hawe'ea, pai' Hi'a-mi to mpowai' -a bima-ku. Uma ria haduaa to ma'ala mpo'ago-ra ngkai Tuama-ku.
26512	43	10	30	Aku' pai' Tuama-ku, hadua lau-wada-kai."
26513	43	10	31	Ngkai ree, to Yahudi mpotima' watu doko' rapana' -ki Yesus bona mate-i.
26514	43	10	32	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Nihilo moto-a mpobabehi bago to lompe' ntuku' hawa' Tuama-ku. Ngkai bago-ku tohe'e, to'uma to masipato' nipatehi-ka?"
26515	43	10	33	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Bela ngkai pobago-nu to lompe', pai' doko' kipatehi-ko. Pai' doko' kipatehi-kole apa' mpokedi' Alata'ala-ko-kona! Api' manusia' biasa-wadi-ko, nu'uli' -kona Alata'ala-ko!"
26516	43	10	34	Na'uli' Yesus: "Hi rala Buku Atura-ni ria te'uki' Lolita Alata'ala hi pangkeni to Yahudi owi, hewa toi moni-na: 'Koi', raponcawa Alata'ala-koi.'
26517	43	10	35	Napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' tetu, uma ria balia' -na. Jadi', ane Buku Tomoroli' mpo'uli' 'Alata'ala-koi' hi tauna to mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala owi, peliu-liu-nami Aku'.
26518	43	10	36	Apa' Aku' toi-e, to nawati' Tuama-ku, napowiwi napowiti' tumai hi dunia'. Jadi', napa pai' ni'uli' -ka mpokedi' -a Alata'ala apa' ku'uli' ka'Aku' -na Ana' -na?
26519	43	10	37	"Ane rapa' -na uma kubabehi bago to ngkai Tuama-ku, neo' -a nipangala'.
26520	43	10	38	Tapi' ane kubabehi moto-mi bago to ngkai Tuama-kue, kana nipangala' -a sabana pobago-ku toe. Nau' Aku' moto uma nipangalai', kana nipangala' kangkai Alata'ala-na pobago-ku. Ane mepangala' -koi hi pobago-ku toe, ni'inca mpai' pai' monoto mpu'u hi nono-ni kahintuwu' -ku hante Tuama-ku, pai' Tuama-ku hintuwu' hante Aku'."
26521	43	10	39	 Mpo'epe toe-di, to Yahudi doko' wo'o-ramo mpohoko' -i, aga tepetibo' moto-i.
26522	43	10	40	Ngkai ree, malai wo'o-imi Yesus hilou hi dipo ue Yordan, hi peniua' -na Yohanes ri'ulu, pai' -i mo'oha' hi ria.
26523	43	10	41	Wori' tauna hilou mpohirua' -ki, ra'uli': "Yohanes uma mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi. Aga hawe'ea to na'uli' mpotompo'wiwi Yesus, makono omea."
26524	43	10	42	Toe pai' wori' tauna hi ree mepangala' hi Yesus.
26525	43	11	1	
26526	43	11	2	Hadua tomane to rahanga' Lazarus mo'oha' hi ngata Betania hante ompi' bine-na Maria pai' Marta. (Maria toe-mi mpai' to mpolanai witi' Yesus hante lana honga pai' naporihi hante wuluwoo' -na.) Hangkani, peda' -i Lazarus.
26527	43	11	3	Ompi' bine-na to rodua toera mposuro tauna hilou hi Yesus, mpo'uli' -ki: "Pue', bale-nu to nupe'ahi', peda' -i."
26528	43	11	4	Kana'epe-na Yesus kareba toe, na'uli': "Haki' -na tetu-e ria, uma napomate-ki. Toe jadi' bona Alata'ala rapomobohe, pai' bona Aku' wo'o, Ana' -na, rapomobohe."
26529	43	11	5	Yesus mpoka'ahi' Marta, Maria, pai' Lazarus.
26530	43	11	6	Aga kana'epe-na kapeda' -na Lazarus, uma-i ulu hilou, bate hi po'ohaa' -na moto-i ro'eo-pi kahae-na.
26531	43	11	7	Timpaliu ro'eo toe-di, pai' lako' na'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Kita-mi hilou nculii' hi tana' Yudea."
26532	43	11	8	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Guru, ko'ia mahae to Yahudi hi ria doko' mpopatehi-ko. Napa wo'o-mi pai' doko' hilou hi ria-koe?"
26533	43	11	9	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ha uma hampulu' rojaa to mobaja rala-na ha'eo? Tauna to momako' hi eo-na, uma-ra tewinci', apa' mpohilo-ra pehini eo to mpobajahi dunia' toi.
26534	43	11	10	Aga tauna to momako' hi bengi-na, bate tewinci' -ra, apa' uma ria to mpobajahi-ra."
26535	43	11	11	Hewa toe-mi lolita Yesus, pai' oti toe na'uli' tena: "Bale-ta Lazarus, leta' -i. Hilou-a mpolike-i."
26536	43	11	12	
26537	43	11	13	Kakoo-kono-na, lolita-na Yesus toe mpowalatu kamate-na Lazarus. Tapi' ana'guru-na uma mpopaha walatu toe, ra'uli' leta' mpu'u-i Lazarus. Toe pai' ra'uli' -ki Yesus: "Pue', ane leta' -i, mo'uri' moto-i mpai'."
26538	43	11	14	Jadi', nalohu lau-miraka batua walatu-na, na'uli': "Mate-imi Lazarus.
26539	43	11	15	Pai' goe' -a apa' uma kukaralai nto'u toe. Apa' napa to jadi' toe mpai' ria, mpokeni kalompea' hi koi', bona mepangala' -koi hi Aku'. Hilou-tamo hi Lazarus."
26540	43	11	16	Tomas, to ra'atu Ntomoropa', mpo'uli' -raka hingka ana'guru-na: "Kita-mi hilou mpotuku' -i, bona mate-ta hangkaa-ngkania hante Hi'a." Jadi' hilou mpu'u-ramo hi tana' Yudea.
26541	43	11	17	 Karata-ra hi ngata Betania, mpolia' opo' mengi-imi Lazarus ratana.
26542	43	11	18	Betania tohe'e mohu' Yerusalem, kira-kira tolu kilo kalaa-na.
26543	43	11	19	Jadi', wori' -ra to Yahudi to tumai mpotanta'u Marta pai' Maria hi kamate ompi' -ra toe.
26544	43	11	20	Marta mpo'epe kaneo' -na rata-mi Yesus, kahilou-nami mpotomu-i. Tapi' Maria, hi tomi moto-i-hana.
26545	43	11	21	Na'uli' Marta hi Yesus: "Pue', ane ke hi rehe'i-ko wengi, ke uma-i mate ompi' -ku.
26546	43	11	22	Aga nau' wae, ku'inca moto: napa-napa to nuperapi' hi Alata'ala tempo toi, bate nawai' -ko."
26547	43	11	23	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Memata moto-ile mpai' ompi' -nue."
26548	43	11	24	Na'uli' Marta: "Io', to ku'inca-le, memata moto mpu'u-i mpai' hi Eo Kiama, nto'u hawe'ea tomate rapopemata."
26549	43	11	25	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' toi-mi to mpopemata tomate, pai' to mpowai' katuwua'. Tauna to mepangala' hi Aku', nau' mate-ra, tuwu' moto-ra mpai'.
26550	43	11	26	Pai' hawe'ea tauna to tuwu' pai' mepangala' hi Aku', bate uma-ra mate, duu' kahae-hae-na. Ha nupangala' to ku'uli' toe-e?"
26551	43	11	27	Na'uli' Marta: "Io' Pue', kupangala' ka'Iko-na Ana' Alata'ala, Magau' Topetolo' to najanci Alata'ala owi to tumai hi dunia'."
26552	43	11	28	Ka'oti-na Marta mpo'uli' toe, hilou-imi hi tomi mpokio' Maria, pai' mpowara' -i na'uli' -ki: "Oe-imi ria Guru, doko' napohirua' -koko!"
26553	43	11	29	Mpo'epe tohe'e, napesahui Maria hilou mpohirua' -ki Yesus.
26554	43	11	30	Nto'u toe, Yesus ko'ia mesua' hi rala ngata, hi mali ngata-i-pidi, hi kahiruaa' -na hante Marta we'i.
26555	43	11	31	To Yahudi to mpodoo eo mpohilo kasosa-na Maria malai ngkai tomi. Ra'uli': "Hilou hi daeo' -i tu, hilou motantangi' hi ria!" Jadi', hilou wo'o-ra-rawo mpotuku' -i.
26556	43	11	32	Karata Maria hi pento'oa-na Yesus we'i, pai' kampohilo-na Yesus, powingkotu' -nami hi nyanyoa-na, pai' na'uli' -ki: "Pue', ane ke hi rehe'i-ko, ke uma-i mate ompi' -ku."
26557	43	11	33	 Kanahilo-na Yesus Maria motantangi' hante tauna to dohe-na, susa' pai' tuna-mi nono-na.
26558	43	11	34	Napekune' -ra: "Ratana hiapa-i?" Ra'uli': "Mai-moko Pue', kipo'ema' -ko hilou bona nuhilo."
26559	43	11	35	Mo'ili-mi ue mata-na Yesus.
26560	43	11	36	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Hilo! Uma mpu'u mowo kama'ahi' -na hi Lazarus!"
26561	43	11	37	Aga ria wo'o-ra to mpo'uli': "Tauna towero napaka'uri'. Ha uma-i bisa mpaka'uri' Lazarus bona ke uma-i-hawo mate-e?"
26562	43	11	38	Ngkai ree, peda' wo'o-mi nono-na Yesus, pai' -i hilou hi daeo'. Daeo' toe, wulou' to ratowi hi panapa bulu', pai' ra'unca hante watu to bohe.
26563	43	11	39	Na'uli' Yesus: "Deru' watu tetu!" Na'uli' Marta, ompi' -na tomate: "Neo' -pi rabea, Pue'. Mohoa-imi, apa' opo' mengi-imi ratana."
26564	43	11	40	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Marta: "Ha uma ku'uli' -mikoko we'i, ane mepangala' -ko, nuhilo moto mpai' kabohe baraka' -na Alata'ala."
26565	43	11	41	Oti toe, raderu' mpu'u-mi watu po'unca daeo'. Yesus ngkongoa' hi langi', na'uli': "Tuama-ku, mpo'uli' -a tarima kasi, apa' nu'epe pomperapia' -ku tohe'i.
26566	43	11	42	Ku'inca, bate nu'epe oa' lolita-ku. Aga tohe'i kupesukui mpo'uli', bona ra'epe tauna to wori' to hi rehe'i lau, bona rapangala' ka'Iko-na mpu'u to mposuro-a."
26567	43	11	43	Oti toe, napesukui mekio': "Lazarus! Tumai-moko!"
26568	43	11	44	Mehupa' -imi tauna to mate toei ngkai rala daeo' -na. Pale-na pai' witi' -na teputu' -pidi hante hompu' -na, pai' woo' -na tehoo' hante lenco. Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Bongka pomputu' -na bona lompe' pomako' -na."
26569	43	11	45	 Wori' to Yahudi to mpokinomo Maria nto'u toe, pai' rahilo napa to nababehi Yesus. Pai' wori' -ramo to mepangala' hi Hi'a.
26570	43	11	46	Aga ria wo'o-ra hantongo' hilou hi to Parisi mpoparata napa to nababehi Yesus toe.
26571	43	11	47	Toe pai' to Parisi hante imam pangkeni mpobabehi porumpua bohe hante topohura agama to ntani' -na. Ra'uli': "Napa-koiwo to kana tababehi? Apa' wori' mpu'u tanda mekoncehi to nababehi-e.
26572	43	11	48	Ane tapelele' oa' -i, hawe'ea tauna mpai' mepangala' hi Hi'a omea-ramo. Ka'omea-na mpai', tantara to Roma tumai mpogero ngata-ta hante Tomi Alata'ala."
26573	43	11	49	Ngkai ree, hadua ngkai laintongo' -ra to rahanga' Kayafas, Imam Bohe hi mpae toe, mpo'uli': "Uma ni'incai napa-napa!
26574	43	11	50	Uma ni'incai kalompea' ntodea. Agina lau-pi tau hadua mate mposampei ntodea, bona neo' mpai' ragero ngata-ta omea."
26575	43	11	51	Patuju-na Kayafas mpo'uli' hewa toe: Yesus kana rapatehi. Tapi' ria wo'o batua to kahanyala-na, to uma-hawo natungkai'. Apa' lawi' hi'a-mi Imam Bohe hi mpae toe-e, lolita-na mpolowa kamate-na mpai' Yesus mpotolo' to Yahudi.
26576	43	11	52	Pai' uma muntu' to Yahudi-wadi. Ngkai kamate-na Yesus toe mpai', hawe'ea ana' Alata'ala to pahawu' -hawu' hi humalili' dunia' rarumpu pai' rapahantuda lau.
26577	43	11	53	Ntepu'u eo toe, hahawa' lau-ramo topoparenta to Yahudi mpopatehi Yesus.
26578	43	11	54	Jadi', toe pai' uma-ipi modao' hi rala tana' -ra to Yahudi, bona neo' -ipi rahiloi ntodea. Malai-imi ngkai ree hilou hi ngata to rahanga' Efraim hi wiwi' papada to wao', pai' mo'oha' hi ree-imi hante ana'guru-na.
26579	43	11	55	Nto'u toe, neo' rata-mi eo bohe agama Yahudi to rahanga' Eo Paskah. Kako'ia rata eo bohe toe, wori' tauna ngkai ngata ntani' -na hilou hi Yerusalem, bona mpobohoi' woto-ra ntuku' ada agama-ra.
26580	43	11	56	Tauna to morumpu hi Yerusalem toe ntora mpopali' Yesus. Bula-ra moromu hi Tomi Alata'ala, momepololitai-ramo, ra'uli': "Beiwa-koiwo pomporataa-ni? Meka' uma-i mpai' tumai mpokaralai posusa'?"
26581	43	11	57	Ane imam pangkeni pai' to Parisi, ria ami' parenta-ra hi ntodea to mpo'uli': "Hema-hema-koi to mpo'inca kahiapa-na Yesus, ncaliu ni'uli' -kakai, bona rahoko' -i."
26582	43	12	1	 Ono eo kako'ia-na Eo Paskah, hilou-imi Yesus hi Betania, ngata katidaa-na Lazarus, to napotuwu' nculii' -e wengi.
26583	43	12	2	Mpobabehi-ra karamea, apa' goe' -ra mpotarima Yesus hi ngata-ra. Marta moruhe, Lazarus mpohimpohura-ki Yesus pai' torata ntani' -na.
26584	43	12	3	Bula-ra ngkoni', tumai-i Maria ngkeni hantanga' lite lana honga. Lana toe rababehi ngkai rali' kaju to mohonga, masuli' lia oli-na. Natua lana toe hi witi' -na Yesus pai' naporihi hante wuluwoo' -na. Mohonga-damo hobo' hi rala tomi.
26585	43	12	4	Hadua ana'guru-na Yesus to rahanga' Yudas Iskariot-- to mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -nae mpai'-- mpo'uli':
26586	43	12	5	"Masuli' lia oli-na lana tetu, nte tolu atu doi pera'. Napa-di-hana pai' uma rapobalu' lau, pai' doi-na rawai' -raka tokabu!"
26587	43	12	6	Kakoo-kono-na, Yudas uma kamposaile' -na mpu'u tokabu. Api' katomanako-nadi! Apa' hi'a to ntimamahi doi-ra, pai' pontu-na na'ala' bongo.
26588	43	12	7	Na'uli' Yesus: "Pelele' moto-i-hawo! Napa to nababehi toi, mpenonoi eo karatana-ku mpai'.
26589	43	12	8	Ane tokabu, ria-pidi loga-ni mpotulungi-ra. Tapi' Aku', neo' uma-pi ria loga-ni mpotulungi-a, apa' uma-apa mahae dohe-ni."
26590	43	12	9	Wori' to Yahudi mpo'epe karia-na Yesus hi Betania, toe pai' mo'iko-ra hilou doko' mpohilo-i. Pai' doko' wo'o-ra mpohilo Lazarus, to napotuwu' nculii' Yesus-e wengi.
26591	43	12	10	Jadi', mohawa' wo'o-ramo imam pangkeni doko' mpopatehi Lazarus.
26592	43	12	11	Apa' ngkai hi'a pai' alaa-na wori' to Yahudi mpalahii-ra pai' mepangala' hi Yesus.
26593	43	12	12	 Kamepulo-na, wori' tauna hi Yerusalem mpo'epe kahilou-na Yesus mpotoa' ngata-ra. Nto'u toe, wori' lia tauna morumpu hi Yerusalem apa' neo' rata-mi Eo Paskah.
26594	43	12	13	Mpo'ala' -ra palampa, pai' hilou-ra mpotomu-i. Ntora mekio' -ra: Une' -imi Pue' Ala!" Pue' mpogane' Magau' to tumai mpokeni hanga' -na!" Pue' mpogane' Magau' to Israel!"
26595	43	12	14	Yesus mpo'ala' hama'a keledai to mongura, pai' nahawi'. Pehawi' -na tohe'e mpopadupa' lolita nabi owi to mpo'uli':
26596	43	12	15	"Neo' -koi me'eka', pue' ngata Sion. Hilo! Etu-i tumai Magau' -ni. Mpohawi' -i hama'a ana' keledai."
26597	43	12	16	Nto'u toe, ko'ia rapaha ana'guru-na napa batua-na to jadi' toe. Aga ka'oti-na Yesus rapatehi pai' rapomobohe, rakiwoi-mi napa to jadi' hi Yesus toe, hewa to telowa ami' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'.
26598	43	12	17	Hi Yerusalem nto'u toe, ria wo'o wori' tauna to dohe Yesus wengi nto'u kanakio' -na Lazarus ngkai rala daeo' pai' mpotuwu' -i nculii'. Tauna toera ntora mpojarita kajadia' toe.
26599	43	12	18	Ngkai toe-mi pai' alaa-na wori' rahi tauna hilou mpotomu-i Yesus, apa' ra'epe Kahi'a-na to mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi toe.
26600	43	12	19	Momepololitai-ramo to Parisi, ra'uli': "Madagi-tamo toi-e! Hilo-dile, hawe'ea tauna hi dunia' mpotuku' -i."
26601	43	12	20	 Ngkai kawori' tauna to hilou hi Yerusalem mepue' nto'u Eo Paskah toe, ria wo'o ba hangkuja dua to Yunani.
26602	43	12	21	To Yunani toera hilou hi Filipus, ra'uli' -ki: "Doko' -ka-kaiwo mpohirua' -ki Yesus." (Filipus tohe'e ngkai ngata Betsaida hi tana' Galilea.)
26603	43	12	22	Filipus hilou mpo'uli' -ki Andreas, pai' hira' roduaa hilou mparata-ki Yesus.
26604	43	12	23	Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Rata-mi tempo-na, Aku' Ana' Manusia' rapomobohe.
26605	43	12	24	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Aku' ma'ala rarapai' -ki pae. Ane pae toe uma ratuja' hi tana' pai' ra'urihi hewa tomate, bate-na oa' -i. Tapi' ane ratuja' -i-damo, wori' -mi mpai' wua' -na.
26606	43	12	25	Tauna to mpentaei konoa-na moto, moronto-ki mpai' katuwu' -na hi eo mpeno-na. Aga tauna to mpobahaka konoa-na hi dunia' toi, mporata-i mpai' katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26607	43	12	26	Hema-koi to doko' jadi' topobago-ku, kana mpotuku' -a, bona hiapa kahiloua-ku, retu wo'o-koi. Tuama-ku mpai' mpobila' -koi to jadi' topobago-ku.
26608	43	12	27	 "Susa' nono-ku toi-e. Uma ku'incai napa to kana ku'uli'. Ria hi rala nono-ku doko' mekakae: 'Mama, bahaka-a-kuwo ngkai kaparia to neo' mporumpa' -a toi-e!' Aga bo toe-mi pai' tumai-a hi rala dunia', bona mpotodohaka kaparia toe.
26609	43	12	28	Ku'uli' hewa toi: Mama, pomobohe-mi hanga' -nu!" Ngkai ree, ria to mololita ngkai langi' mpo'uli' -ki Yesus: "Oti-mile kupomobohe hanga' -kue, pai' kupomobohe tena-pi mpai'."
26610	43	12	29	Ntodea to mpo'epe lolita ngkai langi' toe, mpo'uli': "Toe lou moni kuna!" Aga hantongo' mpo'uli': "Bela-hawo kuna. Ria-hana mala'eka mpololitai-i."
26611	43	12	30	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Lolita to ni'epe toe we'i, rapohowa' uma bona mpotulungi Aku'. Rapohowa' bona mpotulungi koi' -hana.
26612	43	12	31	Rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala kana mpohurai hawe'ea kasalaa' manusia' hi dunia'. Pai' rata wo'o tempo-na Magau' Anudaa' to mpokuasai dunia' toi kana rapopalai.
26613	43	12	32	Aga Aku', ane rapokalangko-apa mpai' hi wongko dunia', kukeni hawe'ea tauna tumai hi Aku'."
26614	43	12	33	Lolita-na Yesus toe, mpowalatu beiwa mpai' karapatehi-na.
26615	43	12	34	Ra'uli' ntodea: "Hi rala Atura Pue' kibasa: Magau' Topetolo' tuwu' duu' kahae-hae-na. Napa-kona pai' nu'uli' Ana' Manusia' kana rapokalangko hi wongko dunia'? Ana' Manusia' to'uma wo'o-pi to nu'uli' tetu-e?"
26616	43	12	35	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Hampai' -damo, pai' baja to mpobajahi-koi tempo toi-e, uma-pi ria dohe-ni. Kaliliu-mokoi mako' bula-na mobaja-pidi, bona neo' -koi narata bengi. Tauna to mako' hi rala kabengia-na, uma ra'incai hiapa kahiloua-ra.
26617	43	12	36	Mepangala' -mokoi hi Aku' bula-ku ria-pidi dohe-ni mpobajahi-koi, bona mobaja nono-ni." Ka'oti-na Yesus mpo'uli' hawe'ea toe, malai-imi ngkai ree, pai' uma-ipi mpopehuwu woto-na hi ntodea.
26618	43	12	37	 Nau' wori' tanda mekoncehi to nababehi Yesus hi mata to Yahudi, uma oa' -ra mepangala' hi Hi'a.
26619	43	12	38	Jadi', madupa' -mi lolita nabi Yesaya owi to mpo'uli': Pue', uma hema to mpangala' kareba to kikeni. Nau' nupopohiloi-ra kabaraka' -nu, uma oa' rapangalai'."
26620	43	12	39	Jadi', uma-ra bisa mepangala', apa' ria wo'o Lolita Alata'ala to na'uki' nabi Yesaya owi, to mpo'uli':
26621	43	12	40	"Na'uli' Pue' Ala: 'Tungkai' kupakawero-ra, bona uma-ra pehilo. Kupakako'o nono-ra, bona nono-ra uma monoto. Ka'omea-na mpai' uma-ra nculii' hi Aku', toe pai' uma-ra kuwai' kalompea'.'"
26622	43	12	41	Lolita toe na'uki' nabi Yesaya owi, apa' nahilo ami' -mi kabaraka' -na Yesus, pai' nalowa-i.
26623	43	12	42	 Aga nau' wae, wori' moto pangkeni to Yahudi to mepangala' hi Yesus. Aga mepangala' bongo-ra-wadi, apa' me'eka' -ra nee-neo' mpai' to Parisi mpopalai-ra ngkai tomi posampayaa.
26624	43	12	43	Apa' konoa-ra doko' ra'une' hingka doo-ra, uma rasaile' pe'une' to ngkai Alata'ala.
26625	43	12	44	 Yesus mpesukui mekio', na'uli': "Tauna to mepangala' hi Aku', uma muntu' Aku' to rapangala'. Mepangala' wo'o-ramo hi Pue' Ala to mposuro-a.
26626	43	12	45	Tauna to mpohilo-a, mpohilo Pue' Ala wo'o-ra to mposuro-a.
26627	43	12	46	Tumai-a hi dunia' toi jadi' baja, bona hawe'ea tauna to mepangala' hi Aku' uma-pi mo'oha' hi rala kabengia-na.
26628	43	12	47	"Tauna to mpo'epe lolita-ku pai' uma ratuku', bela Aku' to mpohuku' -ra. Apa' bela patuju-ku tumai hi dunia' toi bona mpohuku' manusia'. Tumai-ale, bona mpobahaka-ra ngkai huku' -ra.
26629	43	12	48	Tauna to mposapuaka-a pai' uma mpotarima lolita-ku, ria-mi mpai' to mpohuku' -ra. Lolita-ku to kupohowa', toe-mi mpai' to mpohuku' -ra hi Eo Kiama.
26630	43	12	49	Apa' mololita-a uma ngkai konoa-ku moto. Ku'uli' pai' kulolita napa to napahawa' -ka Tuama-ku, apa' Hi'a-mi to mposuro-a tumai.
26631	43	12	50	Pai' ku'inca: hawa' -na toe mpowai' katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na. Jadi', napa to ku'uli' toi-e, bate lolita to na'uli' ami' -maka Tuama-ku."
26632	43	13	1	 Neo' rata-mi eo bohe Paskah. Na'inca Yesus, neo' rata-mi tempo-na mpalahii dunia' pai' hilou nculii' hi Tuama-na. Nape'ahi' -ra to jadi' bagia-na hi dunia' toi, pai' bate napoka'ahi' -ra duu' hi ka'omea-na.
26633	43	13	2	Yesus pai' ana'guru-na ngkoni' -ra ngkabengia. Magau' Anudaa' mpowara' Yudas ana' Simon Iskariot, mpo'usoki-i mpobalu' Yesus hi bali' -na.
26634	43	13	3	Na'inca Yesus, Tuama-na mpowai' -i hawe'ea kuasa-na. Na'inca wo'o kangkai Alata'ala-nai, pai' nculii' hilou hi Alata'ala wo'o-i mpai'.
26635	43	13	4	Toe pai' pokore-nami, naroncu baju-na, pai' na'ala' abe' napehoo' hi hope' -na.
26636	43	13	5	Oti toe, na'ala' ue natua hi batili, natepu'u-mi mpobohoi' witi' ana'guru-na, pai' naporihi hante abe' to hi hope' -na.
26637	43	13	6	Katelili-na hi Simon Petrus, na'uli' Petrus: "Pue', ncako Iko rahi-di mpobohoi' witi' -kue?"
26638	43	13	7	Na'uli' Yesus: "Tempo toi, ko'ia nu'incai napa to kubabehi toi. Mpeno-damo, pai' lako' nu'inca."
26639	43	13	8	Na'uli' Petrus: "Neo', Pue'! Neo' mpu'u nubohoi' witi' -ku!" Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane uma-ko kubohoi', uma ria posidaia' -nu hante Aku'."
26640	43	13	9	Na'uli' Simon Petrus: "Ane wae-di Pue', neo' muntu' witi' -ku-wadi! Hante pale pai' woo' -ku wo'o."
26641	43	13	10	Na'uli' Yesus: "Tauna to lako' oti moniu', uma-pi babo', me'itu' -mi hobo' woto-na, uma-pi mingki' rabohoi' tena. Muntu' witi' -na-damo to kana rabohoi'. Koi', tebohoi' -mokoi, aga uma hawe'ea-ni."
26642	43	13	11	Yesus mololita hewa toe, apa' na'inca ami' kahema-na mpai' to mpobalu' -i hi bali' -na. Toe pai' na'uli': "Tebohoi' -mokoi, aga uma hawe'ea-ni."
26643	43	13	12	Ka'oti-na Yesus mpobohoi' witi' -ra, na'unco' nculii' -mi baju-na, pai' -i mohura, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ha ni'inca wa napa to lako' kubabehi-kokoie?
26644	43	13	13	Aku', nikio' -a Guru-ni pai' Pue' -ni, pai' bate wae mpu'u.
26645	43	13	14	Aku' Pue' pai' Guru-ni mobago hewa hadua batua mpobohoi' witi' -ni. Jadi', koi' wo'o kana momebohoi' ngkawiti'.
26646	43	13	15	Kupopohiloi-koi tonco toe we'i, bona nipenau' kehi-ku: hewa Aku' mpotulungi-koi, koi' wo'o kana mpotulungi doo.
26647	43	13	16	"Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: hadua batua uma meliu tuwu' -na ngkai maradika-na. Hadua suro uma meliu tuwu' -na ngkai to mposuro-i.
26648	43	13	17	Ane ni'inca-damo tudui' toi, marasi' -koi ane nituku'.
26649	43	13	18	 "Napa to ku'uli' -e we'i, uma mpobelahi-koi omea. Ku'inca ami' hema to kupelihi. Tapi' kana madupa' lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': 'Tauna to mpodulu' -ka, hi'a-mi mpai' to jadi' bali' -ku.'
26650	43	13	19	Tohe'i ku'uli' ami' -mikokoi kako'ia-na jadi', bona ane madupa' -pi mpai', nipangala' -mi lolita-ku to mpo'uli' kahema-ku.
26651	43	13	20	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: hema to mpotarima suro-ku, hewa Aku' moto-mi to natarima. Wae wo'o, hema to mpotarima-a, hewa Tuama-ku moto-mi to natarima, apa' Hi'a-mi to mposuro-a."
26652	43	13	21	Ka'oti-na Yesus mololita hewa toe, susa' -mi nono-na, pai' na'uli': "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Hadua ngkai olo' -ni mpai' mpobalu' -a hi bali' -ku."
26653	43	13	22	Momenaa-ramo ana'guru-na nakeni ka'ingu' -ra, apa' uma ra'incai kahema-na to natoa'.
26654	43	13	23	Hadua ana'guru-na to nape'ahi', mohura hi ncori-na.
26655	43	13	24	Simon Petrus mpokini' mata ana'guru to hadua toei, na'uli' -ki: "Ee, pekune' -i pe' Guru-e, ba hema to natoa' -e."
26656	43	13	25	Toe pai' ana'guru toei mpomohui' Yesus, pai' mpekune' -i: "Hema-i, Pue'?"
26657	43	13	26	Na'uli' Yesus: "Tauna to kuwai' roti to oti kulolo' hi rala nede', hi'a-mi mpai'." Kana'ala' -nami hampui' roti, nalolo' hi rala nede', pai' nawai' -ki Yudas, ana' Simon Iskariot.
26658	43	13	27	Kanadoa-na Yudas roti toe, Magau' Anudaa' mesua' -mi hi rala nono-na. Oti toe, na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Napa to doko' nubabehi, babehi-mi sohi'."
26659	43	13	28	Ane doo-ra to ngkoni' dohe-ra, uma ra'incai napa pai' Yesus mololita hewa toe hi Yudas.
26660	43	13	29	Hantongo' -ra mpo'uli' meka' Yesus mpohubui Yudas mpo'oli ba napa-napa to raparaluu hi posusa' -ra, ba mpowai' doi hi tokabu. Apa' Yudas to ntimamahi doi-ra.
26661	43	13	30	Kanadoa-na Yudas roti toe, palai-nami hilou hi mali-na. Nto'u toe, mobengi-mi.
26662	43	13	31	 Palai-na Yudas ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Yesus: "Wae lau Aku' Ana' Manusia' rapomobohe. Pai' napa to jadi' hi Aku' mpai' mpomobohe wo'o Alata'ala.
26663	43	13	32	Ane napa to jadi' hi Aku' mpomobohe Alata'ala, Alata'ala wo'o mpai' mpomobohe-a hante baraka' -na. Pai' sohi' kadupa' -na.
26664	43	13	33	Ana' -ana' -ku, uma-apa mahae dohe-ni. Nipali' -a mpai', aga hewa to oti ku'uli' -raka topoparenta to Yahudi wengi, wae wo'o ku'uli' -kokoi: Hi kahilouaa-ku uma-koi bisa hilou.
26665	43	13	34	"Kuwai' -koi hawa' to bo'u: Momepoka'ahi' -mokoi. Hewa Aku' mpoka'ahi' -koi, wae wo'o koi' kana momepoka'ahi' hadua bo hadua.
26666	43	13	35	Ane momepoka'ahi' -koi, hawe'ea tauna mpo'inca kakoi' -na mpu'u-mi topetuku' -ku."
26667	43	13	36	 Napekune' Simon Petrus hi Yesus: "Hilou hiapa-ko, Pue'?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Hi kahilouaa-ku, ko'ia-ko bisa hilou. Mpeno-damo, nutuku' -a."
26668	43	13	37	Na'uli' tena Petrus: "Ha napa pai' uma-a ma'ala mpotuku' -ko wae-e lau Pue'? Ku'agi mate sabana petuku' -ku hi Iko!"
26669	43	13	38	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ha nu'agi mpu'u mate sabana Aku'? Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Kako'ia-na manu' turua' mpai', mpolia' tolu ngkani-moko mposapu kanu'inca-ku."
26670	43	14	1	 Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka ana'guru-na: "Neo' susa' nono-ni! Mepangala' -mokoi hi Alata'ala, pai' mepangala' wo'o-koi hi Aku'.
26671	43	14	2	Hi tomi Tuama-ku, wori' po'ohaa'. Hilou-a mporodo-kokoi po'ohaa' -ni. Ane ke uma hewa toe, ke uma-hawo ku'uli' -kokoi.
26672	43	14	3	Ane hudu-a-damo mporodo po'ohaa' -ni, nculii' moto-a mpai' tumai mpo'ala' -koi, kukeni-koi hilou hi po'ohaa' -ku, bona hiapa po'ohaa' -ku, hi ree wo'o-koi dohe-ku.
26673	43	14	4	 Ni'inca moto ohea hilou hi po'ohaa' -ku."
26674	43	14	5	Na'uli' Tomas: "Uma-kaiwo ki'incai hiapa kahilouaa-nu Pue'. Beiwa-kaina kaki'inca-na ohea-nae?"
26675	43	14	6	Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' toi-mi ohea, Aku' to makono, pai' to mpowai' katuwua'. Uma haduaa to rata hi Tuama-ku, ane uma ntara hi Aku'.
26676	43	14	7	Ane ntoa' ni'inca-ama Aku' -e, tantu ni'inca wo'o-imi Tuama-ku. Ngkai wae-e lau, ni'inca-imi pai' nihilo-imi."
26677	43	14	8	Na'uli' Filipus: "Pue', popohiloi-ka-kaiwo Tuama-nu, bona oha nono-kai."
26678	43	14	9	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ko'ia oa' -tano nu'incai-ae, Filipus! Hiaa' bo mahae-ama dohe-ni! Hema to mpohilo-a, mpohilo wo'o-ramo Tuama-ku. Jadi', napa-di pai' nuperapi' bona kupopohiloi-koi Tuama-kue?
26679	43	14	10	Ha uma oa' nuparasaya ka'Aku' -na hintuwu' hante Tuama-ku pai' Tuama-ku hintuwu' hante Aku'? Napa to ku'uli' -kokoi toe, uma ku'uli' ntuku' konoa-ku moto. Tuama-ku to tida hintuwu' hante Aku', Hi'a-mi pue' bago.
26680	43	14	11	Pangala' -ama-hana, ka'Aku' -na hintuwu' hante Tuama-ku pai' Tuama-ku hintuwu' hante Aku'. Nau' uma nipangalai' lolita-ku, pangala' -mi apa' nihilo-mi hawe'ea to kubabehi.
26681	43	14	12	 "Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Tauna to mepangala' hi Aku', ma'ala-ra mpobabehi hewa to kubabehi-- ba melabi tena-pi ngkai to kubabehi-- apa' hilou-a mpai' mo'oha' dohe Tuama-ku.
26682	43	14	13	Jadi', napa-napa to niperapi' hante hanga' -ku, bate kuwai' -koi, bona to kubabehi toe mpobila' Tuama-ku.
26683	43	14	14	Ba napa-napa to niperapi' hante hanga' -ku, kuwai' -koi.
26684	43	14	15	 "Ane nipoka'ahi' -a, nituku' -mi hawa' -ku.
26685	43	14	16	Kuperapi' hi Tuama-ku, bona nawai' -koi hadua Topetulungi to ntani' -na, bona Hi'a-damo mpodohei-koi duu' kahae-hae-na.
26686	43	14	17	Topetulungi toei, Hi'a-mi Inoha' Alata'ala, to mpotete' -koi hi tudui' to makono. Tauna to uma mepangala' uma bisa mpotarima-i, apa' uma-i rahiloi pai' uma wo'o-i ra'incai. Aga koi', ni'inca-imi, apa' nadohei-mokoi wae lau, pai' mo'oha' -i mpai' hi rala nono-ni.
26687	43	14	18	 "Uma-koi kupalahii jadi' ilu. Nculii' moto-a mpai' tumai hi koi'.
26688	43	14	19	Hampai' lia-damo, tauna to hi dunia' uma-pi mpohiloi-a. Aga koi', nihilo moto-a. Tuwu' moto-koi mpai', apa' Aku' tuwu' -a.
26689	43	14	20	Ane rata-pi mpai' tempo toe, ni'inca-mi ka'Aku' -na hintuwu' hante Tuama-ku, pai' koi' hintuwu' hante Aku', pai' Aku' hintuwu' hante koi'.
26690	43	14	21	"Tauna to mpotarima pai' mpotuku' hawa' -ku, hira' -mi to mpoka'ahi' -a. Tuama-ku mpoka'ahi' tauna to mpoka'ahi' -a, pai' Aku' wo'o mpoka'ahi' -ra, pai' kupopohiloi-ra woto-ku."
26691	43	14	22	Yudas (aga bela Yudas Iskariot) mpekune' Yesus: "Pue', napa pai' nupopehuwu woto-nu hi kai' -wadi, uma hi hawe'ea tauna hi dunia'?"
26692	43	14	23	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kupopehuwu woto-ku hi tauna to mpoka'ahi' -a pai' to mpotuku' lolita-ku. Tuama-ku mpoka'ahi' tauna to hewa toe. Tuama-ku pai' Aku' hilou hi tauna toera, pai' mo'oha' -makai dohe-ra.
26693	43	14	24	Tauna to uma mpoka'ahi' -a, uma-ra mpotuku' lolita-ku. Lolita to ni'epe ngkai Aku', uma ngkai Aku' moto. Ngkai Tuama-ku to mposuro-a.
26694	43	14	25	 "Hawe'ea toe we'i lau ku'uli' -kokoi nampa' hi ria-a-pidi dohe-ni.
26695	43	14	26	Tapi' ane rata-ipi mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli', Hi'a-mi to mpotudui' -koi butu nyala-na, pai' napopokiwoii-koi hawe'ea to oti-mi ku'uli' -kokoi, apa' Hi'a-mi Topetulungi to nahubui tumai Tuama-ku jadi' sulewata-ku.
26696	43	14	27	"Kalompea' kutu'u-kokoi. Kalompea' to ngkai Aku' moto-mi to kuwai' -kokoi. To kuwai' -kokoi toi-e, uma hewa to nirata ngkai dunia' toi. Neo' susa' nono-ni, pai' neo' me'eka'.
26697	43	14	28	 Ni'epe lolita-ku we'i to mpo'uli': Hilou-a, aga nculii' moto-a mpai' tumai hi koi'. Ane nipoka'ahi' mpu'u-a, nipokagoe' moto kahilou-ku toi hi Tuama-ku, apa' Tuama-ku meliu kabohe-na ngkai Aku'.
26698	43	14	29	Toe-e ku'uli' ami' -mikokoi kako'ia-na jadi', bona ane madupa' -pi mpai', nipangala' -mi.
26699	43	14	30	"Uma-pi wori' loga-ku mpololitai-koi, apa' neo' rata-mi Magau' Anudaa'. Hi'a-mi to mpokuasai dunia' tohe'i, aga uma ria kuasa-na hi Aku'.
26700	43	14	31	Aga toi kana jadi', bona hawe'ea tauna mpo'inca kakupoka'ahi' -na Tuama-ku pai' kutuku' oa' hawe'ea to nahawai' -ka. Mokore-mi, pai' hilou-tamo."
26701	43	15	1	 Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' toi-mi woto kaju to makono, pai' Tuama-ku pue' bonea.
26702	43	15	2	Hawe'ea ra'a to mentaka' hi Aku' to uma mowua', nalali. Pai' hawe'ea ra'a to mentaka' hi Aku' pai' to mowua', napeholui pai' napegalihi, bona kawoo-woria' wua' -na.
26703	43	15	3	Koi', tepegalihi-mokoi-- batua-na, moroli' -mokoi napakaroli' lolita to ku'uli' -kokoi.
26704	43	15	4	"Tida-mokoi hintuwu' hante Aku', pai' Aku' wo'o hante koi'. Ra'a to mohepi' ngkai woto kaju, uma-i mowua'. Ra'a bate kana mentaka' hi woto-na bona mowua' -i. Wae wo'o koi': Sampale-koi mowua' ane tida-koi hintuwu' hante Aku'.
26705	43	15	5	"Aku' toi-mi woto kaju, pai' koi' -mi ra'a-na. Tauna to tida hintuwu' hante Aku' pai' Aku' hante hira', wori' powua' -ra. Aga ane mogaa' -koi ngkai Aku', uma-koi bisa mpobabehi napa-napa.
26706	43	15	6	Hema to uma tida hintuwu' hante Aku' bate ratadi, hewa karatadi-na ra'a to mohepi' duu' -na jadi' bangi. Ra'a to hewa toe, rarumpu pai' ratene' hi rala apu.
26707	43	15	7	Ane tida-koi hintuwu' hante Aku' pai' lolita-ku tida hi rala nono-ni, perapi' -mi-hana hi Alata'ala ba napa-napa konoa-ni, bate nawai' -koile.
26708	43	15	8	Ane mowua' wori' -koi, Tuama-ku rapomobohe. Ane hewa toe-mi po'ingku-ni, topetuku' -ku mpu'u-mokoi.
26709	43	15	9	 Hewa Tuama-ku mpoka'ahi' -a, wae wo'o Aku' mpoka'ahi' -koi. Tida-mokoi mohu' hi Aku' bona nirasai ahi' -ku.
26710	43	15	10	Ane nituku' -mi hawa' -ku, tida mpu'u-koi mohu' hi Aku' pai' nirasai mpu'u ahi' -ku, hewa Aku' wo'o mpotuku' hawa' Tuama-ku pai' -a tida mohu' hi Hi'a pai' mporasai ahi' -na.
26711	43	15	11	"Hawe'ea tohe'i ku'uli' -kokoi, bona goe' nono-ni hante kagoea' to ngkai Aku', pai' bona gana kagoea' -ni.
26712	43	15	12	"Toi-mi hawa' -ku: Momepoka'ahi' -mokoi, hewa Aku' wo'o mpoka'ahi' -koi.
26713	43	15	13	Ane ria tauna to mpewai' tuwu' -na bona doo-na tuwu', bohe mpu'u ahi' -na toe. Uma ria ahi' to meliu ngkai ahi' tauna to mpewai' tuwu' -na bona mpotulungi doo-na.
26714	43	15	14	Doo-ku omea-mokoi, ane nituku' hawa' -ku.
26715	43	15	15	Uma-pokoi kukahangai' batua-ku, apa' batua uma mpo'incai napa to hi rala nono pue' -na. Wae-e lau, doo-ku mpu'u-mokoi, apa' ku'uli' -mikokoi hawe'ea to na'uli' -ka Tuama-ku.
26716	43	15	16	Bela koi' to mpopelihi-a. Aku' -dile to mpelihi-koie. Kuwai' -koi bago hilou hi rala dunia' bona mowua' wori'. Pai' powua' -ni toe uma mpai' moronto, ria kalaua-na duu' kahae-hae-na. Jadi', napa to niperapi' hi Tuama-ku hante hanga' -ku, bate nawai' -koi.
26717	43	15	17	Toi-mi hawa' -ku hi koi': Momepoka'ahi' -mokoi!
26718	43	15	18	 "Ane tauna to uma mepangala' hi Aku' mpokahuku' -koi, kiwoi: Aku' -mi-hana to ri'ulu rapokahuku' -e.
26719	43	15	19	Ane rapa' -na hampodooa-koi hante tauna to uma mepangala', bate rapoka'ahi' -koi, apa' lawi' doo-rakoi. Tapi' kupelihi-mokoi pai' kupatani' -koi ngkai laintongo' -ra, alaa-na uma-pokoi doo-ra. Toe pai' rapokahuku' -koi.
26720	43	15	20	Kiwoi napa to ku'uli' -kokoi we'i: Hadua batua uma meliu tuwu' -na ngkai maradika-na. Ane ntoa' Aku' rabalinai', koi' wo'o mpai' rabalinai'. Ane ria to mpotuku' lolita-ku, bate ratuku' wo'o mpai' lolita-ni.
26721	43	15	21	Hawe'ea tohe'e rababehi hi koi' apa' topetuku' -ku-koi. Hawe'ea tohe'e rababehi hi koi', apa' uma-i ra'incai Alata'ala to mposuro-a.
26722	43	15	22	Ane ke uma-a tumai mpololitai-ra, ke uma-ra-hawo masala'. Tapi', apa' tumai mpu'u-ama mpololitai-rae, toe pai' uma ria wuniia' -na sala' -ra.
26723	43	15	23	Tauna to mpokahuku' -a, mpokahuku' wo'o-ra Tuama-ku.
26724	43	15	24	"Hi laintongo' ntodea kubabehi anu mekoncehi, to ko'ia ria rababehi tau ntani' -na. Ane ke uma kubabehi hewa toe, ke uma-ra masala'. Tapi' rahilo moto-mi napa to kubabehi, pai' rapokahuku' oa' -a, pai' rapokahuku' wo'o-i Tuama-ku.
26725	43	15	25	Aga bate kana hewa toe, bona madupa' lolita to te'uki' hi rala Buku Atura-ra to mpo'uli': 'Rapokahuku' -a nau' uma ria sabana.'
26726	43	15	26	 "Tumai-i mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli', batua-na, Inoha' to mehuwu ngkai Alata'ala pai' to mpotete' -koi hi tudui' to makono. Hi'a-mi mpai' Topetulungi to kuhubui tumai hi koi' ngkai Tuama-ku. Ane tumai-ipi mpai', Hi'a-mi to jadi' sabi' -ku.
26727	43	15	27	Pai' koi' wo'o jadi' sabi' -ku, apa' koi' -mi to dohe-ku ngkai pontepu'ua bago-ku hi dunia'.
26728	43	16	1	 "Hawe'ea tohe'i ku'uli' -kokoi, bona neo' mere' nono-ni duu' -na nibahakai mepangala' hi Aku'.
26729	43	16	2	Rapopalai-koi mpai' ngkai tomi posampayaa. Uma muntu' toe, rata mpai' tempo-na ria tauna to doko' mpopatehi-koi, apa' ra'uli' -rana, toe-mi konoa Alata'ala.
26730	43	16	3	Hawe'ea toe rababehi hi koi', apa' uma ra'incai Tuama-ku, pai' Aku' wo'o, uma-a ra'incai.
26731	43	16	4	Ku'uli' -kokoi tohe'i, bona ane madupa' -pi mpai', nikiwoi-mi ka'oti-nami ku'uli' -kokoi.
26732	43	16	5	Aga wae-e lau, neo' hilou-ama hi Tuama-ku to mposuro-a, pai' uma-koi haduaa to mpekune' -a ba hiapa kahiloua-ku.
26733	43	16	6	Wule' susa' nono-ni-wadi mpo'epe lolita-ku we'i to mpo'uli' neo' hilou-ama.
26734	43	16	7	 Aga kakoo-kono-na, rasi' -nidi ane hilou-ae! Apa' ane uma-a hilou, uma-i mpai' tumai Topetulungi. Aga ane hilou-apa mpai', kuhubui moto-i tumai hi koi'.
26735	43	16	8	"Ane tumai-i mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli', Hi'a-damo to mpakanoto hi manusia' kamojeko' -ra. Napakanoto wo'o kamonoa' -ku pai' pehuku' Alata'ala.
26736	43	16	9	Napakanoto kamojeko' -ra apa' uma-ra mepangala' hi Aku'.
26737	43	16	10	Napakanoto wo'o kamonoa' -ku, apa' hilou-ama mpai' hi Tuama-ku, pai' uma-apa nihiloi.
26738	43	16	11	Napakanoto wo'o kanahuku' -ra mpai' Alata'ala tauna to mojeko', apa' nahuku' -imi Magau' Anudaa' to mpokuasai dunia' tohe'i.
26739	43	16	12	"Wori' -pidi to doko' ku'uli' -kokoi, aga ko'ia nikulei' mpotarima omea tempo toi.
26740	43	16	13	Ane tumai-i mpai' Inoha' Tomoroli', Hi'a-damo to mpotete' -koi pai' mpopo'incai-koi hawe'ea tudui' to makono. Uma-i mololita ntuku' konoa-na moto. Napa to na'epe ngkai Tuama-ku, toe-mi to nalolita. Pai' naparata-kokoi napa to jadi' hi eo mpeno.
26741	43	16	14	Hi'a mpai' to mpomobohe-a, apa' lolita to natarima ngkai Aku', toe-mi to naparata-kokoi.
26742	43	16	15	Hawe'ea to ria hi Tuama-ku, bagia-ku omea-mi. Toe pai' ku'uli': napa to natarima Inoha' Tomoroli' ngkai Aku', toe-mi to naparata-kokoi."
26743	43	16	16	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Hampai' -damo pai' uma-apa nihiloi. Hampai' wo'o-damo, nihilo wo'o-ama."
26744	43	16	17	Ingu' -ramo ana'guru-na, pai' ria-ra to momepekune', ra'uli': "Napa-die pai' na'uli' -taka: 'Hampai' -damo pai' uma-apa nihiloi. Hampai' wo'o-damo, nihilo wo'o-ama'? Napa wo'o pai' na'uli': 'Hilou-a hi Tuama-ku'?"
26745	43	16	18	Momepekune' ncuu-ra, ra'uli': "Napa pai' na'uli' oa' 'Hampai' -damo'? Uma ta'incai batua-na."
26746	43	16	19	Na'inca Yesus kadoko' -ra mpekune' -i. Toe pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ntora momepekune' -koi ba napa batua-na lolita-ku we'i to mpo'uli': 'Hampai' -damo pai' uma-apa nihiloi. Hampai' wo'o-damo, nihilo wo'o-ama.'
26747	43	16	20	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: geo' pai' motantangi' -koi mpai', tapi' tauna to uma mepangala' hi Aku', goe' moto-ra. Susa' mpai' nono-ni, tapi' kasusaa' -ni mobali' jadi' kagoea'.
26748	43	16	21	Kagoea' -ni toe, hewa kagoea' to narata hadua tobine to neo' mo'ana'. Lomo' -na ntodohaka-i, apa' gati tempo-nami mo'ana'. Tapi' ane putu-damo ana' -na, uma-pi napenonoi pontodohakaa-na, goe' -imi apa' putu-mi ana'lei hi rala dunia'.
26749	43	16	22	Wae wo'o mpai' koi'. Tempo toi susa' nono-ni. Tapi' kupohirua' moto-kokoi mpai'. Nto'u toe, goe' nculii' -mokoi, pai' uma hema to mpo'alai' -koi kagoea' -ni tetu.
26750	43	16	23	 "Nto'u toe mpai', uma-pi mingki' nipekune' -a ba napa-napa. Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: napa-napa to niperapi' hi Tuama-ku hante hanga' -ku, bate nawai' -koi.
26751	43	16	24	Duu' hewa toe lau, ko'ia-koi ria merapi' napa-napa hante hanga' -ku. Wule' perapi' -mi-hana, nirata moto mpai', bona gana mpu'u kagoea' -ni."
26752	43	16	25	"Hawe'ea tohe'i ku'uli' -kokoi hante walatu. Tapi' rata mpai' tempo-na, uma-apa mowalatu. Kupololitai-koi hante kalonto' -na mpotompo'wiwi Tuama-ku.
26753	43	16	26	Nto'u toe mpai', merapi' -koi hi Tuama-ku hante hanga' -ku. Uma mingki' Aku' to mperapi' -kokoi hi Tuama-ku,
26754	43	16	27	apa' napoka'ahi' -koi. Napoka'ahi' -koi, apa' nipoka'ahi' -a, pai' nipangala' ka'Aku' -na to ngkai Alata'ala.
26755	43	16	28	 Ngkai Tuama-ku mpu'u-ada, pai' tumai-ama hi dunia' toi. Wae-e lau, kupalahii-mi dunia' toi, nculii' -ama hilou hi Tuama-ku."
26756	43	16	29	Ra'uli' ana'guru-na: "Tempo toi, lonto' -mi lolita-nu Pue', uma-poko mowalatu.
26757	43	16	30	Monoto mpu'u-mi hi kai': Pue' to mpo'inca omea. Uma-pi mingki' ria to mpekune' ba napa-napa hi Iko. Toe pai' kipangala' ka'Iko-na to ngkai Alata'ala."
26758	43	16	31	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ha mepangala' mpu'u-mokoi wae lau?
26759	43	16	32	Kiwoi! Rata mpai' tempo-na-- pai' toi-mi tempo-na-- koi' mpai' pagaa' -gaa' hore-hore nculii' hi tomi-ni, pai' Aku' nipalahii hadudua-ku. Aga uma hadudua-ku mpu'u, apa' Tuama-ku mpodohei-a.
26760	43	16	33	Hawe'ea toi ku'uli' -kokoi, bona mporata-koi kalompea' tuwu' ngkai posidaia' -ni hante Aku'. Bula-ni hi rala dunia' toi-pidi, bate rabalinai' -koi. Aga pakaroho nono-ni, apa' kudagi-mi dunia' toi."
26761	43	17	1	 Ka'oti-na Yesus mpo'uli' hawe'ea toe, mengoa' -imi hi langi' pai' -i mosampaya, na'uli': "Tuama-ku, rata-mi tempo-na! Pomobohe-ama Aku' Ana' -nu, bona Aku' wo'o mpomobohe-ko Mama.
26762	43	17	2	Nuwai' -ama kuasa hi hawe'ea manusia', bona tauna to nuwai' -maka, kuwai' -ra katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26763	43	17	3	Ane ra'inca-ko Mama, ka'Iko-na Alata'ala to makono to uma ria karodua-na, pai' ane ra'inca Yesus Kristus suro-nu, toe-mi ohea-ra mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na.
26764	43	17	4	Hi rala dunia' toi kupopehuwu-mi kabohe tuwu' -nu Mama, kuposipolea-mi bago to nuwai' -ka.
26765	43	17	5	Toe pai' kuperapi' bona nupopehuwu kabohe tuwu' -ku dohe-nu Mama, hewa kabohe tuwu' -ta hangkaa-ngkania kako'ia-na dunia' tohe'i rapajadi'.
26766	43	17	6	 "Ane doo-ku tohe'ira lau, to nuwai' -maka ngkai rala dunia' toi-e, kupopo'incai-ramo kahema-nu Mama. Bagia-nu ami' -ramo, nutonu-ra hi Aku', pai' ratuku' -mi lolita-nu.
26767	43	17	7	Wae lau, ra'inca-mi: hawe'ea to nuwai' -ka, bate ngkai Iko Mama.
26768	43	17	8	Kuparata-miraka hawe'ea lolita to nuparata-ka. Ratarima-mi, pai' ra'inca-mi Aku' toi ngkai Mama mpu'u-a, pai' rapangala' -mi ka'Iko-na to mposuro-a.
26769	43	17	9	"Kuposampayai-ra doo-ku tohe'i-ra lau. Uma kuposampayai hawe'ea tauna hi dunia'. To kuposampayai toi-e, muntu' tauna to nuwai' -maka Mama, apa' lawi' hira' -mi bagia-nu.
26770	43	17	10	Hawe'ea tauna to kupobagia, bagia-nu Mama. Pai' hawe'ea tauna to nupobagia, bagia-ku. Hira' -mi to mpopehuwu kabohe tuwu' -ku.
26771	43	17	11	 "Neo' tilou-ama Mama, uma-apa mahae hi dunia' toi. Aga ane ana'guru-ku toira lau, hi dunia' toi-ra-pidi. O Tuama-ku to moroli', pewili' -ramo hante kabaraka' hanga' -nu-- hante hanga' to nuwai' -ka. Pewili' -ramo bona hanono lau-ra, hewa Mama pai' Aku' hanono lau-ta.
26772	43	17	12	Bula-ku dohe-ra-pidi, Aku' to mpewili' -ra hante kabaraka' hanga' -nu-- hante hanga' to nuwai' -ka. Kujaga-ra pai' uma-ra ria to mporata silaka, ntani' -na ngkai to hadua. Hi'a kana silaka, bona madupa' lolita to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli'.
26773	43	17	13	"Wae-e lau, tilou-ama Mama. Hawe'ea tohe'i ku'uli' bula-ku dohe-ra-pidi hi dunia' toi, bona gana mpu'u kagoea' -ra hante kagoea' to ngkai Aku'.
26774	43	17	14	Kuparata-miraka lolita-nu, alaa-na tauna to uma mepangala' mpokahuku' -ra, apa' bela-ra doo-ra, hewa Aku' wo'o bela-a doo-ra to uma mepangala'.
26775	43	17	15	Uma kuperapi' bona nu'ala' -ra ngkai dunia' tohe'i. Pomperapia' -ku, bona nupetalawai' -ra ngkai anudaa'.
26776	43	17	16	Hewa Aku' bela-a doo-ra to uma mepangala', wae wo'o ana'guru-ku bela doo-ra.
26777	43	17	17	 Pakaroli' -ramo, pajadi' -ra bagia-nu hante tudui' to makono. Lolita-nu Mama, tetu-mi to makono.
26778	43	17	18	Hewa Mama mposuro-a tumai hi dunia', wae wo'o Aku' mposuro-ra hilou hi tau ntani' -na hi dunia'.
26779	43	17	19	Mama, kutonu katuwu' -ku hi Iko jadi' bagia-nu, bona ana'guru-ku toira mporata kalompea', pai' bona hira' jadi' bagia-nu hi kampotuku' -ra tudui' to makono.
26780	43	17	20	 "Uma muntu' ana'guru-ku tohe'i-wadi to kuposampayai. Kuposampayai wo'o tauna to mepangala' mpai' hi Aku' ngkai posabi' -ra.
26781	43	17	21	Pomperapia' -ku, bona hawe'ea-ra hanono lau. Hewa Mama hintuwu' hante Aku', pai' Aku' hante Mama, kuperapi' bona hira' wo'o hintuwu' hante Kita'. Bona hawe'ea tauna mpangala' ka'Iko-na to mposuro-a.
26782	43	17	22	"Kuwai' -ramo kabaraka' to nuwai' -ka Mama, bona jadi' hanono lau-ramo, hewa Kita' wo'o hanono lau.
26783	43	17	23	Aku' hintuwu' hante hira', pai' Mama hintuwu' hante Aku', bona hira' mpai' jadi' hanono lau hante karoli' -roli' -na. Ane hewa toe-damo, hawe'ea tauna mpo'inca kanusuro-ku, pai' kanupoka'ahi' -ra hewa kanupoka'ahi' -ku.
26784	43	17	24	 "Mama, konoa-ku bona hira' to nuwai' -ka toi mo'oha' dohe-ku hi po'ohaa' -ku mpai', bona rahilo kabaraka' -ku. Kabaraka' -ku toi nuwai' -maka, apa' nupoka'ahi' -a ngkai kako'ia-na dunia' rapajadi'.
26785	43	17	25	O Tuama-ku to monoa', tauna hi dunia' toi uma mpo'incai-ko. Aga Aku', ku'inca-ko. Pai' doo-ku tohe'ira lau mpo'inca ka'Iko-na to mposuro-a.
26786	43	17	26	Kupopo'incai-ramo kahema-nu, pai' bate kupohewa toe oa' mpai', bona hira' mporasai ahi' -nu hi rala nono-ra, hewa Aku' mporasai ahi' -nu, pai' bona Aku' mo'oha' hi rala nono-ra."
26787	43	18	1	 Kahudu-na Yesus mosampaya, me'ongko' -imi hante ana'guru-na hilou hi mali ngata. Mpodongka' -ra ue Kidron, pai' -ra hilou hi pampa to hi dipo-na.
26788	43	18	2	Yudas, to mpobalu' Yesus toei, mpo'inca kahiapa-na pampa toe, apa' Yesus pai' ana'guru-na jau-ra morumpu hi ria.
26789	43	18	3	Jadi', imam pangkeni pai' to Parisi mpohubui hampodooa tantara to Roma pai' topojaga Tomi Alata'ala mpo'ema' Yudas hilou hi pampa toe. Mpokeni-ra rewa mpanga'e, lampu pai' hulu'.
26790	43	18	4	Yesus mpo'inca omea napa to kana jadi' hi woto-na. Toe pai' hilou-imi mpotomu tauna toera, pai' napekune': "Hema to nipali'?"
26791	43	18	5	Ra'uli': "Yesus to Nazaret." Na'uli' Yesus: "Aku' -mile toi-e." Yudas to mpobalu' -i mokore hi ree dohe tantara pai' topojaga toera.
26792	43	18	6	Nto'u kana'uli' -na-raka Yesus: "Aku' -mile toi-e," ngkala'ura-ramo pai' modungka-ra hi tana'.
26793	43	18	7	Napekune' wo'o-mi Yesus: "Hema to nipali' -e?" Ra'uli': "Yesus to Nazaret."
26794	43	18	8	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ku'uu-uli' -mi we'i ka'Aku' -nami toi-e. Jadi', ane Aku' mpu'u to nipali', pelele' -ramo doo-ku tohe'i hilou."
26795	43	18	9	(Hante lolita-na Yesus toe, madupa' -mi napa to na'uli' hi rala posampaya-na we'i: "Ngkai hawe'ea tauna to nuwai' -ka, uma ria haduaa to mporata silaka.")
26796	43	18	10	Ngkai ree, Simon Petrus mpowute' piho' -na, natime-ki hadua batua Imam Bohe, bela mpoholu tilinga ka'ana-na. Hanga' -na batua toei, Malkus.
26797	43	18	11	Na'uli' Yesus hi Petrus: "Unco' nculii' piho' -nu! Ha nu'uli' -kona kupetiboi' kaparia to naponoa' ami' -maka Tuama-kue?"
26798	43	18	12	Ngkai ree, tantara to Roma hante tadulako-ra, pai' topojaga to Yahudi mpohoko' Yesus, rahoo',
26799	43	18	13	 pai' -i rakeni hilou hi tomi Imam Bohe. Lomo' -na rakeni-i hilou hi Hanas, piniana-na Kayafas. Kayafas toei Imam Bohe hi mpae toe.
26800	43	18	14	Kayafas toe-mi to mpo'uli' -raka topoparenta to Yahudi wengi: "Agina-pi tau hadua mate mposampei ntodea."
26801	43	18	15	Simon Petrus pai' hadua ana'guru ntani' -na mpotuku' Yesus. Ana'guru to hadua toei, pome'inca-na Imam Bohe. Jadi', mesua' -imi dohe Yesus hi berewe tomi Imam Bohe.
26802	43	18	16	Petrus mepopea hi mali-na, hi wobo' wala. Ngkai ree we'i, ana'guru to hadua toei, lou nculii' hi mali-na mpololitai tobine to mpojaga wobo', bona Petrus rapiliu mesua' dohe-na, pai' napo'ema' -i Petrus mesua' hi rala-na.
26803	43	18	17	Tobine topojaga wobo' toei mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Ha bela iko wo'o ana'guru-na tauna toei-e lou?" Na'uli' Petrus: "Bela!"
26804	43	18	18	Nto'u toe, tempo lengi'. Jadi', ba hangkuja dua batua pai' topojaga mpobaa apu hi berewe hante wuri to morea', pai' -ra mokore ntololikia-na moneru. Petrus wo'o mokore pai' moneru dohe-ra.
26805	43	18	19	Hi rala tomi, Imam Bohe mpopekune' Yesus na'uli' -ki: "Hema omea-ra ana'guru-nue? Napa to nutudui' -raka?"
26806	43	18	20	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kabiasaa-ku, mololita hante kalonto' -lonto' -na hi hawe'ea tauna. Metudui' -a hi tomi posampayaa pai' hi Tomi Alata'ala, hi kabiasaa-ta kita' to Yahudi morumpu. Uma ria to kuwunii' -na.
26807	43	18	21	Jadi', napa pai' nupekune' -ae? Pekune' moto-ra-kowo to mpo'epe-a metudui'. Ra'inca moto mpai' napa to ku'uli'."
26808	43	18	22	Kana'uli' -na Yesus toe, hadua topojaga to mokore hi ncori-na mpohopo' -i, na'uli': "Daho' mpu'u-ko-kona mololita hewa tetu hi Imam Bohe-e!"
26809	43	18	23	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane uma makono to ku'uli', uli' lau-mi hi rehe'i napa sala' -ku. Tapi' ane makono lolita-ku, napa pai' nuhopo' -a?"
26810	43	18	24	Ngkai ree, Hanas mpohubui topojaga mpokeni Yesus hilou hi Imam Bohe Kayafas. Nto'u toe, pale-na Yesus tehoo' oa' -pidi.
26811	43	18	25	Simon Petrus, ria-i-pidi mokore pai' moneru ngkokore dohe topojaga. Ria tauna to mpo'uli' -ki: "Ha bela iko wo'o hadua ana'guru-nae?" Nasapu Petrus, na'uli': "Bela-kuwo aku'!"
26812	43	18	26	Ria wo'o hi ree hadua batua Imam Bohe. Batua toei, ompi' tauna to naholu Petrus tilinga-na. Na'uli' batua toei mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Ha bela iko to kuhilo-e ngone hi pampa toe ria dohe Yesus-e?"
26813	43	18	27	Nasapu wo'o-mi Petrus, na'uli': "Bela!" Nto'u toe, turua' -mi manu'.
26814	43	18	28	 Mepupulo ngkii, Yesus rakeni ngkai tomi Kayafas hilou hi tomi gubernur. Topoparenta to Yahudi moto, uma-ra mesua' hi rala tomi gubernur, apa' gubernur toe, bela-i to Yahudi, pai' ane mesua' -ra hi rala tomi to bela tomi to Yahudi, jadi' babo' -ra ntuku' atura agama-ra, pai' uma-ra ma'ala ngkoni' pongkoni' Paskah.
26815	43	18	29	Jadi', Gubernur Pilatus hilou hi mali-na mpohirua' -raka pai' napekune' -ra: "Napa to nipangadu' -ki tauna toii-e?"
26816	43	18	30	Ra'uli': "Ane ke bela-i tauna to dada'a, ke uma-i kibua' hi Tuama Gubernur."
26817	43	18	31	Na'uli' Pilatus: "Keni hilou nculii', nipohurai-miki sala' -na ntuku' ada agama-ni moto-koiwo!" Ra'uli' to Yahudi toera: "Kai' -le, uma-kai rapiliu mpohuku' mate tauna."
26818	43	18	32	(Toi majadi' bona madupa' napa to na'uli' Yesus mpolowa beiwa mpai' kamate-na.)
26819	43	18	33	Ngkai ree, Pilatus mesua' nculii' hi rala tomi, napehubui bona Yesus rakeni hi nyanyoa-na, pai' napekune' -i: "Ha Iko mpu'u-mi Magau' to Yahudi-e?"
26820	43	18	34	Na'uli' Yesus: "Pompekunea' tetu ngkai Gubernur moto, ba pololita tau ntani' -nadi?"
26821	43	18	35	Na'uli' Pilatus: "Kawe' to Yahudi-a! Hingka to Yahudi-nu moto-kowo hante imam pangkeni to mpokeni-ko hi aku' -e. Napa-di sala' to nubabehi-e?"
26822	43	18	36	Na'uli' Yesus: "Kamagaua' -ku bela ngkai dunia' toi. Ane rapa' -na magau' hi dunia' toi mpu'u-a, tauna to mpotuku' -a bate me'ewa bona neo' -a rahoko' pai' rapewai' hi topoparenta to Yahudi. Tapi' Kamagaua' -ku bela ngkai dunia' toi."
26823	43	18	37	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Pilatus: "Ane wae-di, magau' mpu'u-ko?" Na'uli' Yesus: "Iko moto to mpo'uli' Aku' toi magau'. Pai' -a putu hi dunia' toi, bona mpo'uli' napa to makono. Tauna to mpokono napa to makono, bate mpangala' lolita-ku."
26824	43	18	38	Hampetompoi' Pilatus: "Ah! Napa-i to nu'uli' makono tetu-e?"
26825	43	18	39	Aga, ane ntuku' -ki ada-ni lalau, butu mpae-na hi Eo Paskah, kubahaka-kokoi hadua to ratarungku', ba hema konoa-ni. Jadi', beiwa: dota-koi ane kubahaka-kokoi Magau' to Yahudi toii-e?"
26826	43	18	40	Mejeu' -ra ra'uli': "Neo', neo' Hi'a! Agina Barabas!" (Barabas toe, hadua toperampaki.)
26827	43	19	1	 Oti toe, Pilatus mpohubui tantara-na mpoweba' Yesus.
26828	43	19	2	
26829	43	19	3	Tantara toera mpobabehi hameha' songko ngkai walaa to morui, to hewa songko magau', pai' rasongkoi-ki Yesus. Oti toe, raheai-i hante baju to mperelei hewa baju magau', rapotingkuai' -i pai' ra'uli' -ki: "Wori' tabe, Magau' to Yahudi!" Pai' -i rahopo'.
26830	43	19	4	Oti toe, mehupa' wo'o-imi Pilatus lou hi mali-na, pai' na'uli' -raka to Yahudi: "Hilo, kukeni-imi tumai hi koi', bona ni'inca ka'uma-na kuruai' nau' hanyalaa kasalaa' -na."
26831	43	19	5	Ngkai ree, rakeni mpu'u-imi Yesus hi mali-na, mosongkoi rui pai' mobajui hante baju to hewa baju magau'. Na'uli' Pilatus: "Hilo, etu-imi!"
26832	43	19	6	Nto'u imam pangkeni pai' topojaga mpohilo Yesus, kamejeu' -rami ra'uli': "Parika' -imi! Parika' -imi!" Na'uli' Pilatus: "Ane doko' niparika' -i, ala' -imi, niparika' moto-imi-koiwo, apa' aku', uma-kuna kuruai' kasalaa' -na."
26833	43	19	7	Ra'uli' to Yahudi: "Ane kai' -le, ntuku' -ki atura agama-kai, kana rahuku' mate-i, apa' na'uli' -hana Hi'a Ana' Alata'ala."
26834	43	19	8	Kana'epe-na Pilatus toe, hangkedi' kame'eka' -na.
26835	43	19	9	Mesua' nculii' -imi hi rala tomi, pai' mpekune' tena Yesus: "Ha to apa mpu'u-ko-kowo Iko-e?" Tapi' Yesus, uma-i winihi.
26836	43	19	10	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Pilatus: "Oja' -ko mpotompoi' -ae? Ha uma nu'incai, aku' toi, ria kuasa-ku mpobahaka-ko ba mpoparika' -ko!"
26837	43	19	11	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane Alata'ala uma mpowai' -ko kuasa tetu, uma ria hangkedia' kuasa-nu hi Aku'. Jadi', tauna to mpotonu-a hi iko, meliu kabohe jeko' -ra ngkai iko."
26838	43	19	12	Kana'epe-na Pilatus lolita toe, napali' ohea-na bona mpobahaka Yesus. Aga mejeu' wo'o-ramo to Yahudi, ra'uli': "Ane nubahaka-i-kona, bela-ko ema' -na Kaisar! Yesus tetui mpo'uli' Kahi'a-na magau'. Jadi', mpo'ewa Kaisar-i-hana!"
26839	43	19	13	Kana'epe-na Pilatus lolita-ra toe, nakeni-imi Yesus hi mali-na, pai' -i mohura hi pohuraa pobotuhia to rahanga' Ila' Watu. (Hi rala basa Yahudi hanga' -na Gabata.)
26840	43	19	14	Nto'u toe, neo' tebua' -mi eo-na, eo pomporodoa nto'u posusa' Paskah. Pilatus mpo'uli' -raka to Yahudi: "Etu-imi magau' -ni!"
26841	43	19	15	Mogora-ramo mejeu', ra'uli': "Patehi-i! Patehi-i! Parika' -i!" Na'uli' Pilatus: "Beiwa? Niperapi' kuparika' magau' -nie?" Hampetompoi' imam pangkeni: "Kaisar-wadi-kaina magau' -kai."
26842	43	19	16	 Ka'omea-na Pilatus mpotonu Yesus hi hira' bona raparika'.
26843	43	19	17	Yesus mpaha'a parika' -na hilou hi mali ngata, pai' -i rakeni hilou hi po'ohaa' to rahanga' Bulu' Banga'woo'. (Hi rala basa Yahudi hanga' -na Golgota.)
26844	43	19	18	Hi rehe'e-imi raparika'. Ria wo'o rodua tau ntani' -na to raparika' dohe-na. Hadua hi mali ngki'ii-na, hadua hi mali ngka'ana-na, pai' Yesus hi laintongo'.
26845	43	19	19	 Pilatus mpohubui tantara-na mpotaka' hameha' papan hi parika' -na Yesus. Hi papan toe te'uki': YESUS TO NAZARET, MAGAU' TO YAHUDI.
26846	43	19	20	Ukia' toe ra'uki' hi rala tolu nyala basa: basa Yahudi, basa Latin, pai' basa Yunani. Wori' to Yahudi mpobasa ukia' toe, apa' poparikaa' -na Yesus mohu' ngata.
26847	43	19	21	Jadi', imam pangkeni mpo'uli' -ki Pilatus: "Neo' ra'uki': Magau' to Yahudi! Agina ra'uki': 'Tauna toi mpo'uli' Kahi'a-na magau' to Yahudi.'"
26848	43	19	22	Na'uli' Pilatus: "Napa to ku'uki', bate-nami!"
26849	43	19	23	Kahudu-na tantara mpoparika' Yesus, ra'ala' -mi pohea-na pai' rabagi opo' bagia, hore-hore habagia-ra. Aga baju-na-hawo, uma ria daua-na, apa' ratanu' hantau lau.
26850	43	19	24	Toe pai' mohawa' -ramo tantara, ra'uli': "Neo' raheu' baju toi. Agina ntene' undi-ta, ba hema-ta to mporata." Tohe'i majadi' bona madupa' napa to te'uki' owi hi rala Buku Tomoroli', to mpo'uli': Ra'ala' pohea-ku rabagi-bagi, pai' baju-ku rapompenoai'."
26851	43	19	25	Mohu' kaju parika' Yesus, mokore tina-na pai' hadua ompi' tina-na, tobine wo'o-wadi. Ria wo'o Maria tobine-na Klopas, pai' Maria Magdalena.
26852	43	19	26	Kanahilo-na Yesus tina-na mokore hi ree hi ncori ana'guru-na to nape'ahi', na'uli' -miki tina-na: "Ina', etu-imi mai ana' -nu."
26853	43	19	27	Pai' na'uli' wo'o-miki ana'guru-na toei: "Etu-imi tina-nu." Ngkai ree, ana'guru toei mpewili' tina-na Yesus hi rala tomi-na.
26854	43	19	28	Na'inca Yesus hudu-mi omea. Jadi', bona madupa' napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli', na'uli': "Ngkamara-a."
26855	43	19	29	Hi ree, ria hamanga' ue anggur to mo'onco. Ra'ala' hampuhu' wunga to hewa lomo', ralolo' hi rala anggur toe, ratu'u hi wuntu ra'a kaju hisop, pai' rapopoju'ui-ki wiwi Yesus bona na'inu.
26856	43	19	30	Kanapemita-na Yesus, na'uli': "Hudu-mi!" Oti toe, ntungka' -imi, pai' modupe' -mi inoha' -na.
26857	43	19	31	 Eo karaparika' -na Yesus toe, eo pomporodoa (batua-na, eo kako'ia-na Eo Sabat), pai' ntuku' palia to Yahudi uma ma'ala ria tomate tetoe hi kaju parika' nto'u Eo Sabat. Peliu-liu-nami apa' Eo Sabat tohe'e meliu kabohe-na ngkai to lalau. Toe pai' topoparenta to Yahudi merapi' hi Pilatus bona tauna to raparika' toera rapui' witi' -ra, bona sohi' -ra mate pai' woto-ra rapopana'u.
26858	43	19	32	Jadi', hilou mpu'u-ramo tantara mpopui' witi' -ra to rodua to raparika' dohe Yesus.
26859	43	19	33	Aga karata-ra hi Yesus, rahilo-rawo mpolia' mate-imi. Uma-pi oko rapui' witi' -na.
26860	43	19	34	Aga hadua tantara mpojalo lumpeha-na hante ponci' -na. Karajalo-na tohe'e, mo'ili-mi tumai raa' pai' ue.
26861	43	19	35	Tauna to mpohilo kajadia' toe, hi'a-mi to mpo'uli' napa to nahilo, bona mepangala' wo'o-moko-koiwo. Makono lolita-na, pai' na'inca mpu'u kamakono-na.
26862	43	19	36	Tohe'i jadi' bona madupa' napa to te'uki' owi hi rala Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': "Uma mpai' hamehaa' wuku-na to rapui'."
26863	43	19	37	Ria wo'o lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli': "Hira' mpongoa' -i mpai' to rajalo owi."
26864	43	19	38	 Oti toe, ria hadua tauna to rahanga' Yusuf, ngkai ngata Arimatea. Mepangala' bongo-i hi Yesus, apa' mpoka'eka' -i topoparenta to Yahudi. Kamate-na Yesus toe, Yusuf hilou hi Pilatus, pai' -i mperapi' woto-na bona ratana. Pilatus mpiliu moto-i. Jadi', hilou mpu'u-imi Yusuf mpo'ala' woto-na Yesus.
26865	43	19	39	Dohe Yusuf, ria wo'o Nikodemus, to ria-imi hangkani mpencuai' Yesus ngkabengia. Nikodemus toei ngkeni anu mohonga to rahanga' mur pai' gaharu, kira-kira tolu mpulu' kilo katomo-na.
