26866	43	19	40	To rodua toera mpo'ala' woto Yesus, raputu' hante kain to bula, pai' ragelai' hante anu mohonga toe, ntuku' ada popatana to Yahudi.
26867	43	19	41	Mohu' poparikaa' -na Yesus, ria pampa, pai' hi rala pampa toe, ria wulou' hi panapa bulu' to raporodo hewa daeo'. Daeo' toe bo'u-pidi, ko'ia rapotanai.
26868	43	19	42	Jadi', apa' daeo' toe mohu', pai' neo' ntepu'u wo'o-mi eo pepuea', toe pai' rapesahui-mi mpotu'u woto Yesus hi rala daeo' toe.
26869	43	20	1	 Hi eo Mingku mepupulo ngkii, mobee-bengi-pidi, Maria Magdalena hilou hi daeo'. Rata hi ria, nahilo-hawo, watu po'unca-nae tederu' -mi ngkai wobo' daeo'.
26870	43	20	2	Pokeno-nami hilou hi Simon Petrus pai' ana'guru to hadua to nape'ahi' Yesus, na'uli' -raka: "Ra'ala' -mi-hana woto Pue' ngkai daeo', pai' uma ki'incai hiapa karatu'ua-na!"
26871	43	20	3	Hilou-ramo Petrus hante ana'guru to hadua toei hi daeo'.
26872	43	20	4	Roduaa-ra mokeno, aga meliu kagasi-na ana'guru to hadua ngkai Petrus, toe pai' ri'ulu-i-hana rata hi daeo'.
26873	43	20	5	Mengkabungku' -i mpelongi' hi rala-na, aga uma-i ulu mesua'. Nahilo-hawo kain to rahompui' -ki Yesus bate-na moto hi ree.
26874	43	20	6	Simon Petrus rata ngkabokoa', kaliliu mesua'. Nahilo wo'o-hawo kain hompu' -na hi ree.
26875	43	20	7	Aga kain to rapopohoo' -ki woo' -na Yesus, telulu pai' tetu'u ntani'.
26876	43	20	8	Ngkai ree, ana'guru to hadua, to ri'ulu rata hi daeo' we'i, mesua' wo'o-imi-hawo mpohilo, pai' napangala' -mi.
26877	43	20	9	Duu' rata hi eo toe, ko'ia oa' rapaha napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' owi to mpo'uli': Yesus kana tuwu' nculii'.
26878	43	20	10	Oti toe, nculii' -ramo ana'guru to rodua toera hilou hi tomi-ra.
26879	43	20	11	 Aga Maria Magdalena mokore hi mali daeo', ntora geo'. Bula-na geo', mengkabungku' -i melongi' hi rala daeo'.
26880	43	20	12	Nahilo-hawo rodua mala'eka, moheai to bula, mohura-ra hi karatu'ua woto-na Yesus wengi, hadua tono' hi woo' -na, to hadua tono' hi witi' -na.
26881	43	20	13	Mepekune' mala'eka toera hi Maria ra'uli': "Napa pai' geo' -ko?" Na'uli' Maria: "Apa' ra'ala' -imi Pue' -ku ngkai rei, pai' uma ku'incai hiapa karatu'ua-na."
26882	43	20	14	Ngkai ree, me'ili' -i Maria, nahilo-hawo hadua tauna mokore hi tilingkuria-na. Ntaa' Yesus-midi-hana, aga uma na'incai Kayesus-na.
26883	43	20	15	Mepekune' Yesus hi Maria: "Napa pai' geo' -ko totina? Hema to nupali'?" Na'uli' -hawo we'i Maria, pue' pampa moto to nahilo toe-e. Toe pai' na'uli' -ki: "Ane Iko Tuama to mpo'ala' woto-nae, tudo' -ka-kuwo hiapa pontu'ua-nu, bona ku'ala' -i."
26884	43	20	16	Na'uli' Yesus: "Maria." Pe'ili' -nami Maria hi Yesus, pai' na'uli' hi rala basa Yahudi: "Rabuni!" (batua-na: "Guru").
26885	43	20	17	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Maria: "Neo' -a ulu nukamu, apa' ko'ia-a mengkahe' hilou hi Tuama-ku. Hilou-ko hi ompi' -ku, uli' -raka kahilou-ku hi Tuama-ku bo Tuama-ni, Alata'ala-ku bo Alata'ala-ni."
26886	43	20	18	Kahilou-nami Maria Magdalena mpohirua' -raka ana'guru-na Yesus pai' na'uli': "Kuhilo-imi-kuna Pue'!" Pai' naparata-raka hawe'ea to na'uli' Yesus.
26887	43	20	19	 Ngkabengia eo Mingku toe, ana'guru-na Yesus morumpu hi tomi to tehohoki wobo' -na, apa' mpoka'eka' -ra topoparenta to Yahudi. Muu-mule' rata-imi Yesus mokore hi laintongo' -ra, pai' natabe-ra, na'uli': "Kalompea' rata hi koi'."
26888	43	20	20	Oti toe, natudo' -miraka pale pai' lumpeha-na. Uma-pi mowo kagoe' -ra mpohilo Pue' -ra.
26889	43	20	21	Na'uli' tena Yesus: "Kalompea' rata hi koi'. Hewa Tuama-ku mposuro-a, wae wo'o Aku' mposuro-koi."
26890	43	20	22	Oti toe, natuwui' -ramo hante inoha' -na pai' na'uli': "Doa-mokoi Inoha' Tomoroli'.
26891	43	20	23	Hema-hema to ni'ampungi jeko' -ra, Alata'ala to mpo'ampungi-ra. Ane uma ni'ampungi jeko' -ra, Alata'ala uma mpo'ampungi-ra."
26892	43	20	24	Tomas, hadua ngkai to hampulu' rodua ana'guru Yesus, to ra'atu Ntomoropa', uma-i-hana ria hante doo-na nto'u karata-na Yesus toe.
26893	43	20	25	Toe pai' doo-na ntora mpo'uli' -ki: "Kihilo-imi-kaina Pue'!" Na'uli' Tomas: "Ane ko'ia kuhiloi pakua' to hi pale-na pai' ku'unco' karawe-ku hi pakua' toe, pai' ane ko'ia ku'unco' pale-ku hi jaloa to hi lumpeha-na, bate uma kupangala'."
26894	43	20	26	 Eo Mingku boko', morumpu wo'o-ramo ana'guru-na hi rala tomi. Nto'u toe, Tomas, ria wo'o-imi-hawo dohe-ra. Tehohoki omea wobo', aga nau' wae, muu-mule' rata-imi Yesus mokore hi laintongo' -ra, na'uli' -raka: "Kalompea' rata hi koi'."
26895	43	20	27	Oti toe, na'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Tomas: "Tu'u-mi karawe-nu hi rei, pai' hilo pakua' to hi pale-ku. Mai pale-nu, nupe'unco' hi rala jaloa to hi lumpeha-ku. Neo' -pi morara' nono-nu. Pangala' -mi!"
26896	43	20	28	Na'uli' Tomas: "Pue' -ku! Alata'ala-ku!"
26897	43	20	29	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki: "Mepangala' -ko apa' nuhilo-ama. Marasi' -ra tauna to mepangala' hi Aku', nau' ko'ia-a rahiloi."
26898	43	20	30	Wori' -pidi tanda mekoncehi to nababehi Yesus pai' to rasabii' ana'guru-na, aga uma te'uki' omea hi rala sura toi.
26899	43	20	31	Aga napa to ku'uki' hi rehe'i, ku'uki' bona nipangala' Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo', Ana' Alata'ala, pai' bona mporata-koi katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na ngkai pepangala' -ni hi Hi'a.
26900	43	21	1	 Oti toe, Yesus mpopehuwu woto-na hangkani-pi hi ana'guru-na, hi wiwi' Rano Tiberias. Hewa toi tutura-na:
26901	43	21	2	Ba hangkuja dua ana'guru-na morumpu hi ria. Simon Petrus, Tomas to ra'atu Ntomoropa', Natanael ngkai Kana hi Galilea, to rodua ana' Zebedeus, pai' rodua ana'guru ntani' -na.
26902	43	21	3	Na'uli' Simon Petrus hi doo-na: "Hilou-a-kuna mebau'." Ra'uli' doo-na: "Hilou wo'o-ka-kaiwo." Hilou mpu'u-ramo mohawi' sakaya pai' -ra mojala' hi rano. Aga hamengia toe, uma ria hama'aa woko' jala' -ra.
26903	43	21	4	Parabaja-mi, Yesus mokore hi talinti, aga uma ra'incai Kayesus-na.
26904	43	21	5	Na'uli' -raka: "Ana' -ku, ria wa bau' -nie?" Ra'uli': "Uma-di ria-e."
26905	43	21	6	Na'uli' -raka: "Tene' hi mali ngka'ana sakaya jala' -ni, bate morasi' -koi mpai'." Ratene' mpu'u-mi jala' -ra, pai' uma-pi rakulei' mpodii', apa' uma mowo kawori' -na uru to hi rala-na.
26906	43	21	7	Ngkai ree, ana'guru to nape'ahi' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Pue' -hana toe-e mai!" Mpo'epe toe-di Petrus, kana'unco' -nami baju-na (apa' uma-i mobajui), nahoo' hi hope' -na, pai' mengkalitowo' -imi hilou hi rala ue, monangu hilou hi role-na.
26907	43	21	8	Ana'guru to ntani' -na, bate hi rala sakaya moto-ra, mpodii' jala' to ponu' uru hilou hi wiwi' rano. Uma-ra molaa rahi ngkai role-na, kira-kira ha'atu mete-wadi.
26908	43	21	9	Kamana'u-ra hi role-na, rahilo-rawo ria-mi apu to rapobaa hi ree hante wuri to morea', pai' hi lolo apu ria uru pai' ria wo'o roti.
26909	43	21	10	Na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -raka: "Keni-mi tumai ba hangkuja ma'a uru woko' jala' -nie."
26910	43	21	11	Simon Petrus ngkahe' hi sakaya pai' nadii' jala' -na tumai hi role-na. Jala' toe bihi' hante uru to bohe: ha'atu lima mpulu' tolu ma'a kadea-ra. Aga nau' wae kawori' -na, uma moto morenta jala' toe.
26911	43	21	12	Na'uli' Yesus: "Mai-tamo moduhu." Uma ria haduaa ana'guru to daho' mpekune' -i: "Hema-ko?" apa' monoto-mi hi nono-ra Kahi'a-na mpu'u-mi Pue'.
26912	43	21	13	Hilou-imi Yesus mpo'ala' roti pai' nawai' -raka. Napohewa toe wo'o hante bau' uru.
26913	43	21	14	Tohe'i katolu ngkani-nami Yesus mpopehuwu woto-na hi ana'guru-na ngkai katuwu' -na nculii'.
26914	43	21	15	 Ka'oti-ra ngkoni', na'uli' Yesus mpo'uli' -ki Simon Petrus: "Simon ana' Yohanes, ha nupe'ahi' -a meliu ngkai doo-nu toera lau mpe'ahi' -a?" Na'uli' Petrus: "Io', nu'inca moto Pue', kakupoka'ahi' -nue." Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae, podoo ana' bima-ku."
26915	43	21	16	Oti toe, Yesus mpekune' Petrus karongkani-na: "Simon, ana' Yohanes, ha nupe'ahi' -a?" Na'uli' Petrus: "Io', nu'inca moto Pue', kakupoka'ahi' -nue." Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae, ewu-ra bima-ku."
26916	43	21	17	Ngkai ree, Yesus mpekune' -i katolu ngkani-na: "Simon, ana' Yohanes, ha nupoka'ahi' mpu'u-a?" Peda' -mi nono-na Petrus, apa' Yesus mpekune' -i tolu ngkani ba napoka'ahi' mpu'u-i. Jadi', na'uli' Petrus: "Pue', nu'inca hawe'ea-na. Nu'inca kakupoka'ahi' -nu." Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane wae, podoo bima-ku.
26917	43	21	18	Makono mpu'u lolita-ku toi: Bula-nu mongura-pidi, iko moto mpehoo' abe' hi hope' -nu, pai' -ko hilou hiapa konoa-nu. Aga ane motu'a-poko mpai', nutonu pale-nu rahoo' tau ntani' -na, pai' -ko rakeni hilou hi ka'umaa-na nupokonoi."
26918	43	21	19	Hante walatu toe, Yesus mpolowa beiwa Petrus rapatehi mpai', bona mpobila' Alata'ala. Oti toe, na'uli' wo'o-mi Yesus, mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Tuku' -ama!"
26919	43	21	20	 Ngkai ree, kame'ili' -nami Petrus, mpohilo-i ana'guru to nape'ahi' Yesus mpotuku' -ra. (Ana'guru toe-mi to mohura ncori Yesus bula-ra ngkoni' ngkabengia pai' mpekune' -i: "Pue', hema-idi mpai' to mpobalu' -koe?")
26920	43	21	21	Kanahilo-na Petrus ana'guru toe, napekune' hi Yesus: "Pue', beiwa-i-hawo mpai' doo-ku toii-e?"
26921	43	21	22	Na'uli' Yesus: "Ane konoa-ku tuwu' ncuu-i duu' -ku rata nculii' mpai', uma mingki' nu'inca iko! Wule' tuku' -ama-hana."
26922	43	21	23	Ngkai ree, molele-mi kareba hi topetuku' Yesus, to mpo'uli' ka'uma-na mpai' mate ana'guru toei. Ntaa' bela-di-hawo toe to na'uli' Yesus-e. Api' wae-di-hawo: "Ane konoa-ku tuwu' ncuu-i duu' -ku rata nculii', uma mingki' nu'inca iko."
26923	43	21	24	Ana'guru toe-imi to mpohilo hawe'ea to jadi' toe, pai' to mpo'uli' posabi' -na. Hi'a-mile to mpo'uki' sura toi-e. Pai' ta'inca kamakono-na lolita-na toi.
26924	43	21	25	Wori' -pidi to ntani' -ntani' -na to nababehi Yesus. Ane rapa' -na butu nyala-na to nababehi toe ra'uki' hi rala buku, kupekiri nau' humalili' dunia' toi rapontimamahii-ki, ba kana uma-i liu apa' wori' lia buku.
26925	44	1	1	 Teofilus to rabila': Hi rala sura-ku to lomo' -na, oti-mi ku'uki' hawe'ea to nababehi pai' to napetudui' Yesus, ntepu'u ngkai lomo' pobago-na,
26926	44	1	2	
26927	44	1	3	duu' rata hi eo kara'ongkoa' -na hilou hi suruga. Ka'oti-na rapatehi pai' rapotuwu' nculii', wori' ngkani-i mpopehuwu woto-na hi suro-na, bona monoa' -mi ra'inca katuwu' -na nculii'. Rala-na opo' mpulu' eo, rahilo moto-i, pai' -i mpotudui' -ra beiwa patuju-na Alata'ala mpohore manusia' ngkai huku' jeko' -ra pai' mpopajadi' -ra ntodea-na hi rala Kamagaua' -na. Kako'ia-na me'ongko' hilou hi suruga, hante kuasa Inoha' Tomoroli' natu'u hawa' -na hi suro-na to napelihi-ramo toe.
26928	44	1	4	Rala-na hangkani, bula-na morumpu dohe-ra, nawai' -ra hawa' toi. Na'uli' -raka: "Neo' ulu nipalahii ngata Yerusalem. Popea ulu hi rei duu' -na Tuama-ku mpowai' -koi to najanci-mi, to ku'uli' -mikokoi mperi'ulu.
26929	44	1	5	Apa' Yohanes meniu' hante ue. Tapi' ba hangkuja eo-damo, raniu' -koi hante Inoha' Tomoroli'."
26930	44	1	6	 Hangkani wo'o, nto'u suro-na morumpu hangkaa-ngkania hante Yesus, mepekune' -ra hi Yesus, ra'uli': "Pue', ba tempo toi-mi nubahaka-ta ngkai bali' -ta pai' -ko jadi' Magau' to Israel?"
26931	44	1	7	Na'uli' Yesus: "Tuama-ku moto to mponoa' ba nto'uma kadupa' -na hawe'ea patuju to napakatantu-mi hante kuasa-na. Uma mingki' ni'inca koi'.
26932	44	1	8	Sampale-di, mporata-koi mpai' baraka' ane hompo-ipi Inoha' Tomoroli' hi koi'. Nto'u toe mpai', koi' jadi' sabi' -ku hi Yerusalem, hi tana' Yudea pai' Samaria, duu' rata hi humalili' dunia'."
26933	44	1	9	Ka'oti-na mololita hewa toe, kate'oo-ongkoa' -imi hilou hi langi'. Mengoa' -ramo mpongoa' -i, duu' -na uma-ipi rahiloi apa' naleru limu' -imi.
26934	44	1	10	Bula-ra mengoa' -pidi hi langi' mponaa pe'ongko' -na, ria ncorobaa rodua tomane moheai pohea to mengea' mokore hi ncori-ra.
26935	44	1	11	Ra'uli' to rodua toera: "Ee to Galilea! Napa pai' ntora mengoa' -koi hi langi'? Yesus to nihilo te'ongko' hilou hi suruga toei lou, wae wo'o-i mpai' nculii' tumai ngkai suruga hewa to nihilo-e we'i."
26936	44	1	12	 Ngkai ree, nculii' -ramo suro-na ngkai Bulu' Zaitun hilou hi Yerusalem. Bulu' Zaitun toe, ba hakilo kalaa-na ngkai Yerusalem.
26937	44	1	13	Karata-ra hi ngata, hilou-ramo hi tomi po'ohaa' -ra ngkahe' hilou hi kamar to hi lolo-na. Hanga' suro Pue' Yesus toera: Petrus, Yohanes, Yakobus pai' Andreas, Filipus pai' Tomas, Bartolomeus pai' Matius, Yakobus ana' Alfeus, Simon to Zelot, pai' Yudas ana' Yakobus.
26938	44	1	14	Hawe'ea-ra morumpu hangkaa-ngkania, pai' tida-ra mosampaya. Dohe-ra, ria wo'o ba hangkuja dua tobine, hante Maria tina-na Yesus pai' ompi' -ompi' -na Yesus.
26939	44	1	15	 Rala-na ha'eo, ria ba ha'atu rompulu' -ra morumpu. Nto'u toe, mokore-imi Petrus hi laintongo' ompi' hampepangalaa' -na toera, pai' -i mololita, na'uli':
26940	44	1	16	"Ompi' -ompi', napa to te'uki' hi rala Buku Tomoroli' kana madupa'. Owi hante wiwi Magau' Daud, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpolowa ami' -mi Yudas, to mpakeni tauna to mpohoko' Yesus.
26941	44	1	17	Yudas toei, doo-ta moto-i, pai' napo'ana'guru moto-i Pue' Yesus, hibalia hante kita'."
26942	44	1	18	(Yudas toei mpo'oli tana' hante doi to narata ngkai gau' -na to dada'a. Hi tana' to na'oli tohe'e, mate monawu' -i, mobenta ta'i tina-na, alaa-na ihi' rala-na malali omea.
26943	44	1	19	Hawe'ea pue' ngata Yerusalem mpo'inca omea to jadi' tohe'e. Toe pai' tana' tohe'e rahanga' hi rala basa-ra moto Hakal-Dama. Batua-na, Tana' Raa'.)
26944	44	1	20	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Petrus: "Hi rala Buku Rona' Daud, ria lolita to mpolowa Yudas. Hewa toi moni-na: `Pelele' moto-miki-hawo po'ohaa' -na wao'. Neo' ria ba haduaa to mpo'ohai'.' `Agina huraa-nae na'ala' kahadua-na.'"
26945	44	1	21	
26946	44	1	22	Ngkai ree, napokaliliu Petrus lolita-na, na'uli': "Ompi' -ompi', toe pai' kana ria hadua ngkai olo' -ta tapelihi jadi' sabi' mpodohei-kai mposabii' katuwu' -na nculii' -mi Pue' Yesus. Tauna to tapelihi toe, kana hadua to biasa ami' -mi dohe-ta nto'u-na Pue' Yesus mako' hilou hiapa-apa hante kita', ntepu'u ngkai pobago-na Yohanes Topeniu' duu' rata hi kara'ongko' -nami Pue' -ta ngkai laintongo' -ta."
26947	44	1	23	Ngkai ree, rodua tomane to ratudo'. Hanga' -na to hadua, Yusuf Barsabas, pai' to hadua Matias. (Yusuf toei, ria wo'o to mpohanga' -i Yustus.)
26948	44	1	24	
26949	44	1	25	Oti toe, mosampaya-ramo, ra'uli': "Pue', nu'inca omea nono tauna. Yudas, monawu' -imi-hana ngkai bago-na jadi' suro-nu, pai' -i rahuku' ntuku' -ki gau' -na. Toe pai' kiperapi' Pue', tudo' -kakai hema ngkai hira' to rodua tohe'ira to nupelihi-mi jadi' sampei-na."
26950	44	1	26	Oti-ramo mosampaya, ratene' -mi undi hewa pompenoa' -ra. To natudo' pompenoa' -ra toe, Matias. Jadi', ra'ongko' mpu'u-imi jadi' suro Pue' Yesus, bona hono' hampulu' rodua-ra hewa to lomo' -na.
26951	44	2	1	 Rata mpu'u-mi eo bohe to Yahudi to rahanga' Eo Pentakosta, hawe'ea topetuku' Yesus morumpu mopahantuda.
26952	44	2	2	Muu-mule' ra'epe to moni ngkai langi', hewa pewui ngolu' to bohe. Moni tohe'e ka'epea hobo' hi rala tomi porumpua-ra.
26953	44	2	3	Pai' rahilo-rawo anu to hewa apu to molence mpojila', ngkenele pai' dungku hi butu-butu dua-ra.
26954	44	2	4	Ngkai ree, nakuasai omea-ramo Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' ntepu'u-ramo mololita hante basa-basa to ko'ia ra'incai, ntuku' to napopolibu' -raka Inoha' Tomoroli'.
26955	44	2	5	 Nto'u toe wo'o-hawo, ria hi Yerusalem wori' to Yahudi ngkai ngata humalili' dunia'. Tauna tohe'era paka' to mengkoru hi Pue' Ala.
26956	44	2	6	Kampo'epe-ra moni to hewa ngolu' we'i, mo'iko-ramo tumai morumpu. Ingu' -ra, apa' hore-hore mpo'epe basa-ra moto to rapake' suro Pue' Yesus toera.
26957	44	2	7	Uma mowo kakonce-ra, ra'uli': "Napa-koiwo to jadi' tohe'i-e? Bo paka' to Galilea moto-ra to mololita toera.
26958	44	2	8	Hiaa' napa-di pai' ta'epe-ra mololita hi rala basa-ta moto?
26959	44	2	9	Kita' toi, wori' nyala basa-ta. Ria-ta ngkai tana' Partia, Media, Elam, ngkai Mesopotamia, Yudea pai' Kapadokia. Ria-ta to ngkai tana' Pontus pai' Asia,
26960	44	2	10	ngkai Frigia pai' Pamfilia, ngkai Mesir pai' ngkai tana' Libia to mohu' ngata Kirene. Ria-ta to rata ngkai ngata Roma.
26961	44	2	11	Hantongo' -ta to Yahudi, pai' ria wo'o tau ntani' -na to mesua' -mi hi agama Yahudi. Ria to tumai ngkai tana' Kreta pai' tana' Arab. Hawe'ea-ta himpau mpo'epe-ra mololita hi rala basa-ta moto, mpololita kajadia' bohe to nababehi Alata'ala."
26962	44	2	12	Konce pai' ingu' omea-ramo, pai' momepekune' -ra hadua pai' hadua, ra'uli': "Napa mpu'u-koiwo batua-na to hewa toi-e?"
26963	44	2	13	Aga ria wo'o-ra hantongo' to mepopo'ore', ra'uli': "Malangu-ra-hanale!"
26964	44	2	14	 Ngkai ree, mokore-imi Petrus hante doo-na to hampulu' hadua, pai' -i mpololitai tauna to wori'. Mololita-i napesukui, na'uli': "Ompi' -ompi' to Yahudi, pai' koi' omea to mo'oha' hi Yerusalem! Pe'epei lompe' -koi, apa' napa to majadi' tohe'i kupakanoto-kokoi.
26965	44	2	15	Kai' tohe'i-e, uma-kai malangu hewa to ni'uli', apa' ko'ia-hawo tempo ponginua. Lako' jaa sio mepulo.
26966	44	2	16	To jadi' tohe'i-e, kadupa' -na to nalowa ami' -mi Pue' Ala owi hante wiwi nabi Yoel, hewa toi moni-na:
26967	44	2	17	Na'uli' Alata'ala: `Nto'u kahudua dunia' mpai', Aku' mpewai' Inoha' -ku hi manusia' omea. Ana' -ni tomane pai' ana' -ni tobine mpohowa' mpai' lolita-ku. Kabilasa-ni mpohilo pangila to kupopohiloi-raka. Totu'a-ni mo'ompo' napa to kupopo'ompoi' -raka.
26968	44	2	18	Rata-rata hi batua-ku, tomane ba tobine, kuwai' -ra Inoha' -ku hi eo toe mpai', pai' -ra mpohowa' lolita-ku.
26969	44	2	19	Kupopohiloi-koi anu mekoncehi hi langi', pai' tanda mekoncehi hi wongko dunia' wo'o. Ria mpai' raa' pai' apu pai' rangahu to bue'.
26970	44	2	20	Mobengi mpai' eo, wula molei hewa raa', kako'ia-na rata Eo Pue', eo to bohe pai' to mobaraka' lia.
26971	44	2	21	Nto'u toe mpai', hema-hema to mekakae hi Pue' bate rahore ngkai huku' jeko' -ra.'"
26972	44	2	22	Oti toe, na'umpui' Petrus lolita-na, na'uli': "Ompi' -ompi' -ku to Israel! Pe'epei to ku'uli' -kokoi tohe'i. Yesus to Nazaret, Hi'a-mi to napelihi pai' napakatantu Alata'ala jadi' Magau' Topetolo'. Alata'ala mpopo'incai-koi Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo', apa' nawai' -i kuasa mpobabehi wori' tanda mekoncehi pai' anu mobaraka' pai' kajadia' bohe. Nihilo moto-mi hawe'ea toe ompi', pai' ni'inca kamakono-na.
26973	44	2	23	Yesus toe ratonu hi koi', pai' -i nipatehi, nitonu hi tauna to dada'a bona raparika'. Ntaa' to jadi' toe, bate ntuku' hawa' to napakatantu ami' -mi Alata'ala, apa' na'inca ami' napa to kana majadi'.
26974	44	2	24	Koi' mpopatehi Yesus, aga Alata'ala mpotuwu' nculii' -i, nabahaka-i ngkai kuasa kamatea, apa' bate uma-i ma'ala mate oa'.
26975	44	2	25	Apa' wae to na'uli' Magau' Daud owi mpolowa Yesus, hewa tohe'i: `Kuhilo, bate Pue' oa' to mpodoo-a. Uma kupoka'eka' ba apa-apa, apa' Pue' to mpotulungi-a.
26976	44	2	26	Toe pai' goe' lia nono-ku, pai' ntora ku'une' -ko Pue'. Rodo moto-a mpopea-ko.
26977	44	2	27	Apa' uma nupelele' kao' -ku tida hi po'ohaa' tomate, woto-ku uma nupelele' hi rala daeo' duu' -na pope, apa' Aku' batua-nu to nupelihi.
26978	44	2	28	Nutudo' -maka ohea mporata katuwua' to lompe'. Hono' lia mpai' kagoea' -ku, ane ria-apa mpai' dohe-nu.'"
26979	44	2	29	Ngkai ree, na'uli' wo'o-mi Petrus: "Ompi' -ompi' -ku, ma'ala ta'uli' hante kanoto-noto-na, bela woto-na moto to natoa' lolita Daud toe we'i. Apa' tuama-ta Daud, mate moto-i-hawo pai' -i ratana. Daeo' -na ria hi ngata-ta duu' tempo toi.
26980	44	2	30	
26981	44	2	31	Daud hadua nabi, pai' na'inca ami' napa to nababehi Alata'ala hi eo mpeno. Alata'ala mpobabehi janci-na hi Daud hante mosumpa, na'uli': hadua mpai' ngkai muli Daud na'ongko' jadi' magau' hewa Daud moto. Jadi', toe pai' Daud mpolowa ami' -mi katuwu' -na nculii' Magau' Topetolo', na'uli': uma-i rapelele' hi po'ohaa' tomate, pai' woto-na uma rapelele' hi rala daeo' duu' -na pope.
26982	44	2	32	"Yesus toe-mile to natoa' lolita Daud-e we'i. Apa' Hi'a-mi to napotuwu' nculii' Alata'ala-e. Kai' toi-mi to jadi' sabi' -na.
26983	44	2	33	Alata'ala to Tuama mpo'ongko' -imi, napopohura-i hi huraa karabilaa' hi mali ngka'ana-na, pai' nawai' -imi Inoha' Tomoroli'. Ngkai ree, Yesus mpohubui Inoha' Tomoroli' tumai hi kai', ntuku' janci-na Alata'ala. Jadi', napa to nihilo pai' to ni'epe-mi toe we'i lau, majadi' sabana kuasa Inoha' Tomoroli'.
26984	44	2	34	"Ompi' -ompi', bela-hawo Daud to ngkahe' hilou hi suruga. Tapi' ria lolita-na Daud to mpolowa kangkahe' -na Yesus hilou hi suruga, hewa toi moni-na: Pue' Ala mpo'uli' -ki Pue' -ku: `Mohura-moko hi mali ngka'ana-ku,
26985	44	2	35	duu' -na kupopengkoru hawe'ea bali' -nu hi Iko.'
26986	44	2	36	Jadi', toe pai' hawe'ea to Israel kana mpo'inca mpu'u-mpu'u: Yesus to niparika' -e, Hi'a toe-mi to napelihi Alata'ala jadi' Pue' pai' Magau' Topetolo'."
26987	44	2	37	 Kara'epe-na ntodea lolita Petrus toe, soho' -mi nono-ra, pai' mepekune' -ra hi Petrus pai' hi suro Pue' Yesus ntani' -na, ra'uli': "Ane wae, napa-mi-kaiwo to kana kibabehi?"
26988	44	2	38	Na'uli' Petrus: "Medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, pai' -koi raniu' butu-butu dua-ni jadi' topetuku' Yesus Kristus. Ngkai ree mpai', Alata'ala mpo'ampungi jeko' -ni, pai' nawai' -koi Inoha' Tomoroli'.
26989	44	2	39	Apa' Alata'ala mojanci kanawai' -nata Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' hi muli-muli-ta, duu' rata hi tauna to molaa. Pojanci Alata'ala toe, bate bagia hawe'ea tauna to nakio' Pue' -ta Pue' Ala jadi' topetuku' -na."
26990	44	2	40	Wori' nyala-pi lolita-na Petrus hi ntodea, naparesai' -ra pai' napopo'ingai' -ra, na'uli': "Medea-mokoi! Neo' -pi nituku' tauna to dada'a to tuwu' tempo toi, bona neo' -koi narata pehuku' Alata'ala to mporumpa' -ra mpai'!"
26991	44	2	41	Wori' -mi tauna to mpopangala' lolita Petrus, pai' -ra raniu' jadi' topetuku' Yesus. Hi eo toe, kawori' tauna to mepangala' hi Yesus, tetampai-mi kira-kira tolu ncobu.
26992	44	2	42	 Topetuku' Yesus to bo'u toera ntora mpopetudui' hi suro Pue' Yesus, pai' tida-ra morumpu hangkaa-ngkania. Ngkoni' -ra hangkaa-ngkania, mpopihe-pihe roti mpokiwoi kamate-na Pue' Yesus, pai' mosampaya wo'o-ra hangkaa-ngkania.
26993	44	2	43	Wori' anu mobaraka' pai' tanda mekoncehi to rababehi suro Pue' Yesus. Toe pai' me'eka' lia-ramo ntodea.
26994	44	2	44	Hintuwu' -ramo hawe'ea topepangala' hi Yesus. Rewa-ra raporewa hangkaa-ngkania.
26995	44	2	45	Ria-ra to mpobalu' ihi' tomi-ra, pai' doi oli-na rabagi-bagi hi doo-ra to nakakurai'.
26996	44	2	46	Butu eo-na morumpu-ra hi Tomi Alata'ala. Mpopihe-pihe-ra roti mpokiwoi kamate-na Pue' Yesus, pai' ngkoni' -ra hangkaa-ngkania hi rala tomi-ra hante goe' pai' karoli' -roli' nono-ra.
26997	44	2	47	Ntora mpo'une' -ra Alata'ala, pai' hawe'ea ntodea mpokagoe' -ra. Butu eo-na Pue' mpodonihii kawori' -ra; batua-na, butu eo-na kawoo-woria' tauna to mepangala' hi Pue' Yesus duu' -na tehore ngkai huku' jeko' -ra.
26998	44	3	1	 Rala-na ha'eo, Petrus pai' Yohanes hilou hi Tomi Alata'ala hi tempo posampaya to Yahudi, jaa tolu ncimonou'.
26999	44	3	2	Hi wobo' to rahanga' Wobo' Ncola, ria hadua tomane to pungku ngkai kaputu-na. Butu eo-na rakeni oa' -i-hawo hi wobo' toe bona ma'ala-i merapi' -rapi' hi tauna to hilou hi Tomi Alata'ala.
27000	44	3	3	Kampohilo-na Petrus pai' Yohanes mesua', kaliliu naperapii' -ra.
27001	44	3	4	Petrus pai' Yohanes mponaa topungku toei. Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki: "Penoto' -kai!"
27002	44	3	5	Nanaa mpu'u-ramo, apa' nasarumaka mporata-i doi ngkai hira'.
27003	44	3	6	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Petrus: "Uma mpu'u ria doi-ku. Aga napa to ria hi aku', toe to kuwai' -koko: Hante kuasa Yesus Kristus to Nazaret ku'uli', mako' -moko!"
27004	44	3	7	Ngkai ree, Petrus mpokamu pale ka'ana topungku toei bona mokore-i. Hangaa moroho-mi witi' -na.
27005	44	3	8	Hangkore-i-dile mokore-e, pai' -i momako' hilou tumai. Ngkai ree, mesua' -imi hi rala Tomi Alata'ala dohe Petrus pai' Yohanes, momako' pai' mohajo-hajo mpo'une' Alata'ala.
27006	44	3	9	Wori' tauna mpohilo-i momako' pai' mpo'une' Alata'ala,
27007	44	3	10	pai' ra'inca kahi'a-nami topungku to ntora merapi' hi Wobo' Ncola butu eo-na. Uma mowo kakonce-ra pai' ka'ingu' -ra mpohilo to jadi' toe-e.
27008	44	3	11	Jadi', topungku to lako' rapaka'uri' toei mpotuku' oa' -ra Petrus pai' Yohanes. Karata-ra hi pengkawinaraa to rahanga' Pengkawinaraa Salomo, wori' tauna tumai morumpu ngkarumangkai-ra, apa' konce-ra.
27009	44	3	12	 Kanahilo-na Petrus tauna to wori' toera, na'uli' -raka: "Ompi' -ompi' -ku to Israel! Napa pai' konce-koi mpohilo to jadi' tohe'i-e? Napa to ntora nikamata-kakai? Ba ni'uli' -koina, pai' -i momako' tauna toei-e, apa' ria baraka' -kai, ba ngkai kamoroli' nono-kai? Uma-hawoe'!
27010	44	3	13	Alata'ala to rapue' ntu'a-ta owi, to napue' Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub, Alata'ala toe-imi to mpomobohe Batua-na, Hi'a-mi Yesus. Yesus toei to nitonu hi topoparenta-e, pai' to nisapuaka hi Pilatus, nto'u Pilatus ke mpobahaka-i.
27011	44	3	14	Moroli' pai' monoa' -i-hana, hiaa' nisapuaka-i, pai' niperapi' hi Pilatus bona nabahaka-kokoi hadua topepatehi.
27012	44	3	15	Nipatehi mpu'u-imi Yesus. Tapi' Alata'ala mpotuwu' -i nculii', apa' lawi' Yesus-mi to mpowai' katuwua' to lompe'. Kai' toi-mi sabi' -na, apa' kihilo mata-mi-kaina katuwu' -na nculii'.
27013	44	3	16	Baraka' ngkai hanga' Yesus toe-mi to mpakaroho witi' -na topungku toei-e. Jadi', tauna to nihilo pai' to ni'inca toi, jadi' mo'uri' sabana pepangala' -na hi Yesus. Ngkai pepangala' hi Yesus, toe pai' mo'uri' -imi hewa to nihilo moto-mi.
27014	44	3	17	"Ompi' -ompi', koi' moto-mi hante pangkeni-ta to mpopatehi Yesus-e. Aga ku'inca moto, napa to nibabehi tetu, nibabehi ngkai ka'uma-na-hawo ni'incai kalaua-na.
27015	44	3	18	Aga nau' wae, ngkai napa to nibabehi tetu, madupa' -mi napa to na'uli' Alata'ala owi hante wiwi hawe'ea nabi, to mpo'uli': Magau' Topetolo' kana mporata kaparia.
27016	44	3	19	
27017	44	3	20	Toe-mi ompi' -ompi', medea-mokoi ngkai jeko' -ni, pai' -koi mengkoru hi Pue' Ala, bona na'ampungi jeko' -ni. Ngkai ree mpai', Pue' Ala mporohoi nono-ni, pai' nahubui tumai Yesus hi kita'. Apa' Hi'a-mi to napakatantu ami' Alata'ala jadi' Magau' Topetolo' -ta.
27018	44	3	21	Tempo toi, Yesus mo'oha' hi suruga, pai' bate tida-i hi ria, duu' -na rata mpai' tempo-na Alata'ala mpobo'ui omea, hewa to na'uli' hante wiwi nabi-nabi-na to moroli' owi.
27019	44	3	22	"Ompi' -ompi', ria lolita nabi Musa owi to mpolowa Pue' Yesus, hewa toi moni-na: `Pue' Ala mpai' mpo'ongko' hadua ngkai ompi' -ni moto jadi' nabi, hewa aku' toi. Koi' kana mpotuku' napa to na'uli' -kokoi nabi toei.
27020	44	3	23	Hema to uma mpotuku' napa to na'uli' nabi toei, uma-i rapohibilai' ntodea Alata'ala, kana rahuku' mate-i.'
27021	44	3	24	Nabi-nabi to mpokeni Lolita Pue' owi, ntepu'u ngkai nabi Samuel duu' rata hi nabi-nabi to rata ngkabokoa' ngkai Samuel, hawe'ea-ra mpolowa to jadi' tempo toi.
27022	44	3	25	Koi' -mile ompi' to mporata rasi' to najanci Alata'ala owi hante wiwi nabi-nabi toe-e. Koi' -mi to mporata rasi' ngkai pojanci Alata'ala hi ntu'a-ta owi. Apa' owi Alata'ala mpo'uli' -ki Abraham hewa toi: `Ngkai muli-nu mpai', kugane' hawe'ea tauna hi dunia'.' Hi koi' -mile ompi' kadupaa' -na pojanci toe-e!
27023	44	3	26	Jadi' ompi' -ompi', toe pai' Alata'ala mpotuwu' nculii' Yesus Batua-na, pai' nahubui-i tumai lomo' -lomo' -na hi kita' to Yahudi, bona mpogane' -ta. Pompogane' -na toe, mpomedea-ta ngkai kehi-ta to dada'a."
27024	44	4	1	 Bula-ra Petrus pai' Yohanes mololita-pidi mpololitai ntodea hi Tomi Alata'ala, rata ba hangkuja dua imam pai' to Saduki hante kapala' polisi Tomi Alata'ala, tumai mpohirua' -raka.
27025	44	4	2	To Saduki, uma-rana raparasaya katuwu' -ra nculii' mpai' tauna to mate. Toe pai' moroe lia-ra mpo'epe Petrus pai' Yohanes mpotudui' ntodea katuwu' -na nculii' Yesus. Apa' tudui' -ra toe mpakanoto katuwu' -ra nculii' tauna tomate.
27026	44	4	3	Toe pai' rahoko' -ramo suro to rodua toera, pai' rapopesua' hi rala tarungku'. Apa' neo' mobengi-mi, toe pai' rapotuhu hi ree-ramo ulu, duu' kamepulo-na.
27027	44	4	4	Aga tauna to mpo'epe lolita-ra Petrus pai' Yohanes hi Tomi Alata'ala we'i, wori' -ramo to mepangala' hi Yesus, alaa-na katedoo-donihia lau-mi kawori' topetuku' -na Yesus, duu' -na lima ncobu-ramo.
27028	44	4	5	 Kamepulo-na, topohura agama, pangkeni to Yahudi pai' guru agama, morumpu omea-ra hi Yerusalem.
27029	44	4	6	Porumpu-ra toe, hante Imam Bohe Hanas, pai' hante Kayafas, Yohanes, Aleksander pai' hante ompi' -ompi' Imam Bohe ntani' -na.
27030	44	4	7	Ria-ramo omea, rapehubui-mi bona Petrus pai' Yohanes rakeni mponyanyo-ra. Karata-ra hi ree, mepekune' -ramo topohura toera mpekune' Petrus pai' Yohanes, ra'uli': "Ngkaiapa kuasa-ni mpaka'uri' topungku tetui? Hema to mpowai' -koi kuasa tetu?"
27031	44	4	8	Nto'u toe, Petrus nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' -i mololita, na'uli': "Tuama-tuama pangkeni ntodea pai' topohura agama!
27032	44	4	9	Hewa toe lau niparesa' -kai, apa' mpotulungi-kai tauna to pungku toi-e, doko' ni'inca beiwa-kai mpaka'uri' -i.
27033	44	4	10	Jadi', bona ni'inca pai' bona hawe'ea to Israel mpo'inca, tau toii mo'uri' pai' mokore hi rehe'i ngkai kuasa Yesus Kristus to Nazaret. Yesus toei niparika', tapi' Alata'ala mpotuwu' -i nculii'.
27034	44	4	11	Hi'a toe-imi to natoa' lolita Buku Tomoroli' to mpo'uli' hewa toi: `Watu to nitadi koi' topowangu tomi, watu toe lau-mi to jadi' poko parawatu.'
27035	44	4	12	Uma ria ohea ntani' -na mporata kalompea' ngkai Alata'ala, muntu' Yesus-wadi. Apa' hi humalili' dunia', uma ria haduaa tau ntani' -na, muntu' Yesus-wadi to naparia Alata'ala hi manusia', Hi'a-wadi to mokuasa mpohore-ta ngkai huku' jeko' -ta."
27036	44	4	13	Konce topohura toera mpo'epe Petrus pai' Yohanes mololita hante uma ria kakoo-koroa' -ra, apa' Petrus pai' Yohanes toera, tau biasa-ra-wadi to uma mosikola molangko. Pai' rapelence-ra, kahira' -nami wengi tauna to mpotuku' Yesus.
27037	44	4	14	Aga topohura toera, uma-ra daho' mebaro. Apa' topungku to rapaka'uri' toei, ria wo'o-i-hawo hi ree mokore dohe-ra Petrus pai' Yohanes.
27038	44	4	15	 Toe pai' rapopalai-ra ulu suro Pue' Yesus toera ngkai porumpua-ra, pai' -ra mohawa',
27039	44	4	16	ra'uli': "Tapopai-ramo to rodua toera? Apa' hawe'ea tauna hi Yerusalem mpo'inca kahira' -na to mpobabehi tanda mekoncehi to bohe toe. Hiaa' uma wo'o ma'ala tasapu.
27040	44	4	17	Aga bona neo' hobo' tauna mpo'epe tudui' -ra, agina ta'ekahi-ra pai' tatagi-ra bona neo' -pi rajojo mpotudui' hema-hema mpokahangai' Yesus."
27041	44	4	18	Jadi' oti toe, rakio' nculii' wo'o-ramo Petrus pai' Yohanes mesua', pai' ra'uli' -raka: "Kitagi mpu'u-koie', neo' -pi metudui' ba mpokahangai' hanga' Yesus!"
27042	44	4	19	Ra'uli' Petrus pai' Yohanes: "Pekiri moto-koi, to'uma to napokono Alata'ala: mpotuku' hawa' -ni koi', ba mpotuku' hawa' Alata'ala-di.
27043	44	4	20	Ane kai' -kaina, uma ma'ala kipento'oi mpololita napa to kihilo pai' to ki'epe-mi."
27044	44	4	21	Ngkai ree, hangkedi' kamoroe-ra topohura toera mpokaroe Petrus pai' Yohanes. Tapi' ka'omea-na rabahaka moto-ra, apa' uma ria ohea mpohuku' -ra. Apa' hawe'ea ntodea mpo'une' Alata'ala sabana tanda mekoncehi to rababehi toe.
27045	44	4	22	Apa' tauna to rapaka'uri' toei, umuru-na opo' mpulu' mpae labi-mi.
27046	44	4	23	 Ka'oti-na Petrus pai' Yohanes rabahaka, hilou-ramo mpohirua' -raka doo-ra, pai' ralolita napa to ra'uli' -raka imam pangkeni pai' pangkeni to Yahudi ntani' -na.
27047	44	4	24	Kara'epe-na doo-ra lolita tohe'e, mekakae-ramo hangkaa-ngkania hi Alata'ala, ra'uli': "Pue', Iko to mpajadi' langi', dunia' pai' tahi' hante hawe'ea ihi' -na.
27048	44	4	25	Iko to mpopolibu' ntu'a-kai owi, Magau' Daud. Apa' Daud batua-nu, pai' bula-na nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli', lolita-na mpolowa ami' -mi pe'ewa hawe'ea tauna mpo'ewa Pue' Yesus. Na'uli' hewa toi: `Napa-di pai' moroe rahi-ra tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi-e? Pai' napa wo'o-di pai' ntodea mohawa' doko' mpo'ewa Pue' Ala? Uma ria tuju-na hawa' -ra toe.
27049	44	4	26	Magau' -magau' hi dunia', ngasa' -ramo. Pai' hawe'ea topohawa', hintuwu' -ra doko' mpo'ewa Pue' Ala pai' Magau' Topetolo' to napelihi-mi.'
27050	44	4	27	O Pue', lolita Daud tohe'e madupa' mpu'u-mi. Apa' hi rala ngata toi wengi, hintuwu' mpu'u-ramo Magau' Herodes Antipas pai' Pontius Pilatus, hante ntodea to Yahudi pai' tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi wo'o. Kahintuwua' -ra toe, doko' mpo'ewa Yesus, Batua-nu to Moroli' to nupelihi jadi' Magau' Topetolo'.
27051	44	4	28	Mohawa' -ra toe, mpopatehi Yesus. Ntaa' to rababehi toe mpopadupa' napa to oti nupakatantu ami' -midi! Hawe'ea tohe'e madupa' -mi ntuku' kuasa pai' konoa-nu moto Pue'.
27052	44	4	29	"Wae lau Pue', epe-mi libu' -ra mpongasai' -kai! Toe pai' merapi' -makai hi Pue', kai' batua-nu tohe'i, wai' -kai karohoa bona daho' -kai mpohowa' Lolita-nu.
27053	44	4	30	Popohiloi-ra kuasa-nu Pue', bona tauna to mohaki' ma'ala kipaka'uri', pai' tanda mekoncehi pai' anu mobaraka' ma'ala kibabehi hante kuasa Yesus, Batua-nu to Moroli'."
27054	44	4	31	Ka'oti-ra mosampaya hewa toe, kamoduja-nami tomi porumpua-ra, pai' hawe'ea-ra nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli'. Ngkai ree, daho' mpu'u-ramo mpoparata Lolita Alata'ala hi ntodea.
27055	44	4	32	 Hawe'ea topepangala' hi Yesus, tuwu' hintuwu' pai' hanono lau-ra-damo. Uma ria haduaa to mpo'uli': "Tohe'i anu-ku moto-kuwo." Hawe'ea to ria hi hira' rapodulua hangkaa-ngkania.
27056	44	4	33	Suro Pue' Yesus ntora mpo'uli' posabi' -ra katuwu' -na nculii' Pue' Yesus, pai' uma mowo kamobaraka' -na lolita-ra. Pai' Alata'ala mpogane' -ra omea hante pegane' to bohe lia.
27057	44	4	34	Uma ria haduaa topetuku' Yesus to nakakurai'. Apa' pontu-na, ria-ra to mpobalu' tana' -ra ba tomi-ra,
27058	44	4	35	pai' doi oli-na rakeni hilou ratonu hi suro Pue' Yesus. Doi tohe'e rabagi hi hema-hema to ria kaparaluua-na.
27059	44	4	36	
27060	44	4	37	Wae wo'o-hawo to nababehi Yusuf. Napobalu' tana' -na, pai' doi oli tana' -na natonu-raka suro Pue' Yesus. Yusuf toei hadua to Lewi ngkai tana' Siprus. Suro Pue' Yesus mpohanga' wo'o-i Barnabas. Batua-na: to mporohoi nono.
27061	44	5	1	 Ria wo'o hadua tomane, hanga' -na Ananias, hante tobine-na to rahanga' Safira. Ananias toei, mpobalu' wo'o-i-hawo tana' -na.
27062	44	5	2	Hantongo' doi oli tana' -na toe natonu hi suro Pue' Yesus, na'uli': "Oi-mi omea doi oli tana' -ku." Ntaa' natimamahi moto-di-hana hantongo' -e. Babehia-na toe, kahibaliaa-ra hira' hancamoko.
27063	44	5	3	Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki Ananias: "Napa-di-kona pai' nupelele' Magau' Anudaa' mpokuasai nono-nue, doko' mpakawa' Inoha' Tomoroli' -e? Nu'uli' doi oli tana' -nu nutonu omea-mi, ntaa' nutimamahi moto-di-kona hantongo' -e!
27064	44	5	4	Kako'ia-na nupobalu' tana' tetu, iko moto-kowo pue' -na. Pai' ka'oti-na wo'o nupobalu', oli-na bate-na iko moto-kowo pue' -na. Jadi', napa-di pai' ria patuju nono-nu mpobabehi hewa tetu-e? Bela kai' toi to nupakawa'. Alata'ala-hana to nupakawa'!"
27065	44	5	5	Kana'epe-na Ananias lolita Petrus toe, modungka ncorobaa-imi kaliliu mate. Hawe'ea tauna to mpo'epe to jadi' toe, uma mowo eka' -ra.
27066	44	5	6	Ngkai ree, ba hangkuja dua tomane mpoputu' woto-na Ananias, pai' rakeni hilou ratana.
27067	44	5	7	Ba ria nte tolu jaa ngkai ree, rata wo'o-imi-hawo tobine-na Ananias hi Petrus. Aga uma-hawo na'incai napa to jadi' we'i.
27068	44	5	8	Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki: "Uli' -ka pe', tana' -ni to nipobalu' -e, ba tohe'i omea mpu'u-mi oli-nae?" Na'uli' Safira: "Io', tetu mpu'u-mi omea."
27069	44	5	9	Na'uli' Petrus: "Napa pai' hibalia nono-ni koi' hancamoko, doko' mpemai-mai roe-na Inoha' Pue'? Hilo-dile! Tauna to lako' oti mpotana tomane-nuele, etu-ramo hi wobo'. Iko wo'o mpai' rakeni hilou ratana."
27070	44	5	10	Kana'epe-na lolita Petrus toe, kamodungka-na wo'o-mi-hawo kaliliu mate. Karata-ra tauna to muli' mpotana Ananias, rahilo-rawo mate wo'o-imi-hawo tobine-na. Kara'ongko' -na wo'o-mi-hawo hilou ratana ncori daeo' tomane-na.
27071	44	5	11	Ngkai ree, hawe'ea topepangala' hi Pue' Yesus to mo'oha' hi ree pai' tau ntani' -na wo'o, me'eka' lia-ramo mpo'epe to jadi' toe.
27072	44	5	12	 Wori' tanda mekoncehi pai' anu mobaraka' to rababehi suro Pue' Yesus hi mata ntodea. Hawe'ea tauna to mepangala' hi Pue' Yesus, hanono lau-ra-damo morumpu hi Pengkawinaraa Salomo to hi Tomi Alata'ala.
27073	44	5	13	Tauna to uma mepangala' hi Yesus, uma-ra daho' morumpu dohe-ra. Aga nau' wae, hawe'ea topepangala' rabila' ntodea.
27074	44	5	14	Kahaa-haea kawoo-woria' tauna to mepangala' hi Pue' Yesus, lompe' tomane lompe' tobine.
27075	44	5	15	Wori' tanda mekoncehi to rababehi suro Pue' Yesus, alaa-na wori' topeda' rakeni ntali ali' -ra, rapopoturu hi wiwi' ohea. Apa' rasarumaka ane liu-ipi mpai' Petrus hi ree, nau' ba kampa' kao' -na bela hi woto-ra, mo'uri' -ra.
27076	44	5	16	Jadi', mo'iko-ra-damo tauna ngkai ngata-ngata to mohu', hilou hi ngata Yerusalem mpokeni ompi' -ra to peda' pai' tauna to napesuai' seta. Hawe'ea-ra rapaka'uri'.
27077	44	5	17	 Nto'u toe, Imam Bohe hante doo-doo-na to mpotuku' tudui' to Saduki, mohingi' -ramo hi suro Pue' Yesus. Toe pai' ratepu'u-mi mpobalinai' -ra.
27078	44	5	18	Suro Pue' Yesus toera rahoko' pai' rapotuhu hi rala tarungku' ngata.
27079	44	5	19	Ngkabengia toe, hadua mala'eka Pue' mpobea wobo' tarungku' pai' nakeni-ra hilou hi mali-na. Na'uli' mala'eka toei mpo'uli' -raka:
27080	44	5	20	"Hilou-mokoi mokore hi Tomi Alata'ala, mpoparata hi ntodea hawe'ea lolita to mpowai' katuwua' to bo'u tetu."
27081	44	5	21	Jadi', mepupulo ngkii, hilou mpu'u-ramo hi Tomi Alata'ala pai' -ra mpotudui' ntodea. Nto'u toe wo'o, Imam Bohe pai' doo-na mpokio' hawe'ea pangkeni to Yahudi morumpu mpobabehi porumpua bohe agama Yahudi. Ria-ramo omea, ra'uli' mpo'uli' -raka topobago-ra: "Hilou-mokoi hi tarungku' mpo'ala' suro Pue' Yesus toera ria, pai' keni-ra tumai."
27082	44	5	22	Hilou mpu'u-ramo to rapahawa' toera. Ntaa' karata-ra hi tarungku', uma-rapa ria raratai. Nculii' -ramo hilou hi topohura, ra'uli':
27083	44	5	23	"Kihilo-kaiwo wobo' tarungku' bate-na moto tehohoki piri. Pai' polisi topojaga bate-ra moto mpojaga wobo'. Kibea-kaiwo wobo', uma ria haduaa tauna kiratai hi rala-na!"
27084	44	5	24	Kara'epe-na toe, ingu' -ramo kapala' polisi Tomi Alata'ala hante imam pangkeni, ba napa to jadi' hi suro toera. Pai' koro' wo'o-ra, ba napa-di mpai' to jadi'.
27085	44	5	25	Ngkai ree, rata hadua tauna mpo'uli' -raka: "Epe-koi pe'! Tauna to nitarungku' -ele ngone, oe moto-ra-hana ria, mpotudui' ntodea hi Tomi Alata'ala!"
27086	44	5	26	 Kahilou-rami kapala' polisi hante doo-na hi Tomi Alata'ala, mpo'ala' -ra suro toera. Aga uma-ra raweba', rapelompehi mpu'u mpobawai-ra, apa' me'eka' -ra hi ntodea, nee-neo' mpai' hira' lau to rakahurui, alaa-na ntodea mpopana' -ra hante watu.
27087	44	5	27	Jadi', rakeni-ramo suro toera hilou pai' -ra rabua' hi topohura. Imam Bohe mpoparesa' -ra, na'uli':
27088	44	5	28	"Kitaa-tagi-mokoi wengi, neo' -pi metudui' mpokahangai' hanga' -na Yesus. Hilo pe' to nibabehi-e! Hobo' lau-mi ihi' ngata Yerusalem mpo'epe tudui' -ni tetu! Ba kai' lau-mi to nirai' to masala' hi karapatehi-na tau tetui."
27089	44	5	29	Ratompoi' Petrus hante suro Pue' Yesus ntani' -na, ra'uli': "Kai' bate-na mpotuku' hawa' Alata'ala, bela hawa' manusia'.
27090	44	5	30	Yesus toe-e nipatehi-i-koina, nipaku' hi kaju parika'. Aga Alata'ala to rapue' ntu'a-ta owi mpotuwu' nculii' -imi
27091	44	5	31	pai' na'ongko' -imi napopohura hi mali ngka'ana-na, pai' napajadi' -i Pangkeni pai' Magau' Tompohore-ta ngkai huku' jeko' -ta, bona kita' to Israel medea ngkai jeko' -ta pai' mporata ampu.
27092	44	5	32	Kai' toi-mi to mposabii' hawe'ea toe, kai' hante Inoha' Tomoroli' wo'o to napewai' Alata'ala hi hema-hema to mengkoru hi hawa' -na."
27093	44	5	33	Kara'epe-na topohura lolita-ra toe, gigi-mi nono-ra, pai' doko' rapatehi-ra.
27094	44	5	34	Tapi' ria hadua ngkai olo' -ra to rahanga' Gamaliel. Gamaliel toei, hadua to Parisi pai' guru agama to rabila' hawe'ea tauna. Mokore-imi mpohubui tauna ngkeni-ra suro toera hilou hi mali-na hampai'.
27095	44	5	35	Oti toe, pai' na'uli' -raka topohura: "Ompi' -ompi' -ku to Israel! Penonoi lompe' -koi, ba napa to doko' nibabehi hi tauna tohe'i-era.
27096	44	5	36	Apa' ba hangkuja mpae to liu, ria hadua tomane to rahanga' Teudas. Mpo'uli' -i, hi'a tauna to mobaraka'. Wori' tauna mpotuku' -i, ba ria-ra nte opo' atu. Tapi' ka'omea-na mate rapatehi moto-i, pai' topetuku' -na pagaa' -gaa' -ramo, alaa-na uma-pi kaliliu patuju-ra.
27097	44	5	37	Hangkani wo'o, nto'u sensus, ria wo'o hadua to Galilea, hanga' -na Yudas. Hi'a wo'o mpakeni wori' tauna mpo'ewa topoparenta. Aga rapatehi wo'o-i-hawo, pai' topetuku' -na pagaa' -gaa' wo'o-wadi.
27098	44	5	38	Jadi' ompi' -ompi', toi-ka lolita-ku: neo' tapopai-pai topetuku' Yesus toera lou. Pelele' moto-ra-rawo. Apa' ane ngkai manusia' wadi-hawo tudui' pai' patuju-ra, mogero moto-hawo mpai'.
27099	44	5	39	Tapi' ane ngkai Alata'ala mpu'u-di tudui' -rae, uma-rale ma'ala tadagi-e. Apa' ane hewa toe-ko-koina, lence-na mpo'ewa Alata'ala lau-tamo." Jadi', lolita Gamaliel toe ratarima mpu'u-mi topohura.
27100	44	5	40	Ngkai ree, rakio' nculii' -ramo suro Pue' Yesus, pai' -ra raweba'. Ra'uli' -raka: "Neo' -pi nitudui' tauna mpokahangai' hanga' Yesus!" Pai' oti toe, rabahaka-ramo.
27101	44	5	41	Malai-ramo suro toera ngkai porumpua. Goe' -ra, ra'uli': "Marasi' -ta apa' Alata'ala mpopelihi-ta bona rabalinai' pai' raruge' sabana petuku' -ta hi Yesus."
27102	44	5	42	Butu eo-na hi Tomi Alata'ala ba hi tomi ntani' -na, uma ria kaputua-ra mpotudui' tauna Kareba Lompe', Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo'.
27103	44	6	1	 Kahaa-haea kawoo-woria' -mi tauna to mpotuku' Yesus. Lomo' -lomo' -na, topetuku' Yesus paka' to Yahudi. Aga to hantongo' -ra mobasa Yunani, pai' to hantongo' wo'o mobasa Yahudi moto-ra. Nto'u toe, ngkunuti-ramo topetuku' Yesus to mobasa Yunani, mpongkunutii doo-ra to mobasa Yahudi, ra'uli': "Tobine-kai to balu, uma raratai bagia to rabagi butu eo-na hi to mpe'ahii'."
27104	44	6	2	Toe pai' suro Pue' Yesus to hampulu' rodua mpokio' hawe'ea topetuku' Yesus bona morumpu, pai' ra'uli' -raka: "Uma-hawo lompe' ane kai' mpo'urusi pompobagi koni', apa' uma mpai' hono' loga-kai mpokeni Lolita Alata'ala.
27105	44	6	3	Jadi' ompi' -ompi', agina tapelihi ngkai laintongo' -ta tau pitu to lompe' po'ingku-ra, to nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli' pai' to monoto nono-ra, bona hira' -mi to kiwai' bago mpo'urusi kara-kara pongkoni' toe.
27106	44	6	4	Apa' pobago-kai kai' to poko-na mpu'u, mosampaya pai' mpokeni Lolita Alata'ala."
27107	44	6	5	Lolita suro toera rapo'io' -mi omea. Toe pai' mpopelihi-ramo Stefanus, to mepangala' mpu'u hi Pue' Yesus pai' to nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli'. Rapelihi wo'o: Filipus, Prokhorus, Nikanor, Timon, Parmenas pai' Nikolaus to Antiokhia. Nikolaus toei, bela-i to Yahudi, aga mesua' -imi hi agama Yahudi.
27108	44	6	6	To pitu toera rakeni hilou hi suro Pue' Yesus, pai' suro toera mpojama woo' -ra pai' mosampaya merapi' bona Pue' mpogane' -ra.
27109	44	6	7	Jadi', ngkai toe-mi pai' kawoo-woria' tauna to mpo'epe Lolita Alata'ala. Pai' katedoo-donihia-mi kawori' topetuku' Yesus hi Yerusalem. Imam-imam moto wo'o, wori' -ramo to mepangala' pai' mengkoru hi Pue' Yesus.
27110	44	6	8	 Ane Stefanus, Alata'ala mpogane' mpu'u-i, nawai' -i kuasa mpobabehi wori' tanda mekoncehi to mpopohiloi kabaraka' -na Alata'ala hi ntodea.
27111	44	6	9	Aga ria wo'o-ra to mposapuaka. Tomesapuaka toera, anggota tomi posampayaa to rahanga' Tomi Libertini (batua-na: tomi tauna to rabahaka ngkai karapobatuaa-ra). Anggota tomi posampayaa toe, to Yahudi to ngkai ngata Kirene pai' Aleksandria. Hira' toe hante to Yahudi ngkai tana' Kilikia pai' Asia mpomehono' -ki Stefanus.
27112	44	6	10	Aga uma-ra hompe mpotompoi' lolita Stefanus, apa' Inoha' Pue' Ala mpowai' -i kanotoa nono mololita.
27113	44	6	11	Toe pai' ba hangkuja dua tauna rawai' doi, bona hira' mpobabehi lolita boa' mpobalihi Stefanus, ra'uli': "Ki'epe-i-kaina mporuge' Atura Musa pai' mpokedi' Alata'ala!"
27114	44	6	12	Ngkai ree, mpo'ukei' -ra ntodea hante pangkeni to Yahudi pai' guru agama, bona moroe-ra hi Stefanus. Kahilou-rami mpohoko' -i pai' rakeni hi topohura agama.
27115	44	6	13	Karata-ra hi ree, rapope'onga wo'o-ramo-rawo to tungkai' mosabi' boa'. Ra'uli' sabi' boa' toera: "Tau tohe'ii ntora mporuge' Tomi Alata'ala pai' mporuge' Atura Musa!
27116	44	6	14	Ki'epe-i mololita mpo'uli': Yesus to Nazaret toe mpogero mpai' Tomi Alata'ala pai' mpobalii' hawe'ea ada to tapososora ngkai nabi Musa."
27117	44	6	15	Mpo'epe toe, hawe'ea topohura mponaa Stefanus. Rahilo-rawo, lio-na hewa lio mala'eka.
27118	44	7	1	 Mepekune' Imam Bohe hi Stefanus, na'uli': "Makono mpu'u hewa to ra'uli' bali' -nu toera-e?"
27119	44	7	2	Na'uli' Stefanus: "Ompi' -ompi', tuama-tuama! Pe'epei-ka-kuwo ulu lolita-ku! Owi, nto'u ntu'a-ta Abraham hi tana' Mesopotamia-pidi, kako'ia-na mentoli tumai hi ngata Haran, Alata'ala to bohe kabaraka' -na mehupa' hi ntu'a-ta toei,
27120	44	7	3	na'uli' -ki: `Palahii ngata-nu pai' ompi' -nu. Hilou-ko hi ngata to kutudo' -koko mpai'.'
27121	44	7	4	Toe pai' napalahii mpu'u-mi tana' -ra to Kasdim tumai hi ngata Haran. Hi ngata Haran toe, tuama-na Abraham mate-mi. Pai' oti toe, Alata'ala mpopentoli wo'o-imi Abraham tumai hi tana' tohe'i, to tapo'ohai' -mi tempo toi-e.
27122	44	7	5	Nto'u toe, Alata'ala uma mpowai' tana' toi hi Abraham, nau' hampotomia. Sampale-di, Alata'ala mojanci hi Abraham, na'uli': `Tana' tohe'i mpai' kuwai' -koko, duu' rata hi muli-muli-nu.' Hiaa' nto'u toe, ko'ia-hawo ria ana' -na.
27123	44	7	6	Aga Alata'ala mpo'uli' -ki Abraham hewa toi: `Muli-nu mpai' mesowo' hi ngata doo. Pue' ngata toera mpai' mpobatua-ra pai' mpobalinai' -ra hante makanca rala-na opo' atu mpae.
27124	44	7	7	Tapi' oti toe, Aku' moto mpohuku' pue' ngata to mpobatua muli-nu toera, pai' lako' malai-rada ngkai tana' tetu, tumai mpopue' -a hi tana' tohe'i.' Wae-mi lolita-na Alata'ala hi Abraham.
27125	44	7	8	Oti toe, Alata'ala mpobabehi pojanci posidaia' -na hante Abraham, pai' nahubui bona Abraham pai' hawe'ea muli-na ratini'. Ada petini' toe jadi' tanda pojanci-na Alata'ala hante muli Abraham. Jadi', putu mpu'u-mi ana' Abraham to rahanga' Ishak, natini' -imi hi eo kawalu-na. Oti toe wo'o-hawo, Ishak mpotini' Yakub ana' -na. Pai' Yakub mpotini' ana' -na to hampulu' rodua. Pai' hira' toe-mi to jadi' ntu'a-ta kita' to Yahudi.
27126	44	7	9	"Ntu'a-ta toera mohingi' hi Yusuf ompi' -ra, alaa-na rapobalu' -i pai' -i rapobatua hi tana' Mesir. Aga Alata'ala mpodohei-i,
27127	44	7	10	pai' ka'omea-na nabahaka-imi ngkai hawe'ea kaparia-na. Nawai' -i kapantea to mpokagoe' nono Firaun, magau' hi tana' Mesir, alaa-na Firaun mpo'ongko' -i jadi' gubernur tana' Mesir pai' jadi' topohawa' hi rala tomi-na.
27128	44	7	11	Ngkai ree, rata-mi oro' bohe hobo' hi tana' Mesir pai' tana' Kanaan. Rata-mi oro' bohe toe, wori' tauna to ntodohaka, pai' ntu'a-ta wo'o uma-pi ria pongkoni' -ra.
27129	44	7	12	Ngkai ree, na'epe Yakub, ria-hana pae rapobalu' hi Mesir. Toe pai' nahubui-ramo ana' -ana' -na, ntu'a-ta toera-e, hilou hi Mesir. Tohe'e pomako' -ra to lomo' -na hilou hi Mesir.
27130	44	7	13	Kahilou-ra karongkani-na, nalohu-miraka Yusuf kahi'a-nami ompi' -ra. Nto'u toe lako' na'inca-di Firaun kahema-ra ompi' -na Yusuf.
27131	44	7	14	Oti toe, Yusuf mpakatu kareba hilou hi Yakub tuama-na, mpo'uli' -ki bona hira' hantinaa mentoli hilou hi tana' Mesir. Kawori' tauna to mentoli hilou hi Mesir toe, pitu mpulu' lima.
27132	44	7	15	Jadi', mentoli mpu'u-imi Yakub hi tana' Mesir, pai' tida hi ria duu' -na mate. Wae wo'o hawe'ea ana' -na.
27133	44	7	16	Aga wuku-ra rakeni nculii' moto tumai hi ngata Sikhem pai' ratana hi rala daeo' to na'oli Abraham ngkai muli Hemor hante doi pera'.
27134	44	7	17	 "Mahaa-hae ngkai ree, neo' rata-mi tempo-na Alata'ala mpopadupa' pojanci-na hi Abraham. Momuli-muli-ramo ntu'a-ta hi tana' Mesir, duu' -na wori' lia-ramo.
27135	44	7	18	Ka'omea-na, ria magau' to moparenta hi Mesir, to uma mpokiwoi kahema-na Yusuf.
27136	44	7	19	Magau' toei mposapai ntu'a-ta owi pai' nabalinai' -ra. Nahubui-ra mpotadi ana'lei-ra bona mate.
27137	44	7	20	Nto'u toe, putu-imi-hawo Musa. Musa toei, hadua ana' to subo' lia. Tolu mula-i-wadi rapodoo rala tomi totu'a-na, pai' -i ratadi.
27138	44	7	21	Hi karatadi-na toe, ana' toronaa Firaun mpotima' -i, pai' napodoo naponcawa ana' -na moto-mi.
27139	44	7	22	Jadi', Musa rapoposikola hi hawe'ea kapantea to Mesir, pai' alaa-na mokuasa mpu'u-i hi pololita-na pai' hi pongkale-na.
27140	44	7	23	"Kahono' -na opo' mpulu' mpae-mi umuru-na Musa, ria patuju-na doko' mpencuai' hingka ompi' -na muli Israel.
27141	44	7	24	Karata-na hi ria, mpohilo-i hadua to Israel naweba' hadua to Mesir. Kahilou-nami mpehawa-ki ompi' -na, mpopatehi to Mesir toei.
27142	44	7	25	Na'ulia' -hana Musa, ra'inca moto ompi' -na kahi'a-nami to napopale Alata'ala mpobahaka-ra ngkai karapobatuaa-ra. Ntaa' uma-di ra'incai.
27143	44	7	26	"Kamepulo-na, nahilo wo'o rodua to motuda', paka' to Israel. Jadi', apa' doko' napopohintuwu' -ra, toe pai' na'uli' -miraka: `Napa pai' motuda' moto-mokoi, koi' ntali ompi'?'
27144	44	7	27	Tapi' to hadua to mpoweba' -mi doo-na mpotulaka Musa pai' na'uli' -ki: `Hema to mpo'ongko' -ko jadi' pangkeni to mpobotuhi kara-kara-kai?
27145	44	7	28	Ba doko' mpopatehi aku' wo'o-moko, hewa kampopatehi-nu to Mesir wengi-e?'
27146	44	7	29	Kana'epe-na Musa telohu-mi kehi-na toe, metibo' -imi ngkai tana' Mesir hilou tida hi tana' Midian. Hi ria-i motobinei, pai' -i mo'anai' rodua.
27147	44	7	30	 "Opo' mpulu' mpae ngkai ree, mehupa' hadua mala'eka mpohirua' -ki Musa hi tana' to wao' mohu' Bulu' Sinai. Mala'eka toe mehupa' hi rala julumpu to jela'.
27148	44	7	31	Konce-i Musa mpohilo toe, toe pai' hilou namohui' doko' na'inca ba napa-i-hawo. Nto'u toe, na'epe lolita Pue' to mpo'uli':
27149	44	7	32	`Aku' -mi Alata'ala to rapue' ntu'a-nu. Aku' -mi Alata'ala to napue' Abraham, Ishak pai' Yakub.' Mpo'epe toe, moridi' -imi Musa nakeni eka' -na, pai' uma-ipi daho' mponaa julumpu to jela' toe.
27150	44	7	33	Na'uli' wo'o-mi Pue' mpo'uli' -ki: `Roncu sapatu' -nu, apa' tana' to nupokorei tetu-e, tana' to moroli'.
27151	44	7	34	Kuhilo mpu'u-mi kapai' tuwu' -ra ntodea-ku to Israel hi Mesir. Ku'epe-mi pontodohaka-ra. Toe pai' hompo-ama tumai doko' mpobahaka-ra. Jadi', tumai-ko, kuhubui-ko hilou hi tana' Mesir, bona mpobahaka-ra to Israel.' Toe-mi lolita-na Pue' Alata'ala hi Musa.
27152	44	7	35	"Jadi', Musa to rasapuaka to Israel wengi, hi'a lau-mi to nahubui Alata'ala hilou mpobahaka-ra. Lomo' -na rasapuaka-i, ra'uli': `Hema to mpo'ongko' -ko jadi' pangkeni to mpobotuhi kara-kara-kai?' Hiaa' hi'a mpu'u-mi to nakio' Alata'ala hante wiwi mala'eka to mpololitai-i ngkai rala julumpu. Hi'a mpu'u-mi to na'ongko' Alata'ala jadi' pangkeni to mpobahaka-ra.
27153	44	7	36	Musa toe-mile to mpakeni-ra malai ngkai tana' Mesir. Hi'a-mi to mpobabehi anu mobaraka' pai' tanda mekoncehi hi Mesir, hi Tahi' Molei pai' hi tana' to wao' rala-na opo' mpulu' mpae.
27154	44	7	37	Musa toe wo'o-mi to mpo'uli' -raka to Israel owi hewa toi: `Alata'ala mpai' mpo'ongko' hadua ngkai ompi' -ni jadi' nabi hewa aku' toi.'
27155	44	7	38	Musa toe-mile to mpodoo-ra ntodea to Israel hi tana' to wao' -e. Hi'a-mi to mpo'epe lolita mala'eka to mpololitai-i hi lolo Bulu' Sinai, pai' -i jadi' tauntongo' to mpoparata lolita toe hi ntu'a-ta owi. Hi'a to mpotarima ngkai Pue' Ala lolita to tuwu' to raparata-taka duu' tempo toi-e.
27156	44	7	39	"Aga ntu'a-ta owi, uma-ra-rana dota mengkoru hi Musa. Rasapuaka-i jadi' pangkeni-ra. Doko' nculii' lau-ramo hilou hi tana' Mesir.
27157	44	7	40	Ra'uli' mpo'uli' -ki Harun: `Babehi-taka pinotau to ma'ala tapue', bona pinotau tetu-damo to mpokeni-ta. Apa' uma-pi ki'incai napa to jadi' hi Musa tetui to mpakeni-ta malai ngkai Mesir.'
27158	44	7	41	Ngkai ree, rababehi mpu'u-mi lence ana' japi ngkai bulawa. Rapue' -mi lence to rababehi tetu, rasumale' -ki porewua, pai' mosusa' -ramo mpo'une' babehia pale-ra moto.
27159	44	7	42	 Toe pai' Alata'ala mpalahii-ra, napelele' -ra mpopue' betue' hi langi'. Apa' ria Lolita Pue' Ala to te'uki' hi rala sura nabi-nabi, hewa toi moni-na: `Ee to Israel! Bula-ni hi tana' to wao' rala-na opo' mpulu' mpae, mposumale' -koi porewua jadi' pepue' -ni. Aga bela hi Aku' pepue' -ni tetu.
27160	44	7	43	Mepue' -koi hi pue' to rahanga' Molokh, pai' tomi-na nikeni-keni oa' dohe-ni. Mepue' wo'o-koi hi pinotau to molence betue' Refan. Lence-lence toe-mi to nibabehi bona nipue'. Toe pai' kupelele' moto-koi mpai' ratawani, pai' rakeni hilou duu' rata hi mali ria ngata Babel.'
27161	44	7	44	"Bula-ra ntu'a-ta owi hi tana' to wao', Pue' Ala mpohubui Musa mpobabehi kemah jadi' tomi pepuea' -ra. Kemah toe jadi' tanda karia-na Alata'ala hi laintongo' to Yahudi, pai' rababehi ntuku' lence to napopohiloi Pue' Ala hi Musa. Jadi', kemah pepuea' toe rakeni oa' ntu'a-ta owi bula-ra hi tana' to wao'.
27162	44	7	45	Mahaa-hae ngkai ree, mate-ramo ntu'a-ta hi tana' to wao' toe. Pai' ana' -ra mpokeni kemah pepuea' -ra toe mesua' hi tana' Kanaan toi. Nto'u toe, Alata'ala mpopalai pue' ngata Kanaan, pai' Yosua mpakeni-ra to Israel mpema'ala tana' to tapo'ohai' -mi toi-e. Jadi' kemah pepuea' toe, ria-pidi hi laintongo' to Israel owi, duu' rata hi tempo-na Magau' Daud.
27163	44	7	46	Daud tohe'e mpakagoe' nono Pue' Ala. Mekakae-i hi Pue' Ala, na'uli': `O Alata'ala to napue' Yakub owi, kuperapi' bona nupiliu-a mpowangu tomi po'ohaa' -nu.'
27164	44	7	47	Aga uma napiliu-i. Ana' -na-damo mpai' to rahanga' Salomo to mpowangu Tomi Alata'ala.
27165	44	7	48	"Tapi' kakoo-kono-na, Alata'ala uma-i-hana mo'oha' hi tomi to nababehi manusia'. Apa' meliu kabaraka' -na ngkai hawe'ea to rapue'. Ria hadua nabi owi to mpo'uli' hewa toi:
27166	44	7	49	Na'uli' Pue' Ala: `Langi' pohuraa-ku, pai' dunia' pentodua-ku. Ha tomi napa-i mpai' to doko' niwangu-kae? Hiapa mpai' to natao jadi' tomi katidaa-kue?
27167	44	7	50	Hiaa' bo Aku' -di to mpajadi' hawe'ea-nae!' Wae-mi Lolita Pue'."
27168	44	7	51	 Na'uli' wo'o-mi Stefanus mpo'uli' -raka totu'a to Yahudi: "Uma mowo katu'a maga-ni ompi'! Uma mowo kamengkabatu-ni! Uma mowo kamengkawongo-ni mpe'epei Lolita Pue' Ala! Bate hibalia hante ntu'a-ta owi-koi, mposapuaka oa' Inoha' Tomoroli'.
27169	44	7	52	Uma ria haduaa nabi to uma rabalinai' ntu'a-ni owi. Rapatehi-ra suro-suro Alata'ala owi to mpo'uli' karia-na mpai' Batua Alata'ala to monoa', Hi'a-mi Yesus. Hiaa' hewa toe lau, koi' -mi to mpobalu' Batua Alata'ala toei hi bali' -na. Koi' to mpopatehi-i!
27170	44	7	53	Koi' to mpotarima Atura Pue' Ala to raparata mala'eka hi ntu'a-ta, aga uma nituku'."
27171	44	7	54	 Kara'epe-na topohura toera lolita Stefanus, gigi-mi nono-ra, pai' ngkuku' maga-ramo.
27172	44	7	55	Ngkai ree, Stefanus nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli', pai' -i mengoa' hi langi'. Nahilo-mi baraka' -na Alata'ala, pai' nahilo wo'o Yesus mokore hi mali ngka'ana Alata'ala.
27173	44	7	56	Na'uli' Stefanus: "Hilo-dile! Kuhilo langi' mobea pai' Ana' Manusia' mokore hi mali ngka'ana Alata'ala!"
27174	44	7	57	Ngkai ree, topohura agama toera mpo'ompo tilinga-ra, pai' -ra mejeu' mpesukui bona neo' -pi ra'epei lolita Stefanus. Karaperapai-nami, rahoko' -i,
27175	44	7	58	pai' -i radii' hilou hi mali ngata bona rapatehi-i rapana' hante watu. Sabi' boa' to mpobalihi Stefanus mporoncu baju-ra bona lompe' pepana' -ra. Baju-ra toe rawai' -ki hadua tomane to rahanga' Saulus bona nadongo-raka.
27176	44	7	59	Bula-na Stefanus rapana', mekakae-imi, na'uli': "Pue' Yesus, doa-mi kao' -ku!"
27177	44	7	60	Oti toe, mowingkotu' -i pai' na'uli' napesukui: "Pue', neo' -ra nuhuku' ngkai jeko' -ra toi." Ka'oti-na mololita hewa toe, mate-imi.
27178	44	8	1	 Saulus wo'o-hawo mpokagoe' karapatehi-na Stefanus toe.
27179	44	8	2	Tauna to mengkoru hi Alata'ala mpo'ala' woto-na Stefanus, rapotantangii' hante nono mpu'u, pai' -i ratana.
27180	44	8	3	Hiaa' Saulus-hana, ngasa' mpu'u-i mpobalinai' tauna to mepangala' hi Pue' Yesus. Butu-butu ntomi-na napesua', pai' hema-hema to mepangala' hi Yesus, lompe' tomane lompe' tobine, nahoko' nadii' hilou hi mali-na pai' natonu hi topoparenta bona ratarungku'.
27181	44	8	4	 Jadi', topetuku' Yesus to metibo' ngkai Yerusalem toera, hiapa kahiloua-ra raparata oa' Lolita Pue'.
27182	44	8	5	Wae wo'o-hawo Filipus hilou hi ngata hi tana' Samaria, mpoparata-raka Kareba Lompe' Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo'.
27183	44	8	6	Nababehi wo'o tanda mekoncehi hi ria. Wae kara'epe-na to Samaria lolita Filipus toe, pai' karahilo-na tanda mekoncehi to nababehi, ratarima-mi kareba to nakeni hante nono-ra mpu'u.
27184	44	8	7	Apa' napopalai seta ngkai wori' tauna to rapesuai', alaa-na me'au-au-ramo tauna toera pai' malai mpu'u-mi seta to mpesuai' -ra. Pai' napaka'uri' wo'o wori' tauna topungku pai' tokejo.
27185	44	8	8	Toe pai' goe' lia-ramo to Samaria toera mpotarima Filipus.
27186	44	8	9	Hi rala ngata toe, ria hadua tomane to rahanga' Simon. Simon toei hadua topobali'mata. Mahae-imi mpopehuwu pake' -na to rapokakonce to Samaria. Mpo'uli' -i, hi'a tauna to bohe baraka' -na.
27187	44	8	10	Hi hi'a-damo nono hawe'ea ihi' ngata, lompe' maradika lompe' ntodea, ra'uli': "Simon toei, ria-ki-hana baraka' -na ngkai Alata'ala to rahanga' Kabaraka' Bohe."
27188	44	8	11	Mahae-imi mpakakonce-ra hante pake' -na, duu' -na hawe'ea pue' ngata toe mpotuku' -i pai' mpe'epei hawa' -na.
27189	44	8	12	Aga karata-na Filipus hi ngata-ra, natudui' -ra Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo', pai' natudui' -ra mepangala' hi Yesus bona jadi' ntodea-na Alata'ala hi rala Kamagaua' -na. Jadi', wori' -ramo pue' ngata mepangala' hi Yesus pai' mpopeniu' jadi' topetuku' Yesus, lompe' tomane lompe' tobine.
27190	44	8	13	Ngkai ree, Simon wo'o-hawo mepangala', pai' -i raniu'. Oti-i raniu', metuku' oa' -imi hi Filipus, apa' konce-i mpohilo tanda to mekoncehi pai' tanda baraka' to jadi'.
27191	44	8	14	 Suro Pue' Yesus to hi Yerusalem mpo'epe napa to jadi' hi Samaria, apa' ria to mpo'uli' -raka: "To Samaria toera ria, mpotarima Lolita Alata'ala wo'o-ramo-rawo." Toe pai' mohawa' -ra mpahawa' Petrus pai' Yohanes hilou hi ria.
27192	44	8	15	Karata-ra Petrus pai' Yohanes hi ria, mosampaya-ramo mpekakae-raka to Samaria to mepangala' -mi hi Pue' Yesus, bona Pue' mpowai' -ra Inoha' Tomoroli'.
27193	44	8	16	Apa' ko'ia-ra nakahompoi Inoha' Tomoroli'. Muntu' raniu' -ra mpokahangai' hanga' Pue' Yesus.
27194	44	8	17	Yohanes pai' Petrus mosampaya pai' -ra mpojama to Samaria toera. Jadi', mporata mpu'u-ramo Inoha' Tomoroli'.
27195	44	8	18	Nahilo-hawo Simon, hema-hema to rajama suro Pue' Yesus toera, mporata mpu'u-ramo Inoha' Tomoroli'. Toe pai' Simon mpokeni doi-na hilou hi Petrus pai' Yohanes,
27196	44	8	19	pai' na'uli' -raka: "Wai' -a-kuwo kuasa-ni tetu, bona hema-hema wo'o-kuwo to kujama, mporata-ra Inoha' Tomoroli'."
27197	44	8	20	Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki: "Harala ratadi-dako hi rala naraka, ntali doi-nu wo'o! Ha nu'uli' -kona, pewai' Alata'ala ma'ala ra'oli hante doi?
27198	44	8	21	Uma ria huraa-nu mobago dohe-kai, apa' uma monoa' nono-nu hi poncilo Alata'ala.
27199	44	8	22	Medea-moko ngkai jeko' -nu tetu-e, pai' merapi' hi Pue' bona na'ampungi patuju nono-nu to dada'a.
27200	44	8	23	Apa' ku'inca mohingi' lia-ko, pai' napobatua jeko' -moko."
27201	44	8	24	Na'uli' Simon mpo'uli' -raka Petrus pai' Yohanes: "Perapi' -ka-kuwo hi Pue' bona neo' -a mpai' narumpa' silaka to ni'uli' tetu-e we'i!"
27202	44	8	25	Jadi', kahudu-rami Petrus pai' Yohanes mpoparata Lolita Pue' pai' mporohoi nono-ra to Samaria, nculii' -ramo hilou hi Yerusalem. Hi pomakoa' -ra toe, raparata wo'o Lolita Pue' hi rala wori' ngata hi tana' Samaria.
27203	44	8	26	 Rala-na hangkani, hadua mala'eka Pue' mpololitai Filipus, na'uli': "Hilou-moko tono' hi selatan, hi ohea to ngkai Yerusalem rata hi Gaza." (Ohea tohe'e uma-pi jau ratara.)
27204	44	8	27	
27205	44	8	28	Hilou mpu'u-imi Filipus. Nto'u toe, ria wo'o-hawo hadua to Etiopia to ntara ohea toe nculii' hilou hi ngata-na. To Etiopia toei, tauna to mopangka' bohe, to mpokakamu hawe'ea ihi' tomi raja bine tana' Etiopia to rahanga' Kandake. Ka'oti-na mepue' hi Alata'ala hi Yerusalem, nculii' -imi hi ngata-na mpohawi' kereta to nadii' jara'. Bula-na mohura hi rala kereta-na, mpobasa-i sura nabi Yesaya.
27206	44	8	29	Inoha' Pue' Ala mpololitai Filipus, na'uli': "Hilou-ko mpomohui' kereta toe mai."
27207	44	8	30	Pokeno-nami Filipus hilou mpomohui' kereta toe. Na'epe-hawo, tauna toei mpobasa sura nabi Yesaya. Filipus mpekune' -i, na'uli': "Nu'inca wa batua-na to nubasa tetu-e?"
27208	44	8	31	Na'uli' tau toei: "Beiwa-kona kaku'inca-na, apa' uma ria tauna to mponotohi-ka." Ngkai ree, nabawai Filipus ngkahe' hi rala kereta-na pai' mohura hi ncori-na.
27209	44	8	32	Lolita to nabasa hi rala sura nabi Yesaya, hewa toi moni-na: Hi'a hewa hama'a bima to radii' hilou rasumale'. Hewa ana' bima to uma mobee' ane ragunci wulu-na, wae wo'o uma-i mololita nau' hamelaa.
27210	44	8	33	Raruge' -i pai' rahuku', hiaa' uma ria sala' -na. Uma ria haduaa tauna to mpotutura karia muli-na apa' rapatehi-i-hana."
27211	44	8	34	Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi to Etiopia toei hi Filipus: "Uli' -ka ba hema-i to natoa' nabi toei, ba woto-na moto-di ba tau ntani' -nadi."
27212	44	8	35	Jadi', ntepu'u ngkai pobasa-na toe we'i, Filipus mpakanoto-ki Kareba Lompe' Yesus.
27213	44	8	36	Bula-ra mokereta toe, mpohilo-ra ue hi wiwi' ohea. Na'uli' to Etiopia toei mpo'uli' -ki Filipus: "Hilo, ohe'e mai ue. Niu' -ama-kuwo jadi' topetuku' Yesus." ((
27214	44	8	37	Na'uli' Filipus: "Ane nupangala' mpu'u-imi, ma'ala moto-ko kuniu'." Na'uli' to Etiopia toei: "Kupangala' Yesus Kristus, Hi'a-mi Ana' Alata'ala."))
27215	44	8	38	Ngkai ree, napopento'o-mi kereta-na, pai' -ra mehompo hilou hi rala ue, pai' Filipus mponiu' -i.
27216	44	8	39	Pencore-ra ngkai rala ue, muu-mule' Inoha' Pue' Ala mpo'ala' Filipus ngkai ree, alaa-na to Etiopia toei uma-pi mpohiloi-i ba hiapa-imi. Napokaliliu pomako' -na hante nono to goe'.
27217	44	8	40	Ane Filipus-hawo, muu-mule' mehupa' -imi hi ngata Asdod. Me'ongko' -imi hilou hi ngata Kaisarea, pai' halengko ohea mpoparata-i Kareba Lompe' hi butu-butu ngata to natara.
27218	44	9	1	 Nto'u toe wo'o, ngasa' oa' -imi Saulus mpongasai' pai' mpopatehi topetuku' Pue' Yesus. Hilou-i hi Imam Bohe,
27219	44	9	2	pai' -i mperapi' sura kuasa nakeni hilou hi pangkeni tomi posampayaa hi ngata Damsyik, bona ane ria-ra narata to mpotuku' Tudui' Yesus, nahoko' pai' nakeni-ra nculii' hi Yerusalem, ba tomane ba tobine.
27220	44	9	3	Jadi', pomako' -na hilou hi Damsyik tohe'e, mohu' -imi hi ngata, muu-mule' mehini ncorobaa baja ngkai langi' mpotipuhi-i.
27221	44	9	4	Kamodungka-nami pai' na'epe-hawo topololita to mpo'uli' -ki: "Saulus! Saulus! Napa pai' nubalinai' -a?"
27222	44	9	5	Na'uli' Saulus: "Ha hema-ko Pue'?" Na'uli' topololita toei: "Aku' -mile Yesus, to nubalinai' -e!
27223	44	9	6	Wae-pi, memata-moko, mesua' hi rala ngata. Hi ria-damo mpai' ra'uli' -koko napa to kana nubabehi."
27224	44	9	7	Ane doo-doo Saulus toera, uma-rapa tepololita, kuyu-ramo nakeni eka' -ra. Apa' ra'epe moto wo'o-rawo topololita toe, aga uma rahiloi hema-i to mololita.
27225	44	9	8	Ngkai ree, mokore-imi Saulus mpobini' mata-na, aga uma-ipi pehilo. Jadi', ratete' -i-damo hilou hi rala ngata Damsyik.
27226	44	9	9	Tolu eo kahae-na bate uma-i pehilo, pai' uma wo'o-i ngkoni' ba nginu.
27227	44	9	10	 Hi ngata Damsyik toe, ria hadua topetuku' Yesus, Ananias hanga' -na. Nto'u toe, mopangila-i. Hi rala pangila-na toe, Pue' Yesus mpokio' -i, na'uli': "Ananias!" Na'uli' Ananias: "Oi-a Pue'."
27228	44	9	11	Na'uli' Pue': "Me'ongko' -moko hilou hi ohea to rahanga' Ohea Monoa', hi tomi-na Yudas. Pekune' hi pue' tomi ba ria to Tarsus to rahanga' Saulus. Saulus toei bula-na mosampaya,
27229	44	9	12	pai' hi rala pangila-na nahilo-ko, Ananias. Nahilo-ko hilou mpohirua' -ki pai' mpojama-i bona pehilo nculii' -imi."
27230	44	9	13	Na'uli' Ananias: "Pue', wori' tauna to mpotompo'wiwi Saulus tetui. Wori' pebalinai' -na hi topetuku' -nu to hi Yerusalem.
27231	44	9	14	Hiaa' tumai wo'o-imi hi rehe'i, hante kuasa ngkai imam pangkeni, bona mpohoko' hawe'ea tauna to mekakae hi Iko Pue'."
27232	44	9	15	Na'uli' Pue' mpo'uli' -ki Ananias: "Bate hilou-ko! Apa' Saulus toei ria, tungkai' kupelihi jadi' topobago-ku. Hi'a mpai' to mpoparata hanga' -ku hi to Yahudi pai' hi tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi, duu' hi magau' wo'o.
27233	44	9	16	Ku'uli' moto-ki mpai' kaparia to kana natodohaka sabana petuku' -na hi Aku'."
27234	44	9	17	Jadi', hilou mpu'u-imi Ananias hi tomi to na'uli' Pue' we'i. Karata-na hi ria, najama-i Saulus, na'uli' -ki: "Ompi' -ku Saulus! Pue' Yesus to nuhilo hi lengko ohea katumai-nu toi-e, Hi'a-mi to mpohubui-a tumai mpokinomo-ko. Nahubui-a tumai bona pehilo nculii' -moko, pai' -ko nakuasai Inoha' Tomoroli'."
27235	44	9	18	Nto'u toe, ria to hewa ruke uru molepa' ngkai mata Saulus, pai' pehilo mpu'u-imi. Pokore-nami Saulus, pai' -i raniu' jadi' topetuku' Pue' Yesus.
27236	44	9	19	Oti toe, ngkoni' -imi pai' moroho nculii' -imi.
27237	44	9	20	Bula-na hi Damsyik toe, hilou oa' -i hi tomi-tomi posampayaa to Yahudi hi Damsyik, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Yesus, Hi'a-mi Ana' Alata'ala."
27238	44	9	21	Konce omea-ra to mpo'epe lolita-na, ra'uli': "Ha beiwa-mi-koiwo tohe'i-e? Apa' hi'a toe-mi wengi to mpopatehi tauna to mepue' hi Yesus hi Yerusalem. Pai' patuju-na tumai tetu-e, bona mpohoko' wo'o-ra to hi rehe'i pai' mpokeni-ra hi imam pangkeni hi Yerusalem bona rahuku'."
27239	44	9	22	Aga kaboo-bohea baraka' -na Saulus metudui', napakanoto Kayesus-na Magau' Topetolo'. Jadi', to Yahudi hi Damsyik, uma-pi rakulei' mpobaro-i.
27240	44	9	23	 Ba hangkuja kahae-na ngkai ree, mohawa' -ramo to Yahudi mpopatehi Saulus.
27241	44	9	24	Pohawa' -ra toe, mpodongo hawe'ea wobo' wala ngata, lompe' hi eo-na lompe' hi bengi-na, bona ane liu-ipi mpai', rapatehi-imi. Ntaa' na'inca-di Saulus patuju-ra tohe'e-e.
27242	44	9	25	Jadi', apa' hawe'ea wobo' radongo, Saulus kana mpali' akala-na bona ma'ala-i metibo' ngkai ngata. Toe pai' rala-na hamengi, ba hangkuja dua ana'guru-na Saulus mpokeni-i hilou hi wala tana' to mpotololiki ngata Damsyik, rapopohura-i hi rala karanci, pai' -i ra'ulu hi rala karanci toe ngkai lolo wala tana' hilou hi mali ngata, pai' kaliliu metibo' -imi.
27243	44	9	26	Nculii' -imi Saulus hilou hi Yerusalem. Karata-na hi ria, doko' napobale-miraka topetuku' Yesus, aga rapoka'eka' -i, apa' ko'ia rapangalai' kametuku' -na mpu'u-mi hi Yesus.
27244	44	9	27	Aga Barnabas-hana, hilou-i mpobale-ki Saulus, pai' napo'ema' -imi hilou hi suro Pue' Yesus. Natutura-raka beiwa Saulus mpohilo Pue' Yesus hi lengko ohea kahilou-na hi Damsyik, pai' beiwa Pue' mpololitai-i. Nalolita wo'o-raka kabia' -na Saulus mpokarebai kareba Pue' Yesus hi Damsyik.
27245	44	9	28	Ngkai ree, hampodooa-ramo Saulus hante topetuku' Yesus hi Yerusalem, pai' modao' -i hobo' ngata mpoparata kareba Pue' Yesus hante uma ria kakoroa' -na.
27246	44	9	29	Biasa wo'o-i momewai' ngkalolita pai' momehono' hante to Yahudi to mobasa Yunani. Toe pai' to Yahudi toera doko' mpopatehi-i.
27247	44	9	30	Jadi', kara'inca-na ompi' -ompi' hampepangalaa' -na karia-ra to doko' mpopatehi-i, rabawa-imi hilou hi ngata Kaisarea. Ngkai Kaisarea toe, rapope'ongko' -imi hilou hi ngata Tarsus.
27248	44	9	31	Jadi', nto'u toe uma-pi ria kakoroa' -ra hawe'ea topepangala' hi Pue' Yesus to hi tana' Yudea, Galilea pai' Samaria. Kawoo-woria' tauna to mepangala' hi Yesus pai' kamoroo-rohoa pepangala' -ra. Apa' mengkoru mpu'u-ra hi Pue' Ala, pai' Inoha' Tomoroli' moto to mporohoi nono-ra.
27249	44	9	32	 Petrus modao' mpencuai' topepangala' hi Pue' Yesus hiapa-apa. Rala-na ha'eo, rata-i hi ngata Lida.
27250	44	9	33	Hi ngata Lida toe, mpohirua' -ki hadua tomane, hanga' -na Eneas. Eneas toei walu mpae-imi pungku, uma-i tepemata ngkai poturua-na.
27251	44	9	34	Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -ki: "Eneas, Yesus Kristus mpaka'uri' -ko! Mokore-moko, pai' lulu-mi ali' -nu." Hinto'u toe mpu'u, mokore-imi Eneas.
27252	44	9	35	Hawe'ea tauna hi ngata Lida pai' hi Saron mpohilo kamo'uri' -nami, pai' mepangala' -ramo hi Pue' Yesus.
27253	44	9	36	 Uma molaa ngkai Lida toe, ria wo'o ngata to rahanga' Yope. Hi Yope toe, ria hadua tobine to mepangala' hi Yesus, Tabita hanga' -na. Hi rala basa Yunani hanga' -na Dorkas (batua-na: ruha). Lompe' po'ingku-na, pai' wori' petulungia-na hi tauna to mpe'ahii'.
27254	44	9	37	Nto'u Petrus hi Lida, peda' danca Dorkas toei, kaliliu mate. Ka'oti-na raniu', ratu'u-i hi kamar to hi lolo-na.
27255	44	9	38	Topetuku' Yesus hi Yope mpo'epe karia-na Petrus hi Lida, apa' ngata Yope toe mohu' -wadi hi Lida. Toe pai' rahubui rodua tauna hilou hi Petrus, merapi' bona napesahui tumai hi Yope.
27256	44	9	39	Metuku' mpu'u-imi Petrus hilou dohe-ra. Karata-ra hi Yope, kaliliu rapo'ema' -i hilou hi powataa tomate. Hawe'ea tobine tobalu mpotipuhi Petrus. Geo' -ra pai' rapopohiloi-i baju pai' pohea to nadau-raka Dorkas bula-na tuwu' -pidi.
27257	44	9	40	Ngkai ree, Petrus mpohubui-ra omea mpalahii kamar toe, pai' powilingkudu-nami mosampaya. Ka'oti-na mosampaya, pai' -i mponyanyohi tomate, na'uli' -ki: "Tabita, memata-moko!" Hangaa mobini' mpu'u-mi mata-na mponaa Petrus, pai' kaliliu mohura-imi.
27258	44	9	41	Petrus mpokakamu pale-na pai' mpo'ore' -i duu' -na mokore. Oti toe, nakio' nculii' -ramo topetuku' Yesus pai' tobalu to nahubui malai-e we'i, pai' na'uli' -raka: "Ohe'i-imi bale-ni, tuwu' nculii' -imi."
27259	44	9	42	Kajadia' toe rajarita hobo' hi ngata Yope, alaa-na wori' tauna mepangala' hi Pue' Yesus.
27260	44	9	43	Oti toe, Petrus tida hi Yope ba hangkuja mengi-pidi kahae-na, mo'oha' hi tomi hadua topobago rewa kuliba to rahanga' Simon.
27261	44	10	1	 Hi ngata Kaisarea, ria hadua tomane, hanga' -na Kornelius. Kornelius tohe'ei, pangka' -na kapitee to mpohawai' ha'atu tantara to Roma hi rala hampo'emaa' to rahanga' "Tantara Italia."
27262	44	10	2	Bela-i to Yahudi, aga mengkoru mpu'u-i hi Pue' Ala, pai' hira' hantinaa-ra mepue' hi Alata'ala. Wori' doi nawai' -raka to Yahudi to kabu, pai' tida-i mosampaya hi Alata'ala.
27263	44	10	3	Rala-na ha'eo, ba jaa tolu libe eo wae, mopangila-i Kornelius. Hi rala pangila-na toe, monoto lia nahilo hadua mala'eka Pue' mehupa' pai' mpokio' -i, na'uli': "Kornelius!"
27264	44	10	4	Me'eka' -i Kornelius mponaa mala'eka toei. Metompoi' -i: "Napa-die Pue'?" Na'uli' mala'eka toei: "Goe' -i Alata'ala mpo'epe posampaya-nu, pai' na'inca kamanara-nu mpotulungi tokabu.
27265	44	10	5	Wae-pi, hubui tauna hilou hi Yope mpali' hadua tauna to rahanga' Simon Petrus, pai' kio' -i tumai.
27266	44	10	6	Po'ohaa' -na mohu' hi wiwi' tahi', hi tomi hadua topobago rewa kuliba, Simon wo'o hanga' -na."
27267	44	10	7	Kamalai-na mala'eka to mpololitai-i toe, Kornelius mpokio' rodua pahawaa' -na pai' hadua tantara sarumakaa-na. Tantara sarumakaa-na toe, to mengkoru wo'o-i-hawo hi Pue' Ala.
27268	44	10	8	Kornelius mpo'uli' -raka napa to lako' nahilo we'i hi rala pangila-na, pai' nahubui-ra hilou hi Yope mpopali' Petrus.
27269	44	10	9	 Kamepulo-na, bula-ra hi lengko ohea-pidi to rahubui toera, kamohu' -ra hi Yope, Petrus wo'o-hawo ngkahe' hilou hi pengkawinaraa to hi lolo tomi to molempe ata' -na, hilou mosampaya.
27270	44	10	10	Neo' tebua' -mi eo-na, mo'oro' -imi doko' ngkoni'. Jadi', bula-na mpeka'au kataha' koni', muu-mule' ria pangila-na.
27271	44	10	11	Hi rala pangila-na toe, mpohilo-i langi' tebea pai' ria to hewa kumu' to mowela' ratoe hi opo' huno-na pai' ra'ulu tumai hi tana'.
27272	44	10	12	Hi rala kumu' to ra'ulu toe, mparanyalaa binata, ria omea: to opo' witi' -na, to menyolo, hante danci wo'o.
27273	44	10	13	Oti toe, na'epe Petrus ria to mpololitai-i, na'uli' -ki: "Ee Petrus! Mai-moko, sumale' -ramo binata toera lau, pai' nukoni'."
27274	44	10	14	Na'uli' Petrus: "Uma-e' Pue'! Ko'ia ria kukoni' to rapalii' ba to ra'uli' babo' ntuku' ada agama-kai."
27275	44	10	15	Na'uli' tena topololita toei mpo'uli' -ki Petrus: "Napa to na'uli' Alata'ala lompe', neo' nu'uli' iko babo'."
27276	44	10	16	Pangila toe tolu ngkani nahilo, pai' oti toe, te'ore' nculii' -mi kumu' toe hilou hi langi'.
27277	44	10	17	Ngkai ree, ingu' -imi Petrus mpopekiri ba napa batua-na pangila to lako' nahilo toe. Bula-na mopekiri-pidi, rata-ramo suro Kornelius hi ngata Yope. Mepekune' -ra hi pue' ngata kahiapa-na tomi Simon. Ratudo' -raka tomi to rapali' pai' hilou-ramo mokore hi wobo' wala,
27278	44	10	18	pai' -ra mepekune', ra'uli': "Ba ria hi rehe'i hadua torata to rahanga' Simon Petrus?"
27279	44	10	19	 Bula-na mopekiri-pidi Petrus, Inoha' Tomoroli' mpo'uli' -ki hewa toi: "Epe pe'! Ria tolu tauna tumai mpali' -ko.
27280	44	10	20	Pesahui mana'u. Neo' morara' nono-nu mpotuku' -ra, apa' Aku' -hana to mpohubui-ra."
27281	44	10	21	Jadi', pana'u-nami Petrus ngkai tomi pai' na'uli' -raka to lako' rata toera: "Aku' -mile to nipali' -e. Napa-di to nipali' -kae?"
27282	44	10	22	Ratompoi': "Kai' tohe'i, napowiwi Kapitee Kornelius. Hi'a toe, tauna to monoa' ingku-na. Mengkoru-i hi Alata'ala, pai' -i rabila' hawe'ea to Yahudi. Hadua mala'eka Pue' mpohubui-i mpokio' -ko hilou hi tomi-na, bona na'epe ba napa to nu'uli' -ki."
27283	44	10	23	Petrus mpo'uli' -raka suro Kornelius toera: "Turu rei-tamo ulu hamengi." Turu mpu'u-ramo hamengi hi ree. Kamepulo-na, me'ongko' mpu'u-imi Petrus mpotuku' -ra hilou hi ngata Kaisarea. Pai' ria wo'o ba hangkuja dua ompi' hampepangalaa' ngkai Yope hilou dohe-ra.
27284	44	10	24	Hamengi-ra hi lengko ohea pai' lako' rata-rada hi Kaisarea. Karata-ra hi ria, mpolia' morumpu-ramo Kornelius hante posantina-na mpopea Petrus. Ria wo'o tongki-na pai' bale-na to nakio' morumpu hi tomi-na.
27285	44	10	25	Jadi', karata-na Petrus hi tomi Kornelius, mehompo-imi Kornelius ngkai tomi hilou mpotomu-i. Motingkua' -i hi nyanyoa Petrus mponyompa-i.
27286	44	10	26	Aga Petrus mpotagi-i, na'ore' -i nculii' pai' na'uli' -ki: "Neo' -hawo wae! Mokore-moko. Aku' manusia' wo'o-a-wadi-kuwo, hewa iko."
27287	44	10	27	Bula-na Petrus mpololitai-i, mesua' -ramo hi rala tomi. Nahilo-hawo Petrus, wori' -mi tauna himuhu.
27288	44	10	28	Na'uli' Petrus mpo'uli' -raka: "Ni'inca moto-le, ntuku' atura agama-kai, kai' to Yahudi uma ma'ala mposigalo-kokoi tauna to bela-koi to Yahudi ba mesua' hi rala tomi-ni. Aga Alata'ala mpakanoto-ka hi rala pangila-ku wengi, ka'uma-na ria manusia' to babo' ntuku' ada agama ba to rapalii' mposigalo-raka.
27289	44	10	29	Toe pai' kanikio' -ku tumai, uma-a leba' motance. Jadi', hewa toe lau, doko' ku'inca ba napa pai' nikio' -a tumai."
27290	44	10	30	Na'uli' Kornelius: "Tolu mengi to liu, ba hewa jaa toe-mi lau, bula-ku mosampaya hi tomi-ku jaa tolu libe eo, ria ncorobaa hadua tomane mokore hi nyanyoa-ku. Pohea-na meringkila' -damo.
27291	44	10	31	Na'uli' tauna toei mpo'uli' -ka: `Kornelius, Alata'ala mpo'epe posampaya-nu pai' na'inca kamanara-nu.
27292	44	10	32	Wae-pi, hubui tauna hilou hi ngata Yope mpokio' tauna to rahanga' Simon Petrus. Po'ohaa' -na mohu' hi wiwi' tahi', hi tomi Simon topobago rewa kuliba.'
27293	44	10	33	Toe pai' kupesahui mpotuma tauna tilou mpokio' -ko. Hiaa' lompe' mpu'u nono-nu, baa' he'i-madakoe. Jadi' hewa toe lau, morumpu-makai hi rehe'i natiroi Alata'ala, doko' mpo'epe hawe'ea to nahubui-koko Alata'ala mpo'uli' -kakai."
27294	44	10	34	 Na'uli' Petrus: "Wae lau monoto mpu'u-mi ku'inca, Alata'ala uma mpelence tauna.
27295	44	10	35	Hema-hema to mengkoru hi Hi'a pai' to monoa' kehi-ra, bate natarima-ra, pai' uma napoposisala ba to'apa-ra.
27296	44	10	36	Toi-mi kareba to naparata Alata'ala hi kai' to Yahudi, kareba to mpakanoto ohea-na bona posidaia' Alata'ala hante manusia' ma'ala jadi' lompe' nculii' hante petolo' -na Yesus Kristus. Yesus toei, Pue' hawe'ea manusia'.
27297	44	10	37	Tantu ni'inca moto-mi kajadia' to jadi' hobo' hi tana' to Yahudi. Pontepu'ua-na hi Galilea ka'oti-na Yohanes mponiu' tauna to medea ngkai jeko' -ra.
27298	44	10	38	Ni'inca wo'o tutura Yesus to Nazaret. Alata'ala mpopelihi-i pai' mpowai' -i Inoha' Tomoroli' pai' baraka'. Hiapa pomakoa' -na hi tana' to Yahudi, nababehi to lompe', pai' napaka'uri' hawe'ea tauna to nakuasai Magau' Anudaa', apa' Alata'ala mpodohei-i.
27299	44	10	39	Kai' tohe'i-mi to mpohilo hawe'ea to nababehi hi tana' to Yahudi duu' rata hi ngata Yerusalem. Ka'omea-na, rapatehi-i, rapaku' hi kaju parika'.
27300	44	10	40	Aga hi eo katolu-na, Alata'ala mpotuwu' -i nculii' pai' mpopohiloi-i hi manusia'.
27301	44	10	41	Aga uma hi hawe'ea tauna, muntu' hi kai' to napelihi ami' -mi Alata'ala jadi' sabi' -na. Ka'oti-na Yesus tuwu' nculii', nginu pai' ngkoni' moto-kai dohe-na.
27302	44	10	42	Nahubui-kai mpokeni Kareba Lompe' hi hawe'ea tauna, pai' mposabii' Kahi'a-na mpu'u-mi to napelihi Alata'ala jadi' Topobotuhi hi hawe'ea manusia', lompe' to tuwu' -pidi lompe' to mate-mi.
27303	44	10	43	Hawe'ea nabi owi mpotompo'wiwi-i, ra'uli': hema-hema to mepangala' hi Yesus, jeko' -ra ra'ampungi sabana petolo' -na."
27304	44	10	44	 Bula-na mololita-pidi Petrus, hompo-mi Inoha' Tomoroli' mpokahompoi hawe'ea tauna to mpo'epe lolita-na.
27305	44	10	45	Konce omea-ramo to Yahudi topepangala' hi Yesus to mpodohei Petrus ngkai Yope, apa' tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi mporata Inoha' Tomoroli' wo'o-ramo-rawo.
27306	44	10	46	Monoto-mi kamporata-ra Inoha' Tomoroli', apa' mololita-ra hante basa to nawai' -raka Inoha' Tomoroli', mpo'une' -une' Alata'ala. Ngkai ree, na'uli' -mi Petrus:
27307	44	10	47	"Hilo pe'. Tauna toera lau, mporata-ramo Inoha' Tomoroli' hibalia hewa to jadi' hi kita'. Jadi', hema-koi to daho' mpotagi-ra? Bate kana raniu' wo'o-ramo-rawo jadi' topetuku' Yesus!"
27308	44	10	48	Toe pai' Petrus mpohubui-ra hira' Kornelius bona raniu' mpokahangai' hanga' Yesus Kristus. Oti toe, Kornelius pai' doo-na merapi' hi Petrus bona mo'oha' -i ulu dohe-ra ba hangkuja mengi.
27309	44	11	1	 Ngkai ree, suro Pue' Yesus hante ompi' -ompi' hampepangalaa' to hi tana' Yudea mpo'epe karia-ra to bela-ra to Yahudi mpotarima wo'o-ramo-rawo Lolita Alata'ala.
27310	44	11	2	Toe pai' karata-na Petrus hi Yerusalem, ba hangkuja dua to Yahudi topepangala' hi Yesus mposalai' -i,
27311	44	11	3	ra'uli' -ki: "Napa pai' mesua' -ko-kona hi tomi tauna to babo' ntuku' ada agama-ta, pai' ngkoni' wo'o-ko-kona dohe-rae?"
27312	44	11	4	Ngkai ree, Petrus mpotutura-raka hawe'ea to jadi' ngkai lomo' -na, na'uli':
27313	44	11	5	"Bula-ku mosampaya hi ngata Yope, muu-mule' molinga' -a pai' ria pangila-ku. Hi rala pangila-ku toe, kuhilo kumu' to mowela', ratoe hi opo' huno-na pai' ra'ulu tumai ngkai langi' hompo hi ncori-ku.
27314	44	11	6	Kukamata ihi' -na, kuhilo-kuwo wori' nyala binata to opo' witi' -na, binata to me'ila, binata to menyolo, pai' nte danci wo'o.
27315	44	11	7	Ngkai ree, ku'epe to mpololitai-a, na'uli' -ka: `Petrus, mokore-moko, sumale' -ramo pai' nukoni'.'
27316	44	11	8	"Kutompoi': `Uma-e' Pue'! Ko'ia ria hangkania kukoni' binata to rapalii' ba to babo' ntuku' ada agama-kai.'
27317	44	11	9	"Ku'epe tena lolita tohe'e mpo'uli' -ka: `Napa to na'uli' Alata'ala lompe', neo' nu'uli' iko babo'.'
27318	44	11	10	Tohe'e kuhilo tolu ngkani, pai' te'ore' nculii' -mi hilou hi langi'.
27319	44	11	11	"Nto'u toe wo'o-hawo, rata-mi tolu tauna hi tomi po'ohaa' -ku. To tolu toera, tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi to rahubui ngkai ngata Kaisarea hilou hi Yope mpopali' -a.
27320	44	11	12	Inoha' Tomoroli' mpo'uli' -ka: `Petrus, neo' morara' nono-nu mpotuku' tauna toera.' Jadi', hilou mpu'u-ama dohe-ra. Pai' ria moto sabi' -ku hi rehe'i, apa' ompi' -ta to ono toera mai mpodohei-a hilou hi Kaisarea. Karata-kai hi tomi Kornelius, mesua' -makai hi rala-na.
27321	44	11	13	Kornelius mpotutura-kakai kampohilo-na hadua mala'eka mehupa' hi tomi-na to mpo'uli' -ki: `Hubui tauna hilou hi Yope mpopali' hadua tomane to rahanga' Simon Petrus bona tumai-i.
27322	44	11	14	Hi'a mpai' to mpoparata-koko kareba to mpokeni kalompea' hi iko, duu' -na hi hawe'ea tauna ihi' tomi-nu.'
27323	44	11	15	"Jadi', bula-ku mpololitai-ra-pidi, hompo-mi Inoha' Tomoroli' mpokuasai-ra, hibalia hewa to jadi' hi kita' to Yahudi lomo' -na.
27324	44	11	16	Ngkai ree, kukiwoi-mi lolita Pue' to mpo'uli': `Yohanes meniu' hante ue, aga koi' mpai' raniu' hante Inoha' Tomoroli'.'
27325	44	11	17	Jadi', ompi' -ompi', monoto-mi Alata'ala mpowai' Inoha' Tomoroli' hi hira' to bela-ra to Yahudi, hibalia hewa to nawai' -taka kita', sabana pepangala' -ta hi Pue' Yesus Kristus. Jadi', hema rahi-a aku' toi-e, pai' daho' -a mpolawa' patuju Alata'ala?"
27326	44	11	18	Kara'epe-na toporumpu toera lolita Petrus, rabahakai-mi mposalai' -i. Mpo'une' Alata'ala lau-ramo, ra'uli': "Ane wae-tano, natarima moto-ra-rawo Alata'ala tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi, napalogai-ra medea ngkai jeko' -ra duu' -na mporata katuwua' to lompe' duu' kahae-hae-na."
27327	44	11	19	 Jadi', ntepu'u ngkai karapatehi-na Stefanus, topetuku' Yesus hi Yerusalem rabalinai', pai' wori' -ramo to metibo' hilou hi ngata doo, alaa-na pahawu' -hawu' -ramo. Ria-ra to rata hi tana' Fenisia, ria wo'o-ra to loha hi tana' Siprus pai' hi ngata Antiokhia. Hiapa kahilouaa-ra, mpoparata-ra Lolita Pue' Ala, aga muntu' hi to Yahudi-wadi.
27328	44	11	20	Jadi' ngkai ree, ria wo'o-ra-rawo to mepangala' hi Yesus to ngkai tana' Siprus pai' Kirene. Ngkai hira' toe, ria to hilou hi ngata Antiokhia mpokeni Kareba Lompe' hi tauna to bela-ra to Yahudi, mpo'uli' -raka Kayesus-na Pue'.
